NK130(tho)001:1: // gsang sngags snga 'gyur la bod du rtsod pa snga
NK130(tho)001:2: phyir 'byung ba rnams kyi lan du brjod pa nges
NK130(tho)001:4: na mo gu ru pad+ma sam+b+ha wa ya /
NK130(tho)001:5: dmigs med zab cing rgya che'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK130(tho)001:6: brjod med dbyings nas zab yangs chos sgra sgrog /
NK130(tho)001:7: kun bzang 'od kyi snang ba 'khyil ba'i thugs //
NK130(tho)001:8: zag med yon tan phung po der phyag bgyi //
NK130(tho)001:9: mgon de'i sras dang 'khor dang de rjes 'jug /
NK130(tho)001:10: rgya bod pan gru brgya mtshos bshad pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:11: nyon mongs nad chen 'joms pa'i bdud rtsi mchog /
NK130(tho)001:12: mtha' yas phyir na su zhig log par lta //
NK130(tho)001:13: de lta'ang mkhris nad can la gangs dang dung //
NK130(tho)001:14: ser por snang ba ji bzhin zab mo'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:15: log par mthong ba'i skye bo ches mang ba //
NK130(tho)001:16: 'byung bar bcon ldan 'das kyis mdo las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:17: de phyir bsags pa can gyi gang zag dang //
NK130(tho)001:18: mkhas shing skal ldan blo mig ldan pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:19: don la rten phyir yang dag chos rnams kun //
NK130(tho)001:20: yang dag nyid du slar yang bsgrub mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:21: mos pa dman zhing dge ba'i rtsa ba chung //
NK130(tho)001:22: tha snyad lam la goms pa'i rtog ge ba //
NK130(tho)001:23: mu stegs bag chags 'thas pa bzlog phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:24: don bzang legs bshad gtam gyi sgo dabye'o //
NK130(tho)001:25: de la khyed kyi bstan bcos 'di'i thog mar /
NK130(tho)001:27: d+harma na d+harma bi byak+ta k+aa ri ka n+aa ma /
NK130(tho)001:29: chos dang chos ma yin pa rnam par dbye ba'i rab tu byed pa zhes bya ba /
NK130(tho)001:31: skad dod gzhan rnams ma nor mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:32: rab tu byed pa'i skad dod pra ka ra na zhes thob pa la /
NK130(tho)001:33: k+aa ri ka zhes pa tshig le'ura byas pa zhes pa'i skad dod yin pas tshig skyon byung /
NK130(tho)001:34: gzhung 'dir le'u'i rnam bzhag kyang byas pa mi 'dug pas don skyon byung bas bcos par rigs la /
NK130(tho)001:35: de ltar ma gyur na de'i gtan tshigs smra bar rigs so //
NK130(tho)001:36: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK130(tho)001:37: thugs rje'i char sprin bstan pa'i 'brug sgra snyan //
NK130(tho)001:38: bdud rigs snying 'gems rig pa'i glog phreng 'bar //
NK130(tho)001:39: sngon med klu dbang thub dbang rdo rje 'chang //
NK130(tho)001:40: kun tu bzang po'i zhabs la mgos phyag 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:41: srid dang thar pa'i bde ba ji snyed pa //
NK130(tho)001:42: de kun rgyal ba'i bstan la rag las shing //
NK130(tho)001:43: bstan pa'i snying po rdo rje theg pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:44: de yi mchog rab rnal 'byor bla med yin //
NK130(tho)001:45: 'gro ba phar cher grub pa'i mtha' la rmongs //
NK130(tho)001:46: shas cher mu stegs kla klo'i gzhung lugs 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:47: bod 'dir sangs rgyas pa yang chos min smra //
NK130(tho)001:48: de phyir rnam par dbye ba ngas 'dir bshad //
NK130(tho)001:49: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:50: 'dus pa sdom pa dgyes rdor sogs //
NK130(tho)001:51: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyi //
NK130(tho)001:52: rgyud sde dri ma med pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:53: shas cher u rgyan las byung nas //
NK130(tho)001:54: rgya gar yul du dar bar bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:55: rgyud sde kun gyi mchog gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:57: sham+b+ha la yi yul nas byung //
NK130(tho)001:58: rgya bod mkhas grub kun gyis bkur //
NK130(tho)001:59: rgyud don rnam par gsal bya'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:60: rdo rje snying po spyan ras gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:61: phyag na rdo rje sa ra ha //
NK130(tho)001:62: in+d+ra b+h+au ti lcam dpal mo //
NK130(tho)001:63: klu sgrub zla grags 'phags pa'i lha //
NK130(tho)001:64: ri khrod dbang phyug ku ku ri //
NK130(tho)001:65: dril bu pa dang lo hi pa //
NK130(tho)001:66: ye shes zhabs dang dpal 'dzin sogs //
NK130(tho)001:67: mkhas shing grub pa brgya stong gis //
NK130(tho)001:69: 'grel bshad dbang skur sgrub pa'i thabs //
NK130(tho)001:70: yan lag dang bcas dpag med mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:71: 'dzam bu gling gi yul dang yul //
NK130(tho)001:72: grong dang grong khyer kun tu dar //
NK130(tho)001:73: bod kyi yul 'dir sngon gyi tshe //
NK130(tho)001:74: chos rgyal dam pa'i sku ring la //
NK130(tho)001:75: thub dbang rgyal ba'i chos kyi mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:76: lo pan mkhas grub du mas bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:77: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud sde yang //
NK130(tho)001:78: gsang 'dus sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang //
NK130(tho)001:79: gsang ba zla ba'i thig le dang //
NK130(tho)001:80: rnam snang sgyu 'phrul dra ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:81: rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu ni //
NK130(tho)001:82: phur bu'i skabs te rnam lnga 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:83: tshig dang don la skyon med cing //
NK130(tho)001:84: mkhas rnams yid chos gnas su grags //
NK130(tho)001:86: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan dang //
NK130(tho)001:87: bee ro tsa na mkha' snying po //
NK130(tho)001:88: nyang ban ting 'dzin la sogs te //
NK130(tho)001:89: rje blon nyi shu rtsa lnga la //
NK130(tho)001:90: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:91: rgyud rgyal 'dus pa'i nyams len du //
NK130(tho)001:92: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba bshad //
NK130(tho)001:93: gzhan la gsang bar 'chad na yang //
NK130(tho)001:94: gsang zhing lkog tu bstan pa'i rgyus //
NK130(tho)001:95: mkha' snying bee ro tsa na gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:96: lho brag rgyal mo rong du spyugs //
NK130(tho)001:97: zab mo'i rgyud don ma shes par //
NK130(tho)001:99: phyin chad rgyud sde 'di bsgyur ba //
NK130(tho)001:100: bkag par bkas bcad 'bring por bshad //
NK130(tho)001:101: phyi nas nyang ban ting 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:102: mkhas pa dri med bshes gnyen la //
NK130(tho)001:103: slar yang 'dus pa'i man ngag ni //
NK130(tho)001:104: cung zad tsam zhig gsan ces grags //
NK130(tho)001:105: slob dpon pad+ma'i thugs dam dngos //
NK130(tho)001:106: gshin rje gshed rgyud pra khog snang //
NK130(tho)001:107: 'di ni nam mkha'i snying pos bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:108: 'di la rma ban rin mchog dang //
NK130(tho)001:109: brang ti dza ya rak+shi tas //
NK130(tho)001:111: zhes bya'i pan chen la zhus nas //
NK130(tho)001:112: bsgyur ba'i lugs kyang yod ces grags //
NK130(tho)001:114: brjod bya de dag kyang phal che ba ni don la gnas pa ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:115: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim lnga ni nyams su len
NK130(tho)001:116: pa'i lam gyi mchog yin pas gsang sngags rnying ma
NK130(tho)001:117: bka' gter gnyis ka la grags te /
NK130(tho)001:120: bi ma la mi tra gnyis la lo ts+aa ba lce bkra shis kyis gtugs nas /
NK130(tho)001:122: rgyud phyi ma dang bcas pa bsgyur /
NK130(tho)001:123: man ngag rim lnga yang gsan /
NK130(tho)001:124: de nas slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba ti ser phebs /
NK130(tho)001:125: mnga' bdag gis bsam yas su spyan drangs pas /
NK130(tho)001:126: slob dpon gyis nga'i tshe la gnod gsungs nas 'byon du ma bzhed pa la /
NK130(tho)001:127: rgyal pos lo ts+aa ba 'di btang nas /
NK130(tho)001:128: de'i tshe yang rim lnga zhus /
NK130(tho)001:129: slob dpon des sgyu 'phrul gyi skor cha lag dang bcas pas gtso byas /
NK130(tho)001:130: chos kyi skyes mang po rgyal po la bskur ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:132: phyi nang gnyis kyi lag len mang po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:133: gcig kyang ma lus lag len thams cad bardzangasa //
NK130(tho)001:134: gzigs rtog mdzod la gzhan la shor ta re //
NK130(tho)001:135: bod kyi mi ni sgrin la tshor skyen te //
NK130(tho)001:136: mthong ba thams cad la 'ur byed par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:137: nyes dmigs cha med dam tshig stong par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:138: dmyal rgyu mang zhing 'bras bu brlag par mchi //
NK130(tho)001:139: phyi nang gnyis kyi lag len spa bar mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:142: mnga' bdag nyang gi rdzogs rim bla ma'i dmar khrid dang /
NK130(tho)001:143: chos dbang rin po che'i bla ma gsang 'dus dang /
NK130(tho)001:144: pad+ma gling pa'i nor bu rgya mtsho la sogs par yod la /
NK130(tho)001:145: man ngag lta phreng ni rdzogs chen sems phyogs yin cing /
NK130(tho)001:146: 'dir rim pa lnga'i tha snyad mthun pa yang med do //
NK130(tho)001:147: de'i phyir khyed rang gis kyang /
NK130(tho)001:148: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:149: zer ba las smra rgyu ma rnyed pa 'dra /
NK130(tho)001:150: bee ro rgyal mo rong du spyugs zer ba'ang lo rgyus ma dag pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:151: sba bzhed du rgya'i snyan phras bee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs /
NK130(tho)001:153: bkas bcad 'bring por bshad pa de yang rgyal mo tsha ba rong yin /
NK130(tho)001:154: rgyal mo rong dang tsha ba rong gnyis yul thag
NK130(tho)001:155: ring so so ba yin pa'ang dgongs par mdzod cig
NK130(tho)001:156: / phyin chad rgyud 'di bsgyur ba bkag ces pa'ang rgya chung ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:157: de dus snying ma kho nar ma zad gsang sngags
NK130(tho)001:158: bla med thams cad re zhig bsgyur ba bkag pas
NK130(tho)001:159: so // 'on kyang bya ba'i rgyud yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:161: pra khog snang spyod pa'i rgyud yin par slob dpon shan+ti pas bshad pa yang gzigs 'tshal /
NK130(tho)001:163: slob dpon pad ma 'byung gnas des //
NK130(tho)001:165: rgya chen sde bzhi'i bra phab cing //
NK130(tho)001:166: sbyin sreg lan gsum mdzad bzhed kyang //
NK130(tho)001:167: gnyis las mdzad pa'i long med par //
NK130(tho)001:168: blon po ngan pa'i glen spyugs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:169: rgyal ba'i sras 'di slar gshegs nas //
NK130(tho)001:170: mang yul stod kyi la kha nas //
NK130(tho)001:171: mkha' la 'phur te lho nub kyi //
NK130(tho)001:172: srin po 'dul du byon no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:173: bla bzhed sba bzhed gnyis kar 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:176: rgyal chen bzhi yi pra phab pas //
NK130(tho)001:177: sham pos 'phang thang chu la bskur //
NK130(tho)001:178: thang lhas thog dang yams nad btang //
NK130(tho)001:179: de sogs bstan pa 'dzug pa la //
NK130(tho)001:180: bar chad byed pa'i lha srin kun //
NK130(tho)001:181: byis pa de yis pra la mthong //
NK130(tho)001:182: de la rgyal blon kun yid ches //
NK130(tho)001:183: de nas has po ri yi rtser //
NK130(tho)001:184: mtheb kyu zhig gi gtor ma la //
NK130(tho)001:185: bod kyi lha srin thams cad bkug /
NK130(tho)001:186: lha khang brtsi gcig bka' bsgos pas //
NK130(tho)001:187: bsam yas mi yis brtsigs pa bas //
NK130(tho)001:188: mtshan mo lha 'dres brtsigs pa mtho //
NK130(tho)001:189: klu rgyal mal gro gzi can gyi //
NK130(tho)001:190: yid tsam ma gtogs lha 'dre'i tshogs //
NK130(tho)001:191: lus ngag yid gsum dam la thogs //
NK130(tho)001:192: des na sbyin sreg bya ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:193: gal te sbyin sreg dgos srid kyang //
NK130(tho)001:194: slob dpon zla ba gsum bzhugs par //
NK130(tho)001:195: bla bzhed sba bzhed gnyis ka mthun //
NK130(tho)001:196: zla ba gsum gyi khongs der ni //
NK130(tho)001:197: sbyin sreg lan gsum mi grub pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:198: gtam 'di ha cang ma thal lam //
NK130(tho)001:200: srin po 'dul ba'i mthu yod bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:201: bod kyi blon po 'ga' zhig la //
NK130(tho)001:202: skrag nas slob dpon bzhud pa 'ang mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:203: 'on kyang sdig blon ngan pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:204: slob dpon mchog de'i rdzu 'phrul dang //
NK130(tho)001:205: mthu stobs chen po des skrag nas //
NK130(tho)001:206: mnga' bdag chos rgyal phra mas dpyos //
NK130(tho)001:207: dus der rgyal po'ang the tshom nas //
NK130(tho)001:208: slob dpon gshegs par zhu ba phul //
NK130(tho)001:209: gshegs par chas tshe rgyal po 'gyod //
NK130(tho)001:210: nan gyis bzhugs pa'i zhu ba phul //
NK130(tho)001:211: de la slob dpon chen po des //
NK130(tho)001:212: bsam yas bzhugs par ma gnang la //
NK130(tho)001:213: da dung gdul bya ma rdzogs pas //
NK130(tho)001:214: sgrub gnas rnams su rim gyis bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:215: rgyal po'i bar chad bsal ched du //
NK130(tho)001:216: skabs su 'byon par zhal gyis bzhes //
NK130(tho)001:217: mi lo lnga bcu rtsa drug tu //
NK130(tho)001:218: bod kyi gdul bya rdzogs mdzad nas //
NK130(tho)001:219: srin po 'dul bar gshegs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:220: rnying ma'i lo rgyus 'di nyid dang //
NK130(tho)001:221: bla bzhed sba bzhed don du mthun //
NK130(tho)001:223: de yang ji ltar mthun na phur pa bdag gi lo rgyus las /
NK130(tho)001:224: sdig blon rnams kyis rgyal po la snyan phra gsol //
NK130(tho)001:225: der rgyal po yang the tshom ste slob dpon gshegs par zhu ba phul bas /
NK130(tho)001:226: nga rgya gar du 'gro ba rung ste gsang sngags
NK130(tho)001:227: kyi bstan pa yongs rdzogs bsgyur ma thub pas glo
NK130(tho)001:228: ba ma dga'/ bod kyi ri thams cad nags kyis khyab pa /
NK130(tho)001:230: bye ma thams cad ne'u sing du bsgyur ba /
NK130(tho)001:231: 'brog dgon pa dang byang thang thams cad zhing du
NK130(tho)001:232: bsgyur ba sogs bya ba mang po yod pa la
NK130(tho)001:233: / sems can gyi bsod nams la ma shongs /
NK130(tho)001:234: kye ma bod 'bangs snying re rje gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:235: bsam yas kyi mtha' skor gyi bye ma la bsnyen phur bsgril bas sing mar sngo zhur gyi song /
NK130(tho)001:236: rgyal po la bstan pa bsrung ba'i drag sngags brgya rtsa brgyad dang /
NK130(tho)001:237: phan bya brgya nyi shu la sogs pa gnang /
NK130(tho)001:238: bdag ni srin po'i kha gnon la 'gro bas nga'i
NK130(tho)001:239: chos 'phro lus pa rnams rgya gar nas pan chen
NK130(tho)001:240: bi ma la mi tra spyan drongs la sgyur cig
NK130(tho)001:241: / rgyal po nyid kyang sku tshe nyi zla dang mnyam par bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:242: dgongs pas tshe chu 'di gsol gsungs pas /
NK130(tho)001:244: slob dpon gshegs pa 'dis ma dgyes nas lho bal
NK130(tho)001:245: gyi zhed kyis dug btang ba 'dra yang srid snyam
NK130(tho)001:246: nas spyang thul gyi 'dabs na mar pho bas /
NK130(tho)001:247: de ma thag tu sa la chu mig rdol /
NK130(tho)001:248: chu de la deng sang du'ang chu rje ne'u sing du grags /
NK130(tho)001:249: de nas slob dpon gshegs pa mnga' bdag gis ma bzod de /
NK130(tho)001:250: rgyal khrims zhig na'ang zhig bdag ma gum bar du bzhugs par zhu zhus pas /
NK130(tho)001:251: da dung bod kyi gdul bya ma rdzogs par dgongs nas bsam yas su /
NK130(tho)001:253: sgrub gnas rnams su byon nas rgyud sde so so'i
NK130(tho)001:254: dkyil 'khor zhal phyes nas sgrub pa mdzad de byin
NK130(tho)001:256: bod yul gyi sa gzhi thams cad zhabs kyis bcags te bkra shis shing byin chags par mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:257: sgrub gnas rnams su gter kha mang po sbas /
NK130(tho)001:258: brag la sku dang phyag zhabs kyi rjes bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:259: khyad par du mtsho chen po bzhi la phyag rjes
NK130(tho)001:260: bzhag pa ni chu ma skams kyi bar du gnas
NK130(tho)001:261: par byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa ni deng
NK130(tho)001:262: sang yang gsal / skabs su rgyal po rje 'bangs la chos gsung pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:263: bsam yas kyi dkor srung la rgyal po pe har bsko ba'i dus kyi tshe dang /
NK130(tho)001:264: btsun mo dmar rgyan baza'i mdze nad bsal ba la sogs pa skabs skabs su byon /
NK130(tho)001:265: mnga' bdag gshegs nas sras mu ne btsan po yum gyi dug gis grongs /
NK130(tho)001:266: mu khri btsan po na gzhon /
NK130(tho)001:269: rgya la sogs pas bod phung du cha ba na /
NK130(tho)001:270: mu khri btsan po'i pha dod mdzad de rgyal srid lo gsum bskyangs /
NK130(tho)001:271: de nas rgyal bu la rgyal srid gtad de su
NK130(tho)001:272: yis bshol btab kyang ma gsan par srin pa'i kha
NK130(tho)001:273: gnon la gshegs / de ltar bsam yas kyi sa 'dul ba la sogs pa zla ba gsum bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:274: de nas sdig blon rnams kyi snang ngor gshegs pa ltar yon mchod bka' bsgros te mdzad nas /
NK130(tho)001:275: bod kyi dben rtsa rnams su bzhugs zhes bshad /
NK130(tho)001:276: de ltar dus der slob dpon gshegs su bcug pa
NK130(tho)001:277: dang chos bsnub par sdig blon rnams kyi ma nus
NK130(tho)001:278: la mu khri btsan po'i pha tshab mdzad nas rgyal
NK130(tho)001:280: zhes pa ni lha btsun byang chub 'od kyis bsam
NK130(tho)001:281: yas dkor mdzod nas rnyed pa'i yig tshang las kyang
NK130(tho)001:282: 'byung ngo // gzhan yang rnying ma ba dag rgyal
NK130(tho)001:283: po khri srong lde'u btsan dgung lo drug cu rtsa
NK130(tho)001:285: gzhan dag drug cu rtsa brgyad bzhugs zer /
NK130(tho)001:286: gang ltar yang chos rgyal gshegs rjes lo gsum bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:287: 'di la bka' gdams glegs bam gyi bu chos su jo bo rjes /
NK130(tho)001:288: de'i dus kyi slob dpon pad+ma ni kho bo yin la /
NK130(tho)001:289: de'i chos ni da lta bod kyi sngags pa rnams la grags pa 'di yin no gsung /
NK130(tho)001:290: bla bzhed sba bzhed gnyis kyi lo rgyus de'ang bla bzhed ni /
NK130(tho)001:291: bla chen pos sba bzhed ltar du bris pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:292: sba bzhed rim pa gsum byas nas /
NK130(tho)001:293: gcig rje'i phyag sbal du bzhag gcig dbon sras la bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:294: gcig bod kyi rab tu byung ba rnams la bzhag go //
NK130(tho)001:295: zhes pa'i tshul 'di sdig blon rnams kyi ngor byas pa yin cing /
NK130(tho)001:296: 'di la rnying ma pa rgyus med kha cig /
NK130(tho)001:297: sba ye shes dbang po slob dpon pad+ma la mi dad pas de ltar bcos pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:298: phyis slob dpon gyis rjes su bzung pas de lta
NK130(tho)001:299: ma yin zhes zer te ma go ba yin cing
NK130(tho)001:300: / sba bzhed ni sdig blon rnams kyi ngor rgyal blon rnams kyis bsgrigs pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:301: ye shes dbang pos byas pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:302: de la sogs pa go ba longs na rnying ma'i
NK130(tho)001:303: lo rgyus dang sba bzhed mi mthun pa mi 'byung
NK130(tho)001:305: slob dpon pad+ma gshegs rjes su //
NK130(tho)001:306: dpal gyi bsam yas rmongs nas brtsigs //
NK130(tho)001:307: rab gnas lan grangs brgyad du mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:308: mdzad mkhan po d+hi sa t+wa yin //
NK130(tho)001:309: de la bstan bcos de gnyis mthun //
NK130(tho)001:311: mkhan po bo d+hi sa t+wa yis //
NK130(tho)001:312: rab gnas lan grangs brgyad mdzad pas //
NK130(tho)001:313: slob dpon bzhud pa mi 'grub ste //
NK130(tho)001:314: dus der pan chen brgya rtsa gcig /
NK130(tho)001:315: so sos rab gnas mdzad pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:316: bo d+hi sa t+wa'ang bzhud zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:317: slob dpon bzhugs pa'i gtan tshigs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:318: bsam yas kyi ni lha rnams kun //
NK130(tho)001:319: bod kyi mi la dpe byas te //
NK130(tho)001:320: rta mgrin gling gi dbang chen sku //
NK130(tho)001:321: blon po khu yi stag sna la //
NK130(tho)001:322: dpe gyis la sogs zhal bkod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:323: slob dpon pad+ma mdzad par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:324: spyir na bsam yas rab gnas ni //
NK130(tho)001:325: dus der pan chen so sos mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:326: khyad par slob dpon pad+ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:327: nam mkha'i dbyings su bzhugs nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:328: rdor dbyings dkyil 'khor mkha' la sprul //
NK130(tho)001:330: bsam yas me mo yos la rmangs bting /
NK130(tho)001:332: +aa tsa r+ya bo d+hi sat+wa dang /
NK130(tho)001:333: pad+ma sam+b+ha was rab gnas mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:334: lo bcu gsum du dga' ston byas te /
NK130(tho)001:336: me tog len par lha rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:337: lha khang nang nas phyi la byon //
NK130(tho)001:338: slar yang nang du log par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:339: dus der bsgrigs pa'i bsam yas kyi //
NK130(tho)001:341: dpal 'dzin bden na thams cad sba bzhed sogs kyang go ba long na rnying ma dang mthun pas /
NK130(tho)001:344: de yi bka' srung pe ha ra //
NK130(tho)001:345: mal gro'i sa bdag rgyu 'dal gyis //
NK130(tho)001:346: sngar lung bstan nas rgyal po des //
NK130(tho)001:347: rgya gar shar phyogs za hor gyi //
NK130(tho)001:349: sman bla'i lo rgyus las 'di gsal //
NK130(tho)001:351: za hor zhes pa'i tshig 'di nyid //
NK130(tho)001:352: sman bla'i lo rgyus la yod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:353: rgya gar rgya nag ma phyed par //
NK130(tho)001:354: rgya gar shar phyogs su bsams pa //
NK130(tho)001:355: bo d+hi sat+wa'i dgongs pa min //
NK130(tho)001:357: bye brag za hor zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:358: rgyal po gnas pa'i sgom grwa yin //
NK130(tho)001:359: sngon tshe blon po mgar gyi dus //
NK130(tho)001:360: yul de'i gyad gnyis rgya nag gis //
NK130(tho)001:361: phyir snyegs btang ba blon po des //
NK130(tho)001:362: thabs kyis brid nas bod du slebs //
NK130(tho)001:363: de gnyis brgyud pa 'phyong rgyas kyi //
NK130(tho)001:364: stag rtse'i za hor brgyud 'di yin //
NK130(tho)001:365: sa ho ra zhes bya ba'i yul //
NK130(tho)001:366: rgya gar shar te mkhan po dang //
NK130(tho)001:367: jo bo gnyis ka'i 'khrungs yul yin //
NK130(tho)001:368: sgra de bod kyis zur chag pas //
NK130(tho)001:369: za hor zer te dag pa min //
NK130(tho)001:370: pe har 'di yang hor gyi lha //
NK130(tho)001:371: deng sang du yang hor rnams brten //
NK130(tho)001:372: bod 'dir ji ltar slebs pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:374: bod kyi dmag gi dgra lha ru //
NK130(tho)001:375: rgyal mo chen po rnam sras bskos //
NK130(tho)001:376: de nas bod kyi dmag chas te //
NK130(tho)001:377: 'ba' ta'i sgam grwa bcom pa'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:378: pe har 'khor bcas nam mkhar bros //
NK130(tho)001:379: gnod sbyin pho nyas mda' 'phangs pa //
NK130(tho)001:380: phog nas pe har sa la lhung //
NK130(tho)001:381: de nas lha cha'i phyi la 'brangs //
NK130(tho)001:383: chos 'khor bsam yas la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:384: gtsug lag khang kun bsrung bar bskos //
NK130(tho)001:385: lo rgyus rnam sras ljangs yul ma //
NK130(tho)001:386: sprin gseb ma dang gnyis las bshad //
NK130(tho)001:387: deng sang lha khang phal mo che'i //
NK130(tho)001:388: srung mar rgyal po yod pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:389: rgyu mtshan 'di yis grub pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:390: de dus bod kyi dmag rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:391: slob dpon pad+mas bskur ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:392: rnam thos sras kyi phyag dar ni //
NK130(tho)001:393: mtha' mi mgon brtson gyis bris pa //
NK130(tho)001:394: bsam yas dkon mdzod nas byung ste //
NK130(tho)001:395: da lta chos lung tshogs pa la //
NK130(tho)001:396: ko shubs ma rung grags pa 'ang snang //
NK130(tho)001:397: ltar snang tsam gyi lo rgyus la //
NK130(tho)001:398: ri bang cal ltar mi rgyug par //
NK130(tho)001:399: gtan tshigs 'brel pa'i lo rgyus la //
NK130(tho)001:400: da dung thos par skyed par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:402: de dus bod na rdo rje dbyings //
NK130(tho)001:403: kun rig rnam snang mngon byang sogs //
NK130(tho)001:404: rnal 'byor rgyud sde man chad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:405: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i nyams len dar //
NK130(tho)001:406: grub pa thob pa'ang 'ga' zhig byung //
NK130(tho)001:407: yer pa'i brag la kri yog gi //
NK130(tho)001:408: bskyed rim grub nas 'phur ba'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:409: yer pa'i dkar chag nyid na yod //
NK130(tho)001:412: 'di ni gong du khyed rang gis //
NK130(tho)001:413: phyin chad rgyud sde 'di bsgyur ba //
NK130(tho)001:414: bkag ces bkas bcad khongs su drangs //
NK130(tho)001:415: kri yog grub thob byon tshul gyis //
NK130(tho)001:416: rnying ma chos min bsgrubs bsgrubs nas //
NK130(tho)001:417: zhar la gsar ma'i bla med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:418: med cing smad par ma byas sam //
NK130(tho)001:420: rma ban rin chen mchog ces byas //
NK130(tho)001:421: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud brtsams pas //
NK130(tho)001:422: rgyal pos gsan nas btsal ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:423: lo grangs bcu gnyis gab ces grags //
NK130(tho)001:425: rgyud rgyal gsang ba snying po ni //
NK130(tho)001:427: de rjes pan chen bi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:428: gnyags lo dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras //
NK130(tho)001:429: bsgyur zhing khro phu lo ts+aa bas //
NK130(tho)001:430: rgya dpe de nyid gsal bar gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:431: mkhan chen thar pa lo ts+aa bas //
NK130(tho)001:432: phyi ma'i rgyud la gsar 'gyur mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:433: bsam yas nas bshus rgya dpe las //
NK130(tho)001:434: bcom ldan ral gris bsgyur zhing zhus //
NK130(tho)001:435: slob dpon brgya byin sdong po yis //
NK130(tho)001:436: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor 'grel pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:437: slob dpon bi shwa mi tra yi //
NK130(tho)001:439: jo bo'i bka' gdams pha chos su //
NK130(tho)001:440: rgyud 'di lung yang mang po drangs //
NK130(tho)001:441: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rnam bkod //
NK130(tho)001:442: rgyud 'di nyid la brten nas mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:443: slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rje yis //
NK130(tho)001:444: mdzad pa'i 'grel pa spar khab dang //
NK130(tho)001:445: nyi 'od seng ges mdzad pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:446: khungs thub rgya 'grel dag kyang yod //
NK130(tho)001:447: 'di dag chos kyi spyan mnga' ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:448: thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston sogs //
NK130(tho)001:449: sngon gyi mkhas pas dpang du mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:450: gzhan yang bee ros 'di brtsams pas //
NK130(tho)001:451: tsha ba rong du spyugs so zer //
NK130(tho)001:452: sba bzhed tshad mar 'dzin na ni //
NK130(tho)001:453: rgya yi snyan phra'i dbang song nas //
NK130(tho)001:454: bee ro spyugs par de las bshad //
NK130(tho)001:456: de rjes rgyal po khri dar mas //
NK130(tho)001:457: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsnubs nas shi //
NK130(tho)001:458: rgyal khrims chos khrims gnyis ka bshig /
NK130(tho)001:459: lo pan thams cad sa mthar bros //
NK130(tho)001:460: dpang po med cing 'jigs med pas //
NK130(tho)001:461: bod kyi sngags pa ngan pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:462: las su rdzun rgyud 'ba' zhig brtsams //
NK130(tho)001:463: sbyor sgrol log spyod me ltar mched //
NK130(tho)001:465: dar mas bstan pa bsnubs pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:466: bstan pa phyis dar ma tshugs bar //
NK130(tho)001:467: rab tu byung ba med mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:468: sngags 'chang grub pa brnyes pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:469: khyim pa'i tshul gyis sbas yul bzung //
NK130(tho)001:470: rang gis sgrub pa snying por byas //
NK130(tho)001:471: mdo sngags gsung rab 'gyur ro cog /
NK130(tho)001:472: glegs bam thams cad phyag tu bzung //
NK130(tho)001:473: de nas 'od srung yum btsan dus //
NK130(tho)001:474: khyim pa skye bo rnams kyis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:475: dkon mchog gsum la dad byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:476: lha sa bsam yas la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:477: gtsug lag khang rnams ma nyams shing //
NK130(tho)001:478: dbus gtsang mi drug klu mes sogs //
NK130(tho)001:479: bstan pa phyi dar mgo 'dzug dus //
NK130(tho)001:480: sngon tshe bsgyur ba'i gsung rab la //
NK130(tho)001:481: ci dgar longs spyad chog pa byung //
NK130(tho)001:482: zhes pa deb ther sngon por gsal //
NK130(tho)001:483: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan dus //
NK130(tho)001:484: ji ltar bsgyur ba'i rgya dpe rnams //
NK130(tho)001:485: deng sang bar du bsam yas bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:486: 'di dag jo bo a ti shas //
NK130(tho)001:487: zhib tu gzigs pas shin tu dgyes //
NK130(tho)001:488: de dus bstan pa dar ba tsam //
NK130(tho)001:489: rgya gar du yang ma byung gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:491: sde brgyad mkha' 'gro'i mdzod sogs nas //
NK130(tho)001:492: blangs pas rgyud sde rgya gar las //
NK130(tho)001:493: bod na mang ba de yin gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:494: 'ga' zhig zhal bshus rgya gar bskur //
NK130(tho)001:495: lo rgyus lam yig chen mor ltos //
NK130(tho)001:496: bod kyi sngags pas brtsams zhes pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:497: gtam yang rang bzo kho na yin //
NK130(tho)001:498: 'di la gtan tshigs rnam dag med //
NK130(tho)001:499: bod kyi lo rgyus khungs ma ru //
NK130(tho)001:500: sngags pas brtsams zhes cang mi snang //
NK130(tho)001:501: de phyir pho brang zhi ba 'od //
NK130(tho)001:502: 'gos dang tsa mi lo ts+aa ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:503: springs yig che chung dag las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:504: sgyur byed lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:505: byas so tsam las ma byung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:506: 'di ni hwa shang sun phyungs dus //
NK130(tho)001:507: mnga' bdag che des bkas bcad de //
NK130(tho)001:508: bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba la //
NK130(tho)001:509: dgongs nas spyod pa 'dul ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:510: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum po gnang //
NK130(tho)001:511: bla med rgyud rnams re zhig la //
NK130(tho)001:512: bkag pa'i zol gyis gud du sbas //
NK130(tho)001:513: de phyir dkar chag lhan dkar dang //
NK130(tho)001:514: 'phang thang ma la sogs pa ru //
NK130(tho)001:515: gsang sngags rnying ma lta ci smos //
NK130(tho)001:516: gsar ma'i bla med dag kyang med //
NK130(tho)001:517: sbyor sgrol log spyod me ltar mched //
NK130(tho)001:518: zhes pa'i gtam yang dpyad dgos te //
NK130(tho)001:519: sbyor sgrol gsar ma nas kyang gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:520: lam du longs par ma gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:521: gnyis ka log spyod yin par mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:522: gsang sngags rnying ma kho na ba //
NK130(tho)001:523: log par spyod pa yin nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:524: gzu bor gnas pa'i blo yis soms //
NK130(tho)001:526: mnga' bdag dpal 'khor btsan gyis dus //
NK130(tho)001:527: gnubs ban sangs rgyas ye shes byung //
NK130(tho)001:528: kha thun la sogs gshin rje'i gshed //
NK130(tho)001:529: rta mgrin pad+ma dbang chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:530: ma mo srid pa rgyud lung dang //
NK130(tho)001:531: k+ai la ya ni bcu gnyis pa //
NK130(tho)001:532: de sogs sgrub lugs rgyud brgyad dang //
NK130(tho)001:533: kha skong gi ni rgyud drug dang //
NK130(tho)001:534: de bzhin rgyud kyi rgyal po drug /
NK130(tho)001:535: sgrub pa'i man ngag mtha' yas byas //
NK130(tho)001:536: khyad par ha shang grub mtha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:537: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba bsres //
NK130(tho)001:538: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos skor ni //
NK130(tho)001:539: rmad byung la sogs bcu gsum byas //
NK130(tho)001:541: gnubs ban sangs rgyas ye shes ni //
NK130(tho)001:542: slob dpon pad+ma dngos la thug /
NK130(tho)001:543: dpal 'khor btsan dang dus mi mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:544: yang rdzong shel gyi brag phug tu //
NK130(tho)001:545: grub brnyes nyi zla gdan du bting //
NK130(tho)001:546: sgrags kyi grong khyer bcu bdun po //
NK130(tho)001:547: drag sngags mthu yis thal bar byas //
NK130(tho)001:548: rgyal sras mu khri btsan po la //
NK130(tho)001:549: pe har gnam the'i gnod pa bsal //
NK130(tho)001:550: rgya gar bal por lan bdun byon //
NK130(tho)001:551: mi lo brgya dang bcu bzhi bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:552: mkhas pa de yis bsgyur ba'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:553: de yis byas zhes skur 'debs na //
NK130(tho)001:554: byas kyang byas pa kho nas legs //
NK130(tho)001:555: rgyud rnams sangs rgyas gsung min cing //
NK130(tho)001:556: rang bzos bsgrigs pa'i rtog chos la //
NK130(tho)001:557: grub brnyes byi'u khyu 'phur ba tsam //
NK130(tho)001:558: gnubs pa'i chos las byung 'di mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:559: gshin rje kha thun chos skor 'di //
NK130(tho)001:560: 'gos lo la yang yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:561: gzhan yang 'gos lo lhas btsas kyi //
NK130(tho)001:562: rgyal po sprin gyi shugs can la //
NK130(tho)001:563: zhus pa'i gshin rje 'ga' zhig dang //
NK130(tho)001:565: sprin shugs ma zhes bya ba la //
NK130(tho)001:566: rgyud drug 'grel pa man ngag bcas //
NK130(tho)001:567: ga ya d+ha ri'i zhal khrigs dang //
NK130(tho)001:568: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:569: brgyud pa'i gshin rje tshe bdag dang //
NK130(tho)001:570: jo bo rje yi rta mgrin dang //
NK130(tho)001:571: sa skya pa yi yang phur dang //
NK130(tho)001:572: ras chung lugs kyi phyag rdor dang //
NK130(tho)001:573: zangs lo'i rnam sras 'brom sde lugs //
NK130(tho)001:574: snar thang pa yi lha mo dpal //
NK130(tho)001:575: b+ha ha ra yi stag zhen sogs //
NK130(tho)001:576: rgyud dang sgrub thabs rgya chen po //
NK130(tho)001:577: de rnams jo bo rje la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:578: ma byon gong du gnubs pa la //
NK130(tho)001:579: yod phyir brtsams zhes mi smra ste //
NK130(tho)001:580: khyad par med cing mthun pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:581: de yi chos dang bsdur bas shes //
NK130(tho)001:582: de lta na yang 'gog byed na //
NK130(tho)001:583: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa las //
NK130(tho)001:584: lkog tu gyur pa'i grub mtha' zhig /'dzin pa nyid du khyed cag nges //
NK130(tho)001:585: khyad par hwa shang grub mtha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:586: man ngag lta phreng bsres so zhes //
NK130(tho)001:588: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:589: tshad ldan gzhung du khyer rang gis //
NK130(tho)001:590: khas blangs 'dir ni hwa shang lugs //
NK130(tho)001:591: yas babs la sogs grub pa'i mtha' //
NK130(tho)001:592: tshig 'bru gcig kyang yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:593: de phyir bsnyon du ma shes te //
NK130(tho)001:594: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po yi //
NK130(tho)001:595: thugs dam man ngag lta phreng yang //
NK130(tho)001:596: phyis nas de yi brgyud 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:597: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos su bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:598: sbas yul kahthoga pa la sbyar //
NK130(tho)001:599: de skad zer dgos byung ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:600: kahthoga zhes bya'i dgon pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:601: rga mi dam pa bde gshegs zhes //
NK130(tho)001:602: phag mo gru pa'i yum mched des //
NK130(tho)001:603: bdag med yul du dgon pa btab //
NK130(tho)001:604: sus kyang sbyar ba'i lo rgyus med //
NK130(tho)001:606: dar rje dpal gyi grags pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:607: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:608: dgongs 'dus ye shes rngams pa glog /
NK130(tho)001:609: dur khrod khu byug rol pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:610: sems lung chen mo lnga ru byas //
NK130(tho)001:611: nyang ston smra ba'i seng ge yis //
NK130(tho)001:612: kun byed rgyal po la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:613: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad byas //
NK130(tho)001:614: lce btsun seng ge dbang phyug gis //
NK130(tho)001:615: bi ma la yi snying thig dang //
NK130(tho)001:616: de yi rgyud chen bcu bdun byas //
NK130(tho)001:617: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po yi //
NK130(tho)001:618: thugs dam man ngag lta phreng yang //
NK130(tho)001:619: phyis nas de yi brgyud 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:620: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos su bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:621: sbas yul kahthoga pa la sbyar //
NK130(tho)001:623: kun 'dus la sogs mdo lnga po'i //
NK130(tho)001:625: mtshan brjod 'grel par bi ma las //
NK130(tho)001:626: kun 'dus rig pa'i lung mang drangs //
NK130(tho)001:627: kun byed sems phyogs yin mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:628: sems sde bco brgyad nang tshan min //
NK130(tho)001:629: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:630: mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal //
NK130(tho)001:631: yin par sgra yis sgrub pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:632: 'gos lo yid bzang rtse bas bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:633: bi ma la yi snying thig la //
NK130(tho)001:634: man ngag brgya dang bcu dgu yod //
NK130(tho)001:635: de la rgyud chen bcu bdun dang //
NK130(tho)001:636: kha skang gi ni rgyud bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:637: bka' srung nag mo khros ma'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:638: 'di kan ldang ma lhun rgyal gyis //
NK130(tho)001:639: dbu ru zhwa yi lha khang nas //
NK130(tho)001:640: gter bton khams pa sgom chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:641: gnas brtan rtse mo grags la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:642: slob ma 'ga' la spel ba yod //
NK130(tho)001:643: ldang ma 'da' khar lce btsun slebs //
NK130(tho)001:644: gter chos kun byin ma phyi g.yar //
NK130(tho)001:645: da gzod skyel ba'i chad mdo byas //
NK130(tho)001:646: da gzod dus thog skyel du phyin //
NK130(tho)001:647: snye thang 'or du slebs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:648: ldang ma 'das pa'i gtam thos pas //
NK130(tho)001:649: skyo nas slar log gtsang la 'ongs //
NK130(tho)001:650: des na rgyud chen bcu bdun dang //
NK130(tho)001:651: bi ma la yi snying thig rnams //
NK130(tho)001:652: lce btsun nyid dang ma 'phrad gong //
NK130(tho)001:653: gzhan la grags phyir lce btsun gyis //
NK130(tho)001:654: brtsams chos yin ces ma smra zhig /'di ni de rjes lce btsun gyis //
NK130(tho)001:655: bsam yas mchims phu nas bton pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:656: gter chos zab pa pod bzhi de //
NK130(tho)001:657: bi ma la nas brgyud pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:658: bi ma la yi snying thig gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:659: 'khrul nas brtsams zhes smra bar zad //
NK130(tho)001:660: tshul 'di khong du ma chud pas //
NK130(tho)001:661: rgyus med lan cig khung nas bde //
NK130(tho)001:663: mnga' bdag nyang ban ral pa can //
NK130(tho)001:664: gu ru chos dbang chos lo dang //
NK130(tho)001:665: chos rgyal rin chen gling pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:666: sprul sku o rgyan gling pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:667: tshe bstan rgyal mtshan la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:668: rdzun gyi gter ston mang po byung //
NK130(tho)001:670: de dag brdzun pa'i rdzun lugs ci //
NK130(tho)001:671: shes byed gtan tshigs gang zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:673: bsam bzhin skye ba sprul pa'i sku //
NK130(tho)001:674: 'gro ba'i dpung gnyen mchog rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:675: mkhas pa su zhig log par lta //
NK130(tho)001:676: dang po nyid du byang chub kyang //
NK130(tho)001:677: gdul bya'i dbang po bsam pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:678: rlabs chen gzhan don spyod pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:679: 'phags pa sa chen bzhugs rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:680: g.yul du zhugs pa'i dgra bo bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:681: sdang sems ngan smra kho na yis //
NK130(tho)001:684: bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:685: rta mgrin bde gshegs 'dus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:686: tshe bdag ur mo la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:687: chos gter rdzun ma bsam mi khyab //
NK130(tho)001:689: mkha' 'gro snying thig chos skor byas //
NK130(tho)001:690: gter ston rdo rje gling pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:691: rdo rje sems dpa'i snying thig byas //
NK130(tho)001:693: rdzun ni mi bden pa yi ming //
NK130(tho)001:694: yin nam ma yin khyed la 'dri //
NK130(tho)001:695: yin na gter chos 'di dag la //
NK130(tho)001:696: smin byed dbang dang grol byed lam //
NK130(tho)001:697: lta ba sgom pa spyod pa 'bras //
NK130(tho)001:698: nor dang 'khrul pa ma mchis la //
NK130(tho)001:699: yar mtha' sangs rgyas sgrub pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:700: mar mtha' dgra bgegs sgrol ba yan //
NK130(tho)001:701: sangs rgyas phrin las rab 'byams kun //
NK130(tho)001:702: thogs pa med par 'grub bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:703: rdzun ces mngon sum ma bsnyon zhig /
NK130(tho)001:704: rang gi lugs la ma grags pas //
NK130(tho)001:705: chos ma yin zhes mi bsam ste //
NK130(tho)001:706: chos kyi rnam grangs thams cad las //
NK130(tho)001:707: gsang sngags bla med mang ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:708: jo bo rje yis gsungs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:709: bye brag smra sogs nyan thos kyis //
NK130(tho)001:710: rang la ma grags dbang byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:711: theg pa chen po'i chos spangs pas //
NK130(tho)001:712: de la byams mgon klu sgrub kyis //
NK130(tho)001:713: theg chen bka' ru sgrub pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:714: dus 'di nyid du dran par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:715: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:716: chos tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:717: don yang dus 'dir dran mdzod la //
NK130(tho)001:718: rgya mtsho chen po'i rus sbal dang //
NK130(tho)001:719: khron par gnas pa'i sbal pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:720: ji ltar thugs su mi shong ba //
NK130(tho)001:721: mthong ba chung 'di bshol bar rigs //
NK130(tho)001:723: da lta'ang gu ru'i ming can gyi //
NK130(tho)001:724: gter ston 'ga' zhig yod ces thos //
NK130(tho)001:725: snyigs dus bdud sde shugs ches pas //
NK130(tho)001:726: da dung rdzun gter mang du 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:727: gtsug lag mkhas pa'i gtam spangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:728: rigs mthun blun po yid mgu ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:729: chos de nags la me ltar mched //
NK130(tho)001:730: bod yul rdzun gyi dbang du song //
NK130(tho)001:732: gter ston rim gyis 'byon pa las //
NK130(tho)001:733: 'gro don mdzad pa'i sprul sku dang //
NK130(tho)001:734: bdud rigs zog gter 'ong ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:735: rig 'dzin rgyal bas lung du bstan //
NK130(tho)001:736: dbye ba lta spyod ma 'khrul zhing //
NK130(tho)001:737: dus tshod sa rtags rus dang ming //
NK130(tho)001:738: lus kyi sha mtshan yan chad du //
NK130(tho)001:739: nges pa nyid du lung bstan pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:740: gang zag de ni tshad ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:741: de tshul 'dra la ma yin pa //
NK130(tho)001:742: 'dra min bdud kyi ris gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:743: rnying ma las kyang gsar ma pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:744: khrod na mang ba 'byung ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:745: 'phags pa brgyad stong pa las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:746: lnga brgya'i tha ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK130(tho)001:747: bdud ni mkhan po slob dpon gyi //
NK130(tho)001:748: gzugs can 'ong zhes lung bstan to //
NK130(tho)001:749: da dung rdzun gter mang 'byung lo //
NK130(tho)001:750: nged kyi gzhung lugs khung ma las //
NK130(tho)001:751: grol zhig gling pas gter 'jug sdud //
NK130(tho)001:752: de nas 'ong bar ma gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:753: rigs mthun blun po yid mgu ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:754: chos de nags la me ltar mched //
NK130(tho)001:755: ces pa'ang brtags na mi rigs te //
NK130(tho)001:756: rdzogs chen dbang po rab kyi chos //
NK130(tho)001:757: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dbyangs gcig pa //
NK130(tho)001:758: lta dgongs bla na med pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:759: mkhas rloms rnams kyang spong byed na //
NK130(tho)001:760: blun po shes rab chung ba rnams //
NK130(tho)001:761: ma go bzhin du ci phyir mgu //
NK130(tho)001:763: 'dus pa sdom pa kye rdo rje //
NK130(tho)001:764: dus 'khor rdo rje gdan bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:765: sangs rgyas thod pa sgyu ma che //
NK130(tho)001:766: rdo rje bdud rtsi gshin rje gshed //
NK130(tho)001:767: rje btsun nag po che la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:768: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:769: zab don phyag rgya chen po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:770: theg pa dman zhes khyad du gsod //
NK130(tho)001:771: bka' ma gter ma bgrang mi lang //
NK130(tho)001:772: theg pa rim dgu'i yang rtse ste //
NK130(tho)001:773: zab mo rdzogs pa chen po'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:774: thos pa tsam gyis grol 'gyur lo //
NK130(tho)001:776: rgyal bas gsung pa sde snod gsum //
NK130(tho)001:777: khyad par sngags kyi rgyud sde bzhir //
NK130(tho)001:779: sangs rgyas bstan pa spyi lugs yin //
NK130(tho)001:780: theg pa chung las theg chen 'phags //
NK130(tho)001:781: de las rdo rje theg pa mchog /
NK130(tho)001:782: de la'ang rim gyis mtho dman yod //
NK130(tho)001:783: rdo rje gur gyi rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:784: dman pa rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:785: bya min rnal 'byor de ltag la //
NK130(tho)001:786: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor che //
NK130(tho)001:787: rnal 'byor bla med de ltag la //
NK130(tho)001:788: zhes gsungs bla med nang chen la'ang //
NK130(tho)001:789: pha yi rgyud las ma rgyud mtho //
NK130(tho)001:790: de las gnyis med rgyud mtho zhes //
NK130(tho)001:791: shing rta che rnams thams cad bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:792: rgyud don phyag rgya chen po dang //
NK130(tho)001:793: zab mo rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK130(tho)001:794: lta ba 'dra yang bgrod pa'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:795: myur khyad gnad kyis shin tu che //
NK130(tho)001:796: gsar ma'i sngags dang pha rol phyin //
NK130(tho)001:797: lta ba'i dgongs pa gcig mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:798: lam la nye ring khyad par che //
NK130(tho)001:799: de phyir 'di yang de dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:800: rgyal ba'i gsung rab thams cad las //
NK130(tho)001:801: theg chen gsang sngags mang pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:802: bka' ma gter ma bgrang mi lang //
NK130(tho)001:803: de yang thos pas mi grol na //
NK130(tho)001:804: ma thos pa la ga la grol //
NK130(tho)001:805: dbang rab sngon nas sbyangs pa can //
NK130(tho)001:806: thos pa tsam gyis grol ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:807: me dang spra ba phrad pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:808: rtogs dang grol ba dus mnyam pa //
NK130(tho)001:809: rgyal po sa ha ka ra dang //
NK130(tho)001:810: bram ze chen po sa ra ha //
NK130(tho)001:811: bod kyi grub thob gling ras bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:812: dbang 'bring rang snang longs skur grol //
NK130(tho)001:813: tha ma rang bzhin sprul skur grol //
NK130(tho)001:814: yang tha skye ba brgyud nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:815: grol ba rnying ma'i rang lugs dang //
NK130(tho)001:816: mthun par dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK130(tho)001:818: skye ba phyi mar grol zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:819: de bzhin gsang ba'i mdzod dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:820: rdo rje rtse ma'i rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:821: dbang thob dam tshig ma nyams na //
NK130(tho)001:822: skye ba bdun nam bcu drug na //
NK130(tho)001:823: grol zhes gsungs shing dus 'khor las //
NK130(tho)001:824: ma bsgoms na yang nges pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:825: zhes pa dmigs kyis gsal bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:826: thos pas grol ba ma yin na //
NK130(tho)001:827: 'di ni bsgoms pas grol ba min //
NK130(tho)001:828: da dung thos pa rgya bskyed rigs //
NK130(tho)001:830: ston pa kun tu bzang pos gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:831: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sh+r+ai seng ha //
NK130(tho)001:832: klu sgrub snying po bi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:834: o rgyan yul dang rgya gar gyi //
NK130(tho)001:835: mkhas shing grub pa de thams cad //
NK130(tho)001:836: dam chos 'di yis grol lo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:837: rdzun khungs rgya gar yul nas btsal //
NK130(tho)001:839: 'di ni gong du rang nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:840: o rgyan slob dpon pad+ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:841: man ngag lta phreng bshad pa'i rjes //
NK130(tho)001:842: chos gzhan gsung ba'i long med par //
NK130(tho)001:843: slob dpon gshegs pa'i gtam brgyud kyis //
NK130(tho)001:844: rdzogs chen med par sgrub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:845: slob dpon 'di nyid rdzogs chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:846: pan chen min par smra ba 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:848: rgyal po bka' yi thang yig dang //
NK130(tho)001:850: bka' ma gter ma so so yin //
NK130(tho)001:851: rdzun gyi lo rgyus bsam mi khyad //
NK130(tho)001:854: lo rgyus rnams la 'khrul pa med //
NK130(tho)001:855: gzhan du grags dang ma mthun pa //
NK130(tho)001:856: de nyid rdzun mar 'dod na ni //
NK130(tho)001:857: sangs rgyas byang sems mdzad pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:858: grub thob rnams kyi rnam thar yang //
NK130(tho)001:859: gdul bya so so'i snang ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:860: bstun phyir gcig tu mi gnas pas //
NK130(tho)001:861: de dag kun kyang rdzun mar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:863: kha cig snod ldan ma rnyed pas //
NK130(tho)001:864: sa dang brag la gter du sbas //
NK130(tho)001:865: phyi dus smon lam btab pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:866: skal ldan nga yis bton no lo //
NK130(tho)001:868: 'di ni mtha' gcig tu ma nges //
NK130(tho)001:869: snod ma rnyed nas sbas pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:870: la la dus der slob dpon gzhan //
NK130(tho)001:871: de yi gdul byar gyur pa des //
NK130(tho)001:872: rang gi chos rnams ma 'ongs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:873: don du gter du sbas pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:874: 'brug pa'i ro snyams skor drug bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:875: ras chung ba la ti pu phas //
NK130(tho)001:876: gdams ngag bshad la dus tshod dgos //
NK130(tho)001:877: phyi dus don chen sbos shig gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:878: gsungs bzhin mkhar chur gter du sbas //
NK130(tho)001:879: de nyid 'gro mgon gtsang pas bton //
NK130(tho)001:880: 'gro don nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK130(tho)001:881: kha cig bdud rgyal glang dar mas //
NK130(tho)001:882: bstan pa bsnubs pa de gzigs nas //
NK130(tho)001:883: mi nub phyir du sbas pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:884: kha cig dus kyi 'gyur ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:885: nag phyogs gnon phyir sbas pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:886: sa yi bcud rnams spel ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:887: 'jig rten bde phyir sbas pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:888: 'don du mi rung gter yang yod //
NK130(tho)001:889: thabs la mkhas pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK130(tho)001:890: gzigs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NK130(tho)001:891: rnam grangs brjod kyis ga la lang //
NK130(tho)001:893: gter ma smon lam gtso che bas //
NK130(tho)001:894: dbang skur lung dang man ngag kun //
NK130(tho)001:895: gang dang phrad pa des thob phyir //
NK130(tho)001:896: bla ma'i bka' lung mi dgos lo //
NK130(tho)001:898: 'di ni rgyal ba'i bka' la yang //
NK130(tho)001:899: rjes su gnang dang byin brlabs pas //
NK130(tho)001:900: gzhan gyi ngag kyang bka' ru grub //
NK130(tho)001:901: de phyir 'dir yang rjes su gnang //
NK130(tho)001:902: las can cig dang 'phrad par shog /
NK130(tho)001:903: phrad nas 'gro don byed par shog /
NK130(tho)001:904: ces gsungs dngos sam nyams kyi ngor //
NK130(tho)001:905: dag pa'i snang bar byin brlabs pas //
NK130(tho)001:906: bla ma'i bka' lung med pa min //
NK130(tho)001:908: sangs rgyas ye shes la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:909: sangs rgyas lta bu'i 'phags pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:910: de yis bla go mi chod cing //
NK130(tho)001:911: 'phags pa'i smon lam mi gtso zhes //
NK130(tho)001:912: smra ba 'di ni bdud tshig yin //
NK130(tho)001:914: gsang sngags gsar ma'i khrod na yang //
NK130(tho)001:915: gsang 'dus gnyis med rnam rgyal che //
NK130(tho)001:916: rdo rje 'jigs byed sam lugs dang //
NK130(tho)001:917: bde mchog ra li sum cu gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:918: dus 'khor lce spyang glu gar dang //
NK130(tho)001:919: kye rdor sku gsung thugs gsang mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:920: phyag na rdo rje mi g.yo ba //
NK130(tho)001:921: rdo rje phag mo seng gdong ma //
NK130(tho)001:922: phyag rgya chen po'i rgyud 'ga' dang //
NK130(tho)001:923: mgon po dang ni lha mo'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:924: brgya dang lnga bcu lhag la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:925: rang bzo'i rdzun rgyud du ma snang //
NK130(tho)001:926: rdo rje snying po'i smad 'grel dang //
NK130(tho)001:927: lho pa thams cad mkhyen pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:928: nal ro 'grel chen zhes pa'ang byas //
NK130(tho)001:930: gsang 'dus gnyis med rnam rgyal che //
NK130(tho)001:931: dang por smri tis rang 'gyur mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:932: bar du dge slong chos blos bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:933: tha mar nyang stod rgyal mkhar rtser //
NK130(tho)001:934: sgra pa thugs rje seng ge yis //
NK130(tho)001:935: rgya dpe rnyed nas slar yang bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:936: de phyir rgol ba'i gnas med do //
NK130(tho)001:937: bde mchog ra li sum cu gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:938: gsang ba rdo rje gsang ba gcod //
NK130(tho)001:939: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK130(tho)001:940: nam mkha' mnyam dang nam mkha' che //
NK130(tho)001:941: sku gsung thugs rgyud rin chen phreng //
NK130(tho)001:942: dam tshig che ste thugs rgyud brgyad //
NK130(tho)001:943: stobs po che dang ye shes gsang //
NK130(tho)001:944: ye shes phreng ba ye shes 'bar //
NK130(tho)001:946: ye shes rgyal po gsung rgyud brgyad //
NK130(tho)001:948: gsang ba bdud rtsi dur khrod rgyan //
NK130(tho)001:949: rdo rje rgyal po ye shes bsam //
NK130(tho)001:950: chags pa'i rgyud dang mkha' 'gro sdom //
NK130(tho)001:951: sku rgyud brgyad de nyi shu bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:952: de dag rnal 'byor nyer bzhi la //
NK130(tho)001:953: bsdu sogs yi ge'i brda yis gtad //
NK130(tho)001:954: de dag las ni 'phros pa'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:955: me phreng rdo rje mkha' 'gro gsang //
NK130(tho)001:957: rdo rje grub pa d+r+wa ba sdom //
NK130(tho)001:958: de bzhin gshegs pa thugs kyi snying //
NK130(tho)001:959: dur khrod rgyan gyi rmad byung dang //
NK130(tho)001:960: rnyog pa med dang a ra li //
NK130(tho)001:961: gcig tu bgrang ste bsnan pas brgyad //
NK130(tho)001:962: de ltar ra li sum cu gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:963: pan chen ga ya d+ha ra yis //
NK130(tho)001:964: mkhas pa myos dang 'brog mi la //
NK130(tho)001:965: bshad pa'i gser chos rgya dpe can //
NK130(tho)001:966: yin phyir bod mar ma sgrubs shig /
NK130(tho)001:967: dang po 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba la babs te 'gyur yon la gser zho sum brgya 'bul ba /
NK130(tho)001:968: lo gsum la 'gyur tshar ba byed pa byas pa la /
NK130(tho)001:970: pan+di ta rgya gar la rings nas gser ma 'grub pa la /
NK130(tho)001:971: zur po che la sprin pas gser zho sum brgya byung ba phul bas dgyes te /
NK130(tho)001:972: ma h+aa lo ts+aa ba 'brog mi yin /
NK130(tho)001:973: ga ya d+ha ra pan+di ta yin gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:974: de nas phyis bod du byon tsa na kha rag
NK130(tho)001:975: tu myos lo ts+aa bas zhabs tog byas te gnang
NK130(tho)001:976: / rgya dpe la la mang mkhar myu gu lung
NK130(tho)001:977: na yod pa de la stod lho pa la byung
NK130(tho)001:978: / / de nas dpe 'thor ba deng sang yang 'dug go //
NK130(tho)001:979: mkha' 'gro seng ge'i gdong can ma //
NK130(tho)001:980: bla ma ba ri lo ts+aa bas //
NK130(tho)001:981: rgya gar yul nas spyan drangs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:982: rgya gzhung rtsod pa med pa nyid //
NK130(tho)001:983: yin pa sa skya pa la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:984: de yi brgyud 'dzin thams cad bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:985: rdo rje phag mo rgyal ba'i yum //
NK130(tho)001:986: phyi rol pa yi lhar 'dod dang //
NK130(tho)001:987: de yi rgyud gzhung mang po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:988: mu stegs pa dang 'dres so zhes //
NK130(tho)001:989: bdud chen snying la zhugs rnams smra //
NK130(tho)001:990: bir wa pa dang n+aa ro sogs //
NK130(tho)001:991: 'phags pa'i yul gyi pan grub dang //
NK130(tho)001:992: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos sa skya pa //
NK130(tho)001:994: bod kyi bstan 'dzin che rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:995: thugs dam snying po mnog chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:996: de bzhin 'jigs byed sam lugs nas //
NK130(tho)001:997: rgyud sde phyed dang nyis brgya sogs //
NK130(tho)001:998: rdzun ces dam chos spong ba las //
NK130(tho)001:999: rang bzo yin pa'i shes byed med //
NK130(tho)001:1000: shes byed med bzhin chos spang ba //
NK130(tho)001:1001: dmyal ba'i rgyu las gzhan du min //
NK130(tho)001:1003: dang po dpyal lo chos bzang gis //
NK130(tho)001:1004: bsgyur bas stod smad kun na dar //
NK130(tho)001:1005: dus phyis pan chen nags rin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1006: yar klung mthil du bsgyur zhing gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1007: rgya dpe deng sang du yang snang //
NK130(tho)001:1008: brtag pa gsum dang rton pa bzhis //
NK130(tho)001:1009: legs par brtags shing mi dpyod par //
NK130(tho)001:1010: mkhas mkhas 'dra ba'i mu cor gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1011: chos song 'di la dgos pa ci //
NK130(tho)001:1013: bod yul rmangs pa'i do ra 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:1014: mi rnams sbyangs pa shes rab chung //
NK130(tho)001:1015: yin min dpyod pa'i blo med par //
NK130(tho)001:1016: ma brtags blun po'i dad pas 'jug /
NK130(tho)001:1018: nges pa don gyi chos rnams ni //
NK130(tho)001:1019: rtog ge'i yul las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1020: brtags shing dpyad pas mi mthong bas //
NK130(tho)001:1021: rgyal bas sgrub pa snying por gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1022: rgya bod rig 'dzin gshegs pa'i shul //
NK130(tho)001:1023: bslu ba med pa'i lam mchog la //
NK130(tho)001:1024: rtog dpyod btang bas yid ma ches //
NK130(tho)001:1025: bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1026: gsang sngags gsar ma'i rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1027: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1028: don la the tshom med pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1029: mkhas pa la ni dngos grub nye //
NK130(tho)001:1030: yang na blun po dad pa brtan //
NK130(tho)001:1031: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub nye //
NK130(tho)001:1032: rtog cing dpyod pa'i rtog ge ba //
NK130(tho)001:1033: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub med //
NK130(tho)001:1034: ces sogs gsungs pa ma mthong ngam /
NK130(tho)001:1036: g.yo sgyu can gyi bla ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:1037: blun dad can gyi slob ma 'dus //
NK130(tho)001:1038: chos su bcos pa'i ming gis 'khrul //
NK130(tho)001:1039: chos min stong gi 'chad nyan dar //
NK130(tho)001:1040: ji ltar chos log dar gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:1041: de ltar yang dag dam chos nub //
NK130(tho)001:1042: de phyir bstan pa'i bya ra ba //
NK130(tho)001:1043: yod na chos la brtag par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1045: sngon chad ma byung pa yi chos //
NK130(tho)001:1046: bla ma de yis gsar du bcos //
NK130(tho)001:1047: slob ma blun po des nyan na //
NK130(tho)001:1048: ming gis 'khrul pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1049: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i bka' //
NK130(tho)001:1051: chos ltar bcos pa gang gis 'gab //
NK130(tho)001:1052: chos la chos ltar bcos zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:1053: bon yang bon ltar bcos zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:1054: lta ba log cing sgom pa nor //
NK130(tho)001:1055: phyin ci log gi spyod pa bstan //
NK130(tho)001:1056: chos min chos ltar byas pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:1057: de la chos lta bcos zhes bya //
NK130(tho)001:1058: 'dir ni skyon de gang yang med //
NK130(tho)001:1059: gal te rnying ma chos min na //
NK130(tho)001:1060: sngon dus rnying ma shin tu dar //
NK130(tho)001:1061: de dus gsar ma 'ang shin tu dar //
NK130(tho)001:1062: de ltar rnying ma dar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:1063: gsar ma nub pa'i rnam grangs med //
NK130(tho)001:1064: ji ltar chos log dar gyur pas //
NK130(tho)001:1065: de ltar yang dag chos nub na //
NK130(tho)001:1066: chos la brtag pa'i bya ra ba //
NK130(tho)001:1067: yod kyang chos la brtag rgyu ci //
NK130(tho)001:1068: chos nub rjes su chos la ni //
NK130(tho)001:1069: brtag pa de 'dra shin tu mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:1070: rang nyid chos la sdang ba'i gtam //
NK130(tho)001:1071: yin yin 'dra par bsgrigs na yang //
NK130(tho)001:1072: mkhas pa rnam dpyod mig can dang //
NK130(tho)001:1075: mdo sde 'jig rten gdags pa las //
NK130(tho)001:1076: gang zhig chos la chos min dang //
NK130(tho)001:1077: chos ma yin la chos su smra //
NK130(tho)001:1078: skye bo dam pa dag la sdang //
NK130(tho)001:1079: med par lta ba mnar med ltung //
NK130(tho)001:1082: chos la chos min zhes smra dang //
NK130(tho)001:1083: chos min chos su smra ba gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:1084: dmyal ba wa skad can rnams su //
NK130(tho)001:1085: ltung 'gyur zhes pa'ang dran par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1087: 'di ni khyed kyang dran par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1088: rgyud rgyal rnam snang mngon byang las //
NK130(tho)001:1089: rang sems gtan la ma phebs pas //
NK130(tho)001:1090: chos la chos min zhes smra ba //
NK130(tho)001:1091: dmyal pa dang ni dud 'gro yi //
NK130(tho)001:1094: chos zab khyad du gsod pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1096: mya ngan 'das pa'i mdo las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1098: lo ni bdun brgya lon rjes su //
NK130(tho)001:1099: sdig can bdud kyi chos 'byung zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1100: rgyal ba de yis zhal chems bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:1102: ston pa 'das nas lo bdun brgya //
NK130(tho)001:1103: 'das rjes byung ba'i chos log de //
NK130(tho)001:1104: rdzogs chen yin par smra ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:1105: dar mas bstan pa ma bsnubs gong //
NK130(tho)001:1106: rdzogs chen ming yang med do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1107: gang du nan gyis sgrub pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1108: 'gal ba du ma khyod smra mod //
NK130(tho)001:1109: 'di ni kla klo'i chos lung bstan //
NK130(tho)001:1110: rgyu mtshan dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK130(tho)001:1112: chos rgyal bdun gyis lo brgya brgya //
NK130(tho)001:1115: kla klo 'jug par gsungs de yin //
NK130(tho)001:1117: 'phags pa ba lang bdag gis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1118: chos la chos 'drar bcos pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1119: gzhung dang lta ba 'byung bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1121: 'di ni sngags kyi lung bstan min //
NK130(tho)001:1122: rgyal ba mchog de'i nyan thos rnams //
NK130(tho)001:1123: sde pa bco brgyad gyes pa'i rjes //
NK130(tho)001:1124: yang pa can gyi dge slong gis //
NK130(tho)001:1125: mi rung ba ni gzhi bcu byas //
NK130(tho)001:1126: dgra bcom bdun brgyas de sun phyungs //
NK130(tho)001:1127: bka' bsdu mdzad pa de la dgongs //
NK130(tho)001:1129: dam chos 'dul ba phran tshegs las //
NK130(tho)001:1130: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal chems su //
NK130(tho)001:1131: gang zag la ni dag snang sbyangs //
NK130(tho)001:1132: chos la rtog dpyad gyis shig gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1134: rgyal ba'i bka' 'di'i dgongs don ni //
NK130(tho)001:1135: mu stegs kha cig 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:1136: dge ba sgrub cing sdig spang na //
NK130(tho)001:1137: mu stegs yin kyang ci zhig skyon //
NK130(tho)001:1138: gal te de ltar mi byed na //
NK130(tho)001:1139: nang pa yin kyang ci zhig phan //
NK130(tho)001:1140: zhes sogs spyod pa phyogs 'dra dang //
NK130(tho)001:1141: nya dang ru sbal phag dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:1142: ra ma gnyis dang nag pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1143: mi yi seng ge mi'u thung //
NK130(tho)001:1144: sangs rgyas ngang pa can de bcu //
NK130(tho)001:1146: sangs rgyas chos 'dra ches mang la //
NK130(tho)001:1147: khyad par nyan thos rang rgyal gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1148: chos dang gang zag bdag med la //
NK130(tho)001:1149: phyi rol pa la'ang phyogs 'dra yi //
NK130(tho)001:1150: lta ba yod phyir de 'dres na //
NK130(tho)001:1151: rtag chad lam du 'gyur ba la //
NK130(tho)001:1152: dgongs nas brtag par thub pas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1153: theg dman 'dzin pa'i nyan thos kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1154: sngags la brtag ces gsungs pa min //
NK130(tho)001:1155: gong gi tshig 'bru la rten nas //
NK130(tho)001:1156: sngon gyi nyan thos sen d+ha pas //
NK130(tho)001:1157: theg pa chen po chos min du //
NK130(tho)001:1158: sgrubs kyang mkhas rnams de mi bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:1160: rdo rje theg par 'jug pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1161: chos dang bla ma sdom pa gsum //
NK130(tho)001:1162: brtags shing dpyad nas yid ches gsum //
NK130(tho)001:1163: tshang na nyan du rung bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1165: rdo rje theg pa 'jug pa pos //
NK130(tho)001:1166: bya ba'i rgyud ni 'ga' zhig dang //
NK130(tho)001:1167: 'jam dpal rtsa ba'i rgyud du ni //
NK130(tho)001:1168: tshul khrims 'chal la thub dbang gis //
NK130(tho)001:1169: gsang sngags 'grub par ma gsungs te //
NK130(tho)001:1170: zhes pas so thar dgos pa'ang bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1171: rnal 'byor dang ni bla med rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1172: khyim pa rnams dang thun mong yin //
NK130(tho)001:1173: so thar mdo kyang nyan du rung //
NK130(tho)001:1174: gsang sngags nang pa'i sdom pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1175: dam tshig zhes su grags pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1176: so so thar dang cung mi mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:1177: brtags nas yid ches gsum tshang ba //
NK130(tho)001:1178: nges pa nyid du mi dgos te //
NK130(tho)001:1179: gsang sngags sgra yang ma thos la //
NK130(tho)001:1180: cha dang rgyus kyang ma 'tshal ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:1181: lha klu gnod sbyin mi'am ci //
NK130(tho)001:1182: grul bum srin po dri za dang //
NK130(tho)001:1183: de la sogs pa'i 'khor mang la //
NK130(tho)001:1184: sngon tshe rgyal bas gsang sngags bstan //
NK130(tho)001:1185: de la'ang khyod ni gashe'am ci //
NK130(tho)001:1187: ma brtag blun pa'i dang pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:1188: chos rkyang phyin ci log dang 'phrad //
NK130(tho)001:1189: nyams len log par rgyur ba'i mthus //
NK130(tho)001:1190: sems can dmyal bar ltung bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1192: de la 'di ltar brtag bya ste //
NK130(tho)001:1193: kla klo'am mu stegs chos lugs la //
NK130(tho)001:1194: ma brtags dad pas zhugs pa na //
NK130(tho)001:1195: dmyal la sogs par ltung srid kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1196: 'dir ni blun kyang sangs rgyas kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1197: chos so snyam nas dad pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:1198: zhugs de sems can dmyal ba ru //
NK130(tho)001:1199: skye ba nyid du mi 'gyur te //
NK130(tho)001:1200: phal po che yi mdo las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1201: dad pa lan cig tsam skyes kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1202: bsod nams mchog tu 'gyur ro gsung //
NK130(tho)001:1203: dad pa med pa'i mi rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:1204: dkar pa'i chos ni mi 'byung ste //
NK130(tho)001:1205: sa bon me yis tshig pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1206: myu gu med pa'i dpe yis gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1207: dad pas dmyal bar 'gro ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:1210: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho brgal mi brgal //
NK130(tho)001:1211: lha mi'i bde ba myong mi myong //
NK130(tho)001:1212: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho brgal mi brgal //
NK130(tho)001:1213: 'phags pa'i sa lam bgrod mi bgrod //
NK130(tho)001:1215: dad ldan sems can bslu mi bslu //
NK130(tho)001:1216: dam pa'i chos la rag las pas //
NK130(tho)001:1217: 'di la gzab nas brtag dpyad dgos //
NK130(tho)001:1218: don chung nor gyi nyo tshong la //
NK130(tho)001:1219: bsam gzhig bgros te brtags nas byed //
NK130(tho)001:1221: de ltar ji skad smra ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:1222: de kun chos la rag lus pas //
NK130(tho)001:1223: chos kyang theg pa chen po las //
NK130(tho)001:1224: bla med gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg /
NK130(tho)001:1225: grangs med gsum la ma ltos par //
NK130(tho)001:1226: tshe gcig sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:1227: de las ches mchog theg pa'i rtse //
NK130(tho)001:1228: lo zlas sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:1229: gsang chen rdzogs pa chen po la //
NK130(tho)001:1230: mi dad sdang ba'i sems spong la //
NK130(tho)001:1231: tshe 'dir spyod pa'i skal med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1232: phyi ma'i dus su smon lam thob //
NK130(tho)001:1234: gtan gyi so nam dam chos la //
NK130(tho)001:1237: jo bo chen po a ti shas //
NK130(tho)001:1238: chos la phyogs ris mi bya zhing //
NK130(tho)001:1239: gang mos de la 'jug par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1240: ji skad gsungs pa go bar mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:1243: blun dang 'grub pa'i grogs yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1245: blun dad tsam gyis 'grub re kan //
NK130(tho)001:1246: sa bon so nam go log na //
NK130(tho)001:1248: sdig la dad pas 'bad gyur kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1249: mi lus tsam yang 'grub mi srid //
NK130(tho)001:1252: blun dad nyid du ga la 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1254: mi de blun po ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:1255: rgyu ni mi shes rmong na yang //
NK130(tho)001:1256: gnas skabs rkyen gyi dad pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:1257: dge ba'i sa bon btab pas na //
NK130(tho)001:1260: so nam log dang 'di mi mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:1261: rlan gyis 'jig pa skyob pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1262: thub pa'i dbu steng lham bzhag pas //
NK130(tho)001:1263: de yi dge bas rgyal srid thob //
NK130(tho)001:1264: de sogs lung khungs rgya cher yod //
NK130(tho)001:1265: sdig la dad pas mi lus tsam //
NK130(tho)001:1266: 'grub mi srid pa ha cang thal //
NK130(tho)001:1267: theg pa chen po'i chos tshul 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:1268: spyod pa las ni bsam pa gtso //
NK130(tho)001:1269: phan pa'i bsam pas srog gcod sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1270: sdig las byang chub lam yin te //
NK130(tho)001:1271: las nag rnam smin dkar ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:1272: mang po bskyabs phyir gcig gsod sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1273: mkhas pa rnam la grags pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1274: rgyu 'bras tshul la slob par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:1276: so nam tsam gyi rgyu 'bras lta //
NK130(tho)001:1277: so so skye bos shes mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1278: thar pa thob pa'i rgyu 'bras de //
NK130(tho)001:1279: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod yul yin //
NK130(tho)001:1281: 'o na thar pa thob pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1282: rgyu 'bras sangs rgyas yul yin na //
NK130(tho)001:1283: chos sgor zhugs pa phal mo che //
NK130(tho)001:1284: so so skye ba yin pas na //
NK130(tho)001:1285: rgyu 'bras spyod pa'i yul min nam //
NK130(tho)001:1286: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i sgor zhugs pas //
NK130(tho)001:1287: rgyu 'bras spyod pa'i yul min zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1290: drag po khyab 'jug tshangs pas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1291: rgyal ba'i chos 'khor bskor mi nus //
NK130(tho)001:1292: ston pa bod blun 'chal pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1295: mi tshe ril por sbyangs nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1296: yang dag chos dang ma 'phrad na //
NK130(tho)001:1297: lam log ngal ba don re chung //
NK130(tho)001:1298: lha sa'i jo bo blta'o zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1300: choms rkun chen pos bcom pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:1301: 'di dang phyi ma'i don las nyams //
NK130(tho)001:1303: rgyal ba'i chos 'khor tshangs pas kyang bskor mi nus pa la /
NK130(tho)001:1304: bod blun pos bskor nus na de ches ya mtshan
NK130(tho)001:1305: gyi gnas su gyur pa yin pas lan gdab ma
NK130(tho)001:1306: dgos kyang / bzhad gad du brjod na mkhyen rab mchog gyur 'jam dpal dang /
NK130(tho)001:1307: bka' bsdu mdzad pa'i rgyal sras dang //
NK130(tho)001:1308: rgya bod lo pan 'di tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1309: thub pa'i gsang sngags dgag ma nus //
NK130(tho)001:1310: de sang bod ston phyogs re bas //
NK130(tho)001:1312: chos min snyam du sems sems nas //
NK130(tho)001:1313: yang dag chos la rgyab kyis phyogs //
NK130(tho)001:1314: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sgrub bo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1316: log par lta ba'i lam du 'khyams //
NK130(tho)001:1317: 'di dang phyi ma'i don las nyams //
NK130(tho)001:1318: gsang sngags zab mor log par bltas //
NK130(tho)001:1319: rdo rje'i dmyal ba a la la //
NK130(tho)001:1320: khrag gi yi ger bris pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1321: rdo yi char pa shin tu 'jigs //
NK130(tho)001:1322: 'phan yul yangs pa'i thang chen po //
NK130(tho)001:1323: gas nas sku lus ma spangs par //
NK130(tho)001:1324: dmyal ba'i khab tu gshegs pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:1325: sngon gyi gnas brtan lhas byin dang //
NK130(tho)001:1326: legs pa'i skar ma ji bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:1327: zhes pa'i gtam 'di mi bden nam //
NK130(tho)001:1328: lo rgyus 'di ltar grags pa phyis stag lung ngag dbang grags pas rtsad gcod zhib tu mdzad pas /
NK130(tho)001:1329: khungs thub pa mang pos bden pa kho nar gling gi 'dug gsung /
NK130(tho)001:1331: gal te rang bzo mi byed na //
NK130(tho)001:1332: thub pa'i rgyud sde nyid kyis chog /
NK130(tho)001:1333: der ma 'dus pa bris zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:1334: de 'dra khyod kyis gang nas mthong //
NK130(tho)001:1335: bdag gis gsar du dran ce na //
NK130(tho)001:1336: de phyir bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs //
NK130(tho)001:1337: rdzun rgyud gsar du brtsams pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1338: rang bzo med pa 'byung mi srid //
NK130(tho)001:1339: rgyud sde'i dgongs pa bkrol zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:1341: de nyid gzhan phan che snyam na //
NK130(tho)001:1342: de yis thub pa'i bstan pa dkrugs //
NK130(tho)001:1344: thub pa'i rgyud du ma 'dus pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1345: gsar du bzos pa'i rang bzo ni //
NK130(tho)001:1346: rdzogs chen chos la ci zhig 'dug /
NK130(tho)001:1347: bla med rgyud sde thams cad dang //
NK130(tho)001:1348: zhe phugs skyel so gcig pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1349: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1350: 'dir ni sangs rgyas myur sgrub pas //
NK130(tho)001:1351: de la sdang ba'i yid 'chang ba //
NK130(tho)001:1352: bdud dang 'dra bar ma gyur tam //
NK130(tho)001:1354: gang zhig rgyal las ches mkhas 'ga' yang 'jig rten 'di na yod min zhing //
NK130(tho)001:1355: ma lus shes bya'i de nyid mchog ni kun mkhyen gyis mkhyen gzhan min pa //
NK130(tho)001:1356: de phyir drang srong rang nyid kyis bzhag mdo sde gang yin de mi dkrugs //
NK130(tho)001:1357: thub tshul bshig phyir de yang dam chos la ni gnod pa byed par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1359: 'di ni mgon po byams pa'i bka' //
NK130(tho)001:1360: rtag tu phyag dang mchod pa'i gnas //
NK130(tho)001:1361: kun mkhyen rgyal ba las mkhas pa //
NK130(tho)001:1362: mi srid de phyir rjes 'jug gis //
NK130(tho)001:1363: tshul bzhin ston la ma dkrug ces //
NK130(tho)001:1364: dam chos smra ba thams cad la //
NK130(tho)001:1365: legs par 'doms pa'i bka' yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:1366: khyed kyang kun tu bzang po dang //
NK130(tho)001:1367: rdo rje 'chang las mi mkhas pas //
NK130(tho)001:1368: gsang chen rdzogs pa chen po'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:1369: gsar ma'i rgyud dang ma mthun ces //
NK130(tho)001:1370: bstan pa skyon med ma dkrugs cig /
NK130(tho)001:1372: thub pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho la //
NK130(tho)001:1373: rang bzo'i dug chu ches mong bsres //
NK130(tho)001:1374: 'di yis bstan pa ma dkrugs na //
NK130(tho)001:1375: 'o na bstan la gang gis dkrugs //
NK130(tho)001:1376: thub tshul zab mo phyir bshig pas //
NK130(tho)001:1377: chos la gnod pa cher byed pa //
NK130(tho)001:1379: blun po 'ga' zhig mu cor smra //
NK130(tho)001:1381: spyir na gsar rnying gnyis ka la //
NK130(tho)001:1382: rdzun rgyud yod par grags mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1383: sngon nas da lta'i rnying ma ba //
NK130(tho)001:1384: su yis thub pa'i rgyud sde la //
NK130(tho)001:1385: rang bzo gang zhig bsres pa mthong //
NK130(tho)001:1386: gal te bsres na gsar ma'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1387: kun kyang grul ma btub tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1388: rang bzo'i dug chu bsres pas so //
NK130(tho)001:1389: des na med bzhin smra ba po //
NK130(tho)001:1390: rlung tshad 'tha' pa'i nad pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:1391: rnam shes 'khrul par ma gyur grangs //
NK130(tho)001:1393: theg mchog snying po'i zab lam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1394: nges par kun mkhyen sgrub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1395: bla ma brgyud pa ma nyams dang //
NK130(tho)001:1396: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs ma yal dang //
NK130(tho)001:1397: dbang gi chu bo ma bskam dang //
NK130(tho)001:1398: snyan brgyud zam shing ma chag dang //
NK130(tho)001:1399: tshig gi bshad srol ma nub dang //
NK130(tho)001:1400: lam gyi go rim ma log dang //
NK130(tho)001:1401: nyams len don brgyud ma chad dang //
NK130(tho)001:1402: rang bzo'i dug chus ma spags dang //
NK130(tho)001:1403: dam tshig nyams pa'i sel ma zhugs //
NK130(tho)001:1404: 'di dgu tshang ba nges par dgos //
NK130(tho)001:1405: gsung rab dri med ma gtogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1406: rang bzo'i rdzun la de mi 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:1408: bla ma brgyud pa ma nyams shing //
NK130(tho)001:1409: dam tshig nyams pa'i sel med na //
NK130(tho)001:1410: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs nyams dogs med //
NK130(tho)001:1411: dbang gi chu bo ga la nub //
NK130(tho)001:1412: snyan brgyud tshig gi bshad srol gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:1413: dgos dang mi dgos skabs thob gtso //
NK130(tho)001:1414: tshig gi bshad srol zhes pa de //
NK130(tho)001:1415: tshogs la bshad pa'i chos yin la //
NK130(tho)001:1416: snyan brgyud zhes pa slob bshad de //
NK130(tho)001:1417: de yang tshogs la drang don dang //
NK130(tho)001:1418: slob mar nges don 'chad par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1419: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos tshul 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:1420: gdam ngag lhug par ston pas na //
NK130(tho)001:1421: snyan brgyud zam shing ga la chag /
NK130(tho)001:1422: tshig gi bshad srol ci la nub //
NK130(tho)001:1423: de bzhin lam gyi go rim dang //
NK130(tho)001:1424: nyams len don brgyud ga la nyams //
NK130(tho)001:1426: 'jam dbyangs sa skya pan chen gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1427: rdo rje theg pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK130(tho)001:1428: myur du sangs rgyas thob 'dod na //
NK130(tho)001:1429: smin grol gnyis la 'bod ces gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1430: dgu ru phye bas ci zhig bya //
NK130(tho)001:1432: don gyi snying po stor ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:1434: phal cher de dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1435: 'di la re zhig brtag par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1436: rtsom pa'i nyams ni zhan pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1437: sgra dang brda dang tshig nor dang //
NK130(tho)001:1438: don nor cho ga phyin ci log /
NK130(tho)001:1439: lam gyi go rim 'khrul pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1440: yid ches gzhung la ma grags dang //
NK130(tho)001:1441: dam pa rnams kyis smad pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1442: bstan pa'i nang nas bskrad pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1443: yid ches rgyud gzhung gtan med pas //
NK130(tho)001:1444: gtan tshigs brgyad po 'di mthong nas //
NK130(tho)001:1445: bsnyon med rdzun gyi gzhung du shes //
NK130(tho)001:1447: byis pa smyon pa ba lang rdzi'i //
NK130(tho)001:1448: tshig ltar rang bzhin skal ba ngan //
NK130(tho)001:1449: de phyir rtsom pa'i nyams zhan pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:1450: mdo sde rgyud sde'i tshig ris la //
NK130(tho)001:1451: go bde mi bde sna tshogs yod //
NK130(tho)001:1452: 'on kyang mkhas pas mthong ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:1453: khungs ma yin pa'i nges shes thob //
NK130(tho)001:1454: sbyangs dang shes rab mig ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:1455: khyed kyi gzhung brgya mthong ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:1456: rgan pos byis pa'i gtam thos bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:1457: tshig ris tsam la'ang yid ches med //
NK130(tho)001:1459: rtsom pa'i nyams ni bzang ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:1460: tshig dang sdeb sbyor legs pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:1461: yang dag chos su khas len na //
NK130(tho)001:1462: mu stegs gzhung kun chos su 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1464: don la rten pa la dgongs nas //
NK130(tho)001:1465: sgra bzang zhen pa 'gog phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:1466: tshigs bcad sgra nyams gcod mtshams nyams //
NK130(tho)001:1467: rnam dbye med dang dbyangs gsal phyis //
NK130(tho)001:1468: ring la thung dang thung ngu ring //
NK130(tho)001:1469: sgra yi rkyen nyams 'chol ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:1470: bdag gi tshig la gzhan gyi tshig /
NK130(tho)001:1471: gcig la mang tshig sbyar ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1472: dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud la yod //
NK130(tho)001:1473: rnal 'byor ldan pas don bzung zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1475: ngang pas 'o ma len ltar gsung //
NK130(tho)001:1476: phyag na rdo rje'i stod 'grel las //
NK130(tho)001:1477: stod pa bzhi yi dbang byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:1478: tshig la rten pa gzhung der bkag /
NK130(tho)001:1479: pan chen dri med bshes gnyen gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1480: bod kyi mi rnams go bde'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1481: chos skad dbyings la ma brten pas //
NK130(tho)001:1482: mkhas pas tshig skyon gdags mi rigs //
NK130(tho)001:1483: 'on kyang rgyal ba'i lung smod na //
NK130(tho)001:1484: bdag gzhung ci phyir mi smad ces //
NK130(tho)001:1485: mtshan brjod 'grel pa nyid las bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1486: des na rtsom pa'i nyams zhan kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1487: don gyi nyams ni bzang bas chog /
NK130(tho)001:1489: khyed kyis thog ma'i mtshan tsam las //
NK130(tho)001:1490: skad dod nor bas rang mtshang bstan //
NK130(tho)001:1491: phal cher sngags btu'i skabs na nor //
NK130(tho)001:1492: sngags dang sgra bshad phal cher nor //
NK130(tho)001:1494: bar du dar bas drma ya //
NK130(tho)001:1495: tha mar sangs pas sang+g+ha ya //
NK130(tho)001:1497: ca cha ja dang zha za 'a //
NK130(tho)001:1498: 'di drug rgya gar skad du bsres //
NK130(tho)001:1499: gsal byed brtsegs pa re re la //
NK130(tho)001:1500: dbyangs yig gnyis gsum bzhi yis brgyan //
NK130(tho)001:1502: dang por 'bus pa sogs kyi tshig /
NK130(tho)001:1503: blun pos ba bcol bris pa de //
NK130(tho)001:1504: rnying ma'i rgyud du ming brtags pas //
NK130(tho)001:1505: shes ldan su zhig tshad mar 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:1506: ca cha ja dang zha za 'a //
NK130(tho)001:1507: sam skri ta la ma grags kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1508: 'gro ba gzhan gyi skad la yod //
NK130(tho)001:1509: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po nges //
NK130(tho)001:1510: chos ni mtha' yas skad du bstan //
NK130(tho)001:1511: phal po che yi mdo las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1512: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra ji tsam //
NK130(tho)001:1513: thams cad skad du chos bstan zhes //
NK130(tho)001:1514: thub pas gsungs pa'ang dran par bya //
NK130(tho)001:1515: slob dpon zla ba grags pas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1516: ko ta k+sha la sogs pa'i sgra //
NK130(tho)001:1517: 'jig rten bstan bcos la med cing //
NK130(tho)001:1518: de bzhin gshegs pa'i brdar gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:1519: zhes gsungs bde mchog sdam 'byung rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1520: kla klo'i skad du gsungs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1521: gzhan yang nyan thos sde pa bzhi'i //
NK130(tho)001:1522: mdo sde legs sbyar rang bzhin dang //
NK130(tho)001:1523: zur chag sha za'i skad dang bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:1524: de sogs rnam grangs du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:1525: de bzhi gshegs gsungs dam chos rnams //
NK130(tho)001:1526: legs sbyar kho na'i skad yin ces //
NK130(tho)001:1527: smra ba thos pa chung ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:1528: gsal byed brtsegs pa re re la //
NK130(tho)001:1529: dbyangs yig gsum bzhis brgyan pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:1530: skye ba med pa'i chos dbyings las //
NK130(tho)001:1531: 'gags med ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:1532: rtags nyid yin gyi rjod byed sgra'i //
NK130(tho)001:1533: yi ge yin pa'i nges pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1534: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK130(tho)001:1535: brjod du med pa'i yi ge ni //
NK130(tho)001:1536: gri gug thong gshol tsheg drag gi //
NK130(tho)001:1537: rnam pa can sogs gsal bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1538: gal te brjod pa dag gi ni //
NK130(tho)001:1539: yi ge min par gyur na yang //
NK130(tho)001:1540: bklag tu mi btub ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:1541: gsal byed brtsegs pa gcig klog gam //
NK130(tho)001:1542: phral nas klog pa gang yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1543: ji tsam brtsegs pa de klog na //
NK130(tho)001:1546: dper na ke i ko u dang //
NK130(tho)001:1547: se ki so kur bklag pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:1548: rgyas par gsang ba sgra yi rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1549: rgyud chen rig pa rang shar gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1550: 'grel pa nyid du bltas pas shes //
NK130(tho)001:1551: gzhan yang sgra yis sgrub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1552: gsang sngags yi ge gcig shes kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1553: don ni mang por 'gyur bas na //
NK130(tho)001:1556: rbad rbud kham shag ro myags chums //
NK130(tho)001:1557: thod phreng rtsal dang gro bo lod //
NK130(tho)001:1558: e myags ya rdums mugs shag dun //
NK130(tho)001:1559: bam ril dun thibs trig trig khram //
NK130(tho)001:1560: her shog nir shog rgyug breng breng //
NK130(tho)001:1561: rnal ma rnal te sod la rngams //
NK130(tho)001:1562: badz+ra zhang zhung ma la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1563: sngags la 'chal gtam brgya stong bsres //
NK130(tho)001:1565: rbad rbud kham shag la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1566: phyag rdor gsang ba mngon bstan gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1567: rgyud kyi sngags la'ang 'di ltar yod //
NK130(tho)001:1568: mun du rak+sha hril dim dim //
NK130(tho)001:1569: phob phob shag shag rbad rbad dang //
NK130(tho)001:1570: kha tham thum dang ha kri khug /
NK130(tho)001:1571: tshal pa rbad ling srog tshig nan //
NK130(tho)001:1572: rak+ta rngub rngub choms choms dang //
NK130(tho)001:1573: gtub gtub sod sod khos khos byings //
NK130(tho)001:1574: rmugs rmugs hal hal myos myos rbad //
NK130(tho)001:1575: zhi zhi rdul bun rbad sogs mang //
NK130(tho)001:1576: gtum po phyi ma'i rgyud las kyang //
