NK130(tho)001:1577: n+aa ga shig zlog n+aa ga byer //
NK130(tho)001:1579: tshub tshub rbud dang gu ni zhi //
NK130(tho)001:1580: nyi ma sa la nan dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:1581: phyi ma phyi ma'i rgyud du yang //
NK130(tho)001:1582: kha rag nag pe khra ma ya //
NK130(tho)001:1583: de la sogs pa du ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:1584: jo bo rje yi rta mgrin gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1585: sngags ring la yang 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:1586: rgyal 'gong rgya mtsho'i sha la dom //
NK130(tho)001:1587: ro la khrag 'thung la sogs dang //
NK130(tho)001:1588: grub thob zla ba rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1589: zhal gzigs rta mgrin lcags ral can //
NK130(tho)001:1590: de yi sngags la'ang 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:1591: sha khrag rus la rbad sogs dang //
NK130(tho)001:1592: shangs pa'i rta mgrin gsang sgrub la //
NK130(tho)001:1593: kham rak+sha sa ma ya byer //
NK130(tho)001:1594: de la sogs pa'i bod skad 'dres //
NK130(tho)001:1595: lo chen rin bzang sa skya pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1596: bstan srung p+au tra ming sring sngags //
NK130(tho)001:1597: dza dza sham sham li shig te //
NK130(tho)001:1598: rmugs rmugs spu gri a li ma //
NK130(tho)001:1599: de la sogs pa du ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:1600: rdo rje lce 'bebs rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1601: sa gdon nag po sod sod dang //
NK130(tho)001:1602: phyugs rdzi phata dang n+aa ga 'bar //
NK130(tho)001:1603: rdo rje bde 'phros rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1604: m+aa ra myos bying thum ril dzah //
NK130(tho)001:1605: de bzhin 'phags pa lcags mchu las //
NK130(tho)001:1606: shar shar phob dang rak+sha phob //
NK130(tho)001:1607: stobs po che yi gzungs las ni //
NK130(tho)001:1610: ro dang 'dra ba ma bya che //
NK130(tho)001:1611: srung ba lnga la sogs par yod //
NK130(tho)001:1612: gsar rnying gnyis ka khyad par med //
NK130(tho)001:1614: nyid gzhi mu kha le kro d+hi shwa ri b+ha
NK130(tho)001:1615: ga pad+ma ra ya bde klong 'dus 'dus snying sha
NK130(tho)001:1618: rgya skad bod skad phyed bsres la //
NK130(tho)001:1619: chos skad bon skad 'dres pa'i gzungs //
NK130(tho)001:1620: gzhan gang gnas gyur shin tu mang //
NK130(tho)001:1622: 'di ni kun bzang he ru kas //
NK130(tho)001:1623: dngos bstan nyid du gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1624: de la khyed yid mi ches kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1625: pan chen sh+aakya mchog ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:1627: sngags dang brda skad ma mthun kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1628: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub la //
NK130(tho)001:1629: mi bslu nges phyir de tshad ma //
NK130(tho)001:1630: dper na yul chen so so nas //
NK130(tho)001:1631: grub pa mchog rnams kyis blangs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1632: chos dang glegs bam so so las //
NK130(tho)001:1633: 'phags pa'i yul du bsgyur ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:1634: rdo rje sems dpa'i gnang thob pa //
NK130(tho)001:1635: bka' yi bsdu ba po nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:1636: yul khams so so'i skad nyid du //
NK130(tho)001:1637: bshad pas chog par gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1638: de skad gsungs pa dgongs 'tshal lo //
NK130(tho)001:1640: a ti la ni brten nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1641: yang ti spyi ti zer ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:1642: sha ri ram la brten nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1643: nya ri ram dang chu ri ram //
NK130(tho)001:1645: yang ti spyi ti la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1646: theg pa mang po shin tu 'thad //
NK130(tho)001:1647: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo sde las //
NK130(tho)001:1648: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK130(tho)001:1649: zhes dang 'khor lo sdom pa'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1650: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK130(tho)001:1651: theg pa gsum dang bco brgyad de //
NK130(tho)001:1652: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:1653: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1654: lta ba'i dbye bas byas pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:1655: zhes gsungs pa 'di go bar gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1656: sha ri ram sogs lngar phye ba //
NK130(tho)001:1657: 'di ni gsang sngags gsar mar yang //
NK130(tho)001:1658: chos sku'i ring bsrel sku gdung dang //
NK130(tho)001:1659: sku bal chos kyi ring bsrel dang //
NK130(tho)001:1660: yungs 'bru tsam gyi ring bsrel lngar //
NK130(tho)001:1661: slob dpon byang chub bzang pos bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1662: 'dir yang sku gdung ring bsrel ni //
NK130(tho)001:1663: gzhom du med par ngos bzung nas //
NK130(tho)001:1664: 'byung lnga'i stobs kyis lngar byung la //
NK130(tho)001:1665: 'bras bu ye shes lnga'i dbang gis //
NK130(tho)001:1666: kha dog rnam pa lngar byung ba //
NK130(tho)001:1667: 'di la skyon du ci zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:1668: ma go bzhin du ma bsnyon cig /
NK130(tho)001:1671: de ma ma mo rag mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:1672: ma mo'i skad dod ma ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:1673: bdud kyi skad dod ru dra dang //
NK130(tho)001:1674: ma h+aa san+ti rdzogs chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:1675: san+ti ma h+aa zer la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1676: rgya bod sdeb sbyor ma phyes pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1677: tha snyad go rim nor ba mang //
NK130(tho)001:1679: de ma ma mo rag mo sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1680: gsar ma'i khrod na'ang mgon po'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1681: gsang ba dngos grub 'byung ba ru //
NK130(tho)001:1682: rag mo tsit+ta kha rag ma //
NK130(tho)001:1683: h'u b+h+yo zhes pa 'di gsungs mod //
NK130(tho)001:1684: las rnams myur du 'grub phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:1685: gsang sngags dkrug bsdebs byas pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1686: thugs rgyus med pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1688: gshed po gdong pa drug pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1689: gsar ma rang lugs las kyang grags //
NK130(tho)001:1690: ma mo'i ming la ma ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:1691: btags srog dang por drangs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1692: 'brel ba'i don yin skyon ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:1693: ru dra zhes pa drag po ste //
NK130(tho)001:1694: bdud kyi bye brag yin pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1695: bshad kyang 'gal ba yod min la //
NK130(tho)001:1696: 'on kyang mchod bstod dkyil chog las //
NK130(tho)001:1697: bdud dang ru dra so sor phye //
NK130(tho)001:1698: ma h+aa san+ti rdzogs chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1699: skad dod min na 'jam dpal gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1700: zhal lung nyid du gang gsungs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1701: rdzogs chen skad dod de ston cig /
NK130(tho)001:1703: shad kyi don du tsheg drag 'di //
NK130(tho)001:1704: rgya bod gnyis ka'i lugs dang 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:1706: tshig mthar tsheg drag 'a tshag sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1707: gter yig nges pa'i rtags yin gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1708: rgya gar ba yi rnam bcad dang //
NK130(tho)001:1709: bod kyi shad kyi dod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:1711: dam pa dang po'i sangs rgyas las //
NK130(tho)001:1712: sgra yi gnag lugs khongs chud nas //
NK130(tho)001:1713: sgra la zhen pa spong ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1714: ched du sgra nyams gsungs pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:1716: sgra la zhen pa spong ba de //
NK130(tho)001:1717: tshig la mi rten pa yi don //
NK130(tho)001:1718: yin pa ma go ci zhig nongs //
NK130(tho)001:1719: sgra yi gnas lugs khong chud nas //
NK130(tho)001:1720: sgra zhen spangs zhes gsungs pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1721: rdzun tshig 'di la dgos pa ci //
NK130(tho)001:1723: gtsug tor gdugs dkar la sogs sngags //
NK130(tho)001:1724: bod kyi skad du bsgyur ba'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:1725: khyed dang de dag mi mthun te //
NK130(tho)001:1726: sam skri ta yang ma dag la //
NK130(tho)001:1727: pra kri ta yi lus ma thob //
NK130(tho)001:1728: a ba b+h+ram sha dang yang 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:1729: koo la i ri ti lta bu //
NK130(tho)001:1731: rgya gar yul skad rnams kyang min //
NK130(tho)001:1732: pi sha tsir yang ga la 'grig /
NK130(tho)001:1733: gang phyir skad ris de dag la //
NK130(tho)001:1734: bod kyi skad dang bsres pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1735: rgya bod shan bsres sgros ma tshang //
NK130(tho)001:1736: 'phral la rang bzor byas par shes //
NK130(tho)001:1738: gdugs dkar gzungs sngags bod skad du //
NK130(tho)001:1739: gtsang mar bsgyur bas don ston na //
NK130(tho)001:1740: rgya skad bod skad bsres pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:1741: don mi ston pa'i rgyu mtshan ci //
NK130(tho)001:1742: rgya bod zhang zhung skad bsres pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1743: spu gri a li ma la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1744: pu tra ming sring sngags 'di yang //
NK130(tho)001:1745: sngon tshe legs sbyar skad du yod //
NK130(tho)001:1746: lo chen rin bzang bon po dang //
NK130(tho)001:1747: 'gras dus pu tra ma song bas //
NK130(tho)001:1748: sngags de zhang zhung skad dang bsres //
NK130(tho)001:1749: de yis ban bo brlag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1750: gtam brgyud pra tra'i yig char ltos //
NK130(tho)001:1751: sam skri ta yang ma dag na //
NK130(tho)001:1752: skad rigs gzhan dang ga la 'grig /
NK130(tho)001:1753: koo la i ri ti la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1754: re re tsam zhig ma gtogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1756: yul skad rdo rje'i glu ru blangs //
NK130(tho)001:1757: sngags kyi nus pa 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1759: mgo bo bcad dang gdags pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1760: phata ni rbad du bsgyur ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1761: rtog ge pa la ma grags pas //
NK130(tho)001:1762: smra ba tsam zhig bden rung yang //
NK130(tho)001:1763: ma mthong phyir na med pa min //
NK130(tho)001:1764: bod kyi skad dang ma bsres pas //
NK130(tho)001:1765: skad rigs bzhi'i lus thob na //
NK130(tho)001:1766: klu dang dri za la sogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1767: skad kyang skad rigs bzhir 'gyur te //
NK130(tho)001:1768: bod kyi skad dang ma bsres phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1769: rang sems gtan la ma phebs par //
NK130(tho)001:1770: log lam 'chol ba'i glag col gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1771: bskal pa brgya ru smras gyur kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1772: tshig gcig don dang mi ldan pa //
NK130(tho)001:1773: kye ma khyod ni ci zhig nangs //
NK130(tho)001:1775: gdod nas dag pa'i rnam grangs su //
NK130(tho)001:1776: ka dag mkhas pa'i sdeb sbyor min //
NK130(tho)001:1778: 'di ni dbyings nas dag pa'i don //
NK130(tho)001:1779: mkha' nas dag pa zhes bya ste //
NK130(tho)001:1781: brda rnying pa rnams ka dag zer //
NK130(tho)001:1782: don chen tshig gis mtshon pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1783: skyon gyi rnam pa gang yang med //
NK130(tho)001:1785: tshig kyang sbyor legs mi shes na //
NK130(tho)001:1786: thub pa'i dgongs don ji ltar shes //
NK130(tho)001:1788: rgyal ba'i dgongs don dpag dka' ba //
NK130(tho)001:1789: rtogs pa tshogs gnyis mthu las yin //
NK130(tho)001:1790: tshig gi sdeb sbyor mkhas shes pas //
NK130(tho)001:1791: rgyal ba'i dgongs don rtogs 'gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:1792: mu stegs pa yi pan+di tas //
NK130(tho)001:1793: thub pa'i dgongs don rtogs par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1795: ging pho ging mo zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:1796: mon yul la lar btsun pa'i ming //
NK130(tho)001:1797: lha la ging chen zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:1798: lo pan mkhas la 'di ma grags //
NK130(tho)001:1799: a tri sems pa nyid sang sad //
NK130(tho)001:1800: g.ya' spang skyes gcig gnam the'u dkar //
NK130(tho)001:1801: a phyi chen mo sham sham mo //
NK130(tho)001:1802: bskos rje brang dkar shan shan sne'u //
NK130(tho)001:1804: chos min ban yang 'dra la min //
NK130(tho)001:1805: dmu btsan the'u rang 'gong po gnyan //
NK130(tho)001:1806: 'phags pa'i yul na grags pa min //
NK130(tho)001:1807: sgra gcan la ni khyab 'jug sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1808: ming gi mngon brjod brgya stong nor //
NK130(tho)001:1809: 'di dag tshig gi nor ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:1810: gzhan yang mtha' las 'das pa nor //
NK130(tho)001:1812: lha la ging chen zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:1813: lo pan mkhas la ma grags na //
NK130(tho)001:1814: sngon gyi lha khang phal che bar //
NK130(tho)001:1815: khro bo kang king zhes pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:1816: rgya nag pa yi skad yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:1817: sgra zur nyams pas ging du grags //
NK130(tho)001:1818: a phyi sham sham la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1820: dpal mchog chos dbyings gsung dbang dang //
NK130(tho)001:1821: rdo rje gtsug tor gtsug dgu dang //
NK130(tho)001:1822: gnod sbyin shing ta la sogs su //
NK130(tho)001:1823: srid pa gsum na gnas pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1825: ngan song sbyong ba'i rgyud du yang //
NK130(tho)001:1827: gnod sbyin yi dwags 'dre rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:1828: klu dang klu yi rigs rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:1829: rgyal po bzhi po bri bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:1830: gza' dang skar ma rgyu skar dang //
NK130(tho)001:1831: khro bo ma rung 'tshe ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:1832: bgegs dang byi na ya ga dang //
NK130(tho)001:1833: sems can kun la phan byed pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1834: drang srong skal ba chen po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:1835: mkha' 'gro ma dang ro langs bri //
NK130(tho)001:1836: 'byung ba bzhi yi lha chen po //
NK130(tho)001:1837: khyim dang ri la gnas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1838: shing dang kun dga' nags la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:1839: dur khrod grong khyer gnas pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:1840: ming ngam barda'am yang na ni //
NK130(tho)001:1841: theg le rnams kyang bri bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:1843: sa bdag sngon po dag la bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1844: yi dwags phyi nang sgos khur can //
NK130(tho)001:1846: chu ltar g.yos dang nye 'thung dang //
NK130(tho)001:1847: gnas gnon spyi'u tshugs thur lta drug /'byung po gdon chen bco lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:1848: khro bo ma rungs 'tshe ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:1849: dmyal ba'i srung ma dag la bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1850: bud med ces pa rgan mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:1851: mkha' rag ma sogs bod yul na //
NK130(tho)001:1852: gnas pa bdun po bkod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1854: de yi phyi rol dmyal kun dang //
NK130(tho)001:1855: 'dod chags la sogs byol song bri //
NK130(tho)001:1856: zhes gsungs ngan song gsum po dang //
NK130(tho)001:1857: 'dod chags bya dang zhe sdang sbrul //
NK130(tho)001:1858: nga rgyal rtsang ba gti mug phag /
NK130(tho)001:1859: phrag dog rus sbal dag kyang bkod //
NK130(tho)001:1861: dmyal srung dkyil 'khor dag tu bkod //
NK130(tho)001:1862: de bzhin ri gi a ra lir //
NK130(tho)001:1863: dkyil 'khor du ni dmyal ba bkod //
NK130(tho)001:1864: dus 'khor sku dkyil gsung dkyil du //
NK130(tho)001:1865: 'dab mar gnas pa'i lha rnams ni //
NK130(tho)001:1866: phal cher 'byung po kho nar snang //
NK130(tho)001:1868: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje la //
NK130(tho)001:1869: klu la sogs pas bskor ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:1871: bka' gdams pa yi bstan ma ltar //
NK130(tho)001:1872: srid pa kun la khyab pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1873: lha 'dre rgya bod khyad par med //
NK130(tho)001:1875: bsgrig tu rung ba'i shes byed dang //
NK130(tho)001:1876: bod 'dre bsgrig tu mi rung ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:1877: rgyu mtshan yod na smra bar rigs //
NK130(tho)001:1878: dmu btsan the'u rang 'gong pa gnyan //
NK130(tho)001:1879: ming gi 'dogs lugs ma gtogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:1880: 'phags pa'i yul na med pa min //
NK130(tho)001:1882: las tshogs gzhung na yod mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1883: 'dir ni yi ge mang dogs bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:1884: rwa lo'i 'jigs byed phyag mtshan gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1885: las tshogs mdung la brten pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1886: gnam the'u dkar po zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:1888: zhes dang phyag mtshan bcu gsum pa //
NK130(tho)001:1889: thod tshal la ni brten pa la //
NK130(tho)001:1890: ma mo'i ma dang bdud la du //
NK130(tho)001:1891: btsan la tsa dang rgyal por ra //
NK130(tho)001:1892: klu la n+aa dang dam srir tri //
NK130(tho)001:1893: gshin rjer ya dang sa bdag sa //
NK130(tho)001:1894: de sogs rang rang sa bon ni //
NK130(tho)001:1895: ra khrag dag gis bri bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1896: gzhan yang gnod sbyin 'grog gnas ni //
NK130(tho)001:1897: grong dpon btsan du skyes pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1898: de yi kha dog nag po yang //
NK130(tho)001:1899: bdud btsan rigs su gtogs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:1900: mdung dmar can gyi bstod pa ru //
NK130(tho)001:1901: pan chen shu rang wa rma dang //
NK130(tho)001:1902: zangs dkar lo ts+aa gnyis ka yis //
NK130(tho)001:1903: mgon po dmag la chas tsa na //
NK130(tho)001:1904: btsan gyi rta pa chas pa 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:1905: de skad gsungs pa ma yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:1906: dmu ni grib gnon gdon yin la //
NK130(tho)001:1907: 'gong po rgyal po bye brag ste //
NK130(tho)001:1908: dbye na sde brgyad so sor yod //
NK130(tho)001:1909: lto 'phye chen po gnyan yin te //
NK130(tho)001:1910: rnam sras gzhung las bshad pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1911: bse rag sris rkun the'u rang yin //
NK130(tho)001:1912: spyir na lha srin sde brgyad po //
NK130(tho)001:1913: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rang mdangs yin //
NK130(tho)001:1914: rgya bod gnyis su ma zad pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:1915: yul khams kun tu khyad par med //
NK130(tho)001:1916: sgra gcan la ni khyab 'jug ces //
NK130(tho)001:1917: ming gi rnam grangs yin yod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:1918: tshangs pa khyab 'jug dbang phyug ces //
NK130(tho)001:1919: grags pa'i ya gyal de ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:1921: rgyal ba gsum ni dgongs pa'i brgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1922: rig 'dzin gsum ni brda yi brgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1923: gang zag ga sum ni snyan khung brgyud //
NK130(tho)001:1924: brgyud pa'i babs tshul de ltar smra //
NK130(tho)001:1925: lo rgyus khungs ma rnams su ni //
NK130(tho)001:1926: rgyal ba nyid kyis gsungs pa de //
NK130(tho)001:1927: sdud pa po yis nyan cing bsdus //
NK130(tho)001:1928: glegs bam la yang bkod par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:1930: rgyal bas gsungs shing bsdus pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:1931: glegs bam gsar rnying kun la yod //
NK130(tho)001:1932: gsum tshan bsdebs pa'i brgyud pa'i babs //
NK130(tho)001:1933: rnying ma'i gzhung na bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1934: 'di tsam zhig kyang mi go ba //
NK130(tho)001:1935: gnyid kyis 'thibs sam ci zhig nongs //
NK130(tho)001:1936: rgyal ba gsum yang ci la zer //
NK130(tho)001:1937: sku gsum yin na sku bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:1938: sku lnga sogs kyis der ma nges //
NK130(tho)001:1939: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rigs lnga /
NK130(tho)001:1940: sprul sku rdor sems sam rdo rje 'chang yin zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:1942: mngon byang gi sku la sogs pa'i sku lnga ni sangs rgyas gcig la'ang tshang /
NK130(tho)001:1943: chos skus longs sku la bshad /
NK130(tho)001:1944: longs sku sprul sku la bshad zer ba ni rnying ma'i gzhung na med /
NK130(tho)001:1945: kun bzang rigs lnga rdo rje 'chang //
NK130(tho)001:1946: de la zer na bdun du 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:1947: rgya bal kha che la sogs su //
NK130(tho)001:1949: des na rig 'dzin gsum de su //
NK130(tho)001:1950: snyan brgyud gang zag gsum yang ci //
NK130(tho)001:1951: gang zag snga phyi bsam las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:1952: gsum zhes 'dzin pa e ma mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:1953: 'di ni ston pa chos kyi sku //
NK130(tho)001:1954: nyid las mi gzhan sangs rgyas 'khor //
NK130(tho)001:1955: bstan pa tshig dang yi ge las //
NK130(tho)001:1956: 'das phyir rgyal ba dgongs brgyud zer //
NK130(tho)001:1957: rgyal ba'i zhal las ma gsungs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:1958: 'khor gyi sems dpa' rnams la ni //
NK130(tho)001:1959: shes rab rtog dpyod blo la snang //
NK130(tho)001:1960: zhes pa gsang chen rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:1961: 'di ni sangs rgyas kun la yod //
NK130(tho)001:1962: dbang rnon sngon nas goms stobs can //
NK130(tho)001:1963: brda tsam gyis ni grol ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:1965: gang zag dbang po 'bring man chad //
NK130(tho)001:1966: bla ma'i zhal las rtogs dgos pas //
NK130(tho)001:1967: gang zag snyan khung brgyud par bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:1968: de ltar phyogs tsam ma go yang //
NK130(tho)001:1969: gdon gyis btab pa ji bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:1971: yang khyed kyi theg pa rim dgu la //
NK130(tho)001:1973: kye yi rdo rje theg pa dman //
NK130(tho)001:1974: rdzogs pa chen po matho'o lo //
NK130(tho)001:1975: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba las //
NK130(tho)001:1976: theg pa rim dgu gsungs pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:1977: dpal ldan 'dus pa la brten cing //
NK130(tho)001:1978: de las mtho ba'ang bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:1979: ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum //
NK130(tho)001:1980: 'dus pa'i bskyed rdzogs nyams len gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1981: rim pa tsam gyis so sor phye //
NK130(tho)001:1982: rgyud sde so sor phye ba min //
NK130(tho)001:1984: gsang sngags gsar ma pa rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:1985: bla med gong na gzhan med pas //
NK130(tho)001:1986: ma h+aa a nu a ti yang //
NK130(tho)001:1987: bskyed rdzogs nyams len mtho dman gyi //
NK130(tho)001:1988: rim pas phye ba shin tu bden //
NK130(tho)001:1989: de ltar bshad la rjes yi rang //
NK130(tho)001:1990: 'on kyang man ngag lta phreng du //
NK130(tho)001:1991: theg pa rim dgu gsungs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:1992: de yang gsang 'dus la brten cing //
NK130(tho)001:1993: ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum //
NK130(tho)001:1994: de yi bskyed rdzogs mtho dman gyis //
NK130(tho)001:1995: phye ba yin na gsang 'dus ni //
NK130(tho)001:1996: a ti yo gar grub pas na //
NK130(tho)001:1997: theg pa rim dgu gsungs zer zhing //
NK130(tho)001:1998: rgyud sde so sor ma phye zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2001: a ti yo ga'i lta ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:2002: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK130(tho)001:2003: brjod bral brjod byar byas pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:2004: mkhas pa'i dgongs pa min shes bya //
NK130(tho)001:2005: des na thos pa'i lta ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:2006: dbu ma yan chad thams cad mthun //
NK130(tho)001:2007: de phyir lta ba'i lung sbyor kun //
NK130(tho)001:2008: pha rol phyin bzhin thams cad mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:2009: de rtogs pa yi thabs la ni //
NK130(tho)001:2010: theg pa'i rim pa yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2011: zhes pa'i legs bshad 'di longs shig /
NK130(tho)001:2012: spyir gyi yo ga gsum po de //
NK130(tho)001:2013: bskyed rdzogs rim pas phye ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:2014: rnying ma'i grub mtha' rtsod med yin //
NK130(tho)001:2015: rnying ma'i grub mtha' rnying ma'i lugs //
NK130(tho)001:2017: rgyud rgyal gsang 'dus sdom sogs las //
NK130(tho)001:2018: mtho ba'i rgyud sde ma bshad na //
NK130(tho)001:2019: pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis po las //
NK130(tho)001:2020: gnyis med rgyud sde mtho ba ru //
NK130(tho)001:2021: rgyud dang 'grel pa mkhan po bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:2022: gsar ma rang gis nyan bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:2023: de tsam zhig kyang ma go'am //
NK130(tho)001:2024: de bas rdzogs pa chen po mtho //
NK130(tho)001:2025: rtsol ba can dang rtsol med kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2026: rim pas gong 'og mtho dman byung //
NK130(tho)001:2027: slob dpon zhi ba lha yis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2028: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2029: gong ma gong ma rnams kyis gnod //
NK130(tho)001:2030: ces gsungs pa de dgongs par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:2032: sras dang bcas pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2033: gsung rab snying po theg pa'i mchog /
NK130(tho)001:2034: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud ces bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2035: de las mtho ba med par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2037: 'o na theg pa chung ngu yi //
NK130(tho)001:2038: mdo sde rnams su de dag las //
NK130(tho)001:2039: mtho ba'i theg pa ma gsungs pas //
NK130(tho)001:2040: theg pa chen po spong ngam ci //
NK130(tho)001:2041: chos 'khor thog ma bar pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2042: chos 'khor tha ma ma grags pas //
NK130(tho)001:2043: de yang tshad ma min zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:2044: rnal 'byor rgyud sde man chad du //
NK130(tho)001:2045: de bas mtho ba'i bla med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2046: yod pa nyid du ma gsungs pas //
NK130(tho)001:2049: slob dpon kun dga' snying po yang //
NK130(tho)001:2050: rnal 'byor rgyud las mtho ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:2051: rgyud sde med ces bzhed pas na //
NK130(tho)001:2052: des na khyed kyang bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2053: 'dzam bu'i gling du ma grags pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2054: rgyud sde 'og min stug po bkod //
NK130(tho)001:2056: spyir na sangs rgyas chos kyi tshul //
NK130(tho)001:2057: bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:2059: chung ngu'i blo yis mi gzhal 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:2061: 'di yi man ngag ji ltar bar //
NK130(tho)001:2062: gal te nyams su longs pa na //
NK130(tho)001:2064: khyod la khyad chos ci zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:2066: skye ba 'di las ches myur ba //
NK130(tho)001:2067: lo bdun zla ba bcu gcig gis //
NK130(tho)001:2068: phung po lhag med sangs rgyas pa //
NK130(tho)001:2069: dga' rab 'jam dpal sh+r+ai sing ha //
NK130(tho)001:2070: nyang ban lce btsun me long pa //
NK130(tho)001:2071: de sogs bod dang rgya gar gyi //
NK130(tho)001:2072: 'ja' lus grub pa de rnams ltos //
NK130(tho)001:2073: spyir na 'bras bu lam byed pa //
NK130(tho)001:2074: pha rgyud ma rgyud dag las byung //
NK130(tho)001:2075: 'on kyang gang zag rim gyis pas //
NK130(tho)001:2076: lam de nyams su longs dka' bar //
NK130(tho)001:2077: dgongs nas de thob bya ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2078: bskyed rdzogs lam gyis rgyud spyangs te //
NK130(tho)001:2079: da gzod de la sbyor bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2081: rtogs pa'i 'od gsal rtogs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2082: bsgom pa'i thabs kyis mi mthong bas //
NK130(tho)001:2083: rnam rtog bsgom pa las 'das pa //
NK130(tho)001:2084: phyag rgya chen po'i mi 'gyur bde //
NK130(tho)001:2085: zhes gsungs pa de khyad chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:2086: 'di don kho bos byas pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2087: lam rim thar pa'i sgo gcig ltos //
NK130(tho)001:2089: gal te thos pas grol zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:2090: 'o na sangs rgyas lta ci smos //
NK130(tho)001:2091: grub pa'i spyod pa'ang mi nus pa //
NK130(tho)001:2092: khyod la nyes pa ci zhig byung //
NK130(tho)001:2094: ma thos pa la ga la grol //
NK130(tho)001:2095: thos pa nyams su blangs pas grol //
NK130(tho)001:2096: de la'ang pha rol phyin pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2097: sngags kyi lam gyi nye ring bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:2098: 'di la yang ni yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2100: yi ge 'khor lo btags tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2101: skye 'di nyid la grol zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:2102: 'o na khyim phag bong bu dang //
NK130(tho)001:2103: khyod la thogs shig de nas blta //
NK130(tho)001:2104: gal te ring nas grol zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:2105: de 'dra mtshan nyid theg par yod //
NK130(tho)001:2106: sngags kyi khyad chos tsam yang min //
NK130(tho)001:2107: de phyir khyod kyi sgrub byed min //
NK130(tho)001:2109: 'o na gsang sngags gsar ma las //
NK130(tho)001:2111: jo bo'i grong khyer sgrol 'khor sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2112: btags pas grol bar gsungs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2113: 'khor lo khyi phag bong bu dang //
NK130(tho)001:2114: khyod la thogs shig blta zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:2115: rgyal ba'i gsung rab dri med la //
NK130(tho)001:2116: smyon pa'i tshig ltar mi brtsi ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:2117: thabs mkhas dmyal ba sgrub pa'i tshig /'di 'dra thos na rna ba dgab //
NK130(tho)001:2118: btags pas grol ba zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:2119: sangs rgyas da lta 'grub pa min //
NK130(tho)001:2120: rig pa dngos kyi rtags yod na //
NK130(tho)001:2122: zhes gsungs gzhan gyi don byed na /
NK130(tho)001:2124: mgul du btags te bsregs par bya //
NK130(tho)001:2125: mtshams med lnga po spyad pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:2126: nyan thos rnams dang skal ba mnyam //
NK130(tho)001:2128: so sor 'brang ma nas gsungs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2129: phan yon kyang ni de dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:2131: btags pas grol ba mi mkhyen na //
NK130(tho)001:2132: thams cad mkhyen par mi 'gyur lo //
NK130(tho)001:2133: 'o na mi gtsang zos pa'i rgyus //
NK130(tho)001:2134: grol ba zhig kyang mkhyen dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:2135: min na kun mkhyen min par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2136: 'dod na khyi phag bong bu dang //
NK130(tho)001:2137: mi gtsang khrod kyi srin bu rnams //
NK130(tho)001:2138: rgyu gzhan med kyang grol bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2140: rgyal ba thams cad mkhyen pa des //
NK130(tho)001:2141: rgyud kyi rgyal po gsang 'dus su //
NK130(tho)001:2142: zas su bshang gci zos nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:2143: sangs rgyas byang chub bla na med //
NK130(tho)001:2144: yang dag skyon med thob par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2145: zhes dang bshang gci'i dam tshig gis //
NK130(tho)001:2147: bdud rtsi lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:2148: zos na rdo rje gsum thob 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2149: zhes gsungs sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga //
NK130(tho)001:2150: bla med rgyud sde kun las basngagasa //
NK130(tho)001:2151: de phyir thams cad mkhyen pa des //
NK130(tho)001:2152: mi gtsang thos pas grol ba'ang mkhyen //
NK130(tho)001:2153: khyi phag srin bu la sogs la //
NK130(tho)001:2154: thabs kyis zin pa med pas na //
NK130(tho)001:2155: grol ba nyid du ga la 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2156: de dag mtshungs pa'i go skabs med //
NK130(tho)001:2157: spyir na mi gtsang phyi sa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2158: rgyal ba'i snying po gzungs dang sngags //
NK130(tho)001:2159: mnyam par blta ba'i log lta can //
NK130(tho)001:2160: bdud kyi sgyu mas bslus la ltos //
NK130(tho)001:2162: bris sam bcang ngam klog pas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2163: thar pa'i ring rgyur gyur pa yod //
NK130(tho)001:2164: btags pas tshe 'dir grol lo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2165: glen pa min pa su zhig smra //
NK130(tho)001:2168: cho ga bzhin du legs bris la //
NK130(tho)001:2169: lag pa'am mgul du btags pa na //
NK130(tho)001:2170: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin rlob cing //
NK130(tho)001:2171: de bzhin gshegs pa'i skur rig bya //
NK130(tho)001:2172: de skad gzungs las gsal bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2173: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2174: glen pa zhes ni ma brjod cig /
NK130(tho)001:2176: lta ba khyad par 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2177: rdzogs pa chen po mchog go lo //
NK130(tho)001:2178: sngags kyi khyad chos lta min //
NK130(tho)001:2179: dbu ma las lhag ga la yod //
NK130(tho)001:2181: sngags kyi khyad chos ltar yin pa'i lugs kyang yod de /
NK130(tho)001:2187: dam tshig gi khyad par dang /
NK130(tho)001:2191: zhes phar phyin theg pa las gsang sngags khyad par bdun gyis 'phags par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:2192: 'o na bram ze sa ra has //
NK130(tho)001:2193: dbu ma khas len med pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2194: gol zhes gsungs pa ma yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:2195: dam pa'i chos ni mngon par yang //
NK130(tho)001:2196: khas mi len pa'i lta ba zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2197: lta ba de la cung zad skyon //
NK130(tho)001:2198: 'dir ni gcig dang du bral sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2199: blo yis btags pa'i chos las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:2200: bzang ngan gnyis su ma grub pas //
NK130(tho)001:2201: spang bya thams cad lam du byed //
NK130(tho)001:2202: de ltar lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs //
NK130(tho)001:2203: lta ba nyid kyis byed pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:2204: lta ba khyad par 'phags par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2205: de bas lhag pa'i lta ba zhig /
NK130(tho)001:2206: yod pa nyid du 'dir mi bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:2209: phyag rgya chen po zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:2210: thabs kyis khyad par 'phags so zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2211: zab mo rgyud 'grel kun las byung //
NK130(tho)001:2213: phyag rgya che la rnam pa mang //
NK130(tho)001:2214: lha sku phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK130(tho)001:2215: thabs su 'dod pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2216: skabs 'di'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK130(tho)001:2217: zab mo stong nyid shes rab yin //
NK130(tho)001:2218: rdo rje gur gyi rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2219: gal te stong pa thabs yin na //
NK130(tho)001:2220: de tshe sangs rgyas nyid mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2221: rgyu la 'bras bu gzhan med phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2222: thabs ni stong pa nyid ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:2223: lta ba rnams las logs rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:2224: bdag tu lta ba 'dzin rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2225: bdag tu 'dzin pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2226: rgyal ba rnams kyi stong nyid bstan //
NK130(tho)001:2228: bde ba'i thabs kyis sdom pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:2229: thabs ni ston pa'i gzugs can no //
NK130(tho)001:2230: de skad gsungs pa ji ltar 'gog /
NK130(tho)001:2232: gzhan yang longs sku sprul sku'i bstan //
NK130(tho)001:2233: rdzogs chen chos skus gsungs so lo //
NK130(tho)001:2235: longs sprul bstan pa mi 'thad na //
NK130(tho)001:2236: khyab bdag rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK130(tho)001:2237: bde dgyes sh+aaka thub la sogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2238: gsungs pa'i rgyud rnams de dang de'i //
NK130(tho)001:2239: bstan pa min na ci zhig yin //
NK130(tho)001:2240: de dag gsung ba'i ston pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:2241: longs sprul min na su zhig yin //
NK130(tho)001:2242: dag pa chos dbyings zhing khams su //
NK130(tho)001:2243: zab cing rgya che sangs rgyas chos //
NK130(tho)001:2244: rtag pa rgyun gyi khor mor gnas //
NK130(tho)001:2245: 'di la chos sku'i bstan pa zer //
NK130(tho)001:2246: skyon du gdags rgyu ci zhig 'dug /
NK130(tho)001:2248: nges pa'i don du rgyud thams cad //
NK130(tho)001:2249: brjod du med phyir chos sku'i gsung //
NK130(tho)001:2250: drangs ba'i don du rdzogs chen yang //
NK130(tho)001:2251: chos sku nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu //
NK130(tho)001:2252: spros pa kun las grol ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2253: de yis su la ji ltar smra //
NK130(tho)001:2255: brjod du med pa tsam zhig na //
NK130(tho)001:2256: gal te chos sku'i gsung yin na //
NK130(tho)001:2257: lkugs pa rnams dang sa rdo sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2258: de dag kun kyang chos sku'i gsung //
NK130(tho)001:2259: yin te brjod du med pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2260: de yis su la ji ltar smra //
NK130(tho)001:2261: drang ba'i don du rgyud 'byung ba //
NK130(tho)001:2262: ngo bo'i gsung ni brjod 'das kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2263: rang bzhin gsung ni grags la stong //
NK130(tho)001:2264: thugs rje'i gsung ni yig 'brur gsal //
NK130(tho)001:2265: de phyir rang bzhin thugs rje yi //
NK130(tho)001:2266: gsung gi dbang las rgyud rnams byung //
NK130(tho)001:2268: chos sku gcig tu ma zad de //
NK130(tho)001:2269: sh+aakya thub pa sangs rgyas nas //
NK130(tho)001:2270: ji srid mya ngan 'das kyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:2271: gshegs dang bzhugs dang de bzhin gzims //
NK130(tho)001:2272: spyod lam dag ni thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:2273: mgon de rtag tu mnyam 'jog pas //
NK130(tho)001:2274: don du tshig gcig ma gsungs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2275: gdul bya'i sngon sbyangs las snang dang //
NK130(tho)001:2276: rgyal ba'i thugs rje tshogs pa las //
NK130(tho)001:2277: chos phung brgyad khri bzhi stong byung //
NK130(tho)001:2278: lha yi rnga bo che bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:2279: mi 'bad mi bsam rtog bral yang //
NK130(tho)001:2280: gang la gang gis 'dul ba'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:2281: yon tan mthu las 'byung ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:2282: sangs rgyas rnams kyi spyi lugs yin //
NK130(tho)001:2284: snang grags 'di kun chos kyi dbyings //
NK130(tho)001:2285: don dam bden pa nyid yin la //
NK130(tho)001:2286: don dam bden pa chos dbyings nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2287: kun rdzob 'di ru snang ngo lo //
NK130(tho)001:2288: de ltar ma shes 'khrul pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2291: snang grags chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK130(tho)001:2292: rtogs na chos kyi dbyings yin la //
NK130(tho)001:2293: chos dbyings yod pa ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2295: kun rdzob yin par mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:2296: snang stong gnyis med 'di shes shes //
NK130(tho)001:2297: goms na ci phyir grol mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2299: 'o na so skye thams cad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2300: chos dbyings mngon sum mthong bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2301: kun rdzob dang ni don dam gyi //
NK130(tho)001:2302: bden pa gnyis po gcig tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2304: kun rdzob mthong bas gro lo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2305: rnying ma'i gzhung na bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:2306: kun rdzob rang bzhin ma grub pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2307: bden pa mthong na grol bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2308: so skyes kun rdzob mthong ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2309: chos dbyings mthong zhes su zhig zer //
NK130(tho)001:2310: kun rdzob don dam gnyis med du //
NK130(tho)001:2311: shes tshe bden gnyis gcig tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2312: skyob pa 'phags ma chog klu sgrub kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2313: mya ngan 'das pa bden gcig po //
NK130(tho)001:2314: zhes gsungs pa yang 'di la dgongs //
NK130(tho)001:2316: 'du byed khams dang don dam mtshan nyid dag /
NK130(tho)001:2317: gcig dang tha dad bral ba'i mtshan nyid de //
NK130(tho)001:2318: gcig dang tha dad nyid du gang rtog pa //
NK130(tho)001:2319: de dag tshul min lta la zhugs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2321: lung 'di'i dgongs don gcig tha dad //
NK130(tho)001:2322: gnyis su 'dzin pa bkag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2323: gnyis su 'dzin pa nub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2324: don dam bden pa zer ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:2327: gal te chos dbyings de bzhin nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2328: kun rdzob bden pa 'di yin na //
NK130(tho)001:2329: chos dbyings mi rtag sdug bsngal can //
NK130(tho)001:2332: rgyud rgyal brtag pa gnyis pa las //
NK130(tho)001:2335: 'khor ba sbangs nas gzhan du ni //
NK130(tho)001:2336: mya ngan 'das pa yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:2337: zhes dang 'phags pa brgyad stong par //
NK130(tho)001:2338: gzugs ni sher phyin ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2339: gzugs las gud na'ang shes rab kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2340: pha rol phyin pa med ces gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2341: de phyir kun rdzob snang ba 'di //
NK130(tho)001:2342: dngos su chos dbyings ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2343: 'di las gud na chos kyi dbyings //
NK130(tho)001:2344: yod pa rgyal ba nyid mi bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:2346: rgyal bas chos kun stong nyid ces //
NK130(tho)001:2347: gsungs pa ngo bo nyid la dgongs //
NK130(tho)001:2348: khyed kyang de la dgongs zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:2349: min par khyed kyi gzhungs la gsal //
NK130(tho)001:2350: bi ma la yi snying thig las //
NK130(tho)001:2351: sems ni glo ba'i nang na gnas //
NK130(tho)001:2352: rig pa snying dang glo ba'i nang //
NK130(tho)001:2353: yungs 'bru tsam gyi lha sku lo //
NK130(tho)001:2356: sems dang rig pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:2357: gcig dang tha dad ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2358: rlung sems 'jug pa gcig pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2359: dgongs nas glo ba las rlung gi //
NK130(tho)001:2360: gnas su sems kyang gnas par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2361: rig pa snying la gnas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2362: sems ni glo bar gnas pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:2363: gal te 'thad pa ma yin na //
NK130(tho)001:2364: mig gi rnam par shes pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2365: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad po //
NK130(tho)001:2366: so sor gnas pa'ang mi rigs 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2367: rnam rtog ye shes tha dad phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2368: rnam rtog ma rig chen po des //
NK130(tho)001:2369: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2370: mi rtog ting 'dzin la gnas na //
NK130(tho)001:2371: mkha' ltar gsal zhes rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2372: rig pa ye shes ngo bo de //
NK130(tho)001:2373: snying la yang dag gnas pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:2374: rgyud kyi rgyal po sam+bu tir //
NK130(tho)001:2375: de nyid yul las 'das pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:2376: srog chags kun gyi snying la gnas //
NK130(tho)001:2377: zhes dang bram ze chen po yis //
NK130(tho)001:2378: mkhas rnams bstan bcos 'chad pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2379: lus la ye shes gnas pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:2380: ma rtogs zhes kyang ma gsungs sam //
NK130(tho)001:2381: yungs 'bru tsam gyi lha sku yang //
NK130(tho)001:2382: rgyud kyi rgyal po kha sbyor las //
NK130(tho)001:2383: ye shes lha yi ngo bo nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2384: yungs kar sbom po'i cha tsam dag /
NK130(tho)001:2385: de yi dbus na gnas pa'i lha //
NK130(tho)001:2386: mi gsal gsal ba'i bdag nyid can //
NK130(tho)001:2387: cha med mchog tu phra ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:2388: thig le gzugs can yid kyi dngos //
NK130(tho)001:2389: gzi brjid chen po'i 'od dang ldan //
NK130(tho)001:2390: rtag tu snying gi dbus na gnas //
NK130(tho)001:2391: zhes gsungs rgyud gzhan kun tu'ang gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2392: de kun mu stegs lugs zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:2394: kun byed rgyal po'i nyams len du //
NK130(tho)001:2395: rdo rje lus kyi byed bcing dang //
NK130(tho)001:2396: lus gnad lta stangs thams cad bkag /
NK130(tho)001:2397: spyod lam phal pas yid mgu zhing //
NK130(tho)001:2398: ma dag las snang 'di thams cad //
NK130(tho)001:2399: chos dbyings nyid du shes byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:2400: chos dbyings nyid la chos dbyings spyod //
NK130(tho)001:2401: de ltar goms pas gol sa chod //
NK130(tho)001:2402: skyon kun yon tan nyid 'gyur zhing //
NK130(tho)001:2404: sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur ro lo //
NK130(tho)001:2406: ma bcos sor gzhag phyag rgya che //
NK130(tho)001:2407: lus gnad lta stangs la sogs pas //
NK130(tho)001:2409: phyag rgya chen po gang+ga mar //
NK130(tho)001:2410: byas pa'i chos kyis sangs mi rgya //
NK130(tho)001:2411: bsgom pas sgom med don mi mthong //
NK130(tho)001:2412: de skad ti lo pa yis gsung //
NK130(tho)001:2414: do ha las kyang 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:2415: mi spang mi sgrub mi zhen la //
NK130(tho)001:2416: mi 'gog rang lugs ci bde bar //
NK130(tho)001:2417: spyod pa rab mchog dam pa'o gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2418: bla ma mtshal ba zhang chen pos //
NK130(tho)001:2419: chos rje de'u she ras pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2420: phyag rgya chen po mda' gzhu ma //
NK130(tho)001:2421: gsungs pa de yang dgongs par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:2422: ma dag las snang chos dbyings su //
NK130(tho)001:2423: shes na skyon rnams yon tan du //
NK130(tho)001:2424: 'gyur te kye yi rdo rje las //
NK130(tho)001:2425: dri mas dri ma 'khrud pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:2426: nyon mongs nyid kyis nyon mongs 'dag /
NK130(tho)001:2427: de skad gsungs pa dran par bya //
NK130(tho)001:2429: bar do gsang skor nyams len du //
NK130(tho)001:2430: rgya mtsho ar la gtad pa zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2431: mig gnyis btsir nas mun par blta //
NK130(tho)001:2432: dbang po bslad pa'i mthong snang bsrung //
NK130(tho)001:2433: bi ma la yi snying thig las //
NK130(tho)001:2434: nyi zla mar me'i 'od zer la //
NK130(tho)001:2435: zim bur blta ba'i rdzi ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:2437: nyi ma blta ba'i sgom pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:2438: mu stegs nyi ma pa yi lugs //
NK130(tho)001:2440: mig gnyis btsir nas mun pa ru //
NK130(tho)001:2442: rten 'brel lus la bsgrigs pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2444: gsang sngags nang pa'i khyad chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:2445: de yang brtag pa gnyis pa las //
NK130(tho)001:2446: longs spyod kyi ni rlabs gnyis la //
NK130(tho)001:2447: mthe bong dang ni srin lag gis //
NK130(tho)001:2448: de ni rnal 'byor pa yis btsir //
NK130(tho)001:2449: de las ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2450: zhes gsungs bsre 'pho'i btsan thabs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2451: nyams len btsan thabs skor rnams kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2453: ne tsos nyi ma brtol nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:2454: thar pa mchis par bshad pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2455: sprang bo nyi ma'i dngos grub kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2456: nyi ma bsgrub nas chos bsnubs mod //
NK130(tho)001:2457: de gnyis rjes 'jug mu stegs pa //
NK130(tho)001:2458: nyi mar blta ba'i tshul 'di nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2459: sgom pa ma yin spyod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2460: ri la mchongs dang nyi mar blta //
NK130(tho)001:2461: me lnga brten sogs spyod par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2464: dngos la blta ba thub pas bkag /
NK130(tho)001:2465: phyag rgya chen po'i gzhung lugs las //
NK130(tho)001:2466: snga dro phyi dro nyi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:2467: rgyab bstan nyin gung mig la gnod //
NK130(tho)001:2468: de phyir nyin gung spang zhes gdams //
NK130(tho)001:2469: gang zhig grangs can la sogs bden smra don //
NK130(tho)001:2470: de dag la ni kha zas dug tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2471: ri la mchongs dang nyi mar blta byed dang //
NK130(tho)001:2472: me lnga brten pa la sogs spang zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2474: sbyor ba yan lag drug pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:2475: snga rgongs nyi mar rgyab phyogs te //
NK130(tho)001:2476: nyin phyed spangs nas bsgom pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:2477: btags grol don khrid nyid du bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2478: nyi zla mar me blta ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:2480: thabs la mkhas pa'i khyad chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:2481: so sor sdud pa'i spogs chog tu //
NK130(tho)001:2482: chu dang nyi ma kham phor dang //
NK130(tho)001:2483: mun khang bug pa tshon rtsi can //
NK130(tho)001:2484: de dag blta zhing bsgom pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:2485: sbyor drug pa la grags dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:2487: rang gi rig pa gtad pa las //
NK130(tho)001:2488: bem po 'gul bar nus pa'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:2489: rang gi rig pa gtad pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2490: mi rabs sum stongs sangs rgya lo //
NK130(tho)001:2491: 'o na rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2492: da lta nyid du dgongs na yang //
NK130(tho)001:2493: mkha' mnyam mi yi 'gro ba kun //
NK130(tho)001:2494: sangs rgyas nyid du ces mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2496: chos nyid zad sar 'khyol ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:2497: rig pa gtad pas mi sum stong //
NK130(tho)001:2498: gdon mi za bar grol ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:2499: gsang sngags rten 'brel che bas yin //
NK130(tho)001:2500: rgyu mtshan gsung ngag lam 'bras las //
NK130(tho)001:2501: gang zag gcig ni sangs rgyas tshe //
NK130(tho)001:2502: nyams rtogs spor ba'i rig ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:2503: bar chad sel ba'i chos skyong dang //
NK130(tho)001:2504: dngos grub ster ba'i bla ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:2505: gsol ba 'debs pa'i slob ma bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:2506: lnga tshan gcig ni sangs rgya ste //
NK130(tho)001:2507: rgyud gnyis gcig car grol ba'i dus //
NK130(tho)001:2508: yin zhes bshad pas gsal ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:2509: 'di ni tshom bu gcig yin la //
NK130(tho)001:2510: de yang tshom bu nyung tha yin //
NK130(tho)001:2511: sngon tshe thabs chen gsang sngags 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:2512: lha klu mi yi 'jig rten du //
NK130(tho)001:2513: tshom bu 'bum phrag grol ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:2514: lha dbang brgya byin dang klu rgyal 'jog po'i khab
NK130(tho)001:2515: tu 'jam dpal dang spyan ras gzigs kyis gsang sngags
NK130(tho)001:2516: bshad pas lha klu'i tshom bu 'bum phrag bcas sangs
NK130(tho)001:2517: rgyas / mi yul du rgyal po dza'i gnas su gsang sngags pusta'i char babs /
NK130(tho)001:2518: tshom bu 'bum dang bcas te mngon sangs rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:2520: shes rab pha rol tu phyin pa tshul ba brgya lnga bcu pa'i 'grel ba las /
NK130(tho)001:2521: dbus su rgyal po nyid gtso bo'i skur sangs rgyas /
NK130(tho)001:2522: btsun mo bzhi yum bzhi'i sar /
NK130(tho)001:2523: sras dang sras mo blon 'khor rnams sems dpa' sems mar grol /
NK130(tho)001:2524: 'bangs rnams sgo skyong dang khor yug gi lha'i tshul du sangs rgyas te /
NK130(tho)001:2525: de ltar tshom bu mang tha la rtsa ba'i lha so bdun dang /
NK130(tho)001:2528: nyung tha yang lnga tshom du bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:2530: nyams len rgyud la skyes nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:2531: rnam par rtog pa gang skyes kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2532: nyams dang ro gcig myong ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:2533: rnam rtog spros pa sgom yin lo //
NK130(tho)001:2535: 'di ni dwags po bka' brgyud pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2536: chos skad yin te sgam po pas //
NK130(tho)001:2537: rnam rtog sgom du ma shar na //
NK130(tho)001:2539: sgom chen sgom gyis ma bcings na //
NK130(tho)001:2540: gzhan gyis 'ching bar mi nus gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2541: grub chen mi tra dzo ka'i kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2542: rnam rtog kho rang sgom yin gsung //
NK130(tho)001:2543: spyir yang bka' brgyud 'dzin no cog /
NK130(tho)001:2544: rnam rtog chos sku yin zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2545: de dag rnams dang gtam byos shig /
NK130(tho)001:2547: nyams myong de yis zin phan chad //
NK130(tho)001:2548: snang grags chos nyid du shes pas //
NK130(tho)001:2549: pha ma bla ma bsad gyur kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2550: sdig pa'i las ni mi srid de //
NK130(tho)001:2551: thar lam nyag gcig de yin no //
NK130(tho)001:2552: snang grags chos nyid yin snyam du //
NK130(tho)001:2553: nges shes rgyud la skyes ma thag /
NK130(tho)001:2554: de nas dge sdig gang byas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2555: sangs rgyas lam du 'gyur ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2556: mtshams med lnga po spyod bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:2557: sngags pas sangs rgyas nyid 'gyur te //
NK130(tho)001:2558: sbrul sgong khyung du mi 'gyur bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:2561: nyams myong de yis zin phyin chad //
NK130(tho)001:2562: snang grags chos nyid du shes pas //
NK130(tho)001:2563: pha ma bsad kyang sdig med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2564: snang grags chos nyid shes tsa na //
NK130(tho)001:2565: pha ma gsod pa mi srid de //
NK130(tho)001:2566: 'phags pa mtshams med byed pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:2567: nam yang srid pa ma yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2568: dam pa sangs rgyas la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:2569: sngon byon pan grub rnams kyis bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2570: des na dgongs te gsungs pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2571: rgyud kyi mtha' drug tshul bzhi la //
NK130(tho)001:2572: da dung thos bsam bya bar rigs //
NK130(tho)001:2574: sangs rgyas bstan pa thams cad dang //
NK130(tho)001:2575: khyad par rdo rje theg pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2576: zhugs kyang mi dge ma spangs na //
NK130(tho)001:2577: mnar med dmyal bar de 'gro zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2578: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis de gsungs phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2579: gal te sangs rgyas chos bden na //
NK130(tho)001:2580: rdzogs pa chen po'i spyod pa 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:2581: mtho ris tsam yang 'grub re kan //
NK130(tho)001:2583: 'o na tshig dbang rin po che'i //
NK130(tho)001:2584: dam tshig srog chags gsad par bya //
NK130(tho)001:2585: ma byin par yang khyod kyis longs //
NK130(tho)001:2586: rdzun dang 'dod la khyod kyis spyod //
NK130(tho)001:2587: zhes sogs dgongs te gsungs rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:2588: gdug pa can la byams pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:2589: rtsa ltung bcu par gsungs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2590: rgyud chen brtag pa gnyis pa las //
NK130(tho)001:2591: bstan la gnod par byed pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2592: bla ma sangs rgyas 'jig pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:2593: bla ma thub pa la zhus nas //
NK130(tho)001:2594: snying rjes gsad par bya ba nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2595: zhes dang gzhan yang rgyud rnams las //
NK130(tho)001:2596: dgug bskrad mnan dang gzir ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2597: rengs dang gsad pa'i las kun gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2598: gal te gcig pu bsad na ni //
NK130(tho)001:2599: mong po bde bar 'gyur ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:2600: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK130(tho)001:2601: gzhan du sdig can mchog yin no //
NK130(tho)001:2602: zhes sogs spyod pa de dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:2603: mtho ris 'grub re mna' skyel lam //
NK130(tho)001:2604: rgyud rnams kun kyang khyad gsod dam //
NK130(tho)001:2605: snying rjes sgrol bar gsungs snyam na //
NK130(tho)001:2606: srog gcod gang na sdig gzhan med //
NK130(tho)001:2607: 'on kyang sems nyid stong pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2608: gshis la dge sdig ma grub pas //
NK130(tho)001:2609: skye ba med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK130(tho)001:2610: dge dang sdig pas mi gos pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2611: lugs 'di sangs rgyas dgongs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2612: sems nyid rtogs pa'i gang zag des //
NK130(tho)001:2613: cis kyang mi dge spyod dgos zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2614: rnying ma'i rgyud gzhung gang na'ang med //
NK130(tho)001:2615: sgom po pa yi slob ma zhig /
NK130(tho)001:2616: chos gser rin gyis ja 'thungs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2617: sdig sbyong sgom po pa la zhus //
NK130(tho)001:2618: gser gyi sher snying bzhengs shis gsung //
NK130(tho)001:2619: de yis de ltar khas blangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:2620: gser shog tshol ba'i bar skabs der //
NK130(tho)001:2621: phyag chen bsgoms pas gnas lugs rtogs //
NK130(tho)001:2622: sems la ci yang ma grub pas //
NK130(tho)001:2623: sdig pa sbyang ba'i yul ma rnyed //
NK130(tho)001:2624: de skad sgam po pa la zhus //
NK130(tho)001:2625: de la mnyam med sgam po pas //
NK130(tho)001:2626: de ltar yin no legs zhes basngagasa //
NK130(tho)001:2627: gzu bor gnas pa'i blos brtags na //
NK130(tho)001:2628: phyag rdzogs 'di ltar dgongs pa mthun //
NK130(tho)001:2630: nyams myong ji ltar bzang ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:2631: sdig las nyes pa cher 'jigs pas //
NK130(tho)001:2632: gong ma'i dbang bskur thob rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2633: ltung ba sbyang bar dka' zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2636: shes bzhin gyi ni sgrib pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:2637: gzhan las lci ba nyid du gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2638: gong ma'i dbang bskur thob pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2639: sdig pa 'dag grogs mi byed la //
NK130(tho)001:2640: ltung ba lci ba'i grogs gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:2641: de 'dra'i dbang la dgos pa ci //
NK130(tho)001:2642: dbang don ma 'phrod dbang bskur ba //
NK130(tho)001:2643: thob par mkhas rnams mi bzhed la //
NK130(tho)001:2644: ngo 'phrod dus na dge sdig kun //
NK130(tho)001:2645: mkha' ltar rnam par dag pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2646: de la ltung bas gos 'di mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:2647: dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyis ni //
NK130(tho)001:2648: sdig pa 'dag par gsungs pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2649: de las mtho ba'i dbang thob pas //
NK130(tho)001:2651: mkhas pa rnams kyi bzhad gad gnas //
NK130(tho)001:2652: jo bo chen po rje yis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2653: gsang sngags ltung ba'i sgo mang yang //
NK130(tho)001:2654: rol brgya shal yug ji bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:2655: yig brgya lan cig bzlas pa'am //
NK130(tho)001:2656: yang dag 'jog la bzhag tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2657: de dag thams cad 'byang bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2658: 'di ni snga rabs bka' brgyud pa //
NK130(tho)001:2659: kha cig stong nyid sdig pa'i rtsir //
NK130(tho)001:2660: 'gyur bas stong nyid mi bsgom lo //
NK130(tho)001:2661: de la 'jam dbyags sa pan dang //
NK130(tho)001:2662: rig ral la sogs mkhas pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:2663: thub pa'i gsung las ji skad du //
NK130(tho)001:2665: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK130(tho)001:2666: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK130(tho)001:2667: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK130(tho)001:2669: de sogs lung dang rig pas bkag /
NK130(tho)001:2670: de phyir rgyas par smos ma dgos //
NK130(tho)001:2672: sangs rgyas gsung la ma 'dres par //
NK130(tho)001:2673: rang gi nyams myong dbang byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:2674: lta sgom spyod pa log gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:2675: rdzun rgyud rnams kyis sdig 'di ltos //
NK130(tho)001:2677: rgyal ba'i mdo rgyud thams cad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2678: lta ba lta ba log par snang //
NK130(tho)001:2680: bsam gtan lus kyi chos rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:2681: nang du yang dag 'jog la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2682: mdo rgyud rgya mtsho'i zab lam kun //
NK130(tho)001:2683: thams cad sgom pa log par snang //
NK130(tho)001:2685: gsung rab rgya mtshor gang bshad pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2686: blang dor spyod pa'i rnam bzhag rnams //
NK130(tho)001:2687: thams cad spyod pa log par snang //
NK130(tho)001:2689: khyed kyis bstan bcos 'di nyid du //
NK130(tho)001:2690: rdzogs pa chen po ches min dang //
NK130(tho)001:2691: bka' min sgrub pa'i shes byed du //
NK130(tho)001:2692: de ring rdzun rgyud rtsom na yang //
NK130(tho)001:2693: chos la brten phyir chos ltar 'bri //
NK130(tho)001:2694: lta sgom spyod pa gang shes 'god //
NK130(tho)001:2695: rdzun rgyud yin phyir bkar mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:2696: de skad khyed kyis ma bkod dam //
NK130(tho)001:2697: chos la brten phyir chos ltar bris //
NK130(tho)001:2698: lta sgom spyod pa gang shes bkod //
NK130(tho)001:2700: med na chos la brten pa 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:2701: lta sgom spyod pa ji ltar log /
NK130(tho)001:2702: chos la brten nas chos brtsams pas //
NK130(tho)001:2703: lta sgom spyod pa log 'gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:2704: rgya bod gnyis su dar ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:2705: bstan bcos kun kyang chos log 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2706: snying nas rdzogs chen smod smod nas //
NK130(tho)001:2707: rang tshig snga phyi'ang mi mtshungs pa //
NK130(tho)001:2708: skye ba 'phos pa'i mi bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:2709: gyur na yang dag bsam mno thongs //
NK130(tho)001:2712: chos dbyings rtogs pa'i gang zag la //
NK130(tho)001:2713: dge sdig blang dor ma mchis pas //
NK130(tho)001:2714: spyod pa de la dgongs so lo //
NK130(tho)001:2715: blang dor med pa spyod pa min //
NK130(tho)001:2716: de ni lta ba'i rnam bzhag yin //
NK130(tho)001:2717: spyod pa chos dbyings rtogs nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2718: sgom spang thams cad da gdod spong //
NK130(tho)001:2719: bsgom pas spang bar bya ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:2720: gnyen po thams cad da gdod sgrub //
NK130(tho)001:2721: 'di la sngags dang mtshan nyid kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2722: mdo rgyud thams cad dgongs pa mthun //
NK130(tho)001:2724: bsgom pas spang bar bya ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2725: gnyen po thams cad sgrub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2726: lus ngag bya ba mi 'jug pas //
NK130(tho)001:2727: de ni bsgom yin spyod pa min //
NK130(tho)001:2728: lta ba zhes bya'i ngo bo yang //
NK130(tho)001:2729: ci yang dmigs su med pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2730: spyod pa'i ming tsam ga la yod //
NK130(tho)001:2731: 'di la jo bo'i zhal nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2732: stong nyid rtogs pas grol 'gyur gyi //
NK130(tho)001:2733: bsgom pa lhag ma de don yin //
NK130(tho)001:2734: zhes gsungs lta ba bsgom pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2735: de la spyod pa'i tha snyad med //
NK130(tho)001:2736: don dam bden par ma grub kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2737: kun rdzob las 'bras mi bslu bas //
NK130(tho)001:2738: dge sdig blang dor byed pa de //
NK130(tho)001:2739: chos nyid ngang du ro snyams pa //
NK130(tho)001:2740: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa zer //
NK130(tho)001:2741: rje btsun grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2742: spyod pa nyams su len tsa na //
NK130(tho)001:2743: lta sgom nyams su myong ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:2744: snang ba'i dngos po rgyas btab nas //
NK130(tho)001:2745: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:2746: ces gsungs dam pa phyar chen pos //
NK130(tho)001:2747: ched du bcos pa'i spyod pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2748: zog po rnams kyi zas zong mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:2749: nged kyi spyod pa dgag sgrub bral //
NK130(tho)001:2750: zhes gsungs dgag sgrub bral ba de //
NK130(tho)001:2751: blang dor med pa nyid yin no //
NK130(tho)001:2753: khyod kyi rdo rje gsal ba kra sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2754: dam tshig gzhung dang mthun pa med //
NK130(tho)001:2755: gzhung las sbom po brgyad dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:2756: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi yan lag bcas //
NK130(tho)001:2758: de ni rgyud sde'i go rim gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2759: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi dam tshig dang //
NK130(tho)001:2760: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi mi mtshungs shing //
NK130(tho)001:2761: de bzhin rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:2762: sbob po brgyad pa ma mthun pas //
NK130(tho)001:2763: rje btsun grags pas 'khrul spong du //
NK130(tho)001:2764: sbom po brgyad pa'i rgya gzhung bkag /
NK130(tho)001:2765: bla ma so so'i bzhed tshul gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2766: gnang bkag du mar byung mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2767: rgyud sde gong 'og so so la //
NK130(tho)001:2768: so sor grags pa'i dam tshig kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2769: rgyud kyi dngos bstan su yis khegs //
NK130(tho)001:2770: sems ni nang du khug la sdod //
NK130(tho)001:2772: gsang sngags rdo rje thegs pa'i rgyud sde rnams //
NK130(tho)001:2773: 'jam dpal sku dang pad+ma gsung gi rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:2774: yang dag thugs dang che mchog yon tan dang //
NK130(tho)001:2775: phur pa phrin las ma mo rbod gtong rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:2776: 'jig rten mchod bstod dmod pa drag sngags te //
NK130(tho)001:2777: sgrub pa bka' brgyad zhes byar dbye ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2778: bde gshegs 'dus pa zhes byar bsdu ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:2781: sgrub pa bka' brgyad ces pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2783: nang tshan phur pa yan chad lnga //
NK130(tho)001:2784: rigs lnga khro bo'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK130(tho)001:2785: ma mo rbod gtong zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:2786: kun bzang che mchog he ru kas //
NK130(tho)001:2787: ye shes pa dang 'jig rten gyi //
NK130(tho)001:2788: ma mo mkha' 'gro bsdus pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:2789: don du bde mchog dang mtshungs te //
NK130(tho)001:2790: gnas yul so so'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK130(tho)001:2791: sgo mtshams ma sogs ming gis phye //
NK130(tho)001:2792: don du ma mo mkha' 'gror mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:2794: dkyil 'khor mchod stod drag sngags gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:2795: phyag na rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK130(tho)001:2797: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje la //
NK130(tho)001:2798: 'jigs byed lha klus bskor ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:2799: 'di la skyon du ma sems shig /
NK130(tho)001:2800: bka' brgyad ces byar dbye ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2801: bde gshegs 'dus par bsdu ba zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2803: bka' brgyad dang ni bde 'dus la //
NK130(tho)001:2804: khyad par yod pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:2805: 'byed par byed pa lde'u mig gi rgyud las //
NK130(tho)001:2806: gsang sngags rgyud sde mang po las //
NK130(tho)001:2807: bsdus pa sgrub pa bka' brgyad bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2810: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i rgyud rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:2811: brjod bya lha yi rigs dbye ba //
NK130(tho)001:2812: bya ba'i rgyud la rigs gsum ste //
NK130(tho)001:2813: rdo rje pad+ma de bzhin gshegs //
NK130(tho)001:2814: spyod dang rnal 'byor rgyud sde la //
NK130(tho)001:2815: las dang rin chen bsnan pas lnga //
NK130(tho)001:2816: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud sde ru //
NK130(tho)001:2817: khyab byed rdo rje 'chang dang drug /
NK130(tho)001:2818: thabs kyis mtho dman dbye ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2819: rgyud sde bdun drug lnga'am bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:2820: brjod pa'i tshul gyis dbye ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2821: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su 'dus //
NK130(tho)001:2823: bya ba'i rgyud kyi rigs gsum yang //
NK130(tho)001:2824: spyir btang rags pa tsam yin gyi //
NK130(tho)001:2825: rgyas pa'i rigs dang nor bu'i rigs //
NK130(tho)001:2826: 'khyams po'i rigs dang bcas pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2827: bya ba'i rgyud sde sgo drug yod //
NK130(tho)001:2828: rigs gsum kho na ma 'dzin par //
NK130(tho)001:2829: da dung blta rtog zhib tu 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:2830: spyir gyi bya rgyud rang rkang 'di //
NK130(tho)001:2831: rgyud sde gong mar sbyar mi rigs //
NK130(tho)001:2832: klu sgrub 'phags ma dpal mo yis //
NK130(tho)001:2833: bzang po ngan par bkral mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:2834: ngan pa bzang por rung ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:2835: bya rgyud nang gi bcu gcig zhal //
NK130(tho)001:2836: rnal 'byor cher bkral sgrub thabs mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:2837: rnal 'byor chen por rigs drug kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2838: ma nges rigs brgya la sog bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2839: de dag dbye bsdu yin zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:2840: 'o na gcig tu bsdus pas chog /
NK130(tho)001:2841: rdo rje 'chang las bye ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2842: de lta bas na phyogs re ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:2844: rnying ma rtsad nas 'gog bzhed na //
NK130(tho)001:2845: sdom pa gsum gyi rab dbye las //
NK130(tho)001:2846: pan chen dz+ny+aa na sh+r+ai dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:2847: mu stegs rtsod pa dper mdzad nas //
NK130(tho)001:2848: des na rang gi lung gis ni //
NK130(tho)001:2849: de nyid sum 'byin mi nus pas //
NK130(tho)001:2850: de tshe de yi lung gis ni //
NK130(tho)001:2851: de nyid sum dbyung zhes gsungs ltar //
NK130(tho)001:2852: rnying ma'i lung gis rnying ma nyid //
NK130(tho)001:2854: bla ma lce sogs rdzogs chen chos //
NK130(tho)001:2856: bla ma sro'i rdzogs chen rde'u skor bdun rnams su /
NK130(tho)001:2858: ra rog phad rog khyad med dang //
NK130(tho)001:2859: thugs rje chen po bsgom pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2860: gangs ri bsgom pa khyad med dang //
NK130(tho)001:2861: ma ni pad+me bgrang ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:2862: bod skad wong sgra 'dren pa gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:2863: khyad par med par smra ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2864: chos log mang po rnying mar bsres //
NK130(tho)001:2865: de kun sum 'byin mdzad rigs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2866: dam chos spong ba la rings nas //
NK130(tho)001:2867: de 'dra'i cha tsam ma thos par //
NK130(tho)001:2868: gzhan gyi nor rdzas 'phrog pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2869: rang gi nor ngoms byed pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:2870: gsang sngags rnying ma 'gog pa la //
NK130(tho)001:2871: gsar ma'i bshad yam 'dis ci phan //
NK130(tho)001:2872: ji ltar bon po 'gog pa na //
NK130(tho)001:2873: bon gyi lung gis de 'gog mod //
NK130(tho)001:2874: chos kyi lung dang bshad yam la //
NK130(tho)001:2875: bon pos tshad mar ga la 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:2876: 'on kyang khyed kyis don de'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2877: rnying ma'i gzhung lugs bltas mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2878: chos zab go ba'i skal med pas //
NK130(tho)001:2879: bka' brgyad bde 'dus dbye bsdu sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2880: rdza cag mang po byung snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:2882: khyed kyi thub pa'i dbye ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2883: 'gro drug thub pa drug yin lo //
NK130(tho)001:2884: 'o na thub pa gzhan lnga yis //
NK130(tho)001:2885: mdzad pa bcu gnyis gang du spyad //
NK130(tho)001:2886: chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor //
NK130(tho)001:2887: bstan pa gang yin de 'dzin su //
NK130(tho)001:2888: gal te de dag med na ni //
NK130(tho)001:2889: thub pa yin pa'i sgrub byed gang //
NK130(tho)001:2891: thub pa zhes bya'i sgrub byed kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2892: nyon mongs sdig kun thub pas nas //
NK130(tho)001:2893: thub pa zhes su mtshan brjod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:2894: 'grel pa dag las grags pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:2895: de ltar thub pa gzhan lnga yis //
NK130(tho)001:2896: 'gro ba lnga yi don mdzad tshul //
NK130(tho)001:2897: rang gi rigs dang bsam pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:2898: mthun pa'i tshul gyis 'dul ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:2899: bsod nams chen po'i sku yis 'dul //
NK130(tho)001:2900: theg pa sna tshogs gsung gis 'dul //
NK130(tho)001:2901: mngon shes chen po'i thugs kyis 'dul //
NK130(tho)001:2902: phrin las bsam mi khyab pas 'dul //
NK130(tho)001:2903: yon tan logs su ma smos te //
NK130(tho)001:2904: gong ma bzhi po kun la khyab //
NK130(tho)001:2905: 'di ltar rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK130(tho)001:2906: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis rlabs zhes bya ba /
NK130(tho)001:2907: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje las thon to //
NK130(tho)001:2908: thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis smrel zhi dang /
NK130(tho)001:2909: yas mas kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK130(tho)001:2910: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK130(tho)001:2911: de dag tu yang thub pa chen po bcom ldan
NK130(tho)001:2912: 'das re res 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK130(tho)001:2914: mdzad pa bcu gnyis ji ltar bstan //
NK130(tho)001:2915: zhes pa'ang mi'i 'gro ba 'dul ba la ni mdzad pa bcu gnyis bstan dgos kyang /
NK130(tho)001:2916: dud 'gro la sogs pa'i 'gro ba la ni mdzad pa bcu gnyis bstan kyang ji ltar go /
NK130(tho)001:2917: 'gro ba gzhan bzhi po'ang rigs dang bsam pa mi 'dra bas des thul bar mi 'gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:2920: bcu gnyis mdzad pas mi thul phyir //
NK130(tho)001:2923: sangs rgyas phal po che'i mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:2925: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa ni tshad med de /
NK130(tho)001:2926: 'gro ba gang la gang gis 'dul ba de dang
NK130(tho)001:2927: de'i gzugs dang 'khor dang ming gis de dang de'i
NK130(tho)001:2928: don mdzad do // zhes gsungs pa 'dis gsal ba yin no //
NK130(tho)001:2929: gzhan yang 'dus pa chen po'i mdor //
NK130(tho)001:2930: gang dag glang po ches 'dul ba //
NK130(tho)001:2931: sems can de dag thams cad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2932: de bzhin gshegs pa glang por mthong //
NK130(tho)001:2933: de bzhin stag dang seng ge dang //
NK130(tho)001:2934: gru dang zam pa la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:2935: de dang de yis 'dul ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:2936: gzugs su mthong zhes ma gsungs sam //
NK130(tho)001:2937: mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2938: gang gis srid pa ji srid bar //
NK130(tho)001:2939: 'gro la phan pa sna tshogs dag /
NK130(tho)001:2940: mnyam du mdzad pa'i sku de ni //
NK130(tho)001:2941: thub pa'i sprul sku rgyun mi chad //
NK130(tho)001:2942: ces gsungs brgya byin la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:2943: thub pa min na 'gro drug la //
NK130(tho)001:2944: phan pa sna tshogs mnyam mdzad pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:2945: thub pa'i sprul sku rgyun chad 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2946: rdo rje gur gyi rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:2947: gang du snang nas sems can don //
NK130(tho)001:2948: mdzad cing chang tshong ma sogs su //
NK130(tho)001:2949: snang nas 'gro don mdzad par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:2951: lha dang lha min dbang po sogs //
NK130(tho)001:2952: gang la gang dul de dang de'i //
NK130(tho)001:2953: gzugs kyis 'dul ba'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK130(tho)001:2954: thub pa'i go ni mi chod na //
NK130(tho)001:2955: ha cang thal ba nyid du 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2956: 'gro ba'i bsam pa dang bstun pas //
NK130(tho)001:2957: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2958: mdzad pa lnga brgyar bshad pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:2959: thub dbang dang ni byams pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2960: mdzad pa bcu gnyis mi 'dra ba //
NK130(tho)001:2961: mdo las gsungs pa'ang dgongs par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:2963: slob dpon pad+ma sangs rgyas las //
NK130(tho)001:2964: yon tan gsum gyis lhag go lo //
NK130(tho)001:2965: rdzogs sangs rgyas las lhag pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:2966: gang zag nam mkha'i khongs na med //
NK130(tho)001:2968: nam mkha' dri ma med pa'i mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:2970: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni sems can dag pa rnams la snang ba yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:2971: dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni yongs su snang zhing thar pa'i sa bon 'debs pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:2972: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams las dge ba'i bshes gnyen lhag par zungs shig /
NK130(tho)001:2974: bskal pa stong gi sangs rgyas las //
NK130(tho)001:2975: bla ma gnyan par shes bya ste //
NK130(tho)001:2976: ci phyir bskal pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK130(tho)001:2977: bla ma dag la brtan nas byung //
NK130(tho)001:2978: zhes dang sangs rgyas thams cad ni //
NK130(tho)001:2979: mchod las bla ma'i ba spu gcig /
NK130(tho)001:2980: mchod pa ches mchog 'phags pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:2981: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK130(tho)001:2982: bla ma'i ba spu nyag gcig lhag /
NK130(tho)001:2983: de sogs gsang ba 'dus par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:2984: 'on kyang sangs rgyas mngal du zhugs //
NK130(tho)001:2985: slob dpon pad+ma'i klong las byon //
NK130(tho)001:2986: thub dbang drang nges sna tshogs ston //
NK130(tho)001:2987: slob dpon gsang sngags kho na 'chad //
NK130(tho)001:2988: de bzhin gshegs pa mya ngan 'das //
NK130(tho)001:2989: slob dpon 'das grongs med par bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:2990: de ltar gsum gyis 'phags pa de //
NK130(tho)001:2992: don la bzang ngan yod pa min //
NK130(tho)001:2994: ru dra nag po 'dul ba la //
NK130(tho)001:2995: sangs rgyas thams cad bka' 'gros nas //
NK130(tho)001:2996: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa mngags //
NK130(tho)001:2997: bdud kyi stings pa'i tshig tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:2998: thub dbang zhum zhing skyengs par gyur //
NK130(tho)001:2999: mthu med rang gnas log go lo //
NK130(tho)001:3000: gang gis bdud sde ma thul ba //
NK130(tho)001:3001: de dag sangs rgyas ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:3002: sangs rgyas nyid kyis ma thul ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3003: bdud de 'jig rten gsum na med //
NK130(tho)001:3004: khro bor sprul nas btul ba kun //
NK130(tho)001:3005: sangs rgyas nyid kyis sprul pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3006: mdo sde rgya cher rol pa las //
NK130(tho)001:3007: sa yi lha mo dpang byas shing //
NK130(tho)001:3008: thub pa'i phyag ni brdab tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3009: bdud dpung byer zhing 'thor bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3010: de nyid bsdus sogs rgyud sde las //
NK130(tho)001:3011: thub dbang rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:3012: rdo rje 'dzin pa khros nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:3013: bdud sde thams cad bcom par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3014: dus kyi 'khor lo sdom pa he //
NK130(tho)001:3015: bla med khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3016: thub dbang khros nas bdud sde kun //
NK130(tho)001:3017: bcom zhing zhabs kyis bardzisa pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3018: rgyal ba'i che ba mi shes par //
NK130(tho)001:3019: thub dbang smad nas khro bo mchog /
NK130(tho)001:3020: de bas lhag pa gzhan 'dod pa //
NK130(tho)001:3021: rmongs pa min pas ga la nus //
NK130(tho)001:3023: ru dra byung ba'i dus tshod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3025: bstan pa'i bar du byung bas na //
NK130(tho)001:3026: thub dbang 'jig rten byon pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3027: dga' ldan gnas na bzhugs dus kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3028: lha sras dam pa tog dkar po //
NK130(tho)001:3029: de ni byang chub sems dpa' yin //
NK130(tho)001:3030: sangs rgyas rnams kyis mi thul ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3031: bdud ni yod pa ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3032: las dang so so'i smon lam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3033: 'on te byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK130(tho)001:3034: 'dul ba'i skabs kyang yod pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:3035: bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong gi bdud //
NK130(tho)001:3036: phyag na rdo rjes 'dul ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:3037: gdul bya dus la ma babs na //
NK130(tho)001:3038: snang tshul cir yang 'byung ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:3040: khyed kyis rnying ma'i lo rgyus kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3041: ma go bzhin du bsnyon pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:3042: ru dra'i dus der bcom ldan 'das //
NK130(tho)001:3043: dga' ldan gnas na bzhugs dus yin //
NK130(tho)001:3044: sangs rgyas kun gyis mdags pa la //
NK130(tho)001:3045: de dus thub dbang sangs ma rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:3046: sh+aakya thub pa'i ming yang med //
NK130(tho)001:3047: des na rnying ma'i lo rgyus 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:3048: ru dra dregs pas myos pa la //
NK130(tho)001:3049: rang gi chung ma dus mtshan mas //
NK130(tho)001:3050: khyod pas che ba 'jig rten na //
NK130(tho)001:3051: lang ka mgrin bcu la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:3052: mang ngo smras pas kho khros nas //
NK130(tho)001:3053: kun kyang dbang bsdus bran du byas //
NK130(tho)001:3054: yang ni rang gi chung ma des //
NK130(tho)001:3055: khyod pas che ba dga' ldan na //
NK130(tho)001:3056: dam pa tog dkar yod ces bsgrags //
NK130(tho)001:3057: ru dra khros nas dga' ldan phyin //
NK130(tho)001:3058: dam pa tog dkar phang par blangs //
NK130(tho)001:3059: khri las sa la phab ces bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3060: rang gi gdul bya ma yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:3061: rta phag gnyis kyis 'dul lo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3062: rgyal ba'i sras des der lung bstan //
NK130(tho)001:3063: de phyir ru dra 'dul ba la //
NK130(tho)001:3064: thub dbang mngags pa'i yul ma grub //
NK130(tho)001:3065: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo sde las //
NK130(tho)001:3066: thub dbang mya ngan 'das rjes su //
NK130(tho)001:3067: ru dra nag po byung bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3068: de na'ang thub dbang 'ong don med //
NK130(tho)001:3069: gal te thub pas ma thul ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3071: lo chen khu skyo myos gsum gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3072: rdo rje 'jigs byed lo rgyus su //
NK130(tho)001:3073: drag po 'jigs byed ces bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:3074: mi kun bsad nas de yis zos //
NK130(tho)001:3075: de rjes ma ga d+ha kong sha'i //
NK130(tho)001:3076: mi kun bsad nas za ba la //
NK130(tho)001:3077: thub dbang ser skyar bzhugs pas gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:3078: gan du byon nas chos bstan pas //
NK130(tho)001:3079: ma thul 'phags pas chos bstan pas //
NK130(tho)001:3080: de yis kyang ni ma thul bas //
NK130(tho)001:3081: khros te rta mgrin skur bstan pas //
NK130(tho)001:3082: nags su song la r+ts+wa zo lo //
NK130(tho)001:3083: de nas rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK130(tho)001:3084: nag por khros pas btul ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:3085: gur mgon bram ze mchog sred dang //
NK130(tho)001:3086: gyi ljag lo ts+aa'i lo rgyus las //
NK130(tho)001:3087: nag po chen po dbang phyug bus //
NK130(tho)001:3088: nang nub re bzhin mi brgya bsad //
NK130(tho)001:3089: 'jig rten brlag tu nye ba na //
NK130(tho)001:3090: ta mgrin rgyal pos 'dul bar byon //
NK130(tho)001:3091: khyod la de yi gnyer med ces //
NK130(tho)001:3092: nag pos khyur mid byas nas phyungs //
NK130(tho)001:3093: de sogs lo rgyus dag dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:3095: khyod kyi 'tshang rgya'i dus tshod la //
NK130(tho)001:3096: bskal pa gsum dang mi tshe bdun //
NK130(tho)001:3097: zla drug lo gcig zla drug cu //
NK130(tho)001:3098: rtsol pa byed pa'i theg pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3099: byar med ngo bo 'di bstan pas //
NK130(tho)001:3100: mi rtsol lhun grub bder gnas zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3101: sangs rgyas bstan pa thams cad dang //
NK130(tho)001:3102: khyad par phyag rgya chen po 'gog /
NK130(tho)001:3103: pha rol phyin pa'i ring lam la //
NK130(tho)001:3104: bskal pa grangs med gsum du gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3105: phyag rgya chen po'i nye lam la //
NK130(tho)001:3107: de dag thams cad sun phyung nas //
NK130(tho)001:3108: khyod kyi lam de ci 'dra zhig /
NK130(tho)001:3110: spyir ni gsang sngags nye lam yin //
NK130(tho)001:3111: bya ba'i rgyud kyi sangs rgyas las //
NK130(tho)001:3112: spyod pa'i rgyud kyi sangs rgyas myur //
NK130(tho)001:3113: de bas rnal 'byor rgyud lam nye //
NK130(tho)001:3114: de bas rnal 'byor bla med ni //
NK130(tho)001:3115: ches myur skye ba 'di la thob //
NK130(tho)001:3116: sam+pu ti yi rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3117: bskal pa bye ba grangs med pas //
NK130(tho)001:3118: ji srid sangs rgyas gang 'thob pa //
NK130(tho)001:3119: gang gi dam pa'i bde bas khyod //
NK130(tho)001:3121: mi tshe bdun nas sangs rgyas ba //
NK130(tho)001:3122: phyag rgya chen po'i myur lam min //
NK130(tho)001:3123: de ni dbang bskur thob tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3124: dam tshig nyams par ma gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:3125: skye ba bdun nas sangs rgya zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3126: gsang ba'i mdzod las 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:3127: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK130(tho)001:3128: skye dang skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3129: de yi skye ba bdun na ni //
NK130(tho)001:3130: ma bsgoms na yang sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3132: des na rgyud sde'i mtho dman gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3133: lam la nye ring yod pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:3134: kun byed rgyal po'i lung gi don //
NK130(tho)001:3135: mi rtsol lhun grub sangs rgyas pa //
NK130(tho)001:3136: rtogs dang grol ba dus mnyam yin //
NK130(tho)001:3138: skad cig gcig gis bye brag phyed //
NK130(tho)001:3139: skad cig gcig gi rdzogs sangs rgya //
NK130(tho)001:3140: zhes gsungs pa dang dgongs don gcig /
NK130(tho)001:3141: sems kyi de nyid gang rig pa //
NK130(tho)001:3142: grangs med gsum la ma ltos par //
NK130(tho)001:3143: skye ba phyi ma sangs rgya ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3144: tshul 'di phar phyin la yang yod //
NK130(tho)001:3145: dbu ma bzhi brgya pa las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3146: de nyid shes pas gal te 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:3147: mya ngan 'das pa ma thob kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3148: skye ba phyi ma 'bad med par //
NK130(tho)001:3149: nges par thob 'gyur las bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:3150: zhes gsungs phyir na phar phyin las //
NK130(tho)001:3151: mtho ba'i theg chen gsang sngags la //
NK130(tho)001:3152: skad cig grol ba cis mi 'grub //
NK130(tho)001:3153: grol kyang grol go mi chod na //
NK130(tho)001:3154: khyed kyi sangs rgyas de ci zhig /
NK130(tho)001:3156: khyod kyi ston pa kun tu bzang //
NK130(tho)001:3157: rdo rje 'chang las lhag go lo //
NK130(tho)001:3158: bla med rgyud las gsungs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3159: kun tu bzang po rgyal ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:3160: rdo rje 'chang chen nyid yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3161: zla ba grags pa de skad gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3162: rnal 'byor rgyud du bstan pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3163: kun bzang rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK130(tho)001:3164: de phyir khyod kyi khungs ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:3165: de dag don gyi nor ba bsdus //
NK130(tho)001:3167: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:3168: gdul bya yi ni snang ngo ru //
NK130(tho)001:3169: gtso dang 'khor gyi tshul bstan kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3170: don la thugs rgyud gcig tu nges //
NK130(tho)001:3171: nged kyi ston pa kun tu bzang //
NK130(tho)001:3172: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsungs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3173: rnam snang che dang mi mtshungs na //
NK130(tho)001:3174: mtshan brjod yo ga'i lugs bkral ba //
NK130(tho)001:3175: smri ti'i zhib mo rnam 'thag tu //
NK130(tho)001:3176: de nyid chos skur ma bshad dam //
NK130(tho)001:3177: 'di ni chos sku mdun rgyab med //
NK130(tho)001:3178: de phyir rnam snang kun tu zhal //
NK130(tho)001:3179: slob dpon pad+ma bi ma las //
NK130(tho)001:3181: bsam yas bzhugs pas khungs 'dis chog /
NK130(tho)001:3183: rdo rje theg pa'i khyad chos ni //
NK130(tho)001:3184: dbang dang rim pa gnyis su 'dus //
NK130(tho)001:3185: smin par byed pa dbang yin te //
NK130(tho)001:3186: grol bar byed pa bskyed rdzogs gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:3187: deng sang gsang sngags rnying ma ba //
NK130(tho)001:3188: so sor thar pa'i sdom med par //
NK130(tho)001:3189: dbang bskur len cing sngags par 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:3190: so thar zhus na lhung zhes zer //
NK130(tho)001:3191: dge slong dge tshul dge bsnyen te //
NK130(tho)001:3192: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnam pa gsum //
NK130(tho)001:3193: sngags pa gzhan ni mi srid ces //
NK130(tho)001:3194: kun tu bzang po de skad gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3196: khyed kyis gong 'og ma phyed pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3197: gtam 'di ches mang rgod re bro //
NK130(tho)001:3198: 'di yi dge slong dge tshul sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3199: so sor thar pa dang mi 'grig /
NK130(tho)001:3200: de yang rgyud las 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:3201: bum pa'i dbang ni gang thob pa //
NK130(tho)001:3202: dge bsnyen zhes byar bstan pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:3203: gsang dang shes rab ye shes che //
NK130(tho)001:3204: gang thob de ni dge tshul grags //
NK130(tho)001:3205: bzhi pa de bzhin dge slong ste //
NK130(tho)001:3206: gnas brtan rgan po skye rgu'i bdag /
NK130(tho)001:3207: zhes dang gsar ma'i gzhung 'ga' las //
NK130(tho)001:3208: rig 'dzin nang gi dge slong la //
