NK130(tho)001:3209: so thar gnas pa ma gsungs te //
NK130(tho)001:3210: zhes pa'i lung yang med dam ci //
NK130(tho)001:3211: so sor thar pa'i sdom med par //
NK130(tho)001:3212: dbang bskur len du mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:3213: rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au ti dang //
NK130(tho)001:3214: sras mo go ma de byi dang //
NK130(tho)001:3215: sham+b+ha la yi rigs ldan sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3216: kun la dbang rgyun med par thal //
NK130(tho)001:3219: so thar zhus na ltung zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:3220: rang nyid mthong ba chung ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:3221: rdzogs chen rdo la gser zhun las //
NK130(tho)001:3222: tshul khrims la sogs pha rol tu //
NK130(tho)001:3223: phyin lam rgya mtsho'i gzhir gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:3224: zhes gsungs bslab pa gsum char bstan //
NK130(tho)001:3225: so thar zhus na ltung ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3226: brjod kyang 'gal ba yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:3227: pha rol phyin pa sdud pa las //
NK130(tho)001:3228: bskal pa bye bar dge ba bcu //
NK130(tho)001:3229: spyad kyang dgra bcom rang rgyal 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:3230: tshul khrims skyon byung nyams pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3231: phas pham pas kyang lci zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3232: de bzhin gsar ma'i rgyud 'ga' las //
NK130(tho)001:3233: dmyal bar 'gro ba byang chub kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3234: gtan gyi gegs byed ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:3235: nyan thos dang ni rang sangs rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:3236: byang chub kyi ni gtan gyi gegs //
NK130(tho)001:3237: de skad gsungs pa ji ltar 'gog /
NK130(tho)001:3238: gzhan yang 'di yi dge slong sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3239: so sor thar bzhin min pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:3240: slob dpon bsod snyoms pa dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:3241: jo bo dpal ldan a ti shas //
NK130(tho)001:3242: gsang dbang shes rab ye shes gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:3243: tshangs par spyod la bkag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3244: rgyud rgyal sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las //
NK130(tho)001:3245: 'di la khrus dang sdom mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:3246: dka' thub dka' ba spyod mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:3247: dka' thub sdom pa med pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3248: bde ba dang ni dga' bas 'grub //
NK130(tho)001:3249: de skad gsungs pa ji ltar zlog /
NK130(tho)001:3251: khyod kyi dbang bskur cho ga la //
NK130(tho)001:3252: 'jig rten pa yi dbang rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:3253: rang bzo'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs dang //
NK130(tho)001:3254: dran rgu'i cho ga sna tshogs snang //
NK130(tho)001:3255: bod kyi yul 'dre'i dbang bskur la //
NK130(tho)001:3256: rgya gar cho ga gzhung mar 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:3258: 'jig rten pa yi dbang zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:3259: gsang sngags gsar ma'i rgyud gzhung du //
NK130(tho)001:3260: gsang ba spyi yi rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3261: phyag na rdo rje gzi byin gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3262: dkyil 'khor du ni dbang bskur ba //
NK130(tho)001:3263: de ni rdo rje'i rigs gcig gi //
NK130(tho)001:3265: ma mo gnod sbyin drag po yi //
NK130(tho)001:3266: dkyil 'khor gang dang ci bshad pa //
NK130(tho)001:3267: thams cad de dag kun kyang ni //
NK130(tho)001:3268: dgongs pa med par bri bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:3269: zhes dang dpal mchog dang po las //
NK130(tho)001:3270: zhi ba mdung dang sring mo bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:3271: ma mo brgyad dang ming po gsum //
NK130(tho)001:3272: mtshams bzhir gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:3273: kun kyang 'jig rten lha yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:3274: de phyir 'jig rten pa yi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3275: gsang sngags gsar mar shin tu mang //
NK130(tho)001:3276: rnying ma'i 'jig rten pa yi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3277: rgya gzhung yin min mdzad pa po //
NK130(tho)001:3278: slob dpon nyid kyis phyi ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:3279: yul dang gnas kyis phye ba min //
NK130(tho)001:3280: jo bo'i byang chub lam sgron yang //
NK130(tho)001:3281: bod du mdzad kyang rgya gzhung yin //
NK130(tho)001:3282: de phyir slob dpon pad+ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:3283: mdzad phyir rgya gzhung min pa 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:3285: gtor ma'i dbang bskur zhes bya dang //
NK130(tho)001:3286: de las dbang bzhi rdzogs par 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:3288: spros bcas la sogs ming yang gzhan //
NK130(tho)001:3289: rdul tshon bum pa bsnol ma sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3291: mda' dar me long rma bya shel //
NK130(tho)001:3292: lha sku bum sogs spros med /
NK130(tho)001:3296: srung skud me tog mig 'byed dang //
NK130(tho)001:3300: mched lcam rnam bzhi ston par byed //
NK130(tho)001:3301: mchog dbang bzhi pa bskur ba la //
NK130(tho)001:3303: kye skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob ma rnams nyon cig /
NK130(tho)001:3304: nam mkha'i dbyings na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin
NK130(tho)001:3305: po che la nyi zla gnyis shar nas 'dug pa
NK130(tho)001:3306: de mthong ngam / bar snang gi 'ja' tshon la
NK130(tho)001:3307: rlung gi zhag pas btab nas 'dug pa de mthong
NK130(tho)001:3308: de mthong ngam / ngam / 'byung ba lnga'i grong
NK130(tho)001:3309: khyer du rigs drug gi dmag gis bcom nas ri
NK130(tho)001:3310: rab kyi steng du song ba'i mi dang /
NK130(tho)001:3311: khams gsum gyi 'phrang la shel gyi mo pho btsan
NK130(tho)001:3312: du bzung ba des khams gsum skad cig bskor nas
NK130(tho)001:3313: rang khyim du gnyid du song ba de mthong ngam
NK130(tho)001:3315: spros bcas la sogs dbang bzhi la //
NK130(tho)001:3316: bum gsang shes rab bcu drug 'byed //
NK130(tho)001:3317: bde chen spyi blugs dbang bskur dang //
NK130(tho)001:3318: rgyas gdab tshangs pa'i dbang bskur dang //
NK130(tho)001:3319: chos gos dbang bzhi bcu drug tu 'byed par ma zad /
NK130(tho)001:3320: rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa'i don dbang bzhi nyi shur phye ba'ang yod la /
NK130(tho)001:3321: de dag mi 'thad na dus 'khor bas spros bcas byis pa 'jug pa'i dbang bdun /
NK130(tho)001:3322: 'jig rten pa'i dbang gong ma bzhi /
NK130(tho)001:3323: 'jig rten las 'das pa gong ma'i dbang /
NK130(tho)001:3324: bdag pa'i dbang sogs mang du gsungs pa'ang der 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:3325: lhung bzed mkhar gsil dbang bskur sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3326: khungs med bab col sna tshogs byed //
NK130(tho)001:3327: de bzhin gshegs gsungs rgyud sde bzhir //
NK130(tho)001:3328: bod kyi yul 'dra'i dbang bskur med //
NK130(tho)001:3329: gtor ma'i dbang bskur bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3331: ming yang bum dbang gsang dbang dang //
NK130(tho)001:3332: shes rab ye shes bzhi pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:3333: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud rnams su //
NK130(tho)001:3334: khyad chos dbang bzhi'i ming don mthun //
NK130(tho)001:3335: gsum la rdul tshon dkyil 'khor med //
NK130(tho)001:3336: phyi rol dbang rdzas gang yang med //
NK130(tho)001:3337: srung skud me tog la sogs med //
NK130(tho)001:3338: dbang bzhi bcu drug bskur ba'ang med //
NK130(tho)001:3339: lhung bzed mkhar gsil dbang bskur sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3340: so thar nang gi dbang rdzas med //
NK130(tho)001:3342: gsar ma'i rgyud sde bzhi po la //
NK130(tho)001:3343: bod kyi yul 'dre'i dbang bskur ba //
NK130(tho)001:3344: med kyang rgya 'dre'i dbang bskur mang //
NK130(tho)001:3345: rdo rje 'jigs byed las gshin dang //
NK130(tho)001:3346: lo chen rin chen bzang po yi //
NK130(tho)001:3347: bstan srung pu tra ming sring dang //
NK130(tho)001:3348: bla ma ba ri lo ts+aa ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3349: dbyu gu ma ning spun gsum dang //
NK130(tho)001:3351: de bzhin bod kyi lha 'dre yang //
NK130(tho)001:3352: rje btsun mi la'i tshe ring ma //
NK130(tho)001:3353: 'bri gung pa yi a phyi dang //
NK130(tho)001:3354: 'brug pa'i rdo rje g.yu sgron ma //
NK130(tho)001:3355: kun la rjes gnang bka' gtad mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:3356: ci phyir dbang du 'gro snyam na //
NK130(tho)001:3357: lha de sgrub la dbang ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3358: rgyal rigs spyi dbang bskur ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3359: rgyal rigs de la dbang ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:3361: dbang gi ming du byung tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3362: dbang min mdo las dbang thob pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3363: byang chub sems dpa' zhes gsungs la //
NK130(tho)001:3364: rgyal rigs spyi dbang bskur ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:3365: rnying ma'i dbang bskur phal che ba //
NK130(tho)001:3366: byin rlabs tsam las dbang bskur min //
NK130(tho)001:3367: ci phyir dbang bzhi ma rdzogs lo //
NK130(tho)001:3368: dbang gi ming du btags pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:3369: de la dbang zhes mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:3370: dbang gi ming du ma thogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:3371: de ni dbang zhes brjod mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:3372: dbang bzhi yongs su ma rdzogs pas //
NK130(tho)001:3373: dbang bskur thob par mi 'gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:3374: bya ba'i rgyud kyi dbang bskur la //
NK130(tho)001:3375: chu dang cod pan gnyis las med //
NK130(tho)001:3376: spyod pa'i rgyud las rdo dril ming //
NK130(tho)001:3377: rnal 'byor rgyud du slob dpon bsnan //
NK130(tho)001:3378: kun la dbang bzhi ma tshang bas //
NK130(tho)001:3379: de kun dbang min zhes zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:3380: dbang gi ngo bo 'khrud pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3381: byin gyis rlob pa sogs su bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3382: gsar ma'i gshin rje gshed dmar po'i //
NK130(tho)001:3384: dbang bzhi'i cho ga ji bzhin snang //
NK130(tho)001:3386: dkyil chog dag la ma ltos bar //
NK130(tho)001:3387: bla ma'i phyag gis reg tsam dang //
NK130(tho)001:3388: mdzub mo'i brda tsam rig pa las //
NK130(tho)001:3389: dbang thob byin gyis brlabs pas grol //
NK130(tho)001:3390: bum gsang la sogs bzhir nges pa //
NK130(tho)001:3391: gsang sngags gsar ma'i rang lugs yin //
NK130(tho)001:3392: 'dir ni rig pa rtsal gyi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3393: mkhas pa pan+di ta yi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3394: pusti glegs bam bka' yi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3395: ye shes lha yi dbang bzhir nges //
NK130(tho)001:3396: theg pa gong ma'i skabs thob kyis //
NK130(tho)001:3397: rig pa'i rtsal dbang bco brgyad sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3398: gsar mar med pa'i dbang bskur mang //
NK130(tho)001:3399: 'di kun khyed kyi spyod yul min //
NK130(tho)001:3400: de phyir bde bar gnyid byos shig /
NK130(tho)001:3401: gtor ma'i dbang bskur med ces pa //
NK130(tho)001:3402: ti pu ras chung nas brgyud pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3403: tshe dbang lha gcig bum gcig de //
NK130(tho)001:3404: 'od zer brgya pa la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:3405: tshe dpag med kyi rgyud nas phyung //
NK130(tho)001:3406: 'di ni gtor ma'i dbang yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:3407: tshe dbang de yang khyed 'gog gam //
NK130(tho)001:3408: 'di las dbang bzhi mi rdzogs zer //
NK130(tho)001:3409: dbang bzhi rdzogs la skabs thob gtso //
NK130(tho)001:3410: ma bskur ba la rdzogs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3411: bskur kyang mi rdzogs pa yang yod //
NK130(tho)001:3412: 'di ni bla ma'i dus thabs dang //
NK130(tho)001:3413: slob ma'i bsod nams dbang las yin //
NK130(tho)001:3414: skyo ston bsod nams bla ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:3415: ma gcig jo mo lab sgron la //
NK130(tho)001:3416: dbang bskur ye shes phebs pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:3417: ma gcig dbang gral de nas langs //
NK130(tho)001:3418: gyang dang rtsig pa phug nas bzhud //
NK130(tho)001:3419: dbang bzhi tshar rjes mi rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:3420: ma gcig dbang zab 'di ma thob //
NK130(tho)001:3421: skal ba bsod nams dman no zer //
NK130(tho)001:3422: bla mas tha snyad tshig gi dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3423: de ni khyed cag rnams kyis thob //
NK130(tho)001:3424: yang dag don gyi dbang mchog de //
NK130(tho)001:3425: ma gcig gis ni thob ces gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3426: de sogs gnas skabs du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:3427: dbang bzhi bcu drug bskur ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3428: rgyud sde so so'i dgongs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3429: bum dbang bzhi ru mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:3430: dus kyi 'khor lor bdun du phye //
NK130(tho)001:3431: de bzhin gsang dbang bzhir phye ste //
NK130(tho)001:3432: dpal ldan shes rab nu ma la yang dang por
NK130(tho)001:3433: reg pa gang yin bum pa'i dbang ni de nyid
NK130(tho)001:3434: do // zhes sogs rgyas par rgyud der gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3436: rnam par dbye ba mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:3437: tshig dbang rin po che nyid dang //
NK130(tho)001:3438: bdag po slob dpon che'i dbang bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3439: gsang ba shes rab ye shes sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3440: spros can min na ji skad du //
NK130(tho)001:3441: gang zhig shes rab kyi ni nu ma la reg
NK130(tho)001:3442: gzhan pa bdud rtsi myang dang 'khyud pa gang yin
NK130(tho)001:3443: pa / shes rab dang 'grogs byang chub sems ni
NK130(tho)001:3444: zhu ba dag las bzhi pa'i skad cig bdud rtsi
NK130(tho)001:3445: pa / rtogs pa gang / 'di dag thams cad
NK130(tho)001:3446: nges par 'jig rten pa ste mchog gi snying rje
NK130(tho)001:3447: yis ni lam gyi rgyu ru bstan /
NK130(tho)001:3448: rdul tshan bum pa bsnol ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:3449: rgyu mtshan med pa ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:3450: bum pas byang chub sems mtshon la //
NK130(tho)001:3451: bsnol bas thabs shes zung 'jug mtshan //
NK130(tho)001:3452: bshad tshul gzhan yang du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:3453: mda' gzhu gsar ma'i dbang la'ang 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:3454: mda' dar btags la skyon ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:3455: mkhar gsil la sogs dbang rdzas la //
NK130(tho)001:3456: skyon du 'dogs na gsar ma pas //
NK130(tho)001:3457: kha t+w+aam ga dang thod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3458: phog ma kham phor dbyug pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3459: rnal 'byor pa la mkho ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:3460: dbang rdzas du ma ma bshad dam //
NK130(tho)001:3461: dbyug pas dbang gi rdzas rung la //
NK130(tho)001:3462: mkhar gsil sogs kyis mi rung ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3463: shes byed rgyud na gsungs pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3464: shing rta dung dang me long sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3465: phyi rol dbang rdzas min nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:3466: srung skud me tog la sogs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3467: dkyil chog kun la ma grags sam //
NK130(tho)001:3468: gsum la rdul tshan med ces pa //
NK130(tho)001:3469: klu sgrub slob ma ma ting ki //
NK130(tho)001:3470: ti lo pa dang n+aa ro nas //
NK130(tho)001:3471: brgyud pa'i rim lnga gdan rdzogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3472: gong ma yi ni dbang gsum la //
NK130(tho)001:3474: thod pa chang gis bkang ba re //
NK130(tho)001:3475: rdul tshon chos 'byung re re dang //
NK130(tho)001:3476: ye shes dbab dang me tog dor //
NK130(tho)001:3477: 'di yi phyag len da lta'i bar //
NK130(tho)001:3478: mar pa'i brgyud 'dzin yongs la yod //
NK130(tho)001:3479: mthong ba rnam bzhi ston pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:3480: dbang po'i rim pa brtag phyir yin //
NK130(tho)001:3481: de la skyon du ci zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:3482: chos nyid rang sgra'i ngo sprod la //
NK130(tho)001:3483: 'o dod rol mo la sogs byed //
NK130(tho)001:3484: dbang mchog bzhi pa bskur ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:3486: rgyas gdab tshangs pa'i dbang la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3487: de las gzhan pa'i rnam grangs mang //
NK130(tho)001:3488: blo chung rnams kyi yul ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:3489: gzhan yang lhung bzed chos gos kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3492: rigs lnga'i sdom pa bzung ba'i skabs //
NK130(tho)001:3493: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3494: zhes sogs sdom bzung yin nam min //
NK130(tho)001:3495: min na de dag ji ltar yin //
NK130(tho)001:3496: yin na sdom pa bzung ba'i rjes //
NK130(tho)001:3497: chos gos lhung bzed mkhar gsil sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3498: gtad pa 'di la skyon ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:3499: 'on te sdom pa mi thob na //
NK130(tho)001:3500: sdom pa bzung ba don med 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3502: shing brag sa la khungs phyung bas //
NK130(tho)001:3503: dbang bskur thob par ma bshad de //
NK130(tho)001:3504: sangs rgyas thod pa'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:3505: rmongs pa gang zhig dbang med par //
NK130(tho)001:3506: bdag ni dbang bskur zhes smra ba //
NK130(tho)001:3507: ji srid sangs rgyas bzhugs kyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:3508: slob mar bcas te dmyal bar 'gro //
NK130(tho)001:3510: gter chos dbang rgyun med 'dod pa //
NK130(tho)001:3511: ti pu ras chung 'brug pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3512: ro snyoms skor drug las grags pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3513: bde mchog yab bka' yum bka' sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3514: lho brag mkhar chu'i gter yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:3515: dbang de bskur yang mi thob la //
NK130(tho)001:3516: 'gro mgon gtsang pa rgya ras nas //
NK130(tho)001:3517: mnyam med seng ge dgu tshar sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3518: dbang de bskur zhing zhu ba po //
NK130(tho)001:3519: kun kyang dmyal bar yod zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:3520: chos dang grub thob gong ma la //
NK130(tho)001:3521: thabs kyis skur pa mi gdab 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:3523: ma thob thob ces zer ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:3524: rang bzo'i rdzun gyi dbang bskur la //
NK130(tho)001:3525: dpon slob bsam pa dge mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3526: phan med nges par dmyal bar ltung //
NK130(tho)001:3528: yang dag pa yi dbang bskur rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3529: ma thob thob ces bskur ba na //
NK130(tho)001:3530: dmyal bar 'gro ba gsungs mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3531: rang bzos bsgrig pa'i rdzun dbang de //
NK130(tho)001:3532: sgrig pa pos kyang ma thob na //
NK130(tho)001:3533: zhu ba po yis ga la thob //
NK130(tho)001:3534: bskur thob med pa'i dbang bskur des //
NK130(tho)001:3535: dmyal bar 'gro ba gang nas bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3536: rang bzo rang gis byed bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:3537: rang bzo med pa'i chos la smod //
NK130(tho)001:3538: klad mda' 'phen pa ji lta ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3541: deng sang bzang por rloms pa 'ga' //
NK130(tho)001:3542: rang gis ma thob rdzun dbang bskur //
NK130(tho)001:3543: rdzun gyi dbang lung kho ra yug /
NK130(tho)001:3544: chos de bzhan la ma 'chad cig /
NK130(tho)001:3545: rdzun gyi dbang lung byed pa des //
NK130(tho)001:3546: rdzun med rnams la'ang yid mi ches //
NK130(tho)001:3547: rdzun dang rdzun min dbye dka' bas //
NK130(tho)001:3548: de yi chos brgyud ma 'dzin cig /
NK130(tho)001:3549: rdzogs chen la sogs rang bzo'i dbang //
NK130(tho)001:3550: sangs rgyas rnams kyis ma gsungs shing //
NK130(tho)001:3551: sngon nas brgyud pa med nges pas //
NK130(tho)001:3552: 'di dag dmyal ba'i dbang bskur yin //
NK130(tho)001:3554: rdzun gyi dbang lung khor yug na //
NK130(tho)001:3555: de la rdzun med ga la yod //
NK130(tho)001:3556: rdzun la rdzun du mi shes pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3557: khyed la nongs pa ci zhig byung //
NK130(tho)001:3558: rdzun dang rdzun min mi phyed par //
NK130(tho)001:3559: chos dang chos min 'byed pa mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:3560: rdzogs chen la sogs rnying ma ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3561: dbang la brgyud pa med nges na //
NK130(tho)001:3562: bstan pa'i bdag po sa skya pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3563: gdung rabs rim pa ji tsam zhig /
NK130(tho)001:3564: rnying ma'i grub thob kho na byon //
NK130(tho)001:3565: gdung rabs rnam thar ltos dang gsal //
NK130(tho)001:3566: gzhan yang rgyal ba karma pa //
NK130(tho)001:3567: kun mkhyen rang byung rdo rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:3568: mtshungs med g.yag sde pan chen gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:3569: khyed kyi bla ma ma yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:3571: pan chen bi ma la nas bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3572: bla ma de gnyis bar dag tu //
NK130(tho)001:3573: rdzogs chen snying thig la sogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3574: dbang lung brgyud pa bar ma chad //
NK130(tho)001:3575: grub pa thob pa sha stag byon //
NK130(tho)001:3576: rna ba bal gyis bkags sam ci //
NK130(tho)001:3578: khyod kyis bskyed pa'i rim pa la //
NK130(tho)001:3579: dag bya dag byed ma shes pas //
NK130(tho)001:3580: cho ga'i go rim ma tshang phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3581: sangs rgyas dgyes pa'i sgrub thabs med //
NK130(tho)001:3582: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:3583: rgyu yi rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3584: byang chub sems su zhu ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:3585: 'bras bu'i sku ru bzhengs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3586: lhums su bskyed dang spro ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:3587: skye mched byin gyis brlab pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3588: phra dang thig le'i rnal 'byor dang //
NK130(tho)001:3589: ril por 'dzin pa'i rim pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3590: mos pa lam du byed pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3591: rdzogs pa'i rim pa dag kyang med //
NK130(tho)001:3592: dkyil 'khor dang ni lha rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3593: dag pa bsgom pa'ang phal cher med //
NK130(tho)001:3594: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud sde las //
NK130(tho)001:3595: rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:3596: srid par skye ba sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3597: bskyed pa'i rim pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3598: sems can srid par skye 'dra ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3599: cha mthun rten 'brel zab mo yi //
NK130(tho)001:3600: cho ga'i rim pa ma 'khrul bas //
NK130(tho)001:3601: dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs par bstan //
NK130(tho)001:3602: phyi rol pa yang bskyed rim byed //
NK130(tho)001:3603: dag pa bsgom pa sangs rgyas chos //
NK130(tho)001:3604: sgrib kun spong zhing yon tan kun //
NK130(tho)001:3606: khyed kyi sgrub thabs phal che ba //
NK130(tho)001:3607: rang bzo'i lha dang sngags su snang //
NK130(tho)001:3608: dkyil 'khor sbyin sreg rang bzo mang //
NK130(tho)001:3609: mngon par rtogs pa dbyangs su gyer //
NK130(tho)001:3611: bskyed rim mngon byang lngas bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:3612: cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3613: 'di ni ma h+aa yo ga ru //
NK130(tho)001:3614: gtogs pa 'ga' na gsungs pa'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:3615: gzhan dag rgyu 'bras lhun grub tu //
NK130(tho)001:3617: kun dang mthun pa ga la dgos //
NK130(tho)001:3618: rang rang lugs bzhin byas na 'grub //
NK130(tho)001:3619: theg pa gong mar khas blangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:3620: 'og ma rnams dang mthun dgos na //
NK130(tho)001:3622: yo ga'i grub mtha' khar bton nas //
NK130(tho)001:3623: rnal 'byor bla med rgyud sde la //
NK130(tho)001:3624: de 'dra med ces rgal pa na //
NK130(tho)001:3625: de yis bla med ci la nyams //
NK130(tho)001:3626: snod bcud ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3627: dag pa bsgom pa 'dir mi bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:3628: skye srid sbyong phyir skye ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:3629: mthun pa'i bskyed rim zab yod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3630: gdod nas lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:3631: grub par shes pa'i bskyed rim de //
NK130(tho)001:3632: bskyed chog kun gyi yang rtse yin //
NK130(tho)001:3633: gsang 'dus 'grel ba sgron gsal du sngags pa mtha'
NK130(tho)001:3634: drug gi bshad pa la rgyab kyis phyogs pa rnams
NK130(tho)001:3635: sgra ji bzhin par bstan pa'i 'don pa la brten
NK130(tho)001:3636: nas / rang gi slob dpon gyi man ngag gis /
NK130(tho)001:3637: mngon par byang chub pa lnga'i rim pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:3638: zla ba dang rdo rje'i rim pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:3639: srid pa 'byung ba'i rim gyis brtags pa'i lha'i rnal 'byor la goms par byed mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:3640: yongs su dag pa'i lha'i rnal 'byor ni rtog pa thams cad las 'das pa /
NK130(tho)001:3641: so sor rang gis rig pa /
NK130(tho)001:3642: sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul du gyur la /
NK130(tho)001:3643: phung po rin chen za ma tog gi nang du chud pa /
NK130(tho)001:3644: yod pa dang med pa'i phyogs dang bral ba yi
NK130(tho)001:3645: ge'i rjes su 'brang ba dang rtog ge ba rnams
NK130(tho)001:3647: bla ma'i man ngag 'ba' zhig las khong du chud par bya ba zhig ste /
NK130(tho)001:3649: slob dpon rdo rje dril bu pas //
NK130(tho)001:3650: sems can bardzusa te skye ba ltar //
NK130(tho)001:3651: sa bon med par bskyed par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3652: skye mched ye nas lhar gnas pa //
NK130(tho)001:3653: slar yang byin brlab 'dir mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:3655: dgongs nas phra thig lha khrid sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3656: zab la rgya che 'dir bshad kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3657: de tsam zhig gis mtshon phyir bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:3658: mngon rtogs dbyangs su gyer pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:3659: dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgras //
NK130(tho)001:3660: rgyal kun yon tan rab brjod cing //
NK130(tho)001:3661: bde gshegs thams cad bstod do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3662: phar phyin mdo sde rnams su'ang gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3663: ci phyir sngags la 'di mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:3664: sngags pa rab la shar ba lnga //
NK130(tho)001:3665: 'bring la gsal pa rnam pa lnga //
NK130(tho)001:3666: tha mas bzung ba lngar bshad pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3667: phrin las gyer la bsgom med bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3668: sngags pa rab la shar ba rnam pa lnga //
NK130(tho)001:3669: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas shar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3670: lam gyi ye shes bgrod du med par shes //
NK130(tho)001:3671: snang srid snod bcud dkyil 'khor lhar shar bas //
NK130(tho)001:3672: 'bras bu ye shes lhun grub rdzogs par shes //
NK130(tho)001:3673: sdug bsngal thams cad bde bar shar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3674: snang ba sna tshogs lam du khyer ba shes //
NK130(tho)001:3675: nyon mongs thams cad ye shes shar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3676: rang byung ye shes rang la gnas pa shes //
NK130(tho)001:3677: rnam par rtog pa ye shes shar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3678: 'bras bu sangs rgyas rang las brnyes pa shes //
NK130(tho)001:3679: sngags pa 'bring la gsar ba rnam pa lnga //
NK130(tho)001:3680: stong gsum lha yi gzhal yas khang du gsal //
NK130(tho)001:3681: gzhal yas khang la yang dog med pa'i gnad //
NK130(tho)001:3682: rang lus phung khams lha ru gsal ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3683: bar chad gdon bgegs kun gyis mi tshugs gnad //
NK130(tho)001:3684: phyi snod 'jig rten gtor snod gsal ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3685: gtor ma'i snod la bzang ngan med pa'i gnad //
NK130(tho)001:3686: snang srid snod bcud dam rdzas gsal ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3687: dan can rnams kyis 'khu ldog mi yong gnad //
NK130(tho)001:3688: gnas lugs stong pa nyid du gsal ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3689: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba yi gnad //
NK130(tho)001:3690: sngags pa tha mas bzung ba rnam pa lnga //
NK130(tho)001:3691: lha la rtag brtan ther zug bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3692: phrin las gyer la sgom med bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3693: sngags dang snying po rang rgyud bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3694: rdzas dang gtor chung bshos bur bzung //
NK130(tho)001:3698: de phyir gyer bsgom dbyangs ldan pa //
NK130(tho)001:3699: sngags pa rab 'bring spyod yul yin //
NK130(tho)001:3700: de las gzhan du bstan pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3702: khyed kyis gsang sngags rnying ma 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:3703: tshig mtha' tsam yang ma chod na //
NK130(tho)001:3704: don gyi gting mtha' ga la dpog /
NK130(tho)001:3705: de tsam gyis ni chog phyir bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:3707: rta mgrin pad+ma dbang chen gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3708: ye shes khro bo brgyad po yi //
NK130(tho)001:3709: khog pa dmar por phral nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3710: sgal tshig 'joms shing bardzisa pa byas //
NK130(tho)001:3711: rgyud chen dngos grub brtan gzigs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:3712: le'u sum cu rtsa gnyis par //
NK130(tho)001:3713: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo yis //
NK130(tho)001:3714: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' mnan //
NK130(tho)001:3715: khram kha stong gi dbang mo ches //
NK130(tho)001:3716: sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad bardzisa //
NK130(tho)001:3717: ri rab gling bzhi'i dbang mo chos //
NK130(tho)001:3718: rgyal ba rin chen 'byung ldan bsgyel //
NK130(tho)001:3719: rgya mtsho'i gling gi dbang mo ches //
NK130(tho)001:3720: snang ba mtha' yas gdan du byas //
NK130(tho)001:3721: sa gzhi 'debs pa'i dbang mo ches //
NK130(tho)001:3722: don grub zhon pa sgoms shig lo //
NK130(tho)001:3724: 'di yi rgyud ni ma mthong yang //
NK130(tho)001:3725: rgyud ni mtha' drug tshul bzhi yis //
NK130(tho)001:3726: bcings phyir tshig la brton na 'khrul //
NK130(tho)001:3727: sbyor sgrol la sogs sgra ji bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:3728: min pa nyid du khas len na //
NK130(tho)001:3729: 'di dag sgra ni ji bzhin par //
NK130(tho)001:3730: mkhas pa su zhig khas len byed //
NK130(tho)001:3731: des na lha mo de lnga pos //
NK130(tho)001:3733: sangs rgyas bardzi bar ga la nus //
NK130(tho)001:3734: don gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3735: khams lnga dag pa'i lha mo lngas //
NK130(tho)001:3736: gzugs sogs phung po lngar 'dzin pa //
NK130(tho)001:3738: gur las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:3739: sangs rgyas dngos grub 'dod pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:3740: stobs kyis sangs rgyas phur bus gdab //
NK130(tho)001:3741: gal te dngos grub mi ster na //
NK130(tho)001:3742: rdo rje sems dpa' bsad par bya //
NK130(tho)001:3743: thub pa rnam par snang mdzad rmongs //
NK130(tho)001:3744: rdo rje sems dpa' zhe sdang che //
NK130(tho)001:3746: don yod skyon ni thams cad byed //
NK130(tho)001:3747: 'dren pa lnga ni skyon ldan no //
NK130(tho)001:3749: de sogs gsar ma'i mdo rgyud du //
NK130(tho)001:3751: brtags pa gnyis pa'i rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3752: lte bar gtum mo sbar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:3753: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga bsregs nas //
NK130(tho)001:3754: spyan ma mig la sogs pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:3755: bsregs pas ri bong can ham 'dzag /
NK130(tho)001:3756: ces gsungs dus 'khor rtsa rgyud du //
NK130(tho)001:3757: sangs rgyas lha mo bcu bsad nas //
NK130(tho)001:3758: zhes dang gsang ba 'dus pa las //
NK130(tho)001:3759: rdo rje mi bskyod rab bsgoms nas //
NK130(tho)001:3760: lag tu rdo rje bsgom par bya //
NK130(tho)001:3762: 'od zer sna lngas rab tu gang //
NK130(tho)001:3763: dus gsum pa yi sangs rgyas rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3764: bsgoms nas rdo rjes phye mar brlag /
NK130(tho)001:3765: sku gsung thugs kyi longs spyod tshogs //
NK130(tho)001:3766: rdo rjes phye mar brlag 'gyur ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:3767: bsam gtan mchog de bsgom na ni //
NK130(tho)001:3768: thugs kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3769: rdo rje gsang ba 'di lta bu //
NK130(tho)001:3770: sems can thams cad bsad na ni //
NK130(tho)001:3771: mi bskyod sangs rgyas zhing dag tu //
NK130(tho)001:3772: rgyal ba'i sras su skye bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3773: zhes gsungs mdo sde dag las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3774: pha dang ma ni gsad bya zhing //
NK130(tho)001:3775: rgyal po yul 'khor bcas bcom na //
NK130(tho)001:3776: mi de dag par 'gyur ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:3777: zhes sogs dgongs pa'i skad mtha' yas //
NK130(tho)001:3779: gu ru'i thugs sgrub gsang 'dus su //
NK130(tho)001:3780: bsnyen dus bla ma spyi bor bsgom //
NK130(tho)001:3781: de la skyon yod ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3782: sgrub dus bla mar rang bsgom nas //
NK130(tho)001:3784: khro bo'i dbang phyug rta mgrin bsgoms //
NK130(tho)001:3787: sgrub dus bla mar rang bsgoms kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3789: rta mgrin bsgom par bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3790: glegs bam chung ngu 'di tsam gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3791: le'u gcig kyang ma nges bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:3792: gsang sngags rgyud sde rgya mtsho la //
NK130(tho)001:3793: rgol bar byed pa'i blo stobs can //
NK130(tho)001:3794: rlung dang chu sel 'khrug pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:3795: srog rtsa bus par ma gyur tam //
NK130(tho)001:3797: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3798: rdo rje phag mo'i zhabs 'og tu //
NK130(tho)001:3799: theg brgyad zil gyis mnan pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3800: sh+aaka thub gdan khrir sgoms shig lo //
NK130(tho)001:3801: kye ma blun po snying kham can //
NK130(tho)001:3802: thub pa'i bstan pa 'di ltar dkrug /
NK130(tho)001:3804: rdo rje phag mo'i gdan khri la //
NK130(tho)001:3805: thub pa'i dbang po bzhag pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:3806: rnying ma'i chos 'dir ma mthong yang //
NK130(tho)001:3807: yod kyang skyon yod ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:3808: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gdan khri dag /'degs pa'i seng ge rta glang sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3809: byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3810: dag snang ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK130(tho)001:3811: de dag rnams dang sangs rgyas mnyam //
NK130(tho)001:3814: dag snang ye shes dkyil 'khor nyams //
NK130(tho)001:3816: rigs bdag dbu la 'jog pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:3818: don du 'dra ba ma yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:3819: de skad brjod na ji ltar smra //
NK130(tho)001:3821: sangs rgyas 'dra ba'i ston pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3822: khyed la ci zhig byung nas gnon //
NK130(tho)001:3823: gru chen gnyan pa de spangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:3824: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho ji ltar brgal //
NK130(tho)001:3825: mig gcig nyi ma de bor nas //
NK130(tho)001:3826: thar pa'i lam bzang ji ltar bgrod //
NK130(tho)001:3827: bstan la sdang ba bdud kyi bu //
NK130(tho)001:3828: mu stegs ngan pa chos ltar bcos //
NK130(tho)001:3829: mi zad lta ba ngan par lhung //
NK130(tho)001:3830: 'gro ba bslu ba'i g.yo sgyu can //
NK130(tho)001:3831: sdig can khyod kyi rkang 'og tu //
NK130(tho)001:3832: sangs rgyas bardzisa pa'i log lta 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:3833: nam mkha' med par gyur na yang //
NK130(tho)001:3834: rdo rje'i dmyal las thar par dka' //
NK130(tho)001:3837: shog dril ha la skor gsum du //
NK130(tho)001:3838: bdag nyid gnod mdzes bsgoms nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:3839: rdo rje 'jigs byed dgug cing bstim //
NK130(tho)001:3840: drag po'i shugs kyis gzugs de nyid //
NK130(tho)001:3841: gtub cing bsgral ba'i las byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:3842: 'khor tshogs las kyi gshin rje rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3843: skrag nas las myur byed par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3844: dus kyi 'khor lo'i mngon rtogs las //
NK130(tho)001:3845: rdo rje'i shugs kyis dus 'khor lo'i //
NK130(tho)001:3846: snying gar lcags kyus btab nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:3847: zhags pas bcings te sgrog gis bsdams //
NK130(tho)001:3848: dril bus gzugs la dbabs nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:3849: dam tshig ye shes bsre bar byas //
NK130(tho)001:3850: de kun sdig las yin nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:3851: kri ya sa muts+tsha yi ni //
NK130(tho)001:3852: gza' yum gyi ni dkyil 'khor du //
NK130(tho)001:3853: gza' chen nyi mas gtso bo byas //
NK130(tho)001:3854: 'dab mar gza' dang gza' yum bkod //
NK130(tho)001:3855: thub pa'i dbang po la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:3856: sangs rgyas bzhi po sgo bar byas //
NK130(tho)001:3858: skyon dang ldan pa yin zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:3859: dag snang mi zad rgyan 'khor lo //
NK130(tho)001:3860: mnga' ba'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3861: gnyis 'dzin rtog pa mi mnga' bas //
NK130(tho)001:3863: thabs la mkhas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3865: de la skyon gyi go skabs med //
NK130(tho)001:3867: rdo rje 'chang gi gsung rabs su //
NK130(tho)001:3868: dkyil 'khor chen po'i nang dag tu //
NK130(tho)001:3869: ma gsungs lha 'am mtshan ma bkod //
NK130(tho)001:3870: de dag bdud kyi yin par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3871: gsang sngags gsang bas 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:3872: mngon par rtogs pa gsang bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3873: bskal pa bzang po'i thog ma la //
NK130(tho)001:3874: rdo rje ri dbang zom gyi rtser //
NK130(tho)001:3875: rdo rje 'chang dbang khro bor sprul //
NK130(tho)001:3876: drag po tshangs dbang khyab 'jug bdud //
NK130(tho)001:3877: gshin rje lha min 'byung po sogs //
NK130(tho)001:3878: 'jig rten gsum gyi bdag po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3879: che ba'i nga rgyal gyis dregs nas //
NK130(tho)001:3880: thub pa'i dam tshig ma 'dzin pa //
NK130(tho)001:3881: sprul pa mang pos bkug nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3882: rang dbang med par gdan du bardzisa //
NK130(tho)001:3883: 'khos bcas dam tshig gsum la bkod //
NK130(tho)001:3884: de 'dra'i sgrub thabs rgyud las bshad //
NK130(tho)001:3885: thub dbang gcig pur ma zad de //
NK130(tho)001:3886: dus gsum byung ba'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:3887: kun gyis rdo rje theg mchog gi //
NK130(tho)001:3889: da lta'ang de 'dra sus bsgom la //
NK130(tho)001:3892: bdud rnams bcom nas sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3893: gnas skabs su yang bdud kyi ris //
NK130(tho)001:3895: log par lta ba 'dzin pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3897: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3898: rang gi rkang pas bardzisa pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3900: de la dgos pa ci 'dra yod //
NK130(tho)001:3901: spyi bor bla ma sangs rgyas bsgom //
NK130(tho)001:3902: de yis bsod nams mtha' las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:3903: de dag rkang 'og gnon cing smod //
NK130(tho)001:3905: de bzhin gshegs la gus tsam gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3906: bsod nams srid mthar mi zad gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3907: sangs rgyas brnyas pa'i sdig las 'di //
NK130(tho)001:3909: bla med bla ma'i bla ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:3910: sangs rgyas sras bcas de dag yin //
NK130(tho)001:3911: khro bo'i dbang po rnams kyang ni //
NK130(tho)001:3912: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyag gcig yin //
NK130(tho)001:3913: thub dbang sangs rgyas khros pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:3914: khro bo 'jig rten gsum rgyal te //
NK130(tho)001:3915: 'jam dbyangs khros pa gshin rje'i gshed //
NK130(tho)001:3916: spyan ras gzigs dbang rta mgrin yin //
NK130(tho)001:3917: lag na rdo rje gsang ba'i bdag /
NK130(tho)001:3918: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil par gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3919: de lta de ltar gzhan rnams kyang //
NK130(tho)001:3920: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' nyid //
NK130(tho)001:3921: de yang sprul dang yang sprul gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3923: sa bcu'i dbang phyug 'gro ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:3924: skyabs gnas chen por bzhugs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3925: de dag mnan pa'i rten 'brel gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3926: 'khor ba'i mthar yang khas nyen cing //
NK130(tho)001:3927: dbang chung gzhan gyi bran g.yog dang //
NK130(tho)001:3928: ngan song gsum gyi gnas rten 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3929: skyabs gnas brnyas pa'i rten 'brel gyis //
NK130(tho)001:3930: thar pa'i rgyu 'bras slar log pas //
NK130(tho)001:3931: mi lus tsam yang mi thob na //
NK130(tho)001:3932: srid zhi'i bde ba 'grub re kan //
NK130(tho)001:3934: de don gong du smos pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:3935: dgongs te gsungs pa gsar rnying gi //
NK130(tho)001:3936: rgyud du khyad par med pa snang //
NK130(tho)001:3937: nyams su len pa'i sgrub thabs gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:3938: gsar rnying gnyis ka'i khrod na yang //
NK130(tho)001:3939: sangs rgyas mnan pa'i sgrub thabs med //
NK130(tho)001:3940: yod na khyed kyi skyon de 'bab //
NK130(tho)001:3941: med phyir su la smra ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:3942: gal te rgyud la smod pa na //
NK130(tho)001:3944: de la sogs pa kun kyang smad //
NK130(tho)001:3945: gsar rnying gnyis ka'i chos spangs pas //
NK130(tho)001:3946: thar pa'i go skabs khyed la med //
NK130(tho)001:3947: gzhan yang khyed kyi tshig 'di brtag /
NK130(tho)001:3948: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3949: rang gi rkang pas bardzisa pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:3952: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gtso bor bsgom //
NK130(tho)001:3953: 'khor la gtso bos dbu brgyan pa //
NK130(tho)001:3954: 'di dang don du mi mtshungs sam //
NK130(tho)001:3955: 'on kyang rang nyid tha mal pa //
NK130(tho)001:3956: ma yin sangs rgyas nyid bsgom pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3957: 'og yin de phyir nyes pa med //
NK130(tho)001:3958: min na bde mchog zhabs kyi 'og /
NK130(tho)001:3959: lha chen mnan pa'ang sdig tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:3960: lha chen dbang phyug chen po de //
NK130(tho)001:3961: thal bas khebs pa'i 'jig rten du //
NK130(tho)001:3962: thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs zhes pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:3963: de bzhin gshegs par sangs rgyas zhes //
NK130(tho)001:3964: rdo rje rtse mo'i rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3965: gzhan du spyan ras gzigs dbang gi //
NK130(tho)001:3966: sprul pa yin par bshad pa 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:3967: bde mchog bsgom pa'ang sdig yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:3968: sangs rgyas brnyas pa'i sdig las 'di //
NK130(tho)001:3969: 'khor ba'i mthar yang mi zad lo //
NK130(tho)001:3970: 'o na byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:3971: gnad byed bde bar 'brel ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:3972: de bas lhag pa'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:3973: 'brel tshad don dang ldan pa nyams //
NK130(tho)001:3974: legs skar dang ni lhas sbyin yang //
NK130(tho)001:3975: dmyal ba las ni thon mi srid //
NK130(tho)001:3976: 'dod na bskal chen tshe rdzogs nas //
NK130(tho)001:3977: de gnyis thar bar lungs las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:3978: de las brnyas pa ches che ba //
NK130(tho)001:3979: byed pa'i sdig to can gyi bdud //
NK130(tho)001:3980: de yang byang chub lung bstan mod //
NK130(tho)001:3981: des na khyed kyi tshig 'di yis //
NK130(tho)001:3982: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:3983: skur pa mi bzad btab pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:3984: sdig pa che na 'di che mod //
NK130(tho)001:3985: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' nyid //
NK130(tho)001:3986: de yang sprul dang yang sprul gyi //
NK130(tho)001:3988: sa bcu'i dbang phyug 'gro ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:3989: skyabs su bzhugs zhes tshig 'di yis //
NK130(tho)001:3990: sangs rgyas sprul pa yang sprul rnams //
NK130(tho)001:3991: 'gro ba'i skyabs su ma byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:3992: skyabs gnas brnyas pa chen po yin //
NK130(tho)001:3993: srid zhi'i bde dang mi lus tsam //
NK130(tho)001:3994: 'grub ri mna' yis gang gcus pa //
NK130(tho)001:3995: khyed rang nyid la log nas snang //
NK130(tho)001:3997: khyod kyi dkyil 'khor lha rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:3998: nyang stod khu le na thog gi //
NK130(tho)001:3999: 'gong po khu le lag dgu dang //
NK130(tho)001:4000: yam shud yul gyi btsan 'gong dmar //
NK130(tho)001:4001: 'o yug rdo rje legs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4002: nags shod sku lha gsang ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4003: glags mad'i ba lam dri'u snam //
NK130(tho)001:4004: tsha ba sgang gi g.yu sgron ma //
NK130(tho)001:4005: gtsang gi jo mo kha rag ma //
NK130(tho)001:4006: mon gyi dun ting nag mo sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4007: bod kyi yul 'dre sna tshogs snang //
NK130(tho)001:4008: khungs ma'i rgyud las de mi 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:4009: rgyal ba'i mdo dang rgyud rnams su //
NK130(tho)001:4011: bstan na de la mtha' ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:4012: gzhan du 'byung po zad dam ci //
NK130(tho)001:4013: 'jam dpal rtsa rgyud rig pa mchog /'byung po 'dul byed za ma tog /
NK130(tho)001:4014: gar mkhan mchog dang mi g.yo ba //
NK130(tho)001:4015: dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs ltos //
NK130(tho)001:4017: khu le lag dgu yam shud dang //
NK130(tho)001:4018: spun yin yam shud yul gyi ltar //
NK130(tho)001:4019: ma shes nyang stod du bsam pa //
NK130(tho)001:4020: khu le zhes pa yar 'brog na'ang //
NK130(tho)001:4021: yong mod de rim par phye ba nyer lnga pa /
NK130(tho)001:4023: khu le lag dgu'i ming yang med //
NK130(tho)001:4024: mon gyi dun ting nag mo sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4025: bod kyi yul 'dre tshogs snang lo //
NK130(tho)001:4027: mon bod ma phyed ci zhig nongs //
NK130(tho)001:4028: mtha' 'khob re rer ma zad pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4029: lha klu srin po lto 'phye grul //
NK130(tho)001:4030: gnod sbyin mkha' lding lus hrul srul //
NK130(tho)001:4031: srid par gtogs pa'i lha 'dre kun //
NK130(tho)001:4032: rgyal ba'i spyan sngar lhags nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:4033: kun gyi ming sogs ston bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:4035: thub pas bstan par mi nus pa //
NK130(tho)001:4036: mtshungs pa med pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK130(tho)001:4037: thogs med gzigs pa'i spyan dang ldan //
NK130(tho)001:4038: gsung gi gsang ba bsam mi khyab //
NK130(tho)001:4039: zad pa med pa'i spobs pa mnga' //
NK130(tho)001:4040: shes bya thams cad ston nus bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:4042: ston par ma nus ci zhig nongs //
NK130(tho)001:4043: sangs rgyas spobs pa zad dam ci //
NK130(tho)001:4044: rnying ma'i chos rnams smod smod nas //
NK130(tho)001:4045: sangs rgyas nyid kyang ma smad cig /
NK130(tho)001:4047: rnying ma'i lo pan 'phags pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4048: de phyir don 'gyur mdzad do lo //
NK130(tho)001:4049: 'o na za ma tog la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4050: 'gyur rnying gzhan la'ang ci ma mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4052: rnying ma'i lo pan de dag kun //
NK130(tho)001:4053: 'phags pa yin par yongs la grags //
NK130(tho)001:4054: 'gyur byang so so'i skabs thob gtso //
NK130(tho)001:4055: kun la don 'gyur ga la dgos //
NK130(tho)001:4056: smra rgyu med bzhin smra ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:4057: rang nyid ngal ba kho nar zad //
NK130(tho)001:4059: khyed kyi dkyil 'khor mchod pa la //
NK130(tho)001:4060: sman dang rak+ta gtor ma zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4061: dang por bdud rtsi nang mchod 'bul //
NK130(tho)001:4062: de rjes khrag gi yon chab dang //
NK130(tho)001:4063: de nas gtor ma de rjes la //
NK130(tho)001:4064: phyi mchod rnams dang bstod pa byed //
NK130(tho)001:4065: khungs ma'i rgyud gzhung thams cad nas //
NK130(tho)001:4066: thog mar chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga //
NK130(tho)001:4067: rol mo ba dan rgyal mtshan gdugs //
NK130(tho)001:4068: rgyal srid bdun dang grub pa brgyad //
NK130(tho)001:4070: phyi yi mchod pa kun rdzogs nas //
NK130(tho)001:4071: bstod pa'i rjes la nang mchod dang //
NK130(tho)001:4072: kun gyi mtha' la gtor ma mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4074: 'dir ni mchod pa'i cho ga la //
NK130(tho)001:4075: thog mar phyi yi mchod pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4076: nang gi mchod pa nyid la yang //
NK130(tho)001:4077: khrag dang chang gi yon chab dang //
NK130(tho)001:4078: dbang po'i me tog gsur chen sbos //
NK130(tho)001:4079: zhun chen mar me dri chu'i chab //
NK130(tho)001:4080: sha chen dri chen zhal zas zhi ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:4083: rkang gling thod rnga gsang ba'i lnga //
NK130(tho)001:4084: rol mo la sogs bshad pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4085: gsang mchod bde chen byang chub sems //
NK130(tho)001:4086: de nas sman rag gtor ma 'bul //
NK130(tho)001:4087: de nas tshogs dang bstod pa bshad //
NK130(tho)001:4088: nang gi mchod pa la sogs la //
NK130(tho)001:4089: phyi nang gsang ba'i bye brag gis //
NK130(tho)001:4090: mchod pa'i rnam grangs bsam mi khyab //
NK130(tho)001:4091: chang la bdud rtsi ril bu tsam //
NK130(tho)001:4092: btab pa'i nang mchod tsam gyis min //
NK130(tho)001:4093: de bzhin bdud rtsi sman la yang //
NK130(tho)001:4094: rtsa ba brgyad dang yan lag stong //
NK130(tho)001:4095: de la'ang phyi nang gsang dbye bas //
NK130(tho)001:4096: rnam grangs dpag tu med par yod //
NK130(tho)001:4097: khrag tsam nyid la rak+ta zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4098: de nyid gcig pus 'grub pa min //
NK130(tho)001:4099: nyon mongs 'khor ba bsgral ba'i khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4100: srid pa skyed pa rgyu yi khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4101: rten 'brel bcu gnyis rtsa ba'i khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4102: gtsang dme bral ba bam gyi khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4103: gdug pa bsgral ba'i snying gi khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4104: mkha' dbyings rnam dag pad+ma'i khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4105: rtsi shing dmar po 'byung ba'i khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4106: dug lnga bsgral ba'i ye shes khrag /
NK130(tho)001:4107: de sogs rnam pa du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:4108: gtor ma'ang kha zas tsam gyis min //
NK130(tho)001:4109: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na //
NK130(tho)001:4110: snang ba tshogs lam gtor ma sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4111: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK130(tho)001:4112: gtor ma nyid du ma gyur med //
NK130(tho)001:4113: rgyud lung rgya mtsho rtogs dka' bas //
NK130(tho)001:4114: kho bos byas pa'i bstan bcos na //
NK130(tho)001:4115: shin tu gsal bar yod na yang //
NK130(tho)001:4116: khyed kyis go ba'ang ches dka' la //
NK130(tho)001:4117: go yor log rtog spel bar zad //
NK130(tho)001:4118: snang srid bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:4119: rtogs par gyur pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK130(tho)001:4120: go rim nges dang ma nges pa //
NK130(tho)001:4121: ji ltar mchod kyang mi 'gal te //
NK130(tho)001:4122: kun kyang ye shes rol pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4124: khyod kyi srog chags bsad pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4125: mdangs skong rgyu skong la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4126: bskang gso mdos dang gtor mdos dang //
NK130(tho)001:4127: bskang mdos rgya gar yul na med //
NK130(tho)001:4129: khyed kyi srog chags bsad pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4130: mdangs skong zhes ni ma zer cig /
NK130(tho)001:4131: gson po la ni mdangs yod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4132: bsod nams mdangs dang ldan pa min //
NK130(tho)001:4134: bya nag dang ni lug nag sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4135: rigs dang mthun pa'i kha dog dang //
NK130(tho)001:4136: dbang po tshang phyir mdangs zhes bya //
NK130(tho)001:4137: rgyu yi bskang ba zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:4138: bam sogs srog chags sha la bshad //
NK130(tho)001:4139: mdangs skong rgyu skong rgya gar na //
NK130(tho)001:4140: med na bram ze mchog sred kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4141: mgon g.yag mgon lug 'dzugs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4142: gzhan yang srog chags 'dzugs lugs mang //
NK130(tho)001:4143: mchog sred bde ba'i rdo rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:4144: sh+rad+d+ha ka ra la sogs pas //
NK130(tho)001:4145: mgon po dang ni lha mo la //
NK130(tho)001:4146: n+ri tri'i tsit+ta sa bskangs zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:4147: dgra dang bgegs kyi snying yin la //
NK130(tho)001:4148: mi shas gtor ma brgyan pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4149: srog chags rgyu yi skong min nam //
NK130(tho)001:4150: mdos gtor rgya gar med ces pa //
NK130(tho)001:4151: slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mi dang //
NK130(tho)001:4152: pan chen g+hi ri warma yis //
NK130(tho)001:4153: gtsug gtor gdugs dkar mdos chog dang //
NK130(tho)001:4154: spyod mdzad chos kyi rdo rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:4155: slob dpon 'gro bzang snying po yis //
NK130(tho)001:4156: rnam thos sras kyi mdos chog mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4157: 'di gnyis zangs dkar lo ts+aas bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:4158: bram ze mchog sred nas bzung ste //
NK130(tho)001:4159: mgon po dang ni lha mo'i mdos //
NK130(tho)001:4160: da lta'ang sa skya pa rnams mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4161: dud sol ma dang trag shad la //
NK130(tho)001:4162: mar pa dang ni myos lo ts+aas //
NK130(tho)001:4163: bsgyur ba'i mdos kyang du ma snang //
NK130(tho)001:4165: gsar ma'i cho ga'ang mi dgag 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:4167: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor mchod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4168: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i cho ga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4169: cha mthun dpa' bo'i ston mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:4170: gzhon nu ma yi ston mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:4171: me dang chu yi sbyin sreg dang //
NK130(tho)001:4172: chu sbyin rnams dang changs bu sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4173: gtor ma 'bul ba'i khyad par rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4174: rnam par dag pa'i rgyud sde las //
NK130(tho)001:4175: phyi mchod pa yi cho ga yin //
NK130(tho)001:4176: khyod kyi sbyor sgrol la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4177: nyes med srog chags gsod pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:4178: sangs rgyas bstan la ga la shongs //
NK130(tho)001:4179: de ltar cho ga log pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4180: don gyi nor pa de dag la //
NK130(tho)001:4181: ngan song gsum gyi las gsog cing //
NK130(tho)001:4182: thar pa'i srog rtsa gcod pa mang //
NK130(tho)001:4183: kye ma sdig can bdud 'di ni //
NK130(tho)001:4184: snyigs dus bla ma'i cha lugs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4185: chos dang chos min bsres nas ston //
NK130(tho)001:4186: shes ldan yod na bya ra sgrims //
NK130(tho)001:4188: khyed kyang de ltar ma gyur grang //
NK130(tho)001:4189: dzam+b+ha la la chu sbyin dang //
NK130(tho)001:4190: yi dwags rnams la chu sbyin dang //
NK130(tho)001:4191: 'phrog ma'i changs bu la sogs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4192: mdo lugs yin gyi rgyud las min //
NK130(tho)001:4193: rgyud sde'i phyi rol mchod pa'o zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4194: gsar ma'i cho ga mi bslad 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:4196: ston mo gnyis dang sbyin sreg kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4197: phyi rol mchod pa cung ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:4198: cho ga log na khyed rang log /
NK130(tho)001:4199: nged kyi sgrol ba zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:4200: nyes med sems can gsod pa min //
NK130(tho)001:4201: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu tshangs ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4202: nyams pa bdun ldan zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:4203: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK130(tho)001:4204: dam nyams log dang 'khu ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4206: de ltar bdun dang ldan pa na //
NK130(tho)001:4207: nyes pa de las che ba ci //
NK130(tho)001:4208: ngan song gsum gyi 'gro ba dag /
NK130(tho)001:4209: sdug bsngal de las thar phyin du //
NK130(tho)001:4210: bsgral ba nyid du rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4211: gdug pa can la byams pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:4212: rtsa ltung bcu pa ma yin nam //
NK130(tho)001:4213: de ltar khyed kyis zab mo'i don //
NK130(tho)001:4214: phal cher rna bas ma thos shing //
NK130(tho)001:4215: thos pa dag kyang nor mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4216: yi ge mang por 'gro phyir bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:4218: khyed kyi rdzogs pa'i rim pa la //
NK130(tho)001:4219: lam gyi 'gros dang bsgom pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:4220: theg mchog snying po'i man ngag gi //
NK130(tho)001:4221: gzhung dang mthun pa gcig kyang med //
NK130(tho)001:4223: mthar thug phyag rgya chen po'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:4224: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi don //
NK130(tho)001:4225: yin lugs snying por dril ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:4226: 'dus pa'i rim pa lnga pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4227: 'jam pa'i rdo rje'i zhal gyi lung //
NK130(tho)001:4228: 'khor lo sdom pa'i rim lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4229: rim lnga dpyid dang thig le'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:4230: lhan cig skyes grub rtsa 'grel dang //
NK130(tho)001:4231: grub pa sde bdun 'grel par bcas //
NK130(tho)001:4232: grub chen rnams kyi rdo rje'i glu //
NK130(tho)001:4233: rtsa 'grel la sogs mang du bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:4234: zab mo'i rgyud dang de'i 'grel pa //
NK130(tho)001:4235: 'grel bshad dbang sgrub mang po yi //
NK130(tho)001:4236: snying po lta bu yang dang yang //
NK130(tho)001:4237: phyag rgya chen po'i nye lam bstan //
NK130(tho)001:4238: tshig ris sna tshogs mi sna tshogs //
NK130(tho)001:4239: bshad pa'i tshul yang sna tshogs yod //
NK130(tho)001:4240: lam gyi nyams len snying po la //
NK130(tho)001:4241: thams cad go rim mtshung par gnas //
NK130(tho)001:4242: sbyang gzhi sbyang bya sbyang byed dang //
NK130(tho)001:4243: sbyang ba'i tshul dang lam gyi 'gros //
NK130(tho)001:4244: mngon par rtogs pa skye ba'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:4245: phal cher don la mtshungs par yod //
NK130(tho)001:4246: snying po'i don de sangs rgyas kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4247: yongs su rdzogs par phyogs gcig tu //
NK130(tho)001:4248: go rim 'khrul med legs bstan pa //
NK130(tho)001:4249: rnal 'byor yan lag drug pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4250: dpal ldan gsang ba 'dus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4251: dgyes pa rdo rje 'khor lo sdom //
NK130(tho)001:4252: gshin rje gshed sogs thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:4253: sna tshogs ming gis 'di nyid gsung //
NK130(tho)001:4254: de yi rgyas par bshad pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:4255: phyag na rdo rje'i stod 'grel dang //
NK130(tho)001:4256: dgyes pa rdo rje snying 'grel dang //
NK130(tho)001:4258: sangs rgyas sras dang bcas rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4259: shin tu gsal bar gtan la phab //
NK130(tho)001:4260: bstan pa'i lam rim kun shes phyir //
NK130(tho)001:4261: bye brag smra dang mdo sde pa //
NK130(tho)001:4262: rnal 'byor spyod dang dbu ma pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4263: so so'i bsgom bya mthar thug dang //
NK130(tho)001:4264: khyad par theg mchog snying pa'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:4265: phyag rgya chen po'i ngos 'dzin dang //
NK130(tho)001:4266: de nyid khyad par 'phags tshul dang //
NK130(tho)001:4267: lam gyi rtags tshad yon tan dang //
NK130(tho)001:4268: gegs dang gol sa nor ba'i 'phrang //
NK130(tho)001:4269: sa dang lam gyi bgrod tshul dang //
NK130(tho)001:4271: de yi sgrub byed 'thad pa bcas //
NK130(tho)001:4272: thugs rje mnga' ba'i bla ma des //
NK130(tho)001:4273: ma 'dres gsal bar rdzogs par bstan //
NK130(tho)001:4274: snying po'i lam de sgrub pa'i grogs //
NK130(tho)001:4275: rig pa'i skyes bu'i brtul zhugs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4276: spyod pa gsum dang spyod pa'i dus //
NK130(tho)001:4277: phyogs las rgyal ba'i spyod pa'ang bstan //
NK130(tho)001:4278: khyod dang de dag mi mthun par //
NK130(tho)001:4279: cha med rgyus gtam 'chad pa'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:4281: lam gyi rim pa mtshar cig snang //
NK130(tho)001:4283: de ltar gsar ma'i rdzogs rim dang //
NK130(tho)001:4284: mthun pa gsang sngags rnying ma la //
NK130(tho)001:4285: gcig kyang med ces ma zer cig /
NK130(tho)001:4286: ci phyir 'dus pa'i rim lnga yang //
NK130(tho)001:4287: bka' gter gnyis ka'i khrod na yod //
NK130(tho)001:4288: 'jam pa'i rdo rje'i zhal lung du //
NK130(tho)001:4289: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs 'chang ba //
NK130(tho)001:4290: sgyu ma 'ja' tshon lta bu ru //
NK130(tho)001:4291: rang dang gzhan gyis rgyud sbyor ba //
NK130(tho)001:4292: yang dag gsal ba zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:4293: zhes gsungs pa 'di rdzogs chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:4294: snying po mthar thug 'od gsal yin //
NK130(tho)001:4295: 'dus pa'i snang mched thob gsum yang //
NK130(tho)001:4296: 'di nyid las ni gzhan ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:4297: dus 'khor dgyes sdom gshed sogs las //
NK130(tho)001:4298: phyag rgya chen po'i mthar thug pa //
NK130(tho)001:4299: sbyor ba drug tu gsungs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4300: snying po so sor sdud pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:4301: 'di nyid yin phyir sbyor rdzogs mthun //
NK130(tho)001:4302: dpal ldan 'khor lo sdom pa la //
NK130(tho)001:4303: lu dril gnyis kyi rim lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4304: nag po pa yi rim bzhi yang //
NK130(tho)001:4305: phra thig la sogs rdzogs rim gyi //
NK130(tho)001:4306: lha dang rgyud kyi khyad par las //
NK130(tho)001:4307: mdo dang yang phur ma mo sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4308: 'di dag shas cher mthun par snang //
NK130(tho)001:4309: dpyid thig grub pa sde bdun dang //
NK130(tho)001:4310: lhan cig skyes grub 'grel par bcas //
NK130(tho)001:4311: de sogs phyag chen gzhung rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:4312: rdzogs chen sems phyogs shin tu mthun //
NK130(tho)001:4314: grub chen rnams kyis mngon du gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:4315: de la n+aa ro 'phags pa lha //
NK130(tho)001:4316: zhi ba lha dang nag po ba //
NK130(tho)001:4317: dus zhabs sha ba ri sogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4318: basngagasa brjod rdo rje'i glu ru blangs //
NK130(tho)001:4319: khyad par grub mchog sa ra has //
NK130(tho)001:4320: mang du smra bas ci zhig bya //
NK130(tho)001:4321: chos kyi tshad ni 'di yis chog /
NK130(tho)001:4322: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbus gnas pas //
NK130(tho)001:4323: thig le mthong na rnam par grol //
NK130(tho)001:4324: zhes gsungs rdo rje'i mgur rnams kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4325: go na phal cher rdzogs chen yin //
NK130(tho)001:4326: khyed kyis mu stegs sgom yin lo //
NK130(tho)001:4327: ming dang tshig ris bshad pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:4328: sna tshogs yod pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4329: lam gyi nyams len snying po la //
NK130(tho)001:4330: thams cad go rim mtshungs pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4331: so so'i gzhung la bltas pas shes //
NK130(tho)001:4332: de bzhin mngon rtogs skye tshul yang //
NK130(tho)001:4333: phal cher mtshungs pa'ang dka' bar snang //
NK130(tho)001:4334: bstan pa'i rim pa kun shes phyir //
NK130(tho)001:4339: grub mtha' bzhi la mthar thug gi //
NK130(tho)001:4340: bsgom bya so sor yod min te //
NK130(tho)001:4341: gang dag bde gshegs nyan thos 'gyur bar bya snyam dang //
NK130(tho)001:4342: rang sangs rgyas dang de bzhin chos rgyal 'gyur 'dod pa //
NK130(tho)001:4343: bzod pa 'di la ma brten thob par nus min te //
NK130(tho)001:4344: 'di ni shes rab pha rol phyin mchog spyod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4345: zhes gsungs thabs kyis shan 'byed kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4346: bsgom pa gcig las gsungs pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4347: sa lam rim gyis bgrod pa'ang //
NK130(tho)001:4348: 'di la mnyam med sgam po pas //
NK130(tho)001:4349: phyag rgya chen po chig chod la //
NK130(tho)001:4350: sa lam brtsi ba 'khrul zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4351: spyod pa bzhi dang ma mthun pas //
NK130(tho)001:4352: de ni chos su mi 'dod na //
NK130(tho)001:4353: dam chos 'dul ba'i spyod pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:4354: spyod pa bzhi dang ma mthun pas //
NK130(tho)001:4355: chos ma yin par 'dod dam ci //
NK130(tho)001:4356: don gyi dgongs pa gcig pas chog /
NK130(tho)001:4357: tshig ris spyod pa mi mthun la //
NK130(tho)001:4358: gsar ma la'ang skyon gdags mang //
NK130(tho)001:4359: mtshan dngos nyi ma seng ge /
NK130(tho)001:4360: rdog ston wa ba can gyis ni //
NK130(tho)001:4361: ma mo rol pa'i rgyud dkrugs pas //
NK130(tho)001:4362: ga ya d+ha ra'i gser chos byung //
NK130(tho)001:4363: zhes sogs gzhan lugs phal cher smad //
NK130(tho)001:4364: dpal ldan dgyes pa rdo rje'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:4365: de yis dri ma can du bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:4366: gzhan yang pha rgyud pa dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:4367: lam 'bras gsung ngag rin po che //
NK130(tho)001:4368: snyan snyan bsdus pa'i 'thor chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:4370: phyag chen chos drug la sogs la //
NK130(tho)001:4371: sdom gsum rab dbyer dgag bya dang //
NK130(tho)001:4372: gzhan yang sa skya pan chen gyis //
NK130(tho)001:4373: dwags po bka' brgyud phal cher bkags //
NK130(tho)001:4374: dam chos bdud kyi gcod yul la //
NK130(tho)001:4375: ma jo smyon ma'i gdol chos zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4376: snga rabs mang pos bkags pa yod //
NK130(tho)001:4377: dam pa'i sdug bsngal zhi byed la //
NK130(tho)001:4379: ston chen dge bshes sgom chen pa //
NK130(tho)001:4380: mang po zhig gis bkags nas snang //
NK130(tho)001:4381: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo yang //
NK130(tho)001:4382: bcom ldan rig pa'i ral gri yis //
NK130(tho)001:4383: mu stegs gzhung dang chos mthun pas //
NK130(tho)001:4384: bkag dang brtag pa'i gnas su byas //
NK130(tho)001:4385: de bzhin rje gang red mda' bas //
NK130(tho)001:4386: dus kyi 'khor lo bkag pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4387: rje btsun chen po mi la dang //
NK130(tho)001:4388: dam pa gnyis kas bka' gdams la //
NK130(tho)001:4389: bkyon dang dgag bya mang du mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4390: bod du dar ba'i chos rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:4391: ma smad pa ni med na yang //
NK130(tho)001:4392: thams cad sangs rgyas lam du gcig /
NK130(tho)001:4393: de bas dag pa'i snang ba sbyongs //
NK130(tho)001:4395: khyad par theg mchog snying po yi //
NK130(tho)001:4396: yang dag khyad chos nges ma zin //
NK130(tho)001:4397: nyams len phal pa sna tshogs la //
NK130(tho)001:4398: a ti yo ga'i ming gis brjod //
NK130(tho)001:4400: dag pa bsgom pa la sogs dang //
NK130(tho)001:4401: rtog pas brtags pa'i rtog sgom la //
NK130(tho)001:4402: sngags kyi khyad chos 'dod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4403: dbang po rgya yan gdams ngag la //
NK130(tho)001:4404: nyams len phal par 'dod pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:4405: chos kyi de nyid ma mthong bas //
NK130(tho)001:4406: smra 'di khyed cag shin tu bden //
NK130(tho)001:4407: gser dngul 'thor ba'i sa gzhi la //
NK130(tho)001:4408: rlog hrul drud pas sbar sbur dang //
NK130(tho)001:4409: tsher ma sogs las ci zhig 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:4411: khyod kyi sems klong man ngag sde //
NK130(tho)001:4412: gzhung rnams phan tshun mthun pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4413: dbang bskur lta sgom spyod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4414: lam gyi rim pa nang 'gal nyid //
NK130(tho)001:4415: rgyal lam gzhung bzang la sgrus nas //
NK130(tho)001:4416: phyogs re phyogs re shes na yang //
NK130(tho)001:4417: tshig don nor ba stong gis sbags //
NK130(tho)001:4419: bya rgyud la sogs rgyud sde bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:4420: gzhung rnams phan tshun ga la mthun //
NK130(tho)001:4421: de phyir sems klong man ngag sde //
NK130(tho)001:4422: phyi nang gsang ba gsum yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:4423: 'di gzhung phyogs gcig ga la mthun //
NK130(tho)001:4424: don gyi lta ba gcig yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4425: rgyud sde mtho dman gong 'og gis //
NK130(tho)001:4426: dbang dang cho ga'ang so so yin //
NK130(tho)001:4427: gal te gcig pa zhig dgos na //
NK130(tho)001:4428: kun rigs tsam zhig shes pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:4429: rgyud sde thams cad basgre'am ci //
NK130(tho)001:4430: lam gyi go rim mi mthun pa //
NK130(tho)001:4431: gdul bya'i blo yi rigs dang bstun //
NK130(tho)001:4432: de tsam zhig la skyon 'dogs na //
NK130(tho)001:4433: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4434: bde mchog rim lnga mthun pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4435: de bas rang sems gtan la phob //
NK130(tho)001:4437: 'on kyang khyod la rgyud sde ni //
NK130(tho)001:4438: brgya dang stong dang 'bum phrag snang //
NK130(tho)001:4439: gzhung dang man ngag yin zer ba //
NK130(tho)001:4440: gangs can yul 'di khyab nas gnas //
NK130(tho)001:4441: de phyir n+aa ro'i chos drug dang //
NK130(tho)001:4442: ni gu dang ni lam 'bras bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:4443: rgyud sde'i man ngag bla ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:4444: logs su phyungs pa de yang min //
NK130(tho)001:4447: 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:4448: bzhugs par bshad kyi bod yul 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:4449: 'gyur ba'i sems klong man ngag sde'i //
NK130(tho)001:4450: rgyud sde pusti bdun brgyad snang //
NK130(tho)001:4451: rnying ma'i rgyud kun rdzogs chen min //
NK130(tho)001:4452: thams cad bsdoms pa'i rgyud 'bum la'ang //
NK130(tho)001:4453: glegs bam sum cu rtsa bdun tsam //
NK130(tho)001:4454: de la brgya stong 'bum phrag ces //
NK130(tho)001:4455: snang ba 'khrul lam ci zhig byung //
NK130(tho)001:4456: rgyud don bkral ba'i gzhug gdams kun //
NK130(tho)001:4457: rnying mar rang gi rang lugs yin //
NK130(tho)001:4458: chos drug lam 'bras yin ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:4460: 'on kyang tshig dang don gyi tshul //
NK130(tho)001:4461: cho ga'i go rim gzhung gi 'gros //
NK130(tho)001:4462: khyod gzhung rigs mthun gcig tu chad //
NK130(tho)001:4464: 'di ni gong du khyed rang gis //
NK130(tho)001:4465: khyod kyi sems klong man ngag sde'i //
NK130(tho)001:4466: gzhung rnams phan tshun mthun pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4467: dbang bskur lta sgom spyod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4468: lam gyi go rim nang 'gal nyid //
NK130(tho)001:4469: de skad bshad ma thag dang 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:4471: ji ltar bon pos chos bsgyur ba //
NK130(tho)001:4472: chos la brten phyir dbyibs 'dra yang //
NK130(tho)001:4473: mi mthun rgyus tshugs gtso bor ston //
NK130(tho)001:4474: 'dra la mi mthun bon gyi lugs //
NK130(tho)001:4475: de ltar khyod kyi chos rnams kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4476: 'dra la mi mthun ris su chud //
NK130(tho)001:4477: ming rnams chos dang 'dra ba la //
NK130(tho)001:4478: tshig ris cho ga bon la nye //
NK130(tho)001:4480: chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong la //
NK130(tho)001:4481: bon yang de dang 'dra ba yod //
NK130(tho)001:4482: de phyir gsar rnying gnyi ga la //
NK130(tho)001:4483: phyogs 'dra nyid du yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4484: bon gyi gzhung lugs ltos dang shes //
NK130(tho)001:4486: khyod kyi gzhung 'di sangs rgyas gsung //
NK130(tho)001:4487: tshad mar gyur pa yin nges na //
NK130(tho)001:4488: khyod kyi gzhung dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:4489: yang dag rgyud rnams log par snang //
NK130(tho)001:4490: yang dag rgyud gzhung dam pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4491: tshad mar gyur pa yin nges na //
NK130(tho)001:4492: khyod kyi gzhung rnams log par nges //
NK130(tho)001:4493: de phyir bdud kyi chos su dgos //
NK130(tho)001:4496: tshad mar gyur pa yin nges na //
NK130(tho)001:4497: theg pa che dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:4498: pha rol phyin 'di log par snang //
NK130(tho)001:4499: pha rol phyin pa'i theg pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4500: tshad mar gyur pa yin nges na //
NK130(tho)001:4501: 'dul ba'i gzhung rnams log zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:4502: tshig don go rim mi mthun pa //
NK130(tho)001:4503: theg pa gong 'og kun la yod //
NK130(tho)001:4505: 'di ltar rgyud sde mtha' yas pa //
NK130(tho)001:4506: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos skor 'di //
NK130(tho)001:4507: rgya gar yul du byung ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4508: dbang du gyur pa bden zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:4509: 'o na o rgyan kha che sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4510: 'phags yul rnams su dar bar nges //
NK130(tho)001:4511: rgyud dang mkhas grub dam pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:4512: kun las dpang du mdzad par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:4513: de la theg mchog rgyud sde rer //
NK130(tho)001:4514: rgyud gzhan mang du grags pa yod //
NK130(tho)001:4515: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4516: ming tsam zhig kyang mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:4517: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:4518: gsang ba 'dus pa stong phrag gcig /
NK130(tho)001:4519: rdo rje phreng ba 'bum phrag gsum //
NK130(tho)001:4520: dgongs pa lung ston 'bum phrag bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:4521: lha mo bzhis zhus brgya bdun cu //
NK130(tho)001:4522: zla gsang thig le stong bdun brgya //
NK130(tho)001:4523: rdo rje sa 'og brgya nye shu //
NK130(tho)001:4525: mkha' 'gro bde dang rgya mtsho bde dang nam mkha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:4526: gser gyi char pa dang ni dga' chen za nus dang //
NK130(tho)001:4527: bde chen dgyes pa dang ni gsang ba yid bde dang //
NK130(tho)001:4528: rgyud de rnams la phan pa'i rdo rje mkha' 'gro dang //
NK130(tho)001:4529: sangs rgyas thams cad dgyes pa'i rdo rje dkyil 'khor dang //
NK130(tho)001:4530: gsang ba'i mdzod dang rdo rje bdud rtsi las byung ba //
NK130(tho)001:4531: 'khor lo bde mchog gur dang phun sum tshogs pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4532: zhes dang rdo rje phreng ba las //
NK130(tho)001:4533: rdo rje sems dpa' wam rdo rje //
NK130(tho)001:4534: rdo rje 'jigs byed dbang phyug dang //
NK130(tho)001:4535: he ru ka dang dus 'khor lo //
NK130(tho)001:4536: dang pa'i sangs rgyas la sogs mtshan //
NK130(tho)001:4537: zhes dang gshin rje gshed dmar gyi le'u nyer gnyis pa las /
NK130(tho)001:4538: kyee rdo rje gsungs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4539: thar pa de bzhin sdom par yang //
NK130(tho)001:4540: 'dus pa la sogs rgyud du yang //
NK130(tho)001:4541: zhes dang gshin rje gshed nag pa'i rgyud du //
NK130(tho)001:4542: rgyud kyi mthar thug pa ni 'dus pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:4545: 'di la khyed kyi rgyud kyi lung //
NK130(tho)001:4546: mchan phu rgyab rten du bkod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4547: rdo rje snying po rgyan dang gur //
NK130(tho)001:4548: rdo rje phreng ba gshed dmar nag /
NK130(tho)001:4549: de ltar rgyud sde lnga po der //
NK130(tho)001:4550: rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul rags pa tsam //
NK130(tho)001:4551: gsungs mod rgyud 'bum dkar chag min //
NK130(tho)001:4552: de dag nang du ma 'dus pa //
NK130(tho)001:4553: chos ma yin na gsar ma yi //
NK130(tho)001:4555: kye ma 'di la ngo mtshar med //
NK130(tho)001:4557: rgya gar kha che o rgyan dang //
NK130(tho)001:4558: sham+b+ha la dang bal po yi //
NK130(tho)001:4559: mkhas grub dam pa'i gzhung brgya las //
NK130(tho)001:4560: khyod kyi gzhung lugs ming yang med //
NK130(tho)001:4562: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen snga phyi dang //
NK130(tho)001:4564: de sogs rgya gar slob dpon dang //
NK130(tho)001:4565: o rgyan mkhan po ha ti dang //
NK130(tho)001:4566: kha che'i slob dpon bi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:4567: bal po sh+ai la many+dzu dang //
NK130(tho)001:4568: de sogs so so'i slob dpon gyis //
NK130(tho)001:4569: rgyud 'grel man ngag bstan bcos rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4570: sngon tshe bod 'dir mang du bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:4571: mkhas grub dam pa'i gzhung du'ang //
NK130(tho)001:4572: lam sgron mnyam sbyor 'grel pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4573: mtshan brjod 'grel pa kha che lugs //
NK130(tho)001:4574: de la sogs pa'i bstan bcos su //
NK130(tho)001:4575: brgya byin sdong po jo bo rje //
NK130(tho)001:4576: nyi 'od seng ge bi ma las //
NK130(tho)001:4577: gsang ba'i snying po rngams pa glog /
NK130(tho)001:4578: dur khrod khu byug rol pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4579: sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa sogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4580: lung mang drangs pa ma mthong ngam //
NK130(tho)001:4581: gong du gzhung gdams yin zer bas //
NK130(tho)001:4582: gangs can khyab ces smra ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4583: 'dir ni ming yang med do lo //
NK130(tho)001:4584: smras ma thag tu brjed pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:4585: snying la chu ser zhugs pa 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:4587: bya ba kun las btus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4588: rnal 'byor rdzogs phreng rdo rje phreng //
NK130(tho)001:4589: sgrub thabs rgya mtsho la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4590: dbang dang sgrub gzhung thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:4591: bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:4592: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos skor sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4593: khyod kyi sgrub gzhung cho ga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4594: rgyud gzhung dbang chog ma grags so //
NK130(tho)001:4596: de rnams khrod du ma grags pas //
NK130(tho)001:4597: bka' min chos min du 'gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:4598: mi yi yul du ma grags pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4599: rgyud rnams thams cad chos min 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:4600: phyogs der rnying ma ma grags kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4601: yang dag phur pa la sogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4602: grub thob mang po rgya bod du //
NK130(tho)001:4603: byung ba'i tshul 'di su yis khegs //
NK130(tho)001:4604: 'on te rdzogs chen chos min kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4605: 'jam dpal sh+r+ai sing ye shes mdo //
NK130(tho)001:4607: de sogs rgya gar pan chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:4608: nyang ban ting 'dzin lce btsun dang //
NK130(tho)001:4609: grub chen me long rdo rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:4610: gsang bdag bde chen lhun grub sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4612: rdzogs chen 'dzin pa sha stag yin //
NK130(tho)001:4613: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4614: 'khon dang rgyus dang dpyal dang dpags //
NK130(tho)001:4615: 'o bran so zur gnubs sogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4616: grub thob rim pa bgrang las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:4617: kun kyang rnying ma'i chos brgyud lags //
NK130(tho)001:4618: bod du bstan pa tshugs pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:4619: deng sang bar du sangs rgyas kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4620: bstan pa'ang rnying mas bsrungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4621: sa skya pa yi gur mgon dang //
NK130(tho)001:4622: lce dang dpyal gyi stag zhon dang //
NK130(tho)001:4623: shangs pa bka' brgyud pa dag gi //
NK130(tho)001:4624: phyag drug pa yi rgyan can dang //
NK130(tho)001:4625: snar thang pa yi gri gug dang //
NK130(tho)001:4626: de bzhin do ba'i trag shad dang //
NK130(tho)001:4627: karma pa yi ber nag can //
NK130(tho)001:4628: rgyan gong rdo rje rab brtan ma //
NK130(tho)001:4629: mdor na bod kyi bstan srung rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4630: rnying ma'i bka' gter kho na yin //
NK130(tho)001:4631: lha srin gdug rtsub rnying mas btul //
NK130(tho)001:4632: rkyen ngan bar chad bzlog thabs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4633: phal cher rnying ma'i sgo nas byed //
NK130(tho)001:4634: yar mtha' sangs rgyas sgrub pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:4635: mar mtha' dgra bgegs sgrol ba yan //
NK130(tho)001:4636: dpe la ma lus lag thog khel //
NK130(tho)001:4637: rgya bod mkhas grub phal mo che'i //
NK130(tho)001:4638: gshegs shul bla na med pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4639: de kun nor na nor kyang chog /
NK130(tho)001:4640: nges shes rnyed pa'i sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:4641: bdud kyis sangs rgyas gzugs bstan te //
NK130(tho)001:4642: bsgyur yang 'gyur bar ma gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:4644: bdud kyis sangs rgyas gzugs su bsgyur nas khyod kyi de chos ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:4645: zhes sogs sgo du ma nas bzlog kyang byang chub sems dpa' bsgyur mi nus la /
NK130(tho)001:4646: me chu dang chu mer 'gyur ba la sogs pa 'byung ba chen po gzhan du 'gyur srid kyi /
NK130(tho)001:4647: chos la nges pa rnyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni mi 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:4648: zhes sogs dang brgyad stong pa las /
NK130(tho)001:4649: 'di lta ste bla na med pa'i byang chub las
NK130(tho)001:4650: brtsams nas de kho na nyid kyi gtam byed par
NK130(tho)001:4651: 'gyur / de kho na nyid kyi gtam la mngon par dga' bar 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:4652: de dag la legs par gnas shing shes rab kyi
NK130(tho)001:4653: pha rol tu phyin pa 'di la mnyam par 'jog
NK130(tho)001:4654: par 'gyur te / bdud kyis kyang dbye bar mi nus shing /
NK130(tho)001:4655: sems can gzhan dag gis ni 'dun ba'am sngags kyi
NK130(tho)001:4656: sgo nas dbye bar nus pa lta ci smos zhes
NK130(tho)001:4659: dbang dang sgrub thabs mtha' yas snang //
NK130(tho)001:4660: slob dpon pad+ma'i bla ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:4661: bla ma'i bla ma la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4662: pad+ma lta bu'i grub chen ni //
NK130(tho)001:4663: 'phags pa'i yul na dpag med byung //
NK130(tho)001:4664: de dag so so gang la yang //
NK130(tho)001:4665: dbang dang sgrub thabs yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:4667: 'di yang rang nyid mthong ba chung //
NK130(tho)001:4668: grub thob chen po a byi shis //
NK130(tho)001:4669: pu hrangs btsad po 'od sde dang //
NK130(tho)001:4670: me nyag lo ts+aa la gnang ba //
NK130(tho)001:4671: grub thob brgyad cu rtsa bzhi yi //
NK130(tho)001:4672: dbang dang rjes gnang sgrubs thabs dang //
NK130(tho)001:4673: rdzogs rim rtogs brjod la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4674: chos tshan dgu la pu sti gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:4675: rgya bod gnyis na shin tu dar //
NK130(tho)001:4676: ngo bo rje dang 'brom ston la //
NK130(tho)001:4677: tshad mar mi 'dzin su zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:4678: bka' gdams thig le bcu drug kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4679: bla ma'i dbang khrid zab mo yin //
NK130(tho)001:4681: bla ma sgrub thabs shin tu mang //
NK130(tho)001:4682: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos sa skya pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4683: lam zab bla ma'i rnal 'byor yang //
NK130(tho)001:4684: don du bla ma sgrub thabs yin //
NK130(tho)001:4685: rdo rje theg pa'i dngos grub kun //
NK130(tho)001:4686: bla ma la ni rag lus na //
NK130(tho)001:4687: de yi sgrub thabs cis mi 'thad //
NK130(tho)001:4688: dpal ldan dbus kyi gnas gyur gang //
NK130(tho)001:4689: 'khor lo mchog gi mgon po ni //
NK130(tho)001:4690: bla ma mchog ste dus rtag tu //
NK130(tho)001:4691: zhes pas gnyis med rnam rgyal du //
NK130(tho)001:4692: bla ma dkyil 'khor gtso bor gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4693: khro phu ba la mi tra dzo ki'i dbang dang sgrub thabs kyang yod do //
NK130(tho)001:4695: bod 'dir bstan pa snga dar la //
NK130(tho)001:4696: gsang ba 'dus pa'i dbang bskur dang //
NK130(tho)001:4697: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba byung //
NK130(tho)001:4698: gsang sngags rnying ma'i rgyud lnga bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:4699: rnal 'byor chen po gzhan med pa //
NK130(tho)001:4700: bla bzhed sba bzhed gnyis ka dang //
NK130(tho)001:4701: ldan dkar ma dang 'phang thang ma'i //
NK130(tho)001:4702: dkar chag gnyis ka bltas na shes //
NK130(tho)001:4703: mkhas pas dbang du byed pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4704: dkar chag khungs ma de dag las //
NK130(tho)001:4705: snga 'gyur gsang sngags rnying ma'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:4706: rdzogs chen 'gyur bar ma bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:4708: yig cha de bzhir ma bshad pas //
NK130(tho)001:4709: chos ma yin na phyis dar ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:4710: bde dgyes gdan bzhi dus 'khor sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4711: kun kyang chos ma yin par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:4712: gzhan yang khyed kyis 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:4713: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba las //
NK130(tho)001:4714: thegs pa rim dgu gsungs pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:4715: dpal ldan 'dus pa la brten cing //
NK130(tho)001:4716: de las mtho ba'ang bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4717: ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum //
NK130(tho)001:4718: 'dus pa'i bskyed rdzogs nyams len gyi //
NK130(tho)001:4719: rim pa tsam gyis so sor phye //
NK130(tho)001:4720: rgyud sde so sor phye ba min //
NK130(tho)001:4721: de skad gong du smras pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4722: a ti yo ga zhes pa de //
NK130(tho)001:4723: rdzogs chen min na ci zhig yin //
NK130(tho)001:4724: snga 'gyur gsang sngags rnying ma'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:4725: rdzogs chen 'gyur bar ma bshad dang //
NK130(tho)001:4726: man ngag lta phreng byung ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4727: theg pa rim dgu gsungs zhes pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4730: bstan pa phyis dar gsar 'gyur la //
NK130(tho)001:4731: n+aa ro mee tri sh+aan+ti dang //
NK130(tho)001:4732: dam pa rgya gar jo bo rje //
NK130(tho)001:4733: dbus 'gyur kha che bal po'i yul //
NK130(tho)001:4734: u rgyan yul du byon pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4735: pan chen mkhas shing grub pa brnyes //
NK130(tho)001:4736: sangs rgyas 'dra ba mang gis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4737: rdzogs chen gsung rgyu ma rnyed do //
NK130(tho)001:4739: pha gcig dam pa sangs rgyas la //
NK130(tho)001:4740: sangs rgyas gsang ba la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4741: rdzogs chen ston pa'i bla ma drug /
NK130(tho)001:4742: yod ces zhi byed gzhung las bshad //
NK130(tho)001:4743: rgya gar mkhas pa nyer lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:4745: sogs kyis gsung pa'i rnying ma'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:4747: gsung rgyu ma rnyed ma zer cig /
NK130(tho)001:4748: mnga' bdag chen po mi tra'i pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:4749: rdzogs chen rgya gar bdun brgyud kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4750: med pa nyid du ma sgrub cig /
NK130(tho)001:4753: rngog lo mar sogs lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:4754: kun gyis rdzogs chen ma rnyed de //
NK130(tho)001:4755: ma bsgyur ma bshad brgyud 'dzin med //
NK130(tho)001:4757: lo ts+aa ba ni de dag la //
NK130(tho)001:4758: rdzogs pa chen po ma grags kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4759: dbang mo nye shu rtsa brgyad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4760: zor mdos 'brog mis bsgyur ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:4762: rnying ma'i 'gyur byang du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:4764: mkhas pa sh+r+ai sing ha dang //
NK130(tho)001:4765: slob dpon chen po h'u ka ra //
NK130(tho)001:4766: bal po b+aa su d+ha ra'i yul //
NK130(tho)001:4767: bal po'i sa phyogs gang du yang //
NK130(tho)001:4768: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos 'di med //
NK130(tho)001:4769: rgya gar lam ring bsgrod dka' yang //
NK130(tho)001:4770: ba po lam nye grogs mang bas //
NK130(tho)001:4771: bden rdzun yul der song la dris //
NK130(tho)001:4773: 'o na grub chen o rgyan pas //
NK130(tho)001:4774: bal po thang b+hi h+aa ri na //
NK130(tho)001:4775: rnying ma'i rgya dpe dpag med snang //
NK130(tho)001:4776: bod kyi sngags pa rnams la ni //
NK130(tho)001:4777: nga yis rnying ma'i rgya dpe dang //
NK130(tho)001:4778: pan+di ta ni tshul bkug gi //
NK130(tho)001:4779: khyed rnams mang yul 'dengs byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:4780: sngags pa rnams kyis ma 'grub gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4781: mkhan chen thar pa lo ts+aa bas //
NK130(tho)001:4782: bal por rnying ma'i rgya dpe rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4783: gzigs tshul bu ston chos 'byung ltos //
NK130(tho)001:4784: dus phyis glo bo lo ts+aa ba //
