NK130(tho)001:4785: dpal ldan byang chub bya ba des //
NK130(tho)001:4786: bal po thang b+hi h+aa ri nas //
NK130(tho)001:4787: rnyed pa'i gsang ba snying po'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:4788: 'gyur gsar mdzad cing gtan la phab //
NK130(tho)001:4789: slob dpon chen po h'u ka ra //
NK130(tho)001:4790: rgya gar shar phyogs pa yin la //
NK130(tho)001:4791: 'di yis ru lu gser phreng dang //
NK130(tho)001:4792: lung chen bum smug gnyis ka ru //
NK130(tho)001:4793: gsungs pa'i rdzogs pa chen po de //
NK130(tho)001:4794: rtses thang bsam gtan gling pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4795: bshes gnyen dam pa 'ga' la grags //
NK130(tho)001:4796: chos mchog rdzogs chen snod dkon pas //
NK130(tho)001:4797: rgya gar chos skyong rgyal po dang //
NK130(tho)001:4798: sh+r+ai seng ha la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4799: pan+di ta rnams bka' bgros nas //
NK130(tho)001:4800: rdo rje gdan du gter du sbos //
NK130(tho)001:4801: rgya na med pa de ltar yin //
NK130(tho)001:4802: dngos su dam chos 'di med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4803: pha ma gnyis med rgyud rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4804: rdzogs rim mthar thug yan lag drug /
NK130(tho)001:4805: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim lnga sog /
NK130(tho)001:4806: rdzogs pa chen po khyad par med //
NK130(tho)001:4807: yang chos rgyal dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:4808: bsam yas rgya dpe rwa sgreng dpe //
NK130(tho)001:4809: rgya dpe mang po gzigs gzigs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4810: khyod kyi gzhung rnams ma rnyed do //
NK130(tho)001:4812: 'di ltar mngon sum ma snyon par //
NK130(tho)001:4813: spyir na rnying ma'i rgya dpe rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4814: phal cher bsam yas nyid na bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:4816: phur pa rtsa dum bsgyur ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:4817: rgya dpe de yang bsam yas su //
NK130(tho)001:4818: sngags pa zhig gis phul ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:4819: slob dpon pad+ma'i phyag dpe yin //
NK130(tho)001:4820: kho bo gnas mchog 'di lta bur //
NK130(tho)001:4821: slob dpon sangs rgyas dngos de yi //
NK130(tho)001:4822: phyag dper phrad pa skal ba bzang //
NK130(tho)001:4823: phyir khyer gsungs nas rol mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:4824: spos dang rgyal mtshan gdugs sogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4825: bsu ba dpag med mdzad do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4826: lo rgyus sa pan rnam thar ltos //
NK130(tho)001:4827: bcom ldan ral gri'i gsang snying yang //
NK130(tho)001:4828: bsam yas kyi ni rgya dpe las //
NK130(tho)001:4829: sha gad lo ts+aas bshus te phul //
NK130(tho)001:4830: da lta'ang rnying ma'i rgya dpe rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4831: bsam yas nyid na bzhugs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4833: mkhas grub rin chen bzang po yis //
NK130(tho)001:4834: rdzogs pa chen po'i grub mtha' bkags //
NK130(tho)001:4837: lo chen sngags log sum 'byin du //
NK130(tho)001:4838: gsang sngags 'chol par spyod pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4839: bkags pa ma gtogs rdzogs chen la //
NK130(tho)001:4840: dgag pa ci yang mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:4842: jo bo chen po a ti sha /
NK130(tho)001:4843: bod yul gdan drangs zhus nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:4844: pho brang zhi ba 'od dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:4845: lha btsun ye shes 'od kyis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4846: da lta las zad rgyal po'i khrims nyams pas //
NK130(tho)001:4847: sems can mang po log pas bslus pa 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:4848: log lta byin ci log gi sar 'thogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:4849: rdzogs chen ming btags sngags log bod du dar //
NK130(tho)001:4850: de yis rgyal khams phung ste 'di ltar gyur //
NK130(tho)001:4851: zhes sogs su 'byin bka' shog bod la bardzangasa //
NK130(tho)001:4853: de sogs bka' shog rnams kyi lan //
NK130(tho)001:4856: jo bo spyan 'dren mdzad po yin //
NK130(tho)001:4857: 'on kyang jo bo phebs pa'i dus //
NK130(tho)001:4858: gar log rgyal pos bkrongs nas med //
NK130(tho)001:4859: de phyir khyod kyi lo rgyus 'khrul //
NK130(tho)001:4861: mkhas grub chen po 'gos lo ts+aas //
NK130(tho)001:4862: dang po zur la rdzogs chen gsan //
NK130(tho)001:4863: gsang snying rdzogs chen bshad pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4864: de nas rgya gar yul rnams su //
NK130(tho)001:4865: lan grangs bcu gnyis bar du byon //
NK130(tho)001:4866: grub pa thob pa bdun bcu dang //
NK130(tho)001:4867: mkha' 'gro'i bla ma gnyis la gtugs //
NK130(tho)001:4868: mkhas grub de dag zhal 'cham par //
NK130(tho)001:4869: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos sam de //
NK130(tho)001:4870: rgya gar yul 'dir ming yang med //
NK130(tho)001:4871: chos min bstan pa yin no gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4872: de nas bod la bka' shog bardzongasa //
NK130(tho)001:4873: chos rje sa skya pan chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:4874: sdom pa gsum gyi rab dbye las //
NK130(tho)001:4875: lhas btsas zhes bya'i lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:4876: des kyang chos log sun 'byin pa //
NK130(tho)001:4877: zhes bya'i bstan bcos mdzad nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:4878: chos dang chos min phye'o zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4880: rjes su yi rang basngagasa pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4882: 'gos kyi lan gsum rgya gar byon //
NK130(tho)001:4883: gtan la phab ces de nyid bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:4884: khyed ni lan grangs bcu gnyis zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4886: bdag nyid chen po de yis ni //
NK130(tho)001:4887: zur la gsang snying gsan 'dod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4888: chos tsam ma gnang mnar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:4889: skyo ste rgya gar yul la byon //
NK130(tho)001:4890: gsang snying 'chad pa'i yul yang med //
NK130(tho)001:4891: gal te bshad na gsang snying dang //
NK130(tho)001:4892: gsang 'dus rnam bzhag phal cher mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:4893: de dag dgag pa ci la mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4894: zur la gshe phyir rnying ma bkag /
NK130(tho)001:4896: dbyang phyug nye shu rtsa brgyad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4897: cho 'phrul dpag med byung ba'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:4898: rkyang ro byang chub 'bum zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:4899: snar thang pa yi mkhas pas bshad //
NK130(tho)001:4900: 'di yis gsang ba snying po'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:4901: legs so legs so rgyal ba rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4902: zhes pa yan chad lhad med dang //
NK130(tho)001:4903: man chad lhad dang bcas pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:4904: zhes pa'i yig cha zhig kyang snang //
NK130(tho)001:4906: rje btsun dam pa rgya gar dang //
NK130(tho)001:4907: jo bo a ti sha la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4908: bod du byon pa'i pan chen rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4909: rdzogs pa che la zur gyis sdang //
NK130(tho)001:4911: rje btsun dam pa rgya gar gyis //
NK130(tho)001:4912: bod kyi chos pa thams cad la //
NK130(tho)001:4913: zur za bka' bkyon mang yod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4914: rdzogs chen bkags pa mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:4915: bstan pa'i mnga' bdag jo bo rjes //
NK130(tho)001:4916: chos 'khor bsam yas phebs pa'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:4917: rnying ma'i rgya dpe mang po gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:4919: sde brgyad mkha' 'gro'i mdzod sogs nas //
NK130(tho)001:4920: blangs pa yin nam rgya gar las //
NK130(tho)001:4921: rgya dpe 'di ni mang ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:4922: rjes su yi rang basngagasa pa mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4923: mu stegs nyi ma dngos grub kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4924: ma bsregs gong du rgya nag tu //
NK130(tho)001:4925: byon pa'i sangs rgyas phal po che //
NK130(tho)001:4926: gser 'od dam pa chen po dang //
NK130(tho)001:4928: hwa shang ma h+aa ya na dang //
NK130(tho)001:4929: bee ro dang ni sba sang shis //
NK130(tho)001:4930: bsgyur ba gzigs pas shin tu dgyes //
NK130(tho)001:4931: rgya gar yul na med pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:4933: bod rgyal rje la thal sbyar basngagasa //
NK130(tho)001:4934: lo rgyus lam yig chen mo yod //
NK130(tho)001:4935: des na rdzun gtam 'di bshol cig /
NK130(tho)001:4938: sku mched gsum dang bya yul ba //
NK130(tho)001:4939: mar pa mi la sgam po pa //
NK130(tho)001:4940: phag mo gru pa zhang tshal pa //
NK130(tho)001:4941: dus gsum mkhyen pa karma pa //
NK130(tho)001:4942: stag lung thang pa 'bri gung pa //
NK130(tho)001:4943: mkhas pa blo ldan shes rab sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4944: gangs can bstan 'dzin de dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:4945: dang por rdzogs chen gsan pa yod //
NK130(tho)001:4946: mkhas par gyur nas gnad rig pas //
NK130(tho)001:4947: phyi nas rang gi chos brgyud rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4948: rdzogs pa che la bkod pa med //
NK130(tho)001:4949: theg mchog bstan pa'i mnga' bdag sa skya pa //
NK130(tho)001:4950: dang po rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung 'dzin yang //
NK130(tho)001:4951: phyis nas ngan skyug bzhin du yal bar dor //
NK130(tho)001:4952: zur gyis sdang zhing 'ga' yis sun phyung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:4953: bcom ldan rig pa'i ral gri dang //
NK130(tho)001:4954: mtshungs med dbus pa blo gsal dang //
NK130(tho)001:4955: chos rje kun mkhyen chen po dang //
NK130(tho)001:4956: mkhyen ldan bu ston rin chen sogs //
NK130(tho)001:4957: bstan la sku drin chen rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4958: rgyal ba'i bka' dang bstan bcos rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4959: gsang sngags gsar dang rnying mar bcas //
NK130(tho)001:4960: bod na bzhugs pa thams cad bsdus //
NK130(tho)001:4962: kun gyis rdzogs pa chen po'i skor //
NK130(tho)001:4963: sangs rgyas bstan las phyir dor nas //
NK130(tho)001:4964: btang snyoms kho nar bzhag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4966: bstan 'dzin dam pa de rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:4967: dang por rdzogs chen gsan rjes su //
NK130(tho)001:4968: chos brgyud de la ma bkod pas //
NK130(tho)001:4969: rdzogs chen chos min du 'dod na //
NK130(tho)001:4970: grub thob chen po o rgyan pas //
NK130(tho)001:4971: dang por tsa mi'i sbyor drug zhus //
NK130(tho)001:4972: phyis nas 'brug pa'i chos brgyud bskyang //
NK130(tho)001:4973: nga yis bsnyen sgrub bzhi bstan na //
NK130(tho)001:4974: lung pa grub thob kyis 'gengs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:4976: rang gi chos brgyud 'brug par bkod //
NK130(tho)001:4977: de yis sbyor drug nyams sam ci //
NK130(tho)001:4978: sgam po pa yi bka' 'bum du //
NK130(tho)001:4979: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos 'di ni //
NK130(tho)001:4980: bla ma mar pa'i gsung las ni //
NK130(tho)001:4981: chos ma yin pa skad du gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:4982: nga yis bltas na sa bzhi lnga //
NK130(tho)001:4983: thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK130(tho)001:4984: chos su 'dug ces de nyid la //
NK130(tho)001:4985: rje btsun mi las gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:4986: dpal ldan dus gsum mkhyen pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:4987: chos grags rgya mtsho yan chad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4988: karma pa ni rabs bdun po //
NK130(tho)001:4989: kun kyang rnyid ma gtso bor mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:4990: bstan pa'i bdag po sa skya pa //
NK130(tho)001:4991: gdung rabs dgu yi bar dag tu //
NK130(tho)001:4992: gsang sngags rnying ma 'dzin pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:4993: yang phur sogs kyi grub thob yin //
NK130(tho)001:4994: sems klong man ngag sde sogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:4995: rdzogs chen bzung ba'i rnam thar med //
NK130(tho)001:4996: phyi nas gsar ma mdzad pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:4997: 'khor rog sku mched gnyis kyi dus //
NK130(tho)001:4998: gcung gis 'bro yi ltad mo gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:4999: dbang phyug nyer brgyad 'chams pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5000: gcen la bsnyas pas 'di skad du //
NK130(tho)001:5001: gsang sngags gsang bas 'grub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:5002: khrom la gsang ba bsgrags pa des //
NK130(tho)001:5003: da ni grub thob mi 'byung bas //
NK130(tho)001:5004: khyod rang gsar ma slob ces gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5005: chos log rig ste spangs pa min //
NK130(tho)001:5006: de phyir khyed kyi rdzun gtam 'di //
NK130(tho)001:5007: dpal ldan sa skya pa rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5008: gsan na khrel ba'i gnas min nam //
NK130(tho)001:5009: bcom ldan rig pa'i ral gri yis //
NK130(tho)001:5010: gsang ba snying po bka' ru bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:5011: gter ma rnying ma snyan brgyud sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5012: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'i //
NK130(tho)001:5013: don dang mthun na skyon med yin //
NK130(tho)001:5014: mi mthun rang bzor shes par bya //
NK130(tho)001:5015: zhes gsungs rdzogs chen bkag pa med //
NK130(tho)001:5016: chos rje kun mkhyen chen po des //
NK130(tho)001:5017: bka' 'gyur bsgrigs pa'i lo rgyus med //
NK130(tho)001:5018: gzhan stong ston pa'i lta ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5019: rdzogs chen mthun pa de gzigs nas //
NK130(tho)001:5020: a ti yo ga'i mi mthun phyogs //
NK130(tho)001:5021: a tir 'dod pa snying rje zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5022: rang stong smra ba rnams la brkyon //
NK130(tho)001:5023: lta ba 'di la thugs gtsigs mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:5024: jo nang sku 'bum chen mo na //
NK130(tho)001:5025: rnying ma'i lha khang zhig kyang mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:5026: thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston rjes //
NK130(tho)001:5027: rnying ma bka' gter mang du gsan //
NK130(tho)001:5028: nyang lugs khros ma thugs dam mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:5029: gzhan yang bla ma de dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:5030: btang snyoms bzhag ste spangs pa min //
NK130(tho)001:5031: spang na khyed ltar sun 'byin mod //
NK130(tho)001:5032: brnog chos thugs dam yin par ni //
NK130(tho)001:5033: so so'i rnam thar bltas pas shes //
NK130(tho)001:5035: g.yung ston rdo rje dpal zhes pas //
NK130(tho)001:5036: 'phangs med gser gyi me tog dang //
NK130(tho)001:5037: gsang ba snying po'i rgya dper bcas //
NK130(tho)001:5038: bu ston rin chen grub la phul //
NK130(tho)001:5040: bzhugs par gsol ba btab pa'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:5041: rgya dpe rdzun mar des rig nas //
NK130(tho)001:5042: gsol ba gsan du ma bzhed do //
NK130(tho)001:5044: 'di ni re zhig brtag pa'i gnas //
NK130(tho)001:5046: gsang snying lung 'dren mang po snang //
NK130(tho)001:5047: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor rgya 'grel der //
NK130(tho)001:5048: gsang ba snying po'i lung mang drangs //
NK130(tho)001:5049: 'grel pa de la thugs gtsigs che //
NK130(tho)001:5050: mkhan chen thar pa lo ts+aa bas //
NK130(tho)001:5051: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud phyi ma //
NK130(tho)001:5052: gsar 'gyur mdzad pa thugs la mnga' //
NK130(tho)001:5053: thar bar byon nas sgra gsan dus su bsgyur ba yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:5054: des na gtam 'di bden pa dka' //
NK130(tho)001:5055: gal te bu ston mi bzhed kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5057: de rjes pan chen bi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:5058: gnyags ston dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras //
NK130(tho)001:5059: lo ts+aa byas te yer par bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:5060: mnga' bdag ral pa can gyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:5061: 'di yi bshad bka' shin tu dar //
NK130(tho)001:5062: bar du bcom ldan ral gris bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:5063: slad du glo bo lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:5064: dpal ldan byang chub zhes byas bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:5065: dus phyis 'bri gung lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:5066: nor bu dpal yes bsgyur ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5068: de phyir klan ka rnyed pa med //
NK130(tho)001:5070: deng sang gangs ri'i khrod 'di na //
NK130(tho)001:5071: bstan pa'i bdag po gcig gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:5072: thams cad mkhyen pa kun dgas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5073: rdzogs chen chos kyi gral nas bor //
NK130(tho)001:5075: nya dbon kun dga' zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:5076: khyed kyi bla ma de nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5077: rnying ma'i rgya dpe tshad ldan yang //
NK130(tho)001:5078: rgya gar yul gyi shing shun la //
NK130(tho)001:5079: bod kyi sngags pas lany+dza dang //
NK130(tho)001:5080: rgya yig bris pa yin no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5081: zhe nas dam chos spangs mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5082: pan chen nags kyi rin chen gyis //
NK130(tho)001:5083: bsam yas rgya dpe tshad mar mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:5084: de phyir bod las rgya dpe'i nyams //
NK130(tho)001:5085: rgya gar pan chen mkhas rnams che //
NK130(tho)001:5087: lo pan mkhas pa stong nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5088: lo grangs sum brgya lhag tsam du //
NK130(tho)001:5089: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud bsgyur yang //
NK130(tho)001:5090: bdun bcu tsam las ma 'gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:5091: rdzogs chen bde 'dus la sogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5092: rgyud ni 'bum phrag lhag pa zhig /
NK130(tho)001:5093: rgyal po gcig gi sku ring la //
NK130(tho)001:5094: bsgyur ba'ang brtags na mi bden no //
NK130(tho)001:5096: bod du bstan pa tshugs pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:5097: da lta'i dus ni yan chad du //
NK130(tho)001:5098: pan chen dgu bcu rtsa bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:5099: lo ts+aa'ang nyis brgya lnga bcu las //
NK130(tho)001:5100: mkhas pa rnams kyis ma rnyed na //
NK130(tho)001:5101: khyed kyis stong phrag rnyed 'di mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:5102: mtshan rnams yi ger bris nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:5103: kun la ston pa nyid du rigs //
NK130(tho)001:5104: dgyes pa rdo rje 'bum pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:5105: rgyud sde 'bum phrag yod par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5106: mi yi yul na de lta min //
NK130(tho)001:5108: pusti sum cu rtsa bdun tsam //
NK130(tho)001:5109: byang bu re la rgyud sde re //
NK130(tho)001:5112: rgyal po gcig gi sku ring la //
NK130(tho)001:5113: de dag 'gyur bar mi spyod pa //
NK130(tho)001:5115: rgyal pos yon bdag byas nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5116: lo pan brgya dang rtsa brgyad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5117: de dag mi 'gyur zhes smra ba //
NK130(tho)001:5118: yo byad phongs sam yig mkhan med //
NK130(tho)001:5119: brtags na khyed rang mi bden no //
NK130(tho)001:5121: kun spangs thugs rje brtson 'grus dang //
NK130(tho)001:5122: chos rje rang byung rdo rje sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5123: rdzogs chen chos su smra ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:5124: phal cher gzhan sems bsrung ba tsam //
NK130(tho)001:5125: 'phags pa'i mdzad pa bsam mi khyab //
NK130(tho)001:5126: de dag so skye'i yul min te //
NK130(tho)001:5127: bdud dang lha sbyin rnam thar dang //
NK130(tho)001:5128: myang 'das chen po'i mdo sde ltos //
NK130(tho)001:5129: bdud sdig can bcom ldan 'das kyis sangs rgyas su
NK130(tho)001:5130: lung bstan pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po yin
NK130(tho)001:5131: kyang / bcom ldan 'das kyi mdzad pa'i grogs su
NK130(tho)001:5132: bdud kyi tshul du gnas te chos ma yin pa
NK130(tho)001:5133: sna tshogs ston cing bdud kyi las byed par /
NK130(tho)001:5134: dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po'i le'u bcu gnyis pa las /
NK130(tho)001:5135: lhas sbyin ma 'ongs pa na 'jig rten gyi khams lha'i them skas su /
NK130(tho)001:5136: sangs rgyas lha'i rgyal po zhes bya bar lung bstan /
NK130(tho)001:5137: lha sbyin byang chub sems dpa' chen po sangs rgyas
NK130(tho)001:5138: kyi che ba dbyung ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i
NK130(tho)001:5139: spyod pa shin tu dka' ba spyod par gsungs pa
NK130(tho)001:5140: dang / mya ngan 'das chen gyi bam po gcig pa las /
NK130(tho)001:5142: nga bskal pa bzang po 'dir mu stegs gcer bu ba la yid ches te /
NK130(tho)001:5145: sbyin pa dang mchod sbyin gyi 'bras bu yang med /
NK130(tho)001:5146: dge ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyang med /
NK130(tho)001:5147: dge ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyi rnam par smin pa yang med /
NK130(tho)001:5148: da ltar gyi dus dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyang med /
NK130(tho)001:5149: tshu rol dang pha rol yang med /
NK130(tho)001:5152: lam dang mya ngan las 'das pa med pa'i chos la gnas par gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:5154: byang chub sems dpa' yang dag par mi dge ba'i las de lta bu med mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:5155: sems can rnams grol bar bya ba'i phyir smon lam
NK130(tho)001:5156: chen po'i stobs kyis ngan par blta ba'i lta ba
NK130(tho)001:5158: de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK130(tho)001:5159: da ltar dang ma 'ongs pa dang phyis mi dge
NK130(tho)001:5160: ba'i las myong ba min pa zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:5163: kun spangs rang byung rdo rje yis //
NK130(tho)001:5164: gzhan sems bsrung phyir rdzogs chen zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5165: khyed kyis skur pa mi gdab 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:5166: spyir na gzhan gyi sems bsrung ba //
NK130(tho)001:5167: g.yo sgyu min na 'gal ba med //
NK130(tho)001:5168: khyad par chos min chos yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5169: ston pa chos spong yin par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5170: rgyal ba rang byung rdo rje yang //
NK130(tho)001:5171: de ring khyed kyis ma smad dam //
NK130(tho)001:5172: mdo sde dag gi lung de yang //
NK130(tho)001:5173: 'khyogs po nyid du ma 'dren cig /'o na khyed la 'di skad 'dri //
NK130(tho)001:5174: chos min ston cing bdud kyi las //
NK130(tho)001:5175: sna tshogs byed pa'i bdud sdig can //
NK130(tho)001:5176: byang chub sems dpa' che yin na //
NK130(tho)001:5177: de las gzhan pa'i bdud de su //
NK130(tho)001:5178: rdzogs chen bdud chos yin bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5179: chos de spyod pa'i gang zag kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5180: kun kyang byang chub sems dpar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:5181: des na de la ci phyir sdang //
NK130(tho)001:5182: gcer bu pa las thar phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:5183: gcer bu pa la 'jug dgos na //
NK130(tho)001:5184: sdig pa las ni thar phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:5187: de phyir lung de'i dgongs pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:5188: gcer bu pa rnams 'dul phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:5189: thub pas gcer bu pa'i tshul bstan //
NK130(tho)001:5190: dang po'i sangs rgyas 'jam dpal gyis //
NK130(tho)001:5191: gtsug phud phud bu lcang lo can //
NK130(tho)001:5192: ral pa muny+dza cod pan thogs //
NK130(tho)001:5193: gdod lnga gtsug phud lnga dang ldan //
NK130(tho)001:5194: zur pud lnga pa me tog thod //
NK130(tho)001:5195: de sogs tshul 'chang mu stegs byed //
NK130(tho)001:5196: 'dul phyir de dag tshul ston par //
NK130(tho)001:5197: mtshan brjod 'grel pa nyid las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5200: mu stegs can dag 'dul ba'i phyir byang chub sems
NK130(tho)001:5201: dpa' lo drug tu dka' ba spyad pa yang las
NK130(tho)001:5202: kyi sgrib pa'i rgyus ni ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:5204: bram ze rgya shug dang til dang 'bras 'bru gcig
NK130(tho)001:5205: tsam za zhing zas gzhan mi za bas rnam par
NK130(tho)001:5206: dag par 'gyur bar 'dod pa de dag tshar bcad
NK130(tho)001:5207: pa'i phyir / byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa'i lam
NK130(tho)001:5208: la ma brten par rgya shug dang til dang 'bras
NK130(tho)001:5209: 'bru gcig tsam gyi zas ngan pa za bas rnam
NK130(tho)001:5210: par dag pa mi nus pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:5212: byang chub ni mchog tu rnyed par dka' ba yin
NK130(tho)001:5213: pas dge sbyong mgo reg la byang chub ga la
NK130(tho)001:5216: rim gyis grol bar 'gyur ba'i rgyu'i bar du rgyas par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:5218: gal te 'phags pa min zer na //
NK130(tho)001:5219: 'o na des gsungs tshad ma min //
NK130(tho)001:5222: ci smras tshad ma yin pa dka' //
NK130(tho)001:5224: gang gsungs tshad dmar 'dzin pa'i yul //
NK130(tho)001:5225: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyag gcig gam //
NK130(tho)001:5226: sa la gnas pa'i 'phags pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:5227: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i lus bzung nas //
NK130(tho)001:5228: chos dang chos min shan 'byed cing //
NK130(tho)001:5229: chos min tshar gcod de yin no //
NK130(tho)001:5231: rgyal ba mchog des gdul bya'i ngor //
NK130(tho)001:5232: drang ba'i don dang nges pa'i don //
NK130(tho)001:5233: dgongs dang dgongs min ji bzhin dang //
NK130(tho)001:5234: ji bzhin ma yin pa la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5235: rnam pa sna tshogs bka' la yod //
NK130(tho)001:5236: kun kyang don ldan yin mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5237: nges pa don gyi mdo sde de //
NK130(tho)001:5238: drang don pa la tshad mar min //
NK130(tho)001:5239: drang ba'i don gyi mdo sde yang //
NK130(tho)001:5240: nges don pa la tshad mar min //
NK130(tho)001:5241: de 'dra'i gnas skabs du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:5242: sa la gnas pa'i 'phags pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:5243: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i mchog gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:5244: byams mgon spyan ras gzigs sogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5245: chos dang chos min shan 'byed pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5246: bstan bcos mdzad pa'ang ma mthong la //
NK130(tho)001:5247: khyad par gsang sngags bkags pa med //
NK130(tho)001:5249: klu sgrub ar+ya de ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5250: thogs med chos grags ma khol sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5251: rgyal ba nyid kyis bstan 'dzin du //
NK130(tho)001:5252: lung bstan de dag tshad ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:5254: mkhas mchog 'dzam gling rgyan de dag /
NK130(tho)001:5255: tshad ma yin par kun la grags //
NK130(tho)001:5256: de dag rnams kyi gsung rabs su //
NK130(tho)001:5257: rdzogs chen bkags pa mi gada'o //
NK130(tho)001:5259: gzhan du gtan tshigs sna tshogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5260: brtags na yid ches gnas min pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5261: rdzun gzhung 'di la log sred kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5262: kha 'dzin byed pa'i gang zag kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5264: lto phyir 'brang ba'i g.yo sgyu dang //
NK130(tho)001:5265: shes med blun pa'i log sred gsum //
NK130(tho)001:5266: gang rung zhig tu nges pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5267: bkag la skyon spong ci 'dra yod //
NK130(tho)001:5271: 'phags pa'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i shes
NK130(tho)001:5272: byed du sangs rgyas kyis gcer bu pa las thar
NK130(tho)001:5273: phyin du gcer bu par skye ba bzhes /
NK130(tho)001:5274: zhes mdo sde'i dgongs don log par bkral ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:5275: sa gnas kyi sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang chos dang
NK130(tho)001:5276: chos min ma phye na bstan pa 'dzin pa'i gral
NK130(tho)001:5277: nas phud pa ltar gyur snang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:5278: thub pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho la /
NK130(tho)001:5279: rang bzo'i dug chu ches mang bsres //
NK130(tho)001:5280: zhes pa 'dis gsar ma'i rgyud sde rnam dag rnams kyang dri ma can du btang 'dug pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:5281: man ngag lta phreng rnying ma yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:5282: de'i a ti yo ga rdzogs chen min pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:5283: de'i theg pa rim dgu bskyed rdzogs kyis phye ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:5284: rgyud sde ma phye zhes byas pa 'dis /
NK130(tho)001:5285: 'o na rdzogs rim la theg pa dbye ba byed na /
NK130(tho)001:5288: rim pa lnga la sogs pa yang theg pa ru mi 'gyur ram /
NK130(tho)001:5289: de la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK130(tho)001:5290: gter gyi skabs su bstan pa nub pa dang chos 'byung bar byas /
NK130(tho)001:5291: ji ltar chos log dar gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:5292: de ltar yang dag dam chos nub //
NK130(tho)001:5293: de phyir bstan pa'i bya ra ba //
NK130(tho)001:5294: yod na chos la brtag par bya //
NK130(tho)001:5295: zhes pa'ang chos nub na chos la brtag rgyu ga la 'ong /
NK130(tho)001:5296: de la sogs pa tha snyad kyi tshig rang yang log pa ches mang po dang /
NK130(tho)001:5297: nyams dang rtogs pa shan ma phyed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:5298: chos nyid rtogs pa'i rnam rtog spros pa rnams sgom ma yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:5299: gnas lugs phyag rgya chen po thabs su 'dod pa
NK130(tho)001:5300: la sogs pa don gyi nor ba mtha' yas pa
NK130(tho)001:5301: dang / gong 'og kun tu rang gi gzhung tshig snga phyi 'gal ba shin tu mang bas na /
NK130(tho)001:5302: gzhan yang gtan tshig sna tshogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:5303: brtags na yid ches gnas min pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5304: rdzun gzhung 'di la zhes bkod snang ba yang khyed rang gi gzhung 'dir 'dug la /
NK130(tho)001:5306: kha 'dzin byed pa'i gang zag kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5309: rang nyid mkhas 'dod dang grags pa la sogs pa'i phyir gyur ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:5310: khyed kyi lung dang rig pa thams cad 'khyogs po'i lam du drangs pas na /
NK130(tho)001:5311: tshigs su bcad pa de dag khyed rang bstan bcos dang bcas pa'i thog tu babs par snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:5312: bkag la skyon spong ci 'dra yod //
NK130(tho)001:5313: ces pa la bdag cag gi bstan bcos 'dir /
NK130(tho)001:5314: mdo rgyud kyi lung rnams kyang dgongs don phyin ci ma log par ji lta ba bzhin du bris /
NK130(tho)001:5315: tha snyad kyi rig pa yang rdzun dang rmongs zhen gyis ma spags /
NK130(tho)001:5316: 'khyogs bshad du ma byas 'di nyid do //
NK130(tho)001:5319: rdzogs chen rgyal ba'i bkar sgrub pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5320: gtan tshigs yang dag cig yod ces //
NK130(tho)001:5321: de yi ngag la brtag par bya //
NK130(tho)001:5322: phal cher gtan tshigs med mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5323: thub pa'i bstan pa nyams dma' zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5324: skye rgu bdud kyi dbang du song //
NK130(tho)001:5325: log pa'i lam la zhen par zad //
NK130(tho)001:5327: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa des //
NK130(tho)001:5328: gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i mdo sde las //
NK130(tho)001:5329: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i theg pa mchog /
NK130(tho)001:5331: thub mchog mya ngan 'das pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:5332: lo ni nyer brgyad lon pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5333: rgyal po dzahyi khang steng du //
NK130(tho)001:5334: pusti glegs bam char du babs //
NK130(tho)001:5335: de nas rim gyis rgya gar du //
NK130(tho)001:5336: dar zhes sangs rgyas gsang ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5337: slob dpon bi shwa mi tra dang //
NK130(tho)001:5338: brgya byin sdong pos mdzad pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:5339: rgya 'grel rnams na gsal bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:5340: dga' rab 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang //
NK130(tho)001:5341: rgyal po d+aa na ta lo dang //
NK130(tho)001:5342: rgyal bu r+aa dza ha ti dang //
NK130(tho)001:5343: wa ra ni dang klu 'jog po //
NK130(tho)001:5344: gnod sbyin mo dang ba ri ni //
NK130(tho)001:5345: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang dang //
NK130(tho)001:5346: bu d+ha ku ku r+aa dza dang //
NK130(tho)001:5347: u rgyan mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dza //
NK130(tho)001:5348: go ma de bi a lo k+ai //
NK130(tho)001:5349: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:5350: drang srong pak+shi ta dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:5351: bdag nyid ma dang klu sgrub dang //
NK130(tho)001:5352: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:5354: sh+r+ai seng ha dang kun dga' mo //
NK130(tho)001:5355: rdzogs chen smra ba de dag kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5356: dang po nyid du byon pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:5357: kun dga' mo dang sh+r+ai seng ha //
NK130(tho)001:5358: gnyis la bee ro tsa nas zhus //
NK130(tho)001:5359: de yis bod du dar bar mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:5360: thub pa'i bstan pa nyams dma' bas //
NK130(tho)001:5361: skye rgu bdud kyi dbang du song //
NK130(tho)001:5362: log pa'i lam la zhen pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:5363: gang zag 'byung bar thub pas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5365: des shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa phyir bcil bar 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:5366: de bcil na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK130(tho)001:5367: 'das rnams kyi thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes nyid
NK130(tho)001:5369: de bcil na dam pa'i chos phyir bcil bar 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:5370: de bcil na de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyan thos kyi dge 'dun phyir bcil bar 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:5371: de bcil ba de lta na ni sangs rgyas dang
NK130(tho)001:5372: chos dang dge 'dun la thams cad nas thams cad
NK130(tho)001:5373: rnam pa thams cad du thams cad las phyi rol
NK130(tho)001:5375: ches gzhal du med cing mi dge ba'i las tshan
NK130(tho)001:5376: chen po mngon par 'du byed pa yongs su 'dzin
NK130(tho)001:5378: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bcil bar ci la 'gyur na /
NK130(tho)001:5381: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid /
NK130(tho)001:5384: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa /
NK130(tho)001:5385: sangs rgyas kyi yum rnams ni don gcig ming gi rnam grangs yin te /
NK130(tho)001:5387: gang don dam pa'i bden pa de ni 'jig rten las 'das pa /
NK130(tho)001:5388: rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa /
NK130(tho)001:5389: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i slad du
NK130(tho)001:5390: rang gi sems kyis yongs su brtags pa'i chos dang
NK130(tho)001:5391: bral ba / gzhon nu ma rnams kyis me long la pra bab pa bzhin du /
NK130(tho)001:5392: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi rang gi sems kyi 'od
NK130(tho)001:5393: gsal mngon sum du nam mkha' la snang ba 'dod
NK130(tho)001:5394: pa'i don gyi 'bras bu ster ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:5395: 'bras bu ni 'gyur ba med pa'i bde ba ye shes kyi sems so //
NK130(tho)001:5396: sems 'di gnyis gcig pa nyid ni shes rab dang
NK130(tho)001:5397: thabs kyi bdag nyid rdo rje'i rnal 'byor don chen
NK130(tho)001:5398: po mchog tu mi 'gyur ba dang po'i sangs rgyas
NK130(tho)001:5399: ris med pa dus kyi 'khor lo bcom ldan 'das
NK130(tho)001:5400: rdo rje sems dpar rgyud gzhan thams cad du rab
NK130(tho)001:5401: tu grags so // bcom ldan 'das de nyid ni
NK130(tho)001:5402: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa pha rol tu phyin
NK130(tho)001:5404: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa /
NK130(tho)001:5406: zhes gsungs te zhes pas so //
NK130(tho)001:5407: de bas gtan tshigs rnam dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:5408: rdzogs chen rgyal ba'i bkar sgrub pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5409: ngag 'di nyid la legs brtags nas //
NK130(tho)001:5410: ji ltar nus pa'i lan thob dang //
NK130(tho)001:5411: slar yang log rtog bsal bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:5413: sangs rgyas 'das nas mi lo stong //
NK130(tho)001:5414: bzhi brgya lnga bcu rtsa dgu na //
NK130(tho)001:5415: ma kha'i yul du kla klo'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:5416: mi bzad lta ba ngan pa byung //
NK130(tho)001:5417: rgya gar phyogs bzhi kun tu khyabs //
NK130(tho)001:5419: shar nub kha phye thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:5420: kla klo'i chos lugs 'ba' zhig dar //
NK130(tho)001:5421: da dung lo grangs stong lhag tu //
NK130(tho)001:5422: lta ba ngan pa de gnas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5423: gtan tshigs bzang po de la med //
NK130(tho)001:5424: de ltar sangs rgyas 'das nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:5425: lo stong brgyad brgyar nye ba na //
NK130(tho)001:5426: bdud ris rgyal po khri dar mas //
NK130(tho)001:5427: bod yul sangs rgyas bstan pa bsnubs //
NK130(tho)001:5428: de rjes bdud dang lhan cig tu //
NK130(tho)001:5429: chos log rdzogs pa chen po dang //
NK130(tho)001:5430: mkhas grub du mas sun phyungs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5431: da dung skye rgu de la zhen //
NK130(tho)001:5433: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa des //
NK130(tho)001:5434: nga ni mya ngan 'das pa nas //
NK130(tho)001:5435: lo ni nyis stong lnga brgya na //
NK130(tho)001:5436: bod du dam chos dar 'gyur zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5437: lha mo dri med mdo las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5438: khri srong lde'u btsan byon dus yin //
NK130(tho)001:5439: de nas rgyal po dar ma'i bar //
NK130(tho)001:5440: gdung rabs rim pa gnyis yod pas //
NK130(tho)001:5441: khyed kyis lo yi grangs kyang 'khrul //
NK130(tho)001:5442: de tshe bee ro'i snga 'gyur lnga //
NK130(tho)001:5443: bi ma la yi phyis 'gyur dang //
NK130(tho)001:5444: kun byed la sogs rdzogs chen rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:5445: lo ts+aa so sos byas pa las //
NK130(tho)001:5446: bee ro la sogs spyugs zer zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5448: rdzogs chen byung zhes smra ba 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:5450: sngon du skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:5451: stong nyid snying rje'i nyams len dang //
NK130(tho)001:5452: sems can kun don bsngo ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5453: chos dang 'dra ba mang yod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5456: dngos gzhi stong nyid snying rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:5457: mjug don yongs su bsngo ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:5458: byang chub lam gyi snying po yin //
NK130(tho)001:5459: sangs rgyas skyabs su song tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:5460: yang dag dge bsnyen yin no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5461: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de la dgyes //
NK130(tho)001:5462: khyed ni bstan pa'i nang nas 'bud //
NK130(tho)001:5465: bar du gcod pa'i chos log dgu //
NK130(tho)001:5466: rdzun rgyud rnams la nyer gnas phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5467: dug can kha zas zhim pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:5468: 'gro ba bslu ba'i chos su snang //
NK130(tho)001:5469: gsar du rang bzo byas pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5470: mkhas grub bla ma'i brgyud pa med //
NK130(tho)001:5471: chos la gzu lum ches pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5472: brgyud pa gong ma'i byin rlabs yal //
NK130(tho)001:5473: yang dag cho ga med pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5474: chos brgyud dbang gi chu bo skam //
NK130(tho)001:5475: blun po'i ngan rtog stong 'dres pas //
NK130(tho)001:5476: snyan brgyud man ngag zam shing chab //
NK130(tho)001:5477: rdzun lung brgya yis 'chad dgos pas //
NK130(tho)001:5478: bshad pa'i tshig brgyud 'dre la shor //
NK130(tho)001:5479: dam pa'i gzhung dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5480: lam gyi go rim phyin ci log /
NK130(tho)001:5481: snying po'i zab don nor ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5482: nyams nyen don brgyud bdud kyis zin //
NK130(tho)001:5483: rdzun rgyud dpang por 'dzin dgos pas //
NK130(tho)001:5485: dam pa'i chos la dbang zos dang //
NK130(tho)001:5486: dad ldan sems can bslus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5487: dam chos 'drar snang bstan pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5488: rgyal ba'i sras kyi pham pas phog /
NK130(tho)001:5489: gsang sngags rang bzor mi bya zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5490: rgyal bas gsungs pa khyad bsad pas //
NK130(tho)001:5491: bde gshegs bka' las 'das gyur cing //
NK130(tho)001:5492: dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu gzhan yang //
NK130(tho)001:5493: yang dag rgyud gzhung smad pa las //
NK130(tho)001:5494: rtsa ba'i ltung ba drug pa byung //
NK130(tho)001:5495: phyag rgya chen po'i lam bor nas //
NK130(tho)001:5496: bcu gcig pa dang dgu pas zin //
NK130(tho)001:5497: ma thos thos dang ma mthong mthong //
NK130(tho)001:5498: ma thob thob ces smra ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5499: sprul dang skye pa nga yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5500: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa'ang zhig /
NK130(tho)001:5501: theg mchog snying po'i nyams len la //
NK130(tho)001:5502: nges par bar du gcod pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:5503: 'di dgu tshang ba'i rdzun gter ston rnams /
NK130(tho)001:5505: zhugs kyang cir 'gyur zhib mor soms //
NK130(tho)001:5507: 'gal ba'i phung po 'di dag la lan gdab ma dgos mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:5508: 'on kyang bzhad gad tsam du brjod na /
NK130(tho)001:5509: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan dang //
NK130(tho)001:5510: dar ma 'das rjes byung zer zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5511: gsar du rang bzo byas zhes pa //
NK130(tho)001:5512: 'di las mtshar ba'i gtam ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:5513: rang bzo gsar du byas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5514: brgyud pa gong ma'i byin rlabs yal //
NK130(tho)001:5515: zhes pa'i tshig kyang dpyad par bya //
NK130(tho)001:5516: gong du brgyud pa yod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5517: de la byin rlabs yod pa na //
NK130(tho)001:5518: khyed kyis skur ba 'debs ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5519: mkhas grub bla brgyud med pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5520: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs yal ces pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5522: mkhas grub bla brgyud med bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5523: byin rlabs yal rgyu ci zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:5524: rdzogs chen rang bzo yin bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5525: snyan brgyud zam shing chag rgyu ci //
NK130(tho)001:5526: sngon du skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:5527: stong nyid snying rje'i nyams len dang //
NK130(tho)001:5528: mjug don yongs su bsngo ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5529: chos dang 'dra ba yod bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5530: dam pa'i gzhung dang ga la 'gal //
NK130(tho)001:5531: lam gyi go rim ci phyir log /
NK130(tho)001:5532: stong nyid snying rje nyams len na //
NK130(tho)001:5533: snying po'i zab don ci la nor //
NK130(tho)001:5534: don brgyud bdud kyis ga la zin //
NK130(tho)001:5535: rdzun lung brgya yis 'chad ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5536: de nyid chos kyi snying po yin //
NK130(tho)001:5537: gal te de ni rdzun lung na //
NK130(tho)001:5538: khyed kyis sangs rgyas bstan pa la //
NK130(tho)001:5540: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed nas bzung ste //
NK130(tho)001:5541: stong nyid snying rje nyams su len //
NK130(tho)001:5542: yongs su bsngo ba'i bar byed na //
NK130(tho)001:5543: chos la dbang zos ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:5544: sangs rgyas sgrub pa'i chos ston pas //
NK130(tho)001:5545: sems can slu ba ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:5546: stong nyid snying rje'i nyams len sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5547: dam chos 'drar snang ston pa ru //
NK130(tho)001:5548: 'dod pa blun po khyod min su //
NK130(tho)001:5549: gsang sngags rang bzor byas kyang sla //
NK130(tho)001:5550: gsar rnying rgyud sde phal cher la //
NK130(tho)001:5551: khyod kyis skur pa btab pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5552: rtsa ltung drug pa khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5553: rdzogs pa chen po sun 'byin phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5554: mdo rgyud bstan bcos rnams kyi lung //
NK130(tho)001:5556: dam chos 'drar snang bstan pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:5557: rgyal sras pham pa'ang khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5558: chos la chos su mi 'dzin pas //
NK130(tho)001:5559: dkon mchog gsum la gsum mi 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:5560: de yi tshul yang khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5561: rgyal ba rang byung rdo rje dang //
NK130(tho)001:5562: mtshungs med g.yag sde pan chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:5563: thugs dam snying po rdzogs pa che //
NK130(tho)001:5564: rang gi bla ma'i chos smad pas //
NK130(tho)001:5565: rdo rje slob dpon brnyas pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5566: rtsa lhung dang po khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5567: snying po'i don la ma mos kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5568: smad pa nyid du mi bya ste //
NK130(tho)001:5569: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5570: don nyid dran zhes rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5571: bde gshegs bka' las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5572: rtsa ltung gnyis pa khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5574: chos kyi rtsa ba byang sems nyams //
NK130(tho)001:5575: rtsa lhung lnga pa khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5576: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:5577: som nyi za phyir dgu bas zin //
NK130(tho)001:5578: mthar thug don la skur btabs pas //
NK130(tho)001:5579: bcu gcig pa yang khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5580: dad ldan sems can blo bsgyur bas //
NK130(tho)001:5581: bcu gnyis pa yang khyed la phog /
NK130(tho)001:5582: theg mchog snying po'i nyams len la //
NK130(tho)001:5583: nges par bar du gcod pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:5584: khyod kyi bstan bcos 'di min nam //
NK130(tho)001:5586: dam chos gter nas byung ba la //
NK130(tho)001:5587: dbang lung don brgyud snyan brgyud kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5588: brgyud pa ma chad shin tu dka' //
NK130(tho)001:5589: de phyir sngags la 'di mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:5591: gter ma sngags la mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:5592: rgyal ba 'das pa'i dbu thod nas //
NK130(tho)001:5593: sangs rgyas thod pa'i glegs bam phyungs //
NK130(tho)001:5594: ma h+aa m+aa ya'i rgyud sde yang //
NK130(tho)001:5595: ku ku ri pa'i gter chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:5596: de la sogs pa du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:5597: gnyan lo'i ku ru kul+le dang //
NK130(tho)001:5598: sems khrid yid bzhin nor bu dang //
NK130(tho)001:5599: rdzogs rim rlung sems dbyer med dang //
NK130(tho)001:5600: ro snyams dang ni chos drug sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5601: sngags kyi glegs bam gter ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:5602: gsang sngags gsar ma'i khrod na'ang mang //
NK130(tho)001:5603: dbang lung snyan brgyud don brgyud sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5604: yod kyang khyod yid mi ches mod //
NK130(tho)001:5605: grub thob mang du byon pa la //
NK130(tho)001:5606: dbang lung don brgyud med do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5607: chos dang gang zag mi smad 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:5609: bsod nams sdud pa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK130(tho)001:5610: sred med bu yis zhus pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:5611: kun tu rgyu yi lo rgyus ltar //
NK130(tho)001:5612: mdo sde gter nas 'byung ba srid //
NK130(tho)001:5613: de yang sangs rgyas 'byung ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5614: dam chos gnas dus mi 'byung ste //
NK130(tho)001:5615: bstan pa nub par gyur ba'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:5616: skal ba can la srid mtha' tsam //
NK130(tho)001:5617: bsod nams thams cad sdud pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:5618: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ni nam
NK130(tho)001:5619: yang de bzhin gshegs pa mya ngan las 'da' bar
NK130(tho)001:5620: mi 'gyur la / dam pa'i chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur bar rig par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:5622: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni 'jig
NK130(tho)001:5623: rten gyi khams gzhan na 'dug kyang rung sangs rgyas
NK130(tho)001:5624: rnams zhal ston par mdzad cing chos kyang thos par
NK130(tho)001:5625: mdzad do // chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK130(tho)001:5626: rnams kyi chos kyi gter ri dang ri su la
NK130(tho)001:5627: dang shing dag gi nang du bcug pa dag yod
NK130(tho)001:5628: mdzad do // de / gzungs dang chos kyi sgo
NK130(tho)001:5629: mtha' yas pa glegs bam du byas pa dag kyang
NK130(tho)001:5631: zhes dang bslab btus su sred med kyi bu'i mdo'i bu 'drangs par yang de bzhin du byung la /
NK130(tho)001:5632: mdzangs blun gyi le'u gsum pa kun tu rgyus tshul khrims bsrung ba'i le'ura yang /
NK130(tho)001:5633: sangs rgyas 'od srung gi bstan pa nub tu nye
NK130(tho)001:5634: ba na bram ze kun tu rgyu gnyis kyis bsnyen
NK130(tho)001:5635: gnas kyi sdom pa zhus te /
NK130(tho)001:5637: gcig rgyal por skye bar smon lam btab /
NK130(tho)001:5638: lhar smon pa de chung mas bsdigs pas dus ma yin par zas zos pas klur skyes /
NK130(tho)001:5640: rgyal po de'i bza' shing gir pa'i srung mas shing
NK130(tho)001:5641: thog ku shu kha dog dang dri srung ldan pa
NK130(tho)001:5642: zhig rnyed / de rim gyis rgyal po'i phyag tu
NK130(tho)001:5643: phyin pa phyin chad rtag tu 'di 'dra ba ma
NK130(tho)001:5644: byung na lus du bur bya zer /
NK130(tho)001:5645: bza' shing gir ba'i srung ma mya ngan gyis klubs pa klus thos /
NK130(tho)001:5646: mir sprul te ku shu gser gzhong bkang ba rgyal po la bskur te bsnyen gnas kyi dpe dgos /
NK130(tho)001:5647: ma byung na rgyal khams mtshor btang zer /
NK130(tho)001:5648: rgyal po bred de blun por tshol du bcug des dpe ma rnyed de /
NK130(tho)001:5649: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa nub zin pas re thag
NK130(tho)001:5650: chad mya ngan gyis ngo nag pa phas rig ste
NK130(tho)001:5651: / bdag gi khyim na k+aa ba zhig las 'od 'byung ba yod pas der ltos dang zer /
NK130(tho)001:5652: bltas pas rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi mdo dang bsnyen gnas kyi dpe byung /
NK130(tho)001:5653: klu dang rgyal pos khrims bsrungs pas gnyis ka lhar skyes /
NK130(tho)001:5654: phyis mnyan yod du bcom ldan 'das la chos nyan pas rgyun zhugs thob par gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:5655: lung snga ma gnyis kyi don yang bstan pa nub
NK130(tho)001:5656: pa'i dus su chos gter 'byung bar gsal te chos
NK130(tho)001:5657: 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la bstan pa nub
NK130(tho)001:5658: mi srid bar bstan pa'i shugs kyis gzhan la nub
NK130(tho)001:5660: khyod kyi gter chos 'di dag ni //
NK130(tho)001:5661: dpang du gyur pa'i chos min te //
NK130(tho)001:5662: tshig don cho ga nor ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5663: blun po'i lag rjes yin par gsal //
NK130(tho)001:5664: lar ni mnyan bya'i dam chos la //
NK130(tho)001:5665: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis gsungs nges dang //
NK130(tho)001:5666: mkhas grub dam pas bshad nges dang //
NK130(tho)001:5667: mkhas rnams dpang du mdzad nges dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5669: de dag dgos pa cis kyang 'thad //
NK130(tho)001:5670: sangs rgyas bzhugs dus zab mo'i gter //
NK130(tho)001:5672: phung po lnga po bstan pa'i mdo //
NK130(tho)001:5674: nang na gter du bzhugs pa la //
NK130(tho)001:5675: thub dbang 'khor bcas der byon pas //
NK130(tho)001:5676: ngo mtshar ltas byung de'i rgyu zhus //
NK130(tho)001:5677: mdo 'di'i de'i nang bzhugs zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5678: 'khor gyis zhus pas mdo sde gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5679: de bzhin gsang ba'i ring bsrel gzungs //
NK130(tho)001:5680: bram ze dri med legs snang gis //
NK130(tho)001:5681: rgyal ba spyan drangs lam kha na //
NK130(tho)001:5682: mchod rten rnying ma'i sa phung zhig /
NK130(tho)001:5683: de las sgra 'od sna tshogs byung //
NK130(tho)001:5684: rgyal bas phyag mdzad bskor zhing bshums //
NK130(tho)001:5685: phyag na rdo rjes de'i rgyu zhus //
NK130(tho)001:5686: 'di nang gzungs kyi gter yod gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5687: gzungs de gsung du gsol zhes zhus //
NK130(tho)001:5688: de tshe gzungs dang phan yon gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5689: sangs rgyas dpe la ma ltos pas //
NK130(tho)001:5690: glegs bam dbyung bar ma mdzad kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5691: don du 'di gnyis gter chos yin //
NK130(tho)001:5692: bstan pa nub kyang byang sems la //
NK130(tho)001:5693: chos dang chos kyi gter 'byung na //
NK130(tho)001:5694: de la gzhan gyis zhus pas chog /
NK130(tho)001:5695: bstan pa nub pa ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:5696: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:5697: dgongs nas sangs rgyas zhal ston la //
NK130(tho)001:5698: chos kyang thos par mdzad bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5699: chos gter de la dgos pa ci //
NK130(tho)001:5701: khyad par hor bod rgya nag tu //
NK130(tho)001:5702: lo pan mkhas pas bsgyur nges dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5703: de 'dra ches mang bzhugs bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5704: log pa'i lam la zhen pa mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:5706: bod du chos kyi dag ther la //
NK130(tho)001:5707: rgya nag dang ni hor yul du //
NK130(tho)001:5708: bsgyur ba dgos na ha cang thal //
NK130(tho)001:5709: rgya nag dang ni hor yul du //
NK130(tho)001:5710: med pa'i mdo rgyud ches mang ba //
NK130(tho)001:5711: o rgyan ka che sham+b+ha la //
NK130(tho)001:5712: rgya bal bod na shin tu mang //
NK130(tho)001:5714: khyod kyi rdzun gzhung 'di dag la //
NK130(tho)001:5715: nor ba'i phung po mthong bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5716: rgyal dang de sras dam pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:5717: khung ma yin par ji ltar sgrub //
NK130(tho)001:5719: rnying ma'i gzhung gdams nor srid kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5720: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:5721: de rang ma nor ba yis chog /
NK130(tho)001:5722: de la slar yang sgrub ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5724: 'ga' la lhad kyis spags srid kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5725: tshig don nor ba ma mchis shing //
NK130(tho)001:5726: yid ches gnas gyur cig ston cing //
NK130(tho)001:5728: ji ltar mkhris nad can gyis dung //
NK130(tho)001:5729: dkar po de'ang ser por mthong //
NK130(tho)001:5730: de bzhin lhad med rnying ma'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:5731: bstan yang khyed kyis lhad du mthong //
NK130(tho)001:5732: lhad kyis sbags nas ma nor ba //
NK130(tho)001:5733: gcig kyang med ces ma smra zhig /
NK130(tho)001:5734: mu stegs byed gzhung 'ga' zhig tu //
NK130(tho)001:5735: dge sdig las 'bras bstan pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:5736: de yi tshig don nor ba med //
NK130(tho)001:5737: las 'bras yid ches gnas yin mod //
NK130(tho)001:5739: khyod kyis rang yid ches ce na //
NK130(tho)001:5740: kla klo rnams dang bon po'i lugs //
NK130(tho)001:5741: ma brtags pa nas yid ches pa //
NK130(tho)001:5742: 'di ni blun po'i chos nyid yin //
NK130(tho)001:5743: chos min chos su mos pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:5744: blun dang mi dge'i rnam smin te //
NK130(tho)001:5745: yon tan med la gus pa'ang //
NK130(tho)001:5746: de blun mi dge'i las zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5748: spyir na yid ches brtags las 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:5749: ma brtags pa la yid ches med //
NK130(tho)001:5750: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang gis //
NK130(tho)001:5751: rang dang chos dang slob dpon te //
NK130(tho)001:5752: yid ches rnam pa gsum du gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5753: yid ches rnams kyi nang nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:5754: rang yid ches pa mchog yin ces //
NK130(tho)001:5755: rje btsun mi la ras pa bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:5756: yid ches tshig kyang mi bslu zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5757: slob dpon chos kyi grags pas bshad //
NK130(tho)001:5758: yid ches chos kyis mi 'grub na //
NK130(tho)001:5759: yid ma ches pa'i the tshom de //
NK130(tho)001:5760: dngos grub kun gyi gegs su gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5762: kha cig mngon shes ma thob na //
NK130(tho)001:5763: chos dang chos min mi shes lo //
NK130(tho)001:5764: mig ldan me long blta ba la //
NK130(tho)001:5765: mngon par shes pa ga la dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5767: mig ldan me long blta ba la //
NK130(tho)001:5768: mngon par shes pa mi dgos kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5769: chos dang chos min 'byed pa la //
NK130(tho)001:5770: chos mig rdul bral thob pa dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5771: so so skye bo'i mkhas pas min //
NK130(tho)001:5773: tshig dang don dam cho ga la //
NK130(tho)001:5774: gtsug lag gnyis dang 'gal ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:5775: skyon de nye bar ma mthong na //
NK130(tho)001:5776: mngon shes med par dgag mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:5778: skyon rnams nye bar ma mthong na //
NK130(tho)001:5779: de la dgag tu ci zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:5780: mkhyog pos drang po nyes zer ram //
NK130(tho)001:5782: sngon tshe nyan thos 'ba' zhig gis //
NK130(tho)001:5783: ldem por dgongs pa ma shes shing //
NK130(tho)001:5784: sngar ma thos pa dpang byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:5785: skyon med bzhin du theg chen bkags //
NK130(tho)001:5786: de tshe shes byed med bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5787: 'gog pa chos mig thob bam zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5788: mdo sde rgyan du byams pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:5789: gtan tshigs 'ga' yis bka' ru bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:5790: gal te rdzogs pa chen po yang //
NK130(tho)001:5791: bka' ru sgrub pa'i shes byed bzang //
NK130(tho)001:5792: 'gog la gtan tshigs med mthong na //
NK130(tho)001:5793: mkhas pa rnams kyis blangs bar 'os //
NK130(tho)001:5794: rgyud rnams rgyud 'bum nang du gzhug /
NK130(tho)001:5795: bstan bcos bstan 'gyur nang du gzhug /
NK130(tho)001:5796: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i nang du bcug /
NK130(tho)001:5797: mchod cing basngagasa pa'i 'os yin mod //
NK130(tho)001:5799: rgyud rnams rgyud 'bum bcug tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:5800: yang dag 'grub pa ches dka' ste //
NK130(tho)001:5801: sngags tu nor ba phal cher dang //
NK130(tho)001:5802: pad+ma d+r+wa ba'i rgyud dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:5803: gtsug tor dgu pa la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:5804: ha cang tshig sbyor legs drag pas //
NK130(tho)001:5805: pan+di ta yis byas sam zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5806: the tshom btang snyoms bzhag sogs mang //
NK130(tho)001:5809: gtan tshigs zab cing barlinga la mang //
NK130(tho)001:5810: bka' ru sgrub pa'i shes byed med //
NK130(tho)001:5811: de phyir bstan pa'i gral nas dor //
NK130(tho)001:5812: tshig dang don dang cho ga la //
NK130(tho)001:5813: nor ba mngon sum mthong ba na //
NK130(tho)001:5814: lung dang rig pas de 'gog phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5815: mngon par shes pas ci zhig bya //
NK130(tho)001:5816: sngon tshe rgyal ba thub dbang la //
NK130(tho)001:5817: thams cad mkhyen nam mi mkhyen zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5818: rgyal po bram ze khyim bdag rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5819: nyams sad byas tshul 'dul bar gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5820: thub dbang nyid kyang brtags dgos na //
NK130(tho)001:5821: de yi gsung rabs smos ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5822: brtags nas 'dor len byed pa de //
NK130(tho)001:5823: rnam pa kun tu mkhas pa'i lugs //
NK130(tho)001:5824: chos min shes nas tshar gcod cing //
NK130(tho)001:5825: dam chos shes nas 'dzin pa de //
NK130(tho)001:5826: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bstan 'dzin te //
NK130(tho)001:5827: shes nas dad pa dad pa'i mchog /
NK130(tho)001:5828: rgya gar yul na'ang phyi nang sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5829: grub mtha' rgol dang phyi rgol rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5830: lung dang rig pas bya dgos kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5831: mngon par shes pas ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:5832: rgyal dang de sras mkhas grub rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5833: grub mtha' ngan pa 'gog pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:5834: bka' dang bstan bcos thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:5835: rig pa kho nas legs par bstan //
NK130(tho)001:5836: ji srid rig pa ma bstan pa //
NK130(tho)001:5837: de srid khengs pa can de rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5838: kun mkhyen gyi yang dpang min zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5839: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de skad gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5840: gal te chos min yin shes na //
NK130(tho)001:5841: sngon du legs par zhus zin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5842: thar pa'i bar du gcod pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5843: smod cing spang bar sangs rgyas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5844: thub pas lhag spyod rings 'phur la //
NK130(tho)001:5846: bcom ldan 'das mngon par byung nas yangs pa can
NK130(tho)001:5847: gyi grong khyer sgyu rtsal shes kyi bu rings 'phur
NK130(tho)001:5848: slob ma sum brgya la chos ston pa las ci
NK130(tho)001:5849: yang med pa'i skye mched kyi brtul zhugs gsan /
NK130(tho)001:5850: rgyal po'i khabs kyi grong khyer na reng sa byed
NK130(tho)001:5851: kyi bu lhag spyod slob ma sum brgya la chos
NK130(tho)001:5852: ston pa las 'du shes med 'du shes med min
NK130(tho)001:5853: gyi skye mched kyi brtul zhugs gsan de dag gsan
NK130(tho)001:5854: ma thag tu mngon du byas te lam 'dis ni
NK130(tho)001:5856: mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ba ma yin zhes
NK130(tho)001:5857: sun phyungs nas gshegs pas lhag spyod kyi drung nas
NK130(tho)001:5858: lnga sde bzang po bcom ldan 'das kyi rjes su
NK130(tho)001:5860: ston pa drug po sh+aa ri'i bus //
NK130(tho)001:5861: mnyan nas chos dang bla ma yang //
NK130(tho)001:5862: snod stong bzhin du brdabs te btang //
NK130(tho)001:5863: rgyal po ma skyes dgra yis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5864: mu stegs ston pa rnam drug la //
NK130(tho)001:5865: mnyan nas chos la ma rangs par //
NK130(tho)001:5866: spangs nas bcom ldan 'das la zhus //
NK130(tho)001:5867: chos la brtag pa'i man ngag kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5868: stug po bkod pa'i rgyan gyi lung //
NK130(tho)001:5869: mgon po spyan ras gzigs dbang gis //
NK130(tho)001:5870: dri ma med pa'i 'od du drangs //
NK130(tho)001:5871: bsregs na dmar bcad na dkar brdar na ser pa'i gser bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5872: mkhas pa rnams kyis yongs brtags nas //
NK130(tho)001:5873: bdag gsung blang bya dge slong dag /
NK130(tho)001:5874: gus pa'i phyir ni min no gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5876: rgyal po bram ze khyim bdag rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5877: ston mchog thub pa'i dbang po la //
NK130(tho)001:5878: thams cad mkhyen nam mi mkhyen zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5879: brtag pa log rtog chen po yin //
NK130(tho)001:5880: de la mkhas pa su zhig mgu //
NK130(tho)001:5881: sangs rgyas kun mkhyen los yin mod //
NK130(tho)001:5882: thog tha bar du dge ba'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:5883: de yi gsung rabs brtag ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:5884: 'phags pa min pas byas pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:5885: bstan bcos dag ni brtag pa'i gnas //
NK130(tho)001:5886: brtags nas 'dor len byed dgos na //
NK130(tho)001:5887: phyag rgya gsum dang bslab gsum sogs //
NK130(tho)001:5888: brtags nas gang len gang zhig spong //
NK130(tho)001:5889: bsregs bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5890: yongs su brtag tshul 'thad mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5891: 'on te mu stegs pa rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:5892: sangs rgyas bstan pa mi mtshungs pas //
NK130(tho)001:5893: chos dang bla ma la brtags nas //
NK130(tho)001:5894: snod stong bzhin du brdab bo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5897: de yi dgongs pa'ang phran tshegs las //
NK130(tho)001:5899: ston pa'i bstan pa'o zhes smras na //
NK130(tho)001:5900: tshig dang don la rtog dpyod bya //
NK130(tho)001:5901: mdo sde rnams dang mi mthun zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5902: 'dul ba la yang mi snang la //
NK130(tho)001:5904: chos min phyir de spongs zhes gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:5905: theg mchog rdzogs chen chos sngags kyi mdo sde rnams //
NK130(tho)001:5906: kun dang chos skad mi mthun zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5907: gtsug lag gnyis dang 'gal ba mang //
NK130(tho)001:5908: de phyir mdo dang mthun pa min //
NK130(tho)001:5909: rdo rje theg pa'i 'dul ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:5910: 'pho ba'i bag chags spong ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:5911: de yi khyad chos ma tshang phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5914: 'gyur med snying rje mi shes shing //
NK130(tho)001:5915: lam gyi go rim 'khrul pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5918: gdul bya'i bsam pa mi 'dra bas //
NK130(tho)001:5919: chos rnam so sor bstan pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:5920: kun kyang 'di la sa pan gyis /
NK130(tho)001:5921: de ltar theg pa che chung la //
NK130(tho)001:5922: phan tshun du ni lung 'gal gyis //
NK130(tho)001:5923: so so'i gzhung lugs dgag mi nus //
NK130(tho)001:5926: mdo rgyud gong 'og kun la med //
NK130(tho)001:5927: gtsug lag mdo dang sngags gnyis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:5928: mthar thug skyel so gcig mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5929: gnas skabs chos skad mthun pa med //
NK130(tho)001:5930: de dag la yang skyon blta'am //
NK130(tho)001:5931: rdo rje theg pa'i 'dul ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:5932: rigs lnga spyi dang khyad par dang //
NK130(tho)001:5933: dbang gi dam tshig yin par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:5934: 'pho ba'i chags pa spangs ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:5935: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:5936: rdo rje theg pa'i mdo sde yin //
NK130(tho)001:5938: shes rab ye shes zhes bya ba //
NK130(tho)001:5939: gsum pa'i nyams len dga' bzhi'i 'gros //
NK130(tho)001:5940: 'pho ba'i chags pa spong ba'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:5941: 'di yi gzhung gdams khrod na mang //
NK130(tho)001:5942: gang zag rnams kyis ma sgrub pa //
NK130(tho)001:5943: des na gang zag smad rigs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5944: chos la skur par ga la rigs //
NK130(tho)001:5945: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:5946: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK130(tho)001:5947: zung 'jug bde ba chen po'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:5949: 'gyur med snying rje mi shes lo //
NK130(tho)001:5950: 'o na khyed kyi lugs de ci //
NK130(tho)001:5951: cho ga'i rim pa nor ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:5952: lam gyi go rim 'khrul lo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5953: khyed kyis lan brgyar smras mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5954: smin grol lam mchog tshang bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5955: nor dang 'khrul pa ga la yin //
NK130(tho)001:5958: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK130(tho)001:5959: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs spangs byed gsung //
NK130(tho)001:5960: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par byed pa gang //
NK130(tho)001:5961: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK130(tho)001:5962: rang gi khyad chos ma tshang bas //
NK130(tho)001:5963: don dang ldan pa 'di ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:5964: gtsug lag gnyis dang 'gal bas na //
NK130(tho)001:5965: chos dang nye bar 'brel ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:5966: rang gi sdang bya mi spong bas //
NK130(tho)001:5968: mdo 'dul chos nyid brtag pa gsum //
NK130(tho)001:5969: theg chen rang gzhung la sbyor bar //
NK130(tho)001:5970: dbyig gnyen gyis ni mdo sde rgyan gyi 'grel par /
NK130(tho)001:5972: 'dir yang sngags la sbyar dgos kyi //
NK130(tho)001:5973: sangs rgyas bstan pa tsam zhig gis //
NK130(tho)001:5974: 'di yi sgrub byed nus pa min //
NK130(tho)001:5975: phyag rgya 'bul ba 'od ldan du gsum dang yang dag ldan //
NK130(tho)001:5976: bslab pa gsum ni rab ston cing //
NK130(tho)001:5977: thog ma bar dang mthar dge ba //
NK130(tho)001:5978: sangs rgyas gsung du mkhas pas brjod //
NK130(tho)001:5980: de ltar sngags la sbyar ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:5981: mdo 'dul chos nyid brtag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:5982: brgal lan brtsam du khyed dogs nas //
NK130(tho)001:5983: mdo dang 'dul ba'i lung gis ni //
NK130(tho)001:5984: gsang sngags bsnub pa la brtson mod //
NK130(tho)001:5985: smin grol lam gyis tshe 'dir grol //
NK130(tho)001:5986: sngags kyi khyad chos de las ci //
NK130(tho)001:5987: chos la brten phyir chos ltar bris //
NK130(tho)001:5988: de skad rang gis zer bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:5989: chos dang ma 'brel su zhig zer //
NK130(tho)001:5990: nyon mongs lam du byed pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:5991: 'di yis nyon mongs mi spong na //
NK130(tho)001:5992: rgyud rgyal dgyes pa rdo rje las //
NK130(tho)001:5994: yon tan lnga ni rin chen nyid //
NK130(tho)001:5995: ma dag pa la dug tu 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:5996: dag pas bdud rtsi lta bur 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:5997: zhes gsungs rgyal sras nyon mongs lud //
NK130(tho)001:5998: sangs rgyas chos rnams bskyed do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:5999: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6000: ma spangs rang sar grol ba la //
NK130(tho)001:6001: nyon mongs mi spong su zhig zer //
NK130(tho)001:6003: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud gzhung la //
NK130(tho)001:6004: phyag rgya gsum dang bslab gsum yod //
NK130(tho)001:6005: de dag bon po'i gzhung la'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:6006: 'on kyang tshig don nor ba mang //
NK130(tho)001:6007: zong du bong sha 'tshong ba la //
NK130(tho)001:6008: ri dwags rnga ma bstan dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:6009: sangs rgyas gsung rabs ma yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6010: blo dang ldan pas 'phral du shes //
NK130(tho)001:6012: 'di ltar rdzogs chen gzhung lugs la //
NK130(tho)001:6013: phyag rgya gsum dang bslab pa gsum //
NK130(tho)001:6014: thub pa'i gsung dang mi 'gal la //
NK130(tho)001:6015: bon dang mtshungs pa ma yin kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6016: de ltar rang nyid smra ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:6017: shin tu bden te bdud rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:6018: de las smra rgyu ci zhig 'byung //
NK130(tho)001:6019: de'ang 'phags pa brgyad stong ba las /
NK130(tho)001:6020: bdud sdig can dge sbyong gi cha byad du 'ongs nas /
NK130(tho)001:6021: byang chub sems dpa' theg pa la gsar du zhugs
NK130(tho)001:6022: pa blo chung ba blo zhan pa sdongs par gyur
NK130(tho)001:6023: pa byang chub tu lung ma bstan pa'i rigs kyi
NK130(tho)001:6024: bu de dag la 'di ltar 'grel bar byed de
NK130(tho)001:6025: / gang khyod nyan pa 'di ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:6026: yang ji ltar mdo sde'i nang du gtogs pa 'di
NK130(tho)001:6027: ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yin
NK130(tho)001:6028: no zhes bdud sdig can gyis the tshom za bas
NK130(tho)001:6030: zhes gsungs pa ltar bslab gsum bon la yang yod
NK130(tho)001:6031: do zhes the tshom za bas chos spong du 'jug
NK130(tho)001:6034: de ring rdzun rgyud rtsom na yang //
NK130(tho)001:6035: chos la brten phyir chos ltar 'dri //
NK130(tho)001:6036: lta sgom spyod sogs gang shes bkod //
NK130(tho)001:6037: rdzun rgyud yin phyir bkar mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:6039: tshigs su bcad pa 'di yis ni //
NK130(tho)001:6040: chos dang nyer bar ma 'brel zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6041: gong du rang gis smra ba nyams //
NK130(tho)001:6042: tshul 'di bka' ru mi rung yang //
NK130(tho)001:6043: bstan bcos rtsom pa po thams cad //
NK130(tho)001:6044: 'di tshul kho nar mdzad pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6045: de kun rdzun mar ma sgrub cig /
NK130(tho)001:6047: log pa'i chos la 'jug pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6048: don nor cho ga log pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6049: thar pa'i bar chad mang ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6050: thog ma bar dang mthar mi dge //
NK130(tho)001:6052: mtshan nyid de dag tshang ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6053: yod na gang yang mi dge la //
NK130(tho)001:6054: dge ba yi ni chos rnams la //
NK130(tho)001:6055: mi dge'o zhes na nga smra ba //
NK130(tho)001:6056: de yang bdud kyi byin gyis brlabs //
NK130(tho)001:6057: khyed rang yang ni de 'dod de //
NK130(tho)001:6058: chos min spyod pa'i bdud sdig can //
NK130(tho)001:6059: byang chub sems dpa' che yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6060: gong du smras pa nyid phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:6061: yang 'o na rgyal bas lung bstan rigs //
NK130(tho)001:6062: ci phyir sngar lung ma bstan lo //
NK130(tho)001:6063: mtha' 'khob yul re'i chos log rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6064: thub pas lung bstan ga la lang //
NK130(tho)001:6065: bon dang rdzogs pa chen po gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:6066: glen pa blun pos byas pas na //
NK130(tho)001:6067: tshig don nor ba bzung sla bas //
NK130(tho)001:6068: rgyal ba de phyir 'bad mi mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:6069: chos ltar bcos pa 'byung ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:6070: dam chos brtag pa'i cho ga dang //
NK130(tho)001:6071: thabs la bslu ba'i bdud yod ces //
NK130(tho)001:6072: gsungs pa 'di dag lung bstan yin //
NK130(tho)001:6075: bskal pa grangs mtha' mu med pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:6076: chos kun ma 'dres sa ler gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:6077: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:6078: dri ba mi 'dra sha stag la //
NK130(tho)001:6079: lan ni dus gcig 'debs nus na //
NK130(tho)001:6080: mtha' 'khob tsam re'i chos log kun //
NK130(tho)001:6081: thub pas lung bstan mi lang ba //
NK130(tho)001:6082: sgrib med gzigs pa'i sangs rgyas de //
NK130(tho)001:6083: spobs pa zad dam ci zhig nongs //
NK130(tho)001:6084: bden par smra ba'i mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:6085: sangs rgyas la sems can thams cad kyis dri ba
NK130(tho)001:6086: mi 'dra ba sha stag dris kyang de dag thams
NK130(tho)001:6087: cad la lan dus gcig la 'debs nus par gsungs
NK130(tho)001:6090: cis kyang lung bstan med pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6091: dam chos yang dag yin nges na //
NK130(tho)001:6092: rdzogs chen dgag pa 'di snyed cig /
NK130(tho)001:6093: lung ma bstan phyir chos su nges //
NK130(tho)001:6095: rdzogs chen shes phyin la sogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:6096: chos la chos min zhes smra ba //
NK130(tho)001:6097: de dag phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK130(tho)001:6098: dge slong gzugs kyi bdud 'byung zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6099: rgyal bas mdo las lung bstan pas //
NK130(tho)001:6100: lung ma bstan pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6102: bdud sdig can dge slong gi gzugs su 'ongs nas 'byed par 'gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:6104: rab 'byor ngag gi nyes pa smra ba de lta
NK130(tho)001:6105: bu'i ngo bos bsod nams ma yin pa'i phung po
NK130(tho)001:6107: rab 'byor gang dag shes rab kyi pha rol tu
NK130(tho)001:6108: phyin pa zab mo 'di sun phyung bar sems par
NK130(tho)001:6110: phyir gzhil bar sems pa'i skyes bu gti mug can
NK130(tho)001:6111: de dag legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba 'di
NK130(tho)001:6112: nyid kyi sgor zhugs pa dag tu rab tu 'byung
NK130(tho)001:6113: bar 'gyur ro // zhes sogs lung bstan pa du ma yod do //
NK130(tho)001:6115: kha cig bod du byas kyang rung //
NK130(tho)001:6116: sems la phan na des chog ste //
NK130(tho)001:6117: bod du byas pa'i zas gos kyis //
NK130(tho)001:6119: kla klo mu stegs shan pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:6120: zas gos blang na des chog ste //
NK130(tho)001:6121: de dag chos lugs blang mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:6122: chos dang zas gos ga la 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:6123: sems la phan pa'ang brtag dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:6124: rang gi nyon mongs bri ba'am //
NK130(tho)001:6125: nyams rtog cung zad skyes pa la //
NK130(tho)001:6126: sems la phan no snyam par zad //
NK130(tho)001:6127: mu stegs byed kyi mnyam gzhag gis //
NK130(tho)001:6128: mngon shes lnga yang skye srid pas //
NK130(tho)001:6129: sems la phan te thar lam min //
NK130(tho)001:6130: nyan thos rang sangs rgyas lam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6133: pha rol phyin pa'i ring lam yang //
NK130(tho)001:6134: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam min //
NK130(tho)001:6135: phan par rloms pa 'ga' zhig gis //
NK130(tho)001:6136: spang la ngan song sgrub pa'ang srid //
NK130(tho)001:6137: mdo rgyud bstan bcos zab mo yi //
NK130(tho)001:6138: lam rim yongs rdzogs mi shes par //
NK130(tho)001:6139: rang gi nyams myong gtsor 'dzin pa //
NK130(tho)001:6140: phal cher gol sar ltung ba'i rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:6141: 'od srung slob ma rnam gnyis dang //
NK130(tho)001:6142: drang srong rig mchog la yin pa //
NK130(tho)001:6143: slob ma 'bum phrag du mar bcas //
NK130(tho)001:6144: rang gi nyams rtogs bzang po la //
NK130(tho)001:6145: lung rig med pa'i mchog 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6146: dmyal bar ltung ba'i gtam yang nyon //
NK130(tho)001:6147: sngon sangs rgyas 'od srung gi bstan pa la dge
NK130(tho)001:6148: slong rnams kyis bsgoms pas nyams rtogs cung zad skyes
NK130(tho)001:6149: pa la dgra bcom pa thob snyam pa las /
NK130(tho)001:6150: 'chi khar gnad gcod kyi tshor bas log lta skyes
NK130(tho)001:6151: te nged kyi sgom bzang po 'di lta bu skyes
NK130(tho)001:6152: kyang dgra bcom pa ma thob pas sangs rgyas kyis
NK130(tho)001:6153: dgra bcom pa yod gsungs pa bden re kan snyam
NK130(tho)001:6154: nas shi bas ngan song rnams su skye /
NK130(tho)001:6155: de nas thar nas lo mang por mtha' 'khob rnams su skyes te /
NK130(tho)001:6156: mthar yul de re'i khye'u gnyis su skyes pa'i bar du log lta can du gyur /
NK130(tho)001:6157: bcom ldan 'das la dad nas rab tu byung bas gdod dgra bcom pa thob bo //
NK130(tho)001:6158: drang srong rig mchog ma yin pa zhes bya ba
NK130(tho)001:6159: slob ma 'bum phrag du ma dang bcas pas bsgom
NK130(tho)001:6160: pas nyams rtogs bzang po skyes /
NK130(tho)001:6161: dgra bcom thob snyam nas shi bas 'od gsal gyi lhar skyes /
NK130(tho)001:6162: bdag cag gi nyams rtogs de lta bus kyang skye
NK130(tho)001:6163: ba ma chod pas 'jig rten na myang 'das yod
NK130(tho)001:6164: zer ba mi bden snyam pa dang tshe 'phos nas
NK130(tho)001:6165: log lta des dmyal bar ltung ba las /
NK130(tho)001:6166: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i sngon gyi skye ba
NK130(tho)001:6167: ston pa shes rab sna tshogs bya bas dmyal bar
NK130(tho)001:6168: song nas byin gyis brlab cing chos bshad pas /
NK130(tho)001:6169: gdod mtho ris su skyes shing lam sgrub pas so //
NK130(tho)001:6170: bod du byas tshad chos min na //
NK130(tho)001:6171: khyed kyi bstan bcos ci rung lo //
NK130(tho)001:6172: rang gis bstan bcos rtsom pa na //
NK130(tho)001:6173: rgya bod gar yang dgag bya min //
NK130(tho)001:6174: bka' ma grub pa'i gzhung yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6175: rdzun gyi mdo rgyud sogs byed na //
NK130(tho)001:6176: gsar rnying su la snang yang rung //
NK130(tho)001:6177: bstan 'dzin rnams kyis dgag bya yin //
NK130(tho)001:6179: smra ba de dag phal cher kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6180: rang blo'i lam du drangs pas 'khrul //
NK130(tho)001:6181: nyams rtogs gnyis po shan ma phyed //
NK130(tho)001:6182: 'di ni shin tu gol ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:6183: bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugs med bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:6184: phyi rol pa yi mnyam bzhag dang //
NK130(tho)001:6185: zhi gnas rtse gcig pa rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:6186: spyan dang mngon par shes pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:6187: gnas skabs yon tan du ma bskyed //
NK130(tho)001:6188: rtogs pa'i shes rab mi ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:6189: ting 'dzin de las sad pa na //
NK130(tho)001:6190: rnam rtog sngar shul chug pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:6191: chos ma bden snyam log lta skye //
NK130(tho)001:6192: rgyu des ngan song 'khor bar ltung //
NK130(tho)001:6193: gsang ba'i theg pa chen po 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:6194: nyams dang rtogs pa shan phye ste //
NK130(tho)001:6195: lhag mthong rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK130(tho)001:6196: phyir mi ldog par gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6197: 'di ni bka' brgyud pa la'ang grags //
NK130(tho)001:6198: lha ru skye ba'i bsam gtan kun //
NK130(tho)001:6199: zhi gnas nyag gcig yin par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6200: de las skyes pa'i bde gsal dang //
NK130(tho)001:6202: 'di la lhag mthong yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:6203: des na de gnyis shan phye ste //
NK130(tho)001:6204: sems la phan pa'i nyams tsam gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6205: thar pa thob pa bgegs rigs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6206: nyams rtogs sgrel nas smra ba 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:6207: phyag rgya chen po'ang khyad du bsad //
NK130(tho)001:6208: ji srid nam mkha' zad kyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:6209: thar pa'i go skabs spangs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6210: de ltar khyed kyis rdzogs chen chos //
NK130(tho)001:6211: ming tsam med par nub na snyam //
NK130(tho)001:6212: 'bad pa chen pos bkag mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6213: khyed las smon lam shes rab stobs //
NK130(tho)001:6214: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul ches che ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:6215: bdud tshogs sde dang dpung bcas pas //
NK130(tho)001:6216: bsnub pa nyid du mi nus na //
NK130(tho)001:6217: khyod kyis bsnub par ga la nus //
NK130(tho)001:6218: de phyir snying las chung ngur mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:6220: rang ngam gzhan gyi grub pa'i mtha' //
NK130(tho)001:6221: chos la smod pa drug pa zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6222: rtsa ba'i ltung bar gsungs pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6223: phyi rol gzhung dang rdzun rgyud kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6224: smad na dam tshig nyams so lo //
NK130(tho)001:6225: 'o na rgyal dang de sras dang //
NK130(tho)001:6226: mkhas grub kun gyi de smad phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6227: de dag dam nyams yin nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:6229: rnam gzig mar me rin chen gtsug /
NK130(tho)001:6230: grangs med gsum du byon pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:6231: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK130(tho)001:6232: da ltar bzhugs dang slad nas 'byon //
NK130(tho)001:6233: thub ba skyes mchog de kun gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6234: rdzogs chen rdzun gzhung yin no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6235: gsungs pa yod na ston par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:6236: bka' bsdu mdzad dang dgongs 'grel mkhan //
NK130(tho)001:6237: 'jam dpal phyag rdor spyan ras gzigs //
NK130(tho)001:6238: de sogs rgyal sras sems dpa' che //
NK130(tho)001:6239: su yis rdzogs chen bkag pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6240: tshi 'bru tsam zhig ston par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:6241: rgyan drug mchog gnyis la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6242: rgya gar pan grub de rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:6243: bod kyi yul 'dir byon pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:6244: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i bshes gnyen yang //
NK130(tho)001:6245: skar tshogs ji bzhin grangs las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:6246: kun gyis rdzogs chen bkag pa med //
NK130(tho)001:6248: de la sogs pa'i 'byams yig la'ang //
NK130(tho)001:6249: brtag na zhe nas bkag pa med //
NK130(tho)001:6250: khyed kyis snying nas chos spangs pas //
NK130(tho)001:6251: rtsa ltung drug pa mi phog na //
NK130(tho)001:6252: chos ma spangs la phog gam ci //
NK130(tho)001:6253: spyir na gsar rnying 'ga' zhig la //
NK130(tho)001:6254: bslad pa yod par grags mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6255: gsang sngags rnying ma'i snga 'gyur lnga //
NK130(tho)001:6256: ma gtogs chos ma yin no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6257: spangs phyir 'di la chos spong zer //
NK130(tho)001:6259: rtsa ba'i ltung ba drug pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6260: sngags dang pha rol phyin pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:6261: dri ma med la smod pa zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6262: spyan ras gzigs kyis de skad gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6263: kha cig rnam snang mngon byang las //
NK130(tho)001:6264: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:6265: mu stegs can la mi smod ces //
NK130(tho)001:6266: gsungs phyir lta ngan mi smad lo //
NK130(tho)001:6267: de ni gang zag mu stegs can //
NK130(tho)001:6268: dgos pa med la smod par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6269: mu stegs can gyi lta ngan rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6270: rgyal ba sras dbon kun gyis bkags //
NK130(tho)001:6272: rtsa ltung drug pa zhes pa de //
NK130(tho)001:6273: rang ngam gzhan gyi grub pa'i mtha' //
NK130(tho)001:6274: chos la smod pa drug pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6275: de skad b+ha ba'i lha yis bshad //
NK130(tho)001:6276: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang gis //
NK130(tho)001:6277: dri med sngags dang pha rol phyin //
NK130(tho)001:6278: smod pa drug par gsungs pa de //
NK130(tho)001:6279: rang gi grub mtha' smod la dgongs //
NK130(tho)001:6280: de bzhin gzhan gyi grub mtha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:6281: ngan song sbyong ba'i brtag par yang //
NK130(tho)001:6282: mu stegs can la smad mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:6283: zhes gsungs d+aa ri ka pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6284: rje btsun grags pa la sogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:6285: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi 'grel mdzad rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6286: phyi nang grub mtha' gang smod pa //
NK130(tho)001:6287: de ni rtsa ltung drug par bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:6288: rgyal dang rgyal sras mkhas grub rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6289: lta ba ngan pa 'gog mdzad pa //
NK130(tho)001:6290: gdul bya log lam bzlog bya'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6291: thugs rje'i dbang gis 'gog mdzad kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6293: n+aa ro pa 'dra'i skyes mchog kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6294: mu stegs rtsod pa pham mdzad pas //
NK130(tho)001:6295: tshe gcig sangs rgyas nyams so zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6296: te lo pa yis ma gsungs sam //
NK130(tho)001:6297: des na bye brag smra ba nas //
NK130(tho)001:6298: sems tsam bar gyi lta ba rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6299: dbu ma pa yis sun phyungs ltar //
NK130(tho)001:6300: theg pa dma' ba tsam zhig tu //
NK130(tho)001:6301: smra ba tsam la skyon med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6302: snying nas gzhan chos smod pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:6303: rtsa ba'i ltung ba drug par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6304: phyogs 'dzin nyes pa kun gyi 'byung khungs phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6305: sdang zhugs tshul gyis gzhan sde'ang smad mi rung //
NK130(tho)001:6307: mu stegs kyi gzhung smad pa rtsa ltung drug pa phog pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK130(tho)001:6308: bshags pa'i gnas yin par rgya bod kyi bla ma
NK130(tho)001:6309: rnams mthun la ltung ba ma phog na bshags rgyu
NK130(tho)001:6312: kha cig grong rtags bzang ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6313: rdzogs chen smra ba chos yin lo //
NK130(tho)001:6314: grong rtags bzang po gang la byed //
NK130(tho)001:6315: mdo 'am rgyud kyi lung ci yod //
NK130(tho)001:6316: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK130(tho)001:6318: sa g.yos phyogs tshig skar mda' ltung //
NK130(tho)001:6319: rlung sogs ltas ngan 'byung bar bshad //
NK130(tho)001:6321: skye rgu'i bsod nams zad pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6323: lha yul skyes na me tog 'bab //
NK130(tho)001:6324: sku dang yi ge thugs ljags spyan //
NK130(tho)001:6325: 'phags pa rnams la byon pa med //
NK130(tho)001:6326: chos la sdang ba'i bon po la //
NK130(tho)001:6327: sku dang yi ge thugs ljags 'byon //
NK130(tho)001:6329: 'phags pa gsum gyi ring bsrel ni //
NK130(tho)001:6330: yon tan stobs kyis 'byung ngo zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6331: mdo yi lung rgyab 'di yis chog /
NK130(tho)001:6332: sku dang yi ge 'byon pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6333: gsang sngags pa yi khyad chos te //
NK130(tho)001:6334: jo bo chen po rje yis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6335: bskyed rim can la lha sku 'byon //
NK130(tho)001:6336: tshul khrims gtsang la me tog 'bab //
NK130(tho)001:6337: byang chub sems la ring srel 'dzag /
NK130(tho)001:6338: skye med don mtshon yi ge a //
NK130(tho)001:6339: phyir mi ldog pa dung 'khyil te //
NK130(tho)001:6340: 'khor ba mi spong sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:6341: thugs dang ljags ni 'byon par bshad //
NK130(tho)001:6342: ces sogs glegs bam nyid du bshad //
NK130(tho)001:6343: skyes bu chen po gang gshegs pas //
NK130(tho)001:6344: skye rgu bsod nams zad pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6345: mi rung ltas kyang 'byung mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6346: de rang grol ba'i yon tan dang //
NK130(tho)001:6347: gdul bya'i bsod nams spel phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:6348: sku gsung thugs rten byon pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:6349: rje btsun sa skya pan chen la //
NK130(tho)001:6350: gtsug tor dbus su kyee rdo rje //
NK130(tho)001:6351: phrag par kha sar pa ni dang //
NK130(tho)001:6352: lha sku dpag tu med pa byon //
