NK130(tho)001:6353: 'gro mgon gtsang pa rgya ras kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6354: sgal tshigs nyi shu rtsa gcig la //
NK130(tho)001:6355: spyan ras gzigs dbang nyer gcig byon //
NK130(tho)001:6356: mkhas pa gung ru'i dbu thod la //
NK130(tho)001:6358: skye med don mtshon a yig dang //
NK130(tho)001:6360: yi ge drug pa la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6361: byon pa'i bshes gnyen bsam las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:6362: mnyam med dwags po lha rje la //
NK130(tho)001:6363: thugs ljags byon pa la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6364: sngon byon skyes mchog de dag gi //
NK130(tho)001:6365: so so'i rnam thar bltas pas shes //
NK130(tho)001:6366: 'on kyang khyed ni de yi tshul //
NK130(tho)001:6367: bzang po yin par mi sems mod //
NK130(tho)001:6369: kha cig nus pa 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6370: rdzun rgyud rnams kyang chos yin lo //
NK130(tho)001:6371: mu stegs kla klo bon la yang //
NK130(tho)001:6372: tshe 'di'i nus pa chen po yod //
NK130(tho)001:6373: kha cig rdzogs pa chen po pa //
NK130(tho)001:6374: nor ldan bsod nams chen po la //
NK130(tho)001:6375: bod kyi sde bdag 'di thams cad //
NK130(tho)001:6376: rdzogs chen mi shes gsar ma pa //
NK130(tho)001:6377: kha cig rnying ma dor nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:6378: gsar la zhugs pa mi shes lo //
NK130(tho)001:6379: sa skya pa dang 'gri gung pa //
NK130(tho)001:6380: mar pa mi la yang dgon pa //
NK130(tho)001:6381: 'gos dang rngog dang khu dang myos //
NK130(tho)001:6382: dpyal zhang 'brom ston bu dol sogs //
NK130(tho)001:6383: thams cad 'byor ldan grags chen snyan //
NK130(tho)001:6384: so zur gnubs sogs khral gyis mnar //
NK130(tho)001:6386: nus pa chos su sgrub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6387: nor dang bsod nams che bas dang //
NK130(tho)001:6388: shis dang mi shis la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6389: 'jig rten skye bo'i phal tshig la //
NK130(tho)001:6390: sdang 'dod kun slong ngan pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:6392: byis pa'i ngang tshul nyid du zad //
NK130(tho)001:6393: so zur gnubs sogs khral gyis mnar //
NK130(tho)001:6394: ces pa'ang don la cung mi gnas //
NK130(tho)001:6395: rong gi khu lung la sogs na //
NK130(tho)001:6396: so dang gnubs par gtogs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:6397: grong sngags 'ga' la khral ris snang //
NK130(tho)001:6398: zur ba'i yang 'ug la sogs la //
NK130(tho)001:6399: khral rigs da lta'i bar du med //
NK130(tho)001:6400: chos dang gang zag la sdang ba //
NK130(tho)001:6401: chos kyi rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK130(tho)001:6402: spangs pas rtsa ltung lnga pa phog /
NK130(tho)001:6403: sems can rnams la byams pa spang //
NK130(tho)001:6404: des ni rtsa ltung bzhi pas zin //
NK130(tho)001:6405: zab mo gsang ba sngags kyi don //
NK130(tho)001:6406: skur 'debs skye bo yongs la bsgrags //
NK130(tho)001:6407: bdun pa'i gsang sgrog nyid kyang phog /
NK130(tho)001:6408: bud med ma smad tsam zhig dang //
NK130(tho)001:6409: rang gi phung por ma brnyas pas //
NK130(tho)001:6410: brgyad dang bcu bzhis ma gos kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6411: gzhan du rtsa ltung bcu gnyis kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6412: gong bu chen por khyod gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:6413: 'bad pas bshags sdom bya bar rigs //
NK130(tho)001:6415: 'di dag bkag kyang mi khegs pas //
NK130(tho)001:6416: smra ba ngal bar zad ce na //
NK130(tho)001:6417: kun gyi sdig pa mi khegs kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6418: 'ga' la phan phyir sangs rgyas byon //
NK130(tho)001:6420: 'di yang mkhas pa'i gtam ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:6421: de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK130(tho)001:6422: yul khams gcig dang rgyal po gcig /
NK130(tho)001:6423: grong khyer gcig gi don du min //
NK130(tho)001:6424: lha bcas 'jig rten thams cad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6425: skyabs mgon rten dang dpung gnyen du //
NK130(tho)001:6426: byon ces sman pa mkhas pa'i dpes //
NK130(tho)001:6427: skyob pa mchog des mdo las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6428: gra tshang re yi slob dpon dang //
NK130(tho)001:6429: dgon sde re yi mkhan po ltar //
NK130(tho)001:6430: brgya stong tsam re'i tshogs dpon du //
NK130(tho)001:6431: sangs rgyas byon par gang blta ba //
NK130(tho)001:6432: sngon chad dge ba'i 'bras chung bas //
NK130(tho)001:6433: da lta'ang mos pa dma' ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:6435: shes rab ldan pas 'di thos na //
NK130(tho)001:6436: la la la la dpyod pa'i gzhi //
NK130(tho)001:6437: la la la la blang dor shes //
NK130(tho)001:6439: de ltar ji skad smra ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:6440: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i rnam bzhag la //
NK130(tho)001:6441: lan grangs stong du rgol med kye //
NK130(tho)001:6442: mkhas pa blo gros mig ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:6443: bltas tshe snying po cang mi snang //
NK130(tho)001:6444: gsar 'gyur bstan pa'i rnam bzhag la //
NK130(tho)001:6445: blang ba'i gzhi yang cung zad snang //
NK130(tho)001:6446: de phyir de la rjes yi rang //
NK130(tho)001:6448: 'dzam bu'i gling na sangs rgyas byon //
NK130(tho)001:6449: skye rgu phal cher phyi rol pa //
NK130(tho)001:6450: thub pa'i slob ma srid mtha' tsam //
NK130(tho)001:6452: kye ma thub slob srid mtha' tsam //
NK130(tho)001:6453: de skad nam yang ma smra zhig /
NK130(tho)001:6454: gdul bya dus la ma bab na //
NK130(tho)001:6455: sangs rgyas 'jig rten ga la byon //
NK130(tho)001:6456: mu stegs ston pa 'khor mang ba //
NK130(tho)001:6457: 'od srung slob ma ral pa can //
NK130(tho)001:6458: khri dang stong phrag drug bcas dang //
NK130(tho)001:6459: nye rgyal dang ni pang nas skyes //
NK130(tho)001:6460: 'khor bcas thub pa'i slob mar gyur //
NK130(tho)001:6461: 'dus pa snga phyi bar gsum gyi //
NK130(tho)001:6462: nyan thos grangs kyang rgya cher byung //
NK130(tho)001:6463: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun gyi //
NK130(tho)001:6464: 'dus pa bgrang du ga la spyod //
NK130(tho)001:6465: lha dang mi yi skye rgu'i tshogs //
NK130(tho)001:6466: grangs med byang chub lam la bkod //
NK130(tho)001:6467: dgra bcom rgyun zhugs phyir mi 'ong //
NK130(tho)001:6468: phyir 'ong sogs la bkod pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:6469: bsam gyi mi khyab brjod las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:6470: da dung thos pa rgya skyed cig /
NK130(tho)001:6472: de slad mang po'i sdig can 'gyu //
NK130(tho)001:6473: 'on kyang sdig pa bsags rnams kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6474: nam zhig 'khor ba mtha' can du //
NK130(tho)001:6475: 'byung ba de nyid thabs yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6476: thugs rje mnga' ba zhing 'dir gshegs //
NK130(tho)001:6477: de ltar kho bo'i bstan bcos 'di //
NK130(tho)001:6478: ji bzhin rtogs pa'i mkhas pa nyung //
NK130(tho)001:6481: zab mo'i chos la log lta ba //
NK130(tho)001:6482: chos mchog spangs pa'i mi de ni //
NK130(tho)001:6484: 'jam dpal rtsa ba'i rgyud las gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6485: 'khor ba mtha' can gyur srid kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6486: dbul zhing nad mang glen pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6487: kla klo dag tu skye bar 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:6489: de ni mdze can nad par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:6490: lkugs shing 'on pa yan lag nyams //
NK130(tho)001:6491: blo nyams long ba nyid dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:6492: rtsub cing rtag tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK130(tho)001:6493: sa steng yi dwags lta bur snang //
NK130(tho)001:6494: de sogs nyes dmigs rgya cher gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6495: gzhan yang gsang ba grub pa las //
NK130(tho)001:6496: rdo rje theg pa la smod pa //
NK130(tho)001:6498: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK130(tho)001:6499: ma gus par ni byed pa gang //
NK130(tho)001:6500: bde gshegs mtshan ma la bstan kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6501: de ni nges par mnar med 'gro //
NK130(tho)001:6502: zhes gsungs khyed kyis rnying ma'i lha //
NK130(tho)001:6503: mu stegs bon gyi lha ru bltas //
NK130(tho)001:6504: chos ma yin par nan gyis bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:6505: nyams nyen mkhan gyi kun spyod 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:6506: sangs rgyas 'grub re mna' yis gcus //
NK130(tho)001:6507: sngags kyi dkon mchog gsum spangs pas //
NK130(tho)001:6508: bde gshegs mtshan ma la brten kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6511: 'jig rten gsum mgon dri ma gsum spangs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6512: kun bzang sgyu 'phrul bka' brgyad 'dus pa mdo //
NK130(tho)001:6513: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i lha tshogs thugs rje can //
NK130(tho)001:6514: thub dbang bstan pa'i snying po 'di spong ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:6515: 'gro rnams rdo rje'i khabs nas drangs mdzod la //
NK130(tho)001:6516: thar pa'i lam la 'god par mdzad du gsol //
NK130(tho)001:6517: da khyed kyi bstan bcos 'di'i sbyar byang las //
NK130(tho)001:6518: gzhan la phan dga' byams dang snying rje'i blos //
NK130(tho)001:6519: skye rgus lam dang lam min shes phyir byas //
NK130(tho)001:6520: sdang zhugs rnams la kho bos bzod par gsol //
NK130(tho)001:6521: bstan pa 'dzin pa rnams la phrin du bzhes //
NK130(tho)001:6522: chos min rnams kyi de nyid 'di yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6523: gzu bor gnas blos 'thad pa'i snying po bstan //
NK130(tho)001:6524: thub dbang rgyal pa'i bstan pa nyams dma' bas //
NK130(tho)001:6525: legs bshad gzhan la phan pa'ang dus kyis dka' //
NK130(tho)001:6526: 'di 'dra theg mchog snying po'i rnal 'byor ba //
NK130(tho)001:6527: dri med nam mkha'i sgra gcan dpal gshin rje //
NK130(tho)001:6528: des bstan dge ba'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas des //
NK130(tho)001:6529: 'gro kun kun mkhyen ye shes 'grub gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:6530: chos dang chos ma yin pa rnams par 'byed pa
NK130(tho)001:6531: rnam par dbye ba'i rab tu byed pa zhes bya
NK130(tho)001:6532: ba / sh+aakya'i rgyal ba'i bstan pa lo nyis stong nyis brgya dang sum cu rtsa gnyis lon pa /
NK130(tho)001:6533: dbang po'i lo dbyar zla tha chung gro zhun gyi zla ba phyogs phyi ma'i tshes brgyad la /
NK130(tho)001:6534: yul byang phyogs kyi rgyud du byung ba thub pa'i bstan pa la /
NK130(tho)001:6535: phan pa dang rigs par smra ba'i btsun pa rgya mtsho'i sprin 'brug sgra bzang pos /
NK130(tho)001:6536: dpal e wam gi ri khrod lho gling nor bu'i
NK130(tho)001:6537: sgang 'od bzang nyi ma'i rdzong du sbyar ba 'jig
NK130(tho)001:6538: rten na nyi zla ltar gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:6540: de dag tshig sbyor legs mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6542: gzu bo'i blo yis bstan pa na //
NK130(tho)001:6543: de la yid brtan rung mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6544: sbyor ba skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:6545: lta spyod stong nyid snying rje'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:6546: yongs su bsngo ba'i bar gyis ni //
NK130(tho)001:6547: sangs rgyas chos su ma byas pas //
NK130(tho)001:6548: gzhan phan byams blos byas zer kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6550: dga' ba bskyed kyang gnod pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:6551: 'on kyang khyed la sdig ma gyur //
NK130(tho)001:6552: da ni bdag gis ji ltar bris pa'i rgyu mtshan smras pa /
NK130(tho)001:6553: khyed kyi bstan bcos yongs rdzogs 'di'i //
NK130(tho)001:6554: yig cha dkon kyang rags rim tsam //
NK130(tho)001:6555: legs bshad gser gyi thur ma ru //
NK130(tho)001:6556: pan chen sh+aakya mchog ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:6557: dgongs pa can du drangs pa la //
NK130(tho)001:6558: mkhas pa mchog de'i dgongs pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6559: sus kyang go bar ma mchis pas //
NK130(tho)001:6560: phal ches gzhung de drang por 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:6561: de la rnying ma pa kha cig /
NK130(tho)001:6562: sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i blo med par //
NK130(tho)001:6563: mkhas mchog de la skur 'debs pas //
NK130(tho)001:6564: sdig pa'i las de bzlog bya'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:6565: sngon chad de la lan zhig byas //
NK130(tho)001:6566: dus phyis chos rgyal mi'i dbang po //
NK130(tho)001:6567: gang des dpe dang bkas gnang nas //
NK130(tho)001:6568: 'di la sngon chad lan thebs so //
NK130(tho)001:6569: ma byung phyir na phal cher zhig /'di yis bslus pa byung snang bas //
NK130(tho)001:6570: shin tu thebs pa'i lan thob ces //
NK130(tho)001:6571: bka' yi khur chen bstsal pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:6572: khyed kyis rdzogs pa chen po'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:6573: zhe nas bsnub pa'i bsam pa 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:6574: sangs rgyas thams cad bslus pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6576: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bslus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:6577: zhes bya ba ni de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa
NK130(tho)001:6578: gang yin pa de ni ngas byas kyi bstan bcos
NK130(tho)001:6579: 'di ni sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa ma yin no
NK130(tho)001:6580: // zhes smra bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bslu bar byed pa dag kyang snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:6581: dam pa'i chos la smad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:6582: zhes bya ba ni dam chos bslus sam sdig pa chen po byed pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:6583: 'di dag ni sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa ma yin
NK130(tho)001:6584: te 'di dag ni snyan ngag mkhan gyis byas pa
NK130(tho)001:6585: yin / zhes de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i tshig don spong bar byed pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:6587: tshig rtsub sgros ngar zur rno ba //
NK130(tho)001:6588: kho nar snang bas de yi lan //
NK130(tho)001:6589: de ltar rtsub mor bris pa la //
NK130(tho)001:6590: mkhas pa dag gis bzod mdzad rigs //
NK130(tho)001:6591: ci phyir khyed kyis bstan bcos 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:6592: gal te rdzogs pa chen po'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:6593: bka' ru sgrub pa'i shes byed bzang //
NK130(tho)001:6594: 'gog la gtan tshigs med mthong na //
NK130(tho)001:6595: mkhas pa rnams kyi blang bar 'os //
NK130(tho)001:6596: zhes gsungs phyir na de ltar lan /
NK130(tho)001:6597: thebs par btab la nyes pa med //
NK130(tho)001:6598: gnod lan gnod pa byed lta bu'i //
NK130(tho)001:6599: ma rabs lugs ngang 'di mi mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:6600: rtsod tshe klu sgrub yab sras la'ang //
NK130(tho)001:6601: mchil lhwam 'gram par brgyab pa sogs //
NK130(tho)001:6602: de lta'i kun spyod yod ces thos //
NK130(tho)001:6603: rtsod pas mkhon du mi 'dzin pa //
NK130(tho)001:6604: mkhas pa rnams kyi spyi lugs yin //
NK130(tho)001:6605: 'on kyang bdag gis ma go zhing //
NK130(tho)001:6606: ma shes nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK130(tho)001:6607: de yang mkhas pa rnams la bshags //
NK130(tho)001:6608: spyir na bdag nyid mkhas pa min //
NK130(tho)001:6609: mkhas pa brin pa'i dus kyang min //
NK130(tho)001:6610: de phyir rtsom pa'i blo med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6611: de ma yin la der 'dzin gyi //
NK130(tho)001:6612: phra ma snga btsan dbang po che //
NK130(tho)001:6613: 'di yis bslus pa ches mang bas //
NK130(tho)001:6614: de dag kun la phan phyir dang //
NK130(tho)001:6615: sa skyang chos kyi rgyal po yi //
NK130(tho)001:6616: bka' yi khur chen ma bzlog pas //
NK130(tho)001:6617: rags rim tsam zhig bkod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:6618: dus mthar bzhi pa'i tshigs su bcad pa tsam //
NK130(tho)001:6619: bshad la bsod nams dpag tu med do zhes //
NK130(tho)001:6620: thub pa chog des gsungs phyir dge ba des //
NK130(tho)001:6621: 'gro kun rdo rje'i theg pa 'jug gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:6622: gnas ngan len gyi 'gro ba mtha' dag dang //
NK130(tho)001:6623: khyad par dam chos spangs pa'i las 'bras kyis //
NK130(tho)001:6624: dmyal med shin tu bzod dkas gdung pa dag /
NK130(tho)001:6625: thar pa thob nas bde la reg gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:6627: da ni zhar la sdon gyi dus su grags pa'i lha bla ma rnam gnyis dang /
NK130(tho)001:6628: bdag nyid chen po 'gos lo ts+aa ba khug pa
NK130(tho)001:6629: lhas btsas kyi bka' shog 'byams yig lan du gsol
NK130(tho)001:6631: de la lha bla ma ye shes 'od 'di ni
NK130(tho)001:6632: 'jam dpal rtsa ba'i rgyud las lung bstan pa'i rgyal
NK130(tho)001:6633: po byang chub sems dpa' chen po yin te /
NK130(tho)001:6634: 'dis bstan pa phyis dar gyi mgo brtsams pa'i dus der ni /
NK130(tho)001:6637: kha cig trong nge yin zer /
NK130(tho)001:6638: rgyal po glang dar mas bstan pa bsnubs pa'i rjes
NK130(tho)001:6639: su klu mes la sogs pas dge 'dun gyi sde
NK130(tho)001:6640: gtsugs / so sor thar pa'i sdom pa'i bka' ma
NK130(tho)001:6641: chad kyang dge 'dun rnams slob dpon sun phyungs nas
NK130(tho)001:6642: gtsugs / / chos kyi gzhung lugs la rang gis gzhung rtsa 'grel la gzhigs nas rtog chos 'chad /
NK130(tho)001:6643: lta ba tha dad pa mi mthun pa zing zing ba ltar gyur /
NK130(tho)001:6644: sham thabs sngon po can dang +aatsar+ya dmar po zhabs
NK130(tho)001:6645: kyis gsang sngags kyi chags lam bsgyur bas mnga' ris
NK130(tho)001:6646: stod kyi dge 'dun rnams la chags lam dar /
NK130(tho)001:6647: de'i steng du sngags pa rnams kyang slob dpon med
NK130(tho)001:6648: par chos rang gis gzhigs pa'i rtog chos 'chad cing
NK130(tho)001:6649: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin par spyod
NK130(tho)001:6650: / bstan pa yod kyang lta spyod rnal ma med pas /
NK130(tho)001:6651: bod du bstan pa rnam dag 'dzugs par dgongs nas sngags pa rnams la bka' shog 'di bardzangasa /
NK130(tho)001:6652: rab tu byung ba rnams la sde snod gsum phyin
NK130(tho)001:6653: ci log par ston shes pa'i pan+di ta zhig spyan
NK130(tho)001:6654: ma drangs na mi thul bar dgongs nas jo bo
NK130(tho)001:6655: rje spyan 'dren pa btang yang spyan ma 'drongs /
NK130(tho)001:6656: pan+di ta gzhan 'ga' spyan drangs kyang smon lam gyi
NK130(tho)001:6657: shugs chung bas bod du bstan pa skyon med ma
NK130(tho)001:6658: tshugs / bar der lo ts+aa ba chen po rin
NK130(tho)001:6659: chen bzang po dpon g.yog nyi shu rtsa gcig kha
NK130(tho)001:6660: cher chos slob pa la bardzangasa pa las /
NK130(tho)001:6661: skabs shig tu gar log gi dmag gis lha bla ma bzung pas btson khang du sku gshegs /
NK130(tho)001:6662: de'i zhal chems ltar rang gi sras lha btsun pa byang chub 'od kyis jo bo rje spyan 'drongs /
NK130(tho)001:6663: bod du bstan pa rnam dag btsugs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6664: zhes spyir btang ba'i lo rgyus 'dis kyang bstan pa
NK130(tho)001:6665: spyi dang chab shog 'di dag gi go ba longs
NK130(tho)001:6666: pa yod do // de ltar yang lha bla ma
NK130(tho)001:6667: 'dis ni sngags rnying ma'i chos bkag pa ma yin
NK130(tho)001:6668: pa yod do // / chos de spyod pa'i gang
NK130(tho)001:6669: zag rnams kyis rgyud sde'i don ma go bar sbyor
NK130(tho)001:6670: sgrol la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin par bzung nas
NK130(tho)001:6671: spyod pa de bkag pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6673: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa sngags gsar rnying gnyis ka nas mthun par bshad /
NK130(tho)001:6674: bam sgrub kyang ro langs gser sgrub ces mkha' spyod
NK130(tho)001:6675: la sogs pa'i grub chen brgyad gsar ma'i rgyud du
NK130(tho)001:6676: byung / bdud rtsi ril bu sgrub pa la'ang rnying
NK130(tho)001:6677: ma pa sman sgrub zer bas don du 'dra yang
NK130(tho)001:6678: byung / / spyod tshul de rnams dngos grub sgrub
NK130(tho)001:6679: pa la sogs pa'i skabs su dgos pa ma go
NK130(tho)001:6680: bar thams cad kyis 'byol nyog tu spyad pa la
NK130(tho)001:6682: de bas na nga'i bka' shog 'di la yid mi dga' ba ma byed /
NK130(tho)001:6683: gal te phog thug byung na khyed rang la lta
NK130(tho)001:6684: ba rnam par dag pa yod bzhin du de'i go
NK130(tho)001:6687: pu hrangs kyi rgyal po lha bla ma'i zhal snga
NK130(tho)001:6688: nas bod yul dbus kyi sngags pa rnams la bardzangasa
NK130(tho)001:6689: pa / gnyen po mdzad cing lta ba bsrang bar zhu'o //
NK130(tho)001:6690: 'o kol mi mjed lho yi 'dzam gling 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:6691: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa sku bltams te //
NK130(tho)001:6692: brgyad khri bzhi stong nyon mongs gnyen po ru //
NK130(tho)001:6693: sde snod gsum la brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6694: rgyu dang gnyen po don du gsungs pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6695: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med rnam pa lnga //
NK130(tho)001:6696: de las bzlog pa'i chos kyi rgyu 'bras ni //
NK130(tho)001:6697: bden bzhi'i sgor zhugs nyis brgya lnga bcu gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6698: mthong dang goms pas nyon mongs brgyad bcu gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:6699: nyan thos theg par nyi ma'i gnyen gyis gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6700: phyi nang chos rnams rten 'brel bcu gnyis su //
NK130(tho)001:6701: rtogs nas rang gis byang chub rim gyis sgrub //
NK130(tho)001:6702: ya ma zung gi rdzu 'phrul mthu ldan pa //
NK130(tho)001:6703: rang rgyal theg par 'gro ba'i mgon pos bstan //
NK130(tho)001:6704: bden pa gnyis kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing //
NK130(tho)001:6705: phyi nang chos rnams stong pa'i ngo bo mkhyen //
NK130(tho)001:6706: pha rol phyin rnams rim gyis rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK130(tho)001:6707: bla na med pa'i theg par ston pas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:6709: 'dir sngags kyi tshul yod pa yang sbas te /
NK130(tho)001:6710: sngags pa rnams kyang sde snod gsum la bslab cing
NK130(tho)001:6711: de'i tshul la spyod pa zhig byung na de nas
NK130(tho)001:6712: rim gyis gsang sngags rnam par dag pa la slob
NK130(tho)001:6713: par dgongs pa'o // tshigs bcad de dag gi don bsdu na /
NK130(tho)001:6714: gsang sngags gsungs pa sbas te ston pas sde snod
NK130(tho)001:6715: gsum gsungs pa'i tshul rnam bzhag dang bcas pa bstan
NK130(tho)001:6716: nas / de'i nang nas kyang mchog tu gyur pa phar phyin theg pa yin mod /
NK130(tho)001:6717: de'i lta spyod stong nyid snying rje dang sngags pa rnams mthun pa ni lta ci smos /
NK130(tho)001:6718: theg dman nyan rang dang yang mthun pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6719: ji ltar mi mthun zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:6720: grong na gnas pa'i mkhan po sngags pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6721: theg pa de gsum gang dang 'brel med par //
NK130(tho)001:6722: nged cag theg chen yin zhes zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6723: theg pa chen po'i tshul spyad gtan med par //
NK130(tho)001:6724: theg pa chen po yin zhes zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6725: sprang po rgyal po yin zhes zer ba 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:6726: theg chen min par theg chen khas che ba //
NK130(tho)001:6727: bod bus seng ge'i pags pa gyon pa 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:6728: gzung 'dzin gnyis spangs tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:6729: sa bcu'i rgyal tshabs 'phags pa byams pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:6730: shes bya'i sgrib pa da dung ma byang na //
NK130(tho)001:6731: de bas snyigs ma'i sems can 'phags sam ci //
NK130(tho)001:6732: 'dod lnga bud med rdzab las ma thar bar //
NK130(tho)001:6733: chos kyi sku yin zer ba ya mtshan che //
NK130(tho)001:6734: mi dge bcu spyod khyi phag brtul zhug can //
NK130(tho)001:6735: mu stegs 'ban 'ji ba yi chos spyod khyed //
NK130(tho)001:6736: nged cag sangs rgyas yin ces zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6737: bdud kyis bslus sam yang na smyo bar nges //
NK130(tho)001:6739: khyed chos skur 'dod pa la sogs pa tshig dang spyod pa mi mthun pas bdud kyis bslus pa'am /
NK130(tho)001:6740: smyo ba yin na ma gtogs da phyin chad de ltar ma byed ces pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:6741: gna' sngon bod yul dbus su chos byung ba //
NK130(tho)001:6742: ngan song sgo gcod thar pa'i lam ston pa //
NK130(tho)001:6743: sde snod rin chen gsum po dar zhing rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:6744: sngon gyi rgyal po byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK130(tho)001:6745: bka' dang bstun nas chos log 'di bkag ste //
NK130(tho)001:6746: kun gyi lta bsrang mtho ris sgo phye bas //
NK130(tho)001:6747: sems can mang po bla med lam du chud //
NK130(tho)001:6749: de ltar lha bla ma nga nyid kyis da lta khyed rnams la gdams pa 'di ni /
NK130(tho)001:6750: sngon gyi rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa' dag gi dus su'ang byung ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:6751: de'i dus su gsang sngags bsgyur pa las kha cig
NK130(tho)001:6752: gis da lta khyed rnams kyi spyod pa ltar rgyud
NK130(tho)001:6753: sde'i dgongs don ma longs par sgra ji bzhin pa
NK130(tho)001:6755: thabs shes rab kyi rnal 'byor nyams dmas bar byed
NK130(tho)001:6756: cing rang gzhan phung ba'i tshul la 'jug par gzigs
NK130(tho)001:6757: nas / slad nas bka' bstsal pa ma gtogs rnal
NK130(tho)001:6758: 'byor chen po'i rgyud rnams bsgyur du med par bkas
NK130(tho)001:6759: bcad de zhes thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston gsungs
NK130(tho)001:6761: dus der lta ba klu sgrub kyi lugs /
NK130(tho)001:6763: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum bkas bcad do //
NK130(tho)001:6764: gzhan rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud rnams dngos su bsgyur ba dang spyod pa bkag pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6765: da lta las zad rgyal po'i khrims nyams pas //
NK130(tho)001:6766: rdzogs chen ming btags chos log bod du dar //
NK130(tho)001:6767: lta ba phyin ci log gi sar thogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6768: chos par ming btags sngags log bod du dar //
NK130(tho)001:6770: ci rdzogs chen ming btags chos log bod du dar //
NK130(tho)001:6771: zhes pas rdzogs chen bkag go zhe na ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:6772: rdzogs chen du ming btags pa'i lta ba phyin ci
NK130(tho)001:6773: log gi sar thogs pa 'di dar bas sngags log
NK130(tho)001:6774: spyod pa la ming chos par btags pa 'dis rgyal
NK130(tho)001:6775: khams phung po zhes pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:6776: rdzogs chen gyi ming du btags pa de dar bas skyon ci byung zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:6777: de yis rgyal khams phung ste 'di ltar gyur //
NK130(tho)001:6778: sgrol ba dar bas ra lug dmyal thag gcod //
NK130(tho)001:6779: sbyor ba dar bas mi rigs 'chol par 'dres //
NK130(tho)001:6780: sman sgrub dar bas nad pa'i gso rkyen chad //
NK130(tho)001:6781: sman sgrub dar bas khyi phag 'tsho ba chad zer ba dag go //
NK130(tho)001:6782: bam sgrub dar bas dur sa'i mchod pa stong //
NK130(tho)001:6783: mchod sgrub dar bas mi la gson sgrol byung //
NK130(tho)001:6784: srin po sha za mchod pas mi nad phyugs nad byung //
NK130(tho)001:6785: mi gsur dud pa btang bas yul gyi lha klu 'phangs //
NK130(tho)001:6786: de ltar spyod pa theg chen yin nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:6787: zhes spyod pa des gzhan phung ba'i tshul de ltar byung ngo zhes ston pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:6789: khyed cag grong gi mkhan po sngags pa'i spyod tshul 'di //
NK130(tho)001:6790: rgyal khams gzhan du thos nas gzhan dag ngo mtshar rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:6791: nged cag sangs rgyas yin no zer ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6792: las kyi srin po bas ni snying rje chung //
NK130(tho)001:6793: khra dang spyang ki bas ni sha dad che //
NK130(tho)001:6794: bod rangs glang rangs bas ni 'dod chags che //
NK130(tho)001:6795: khang rul sbur gog bas ni skyar dad che //
NK130(tho)001:6796: khyi dang phag pa bas ni gtsang tsog chung //
NK130(tho)001:6797: zhes pa dag rgyal khams gzhan du thos na mi rnams khrel ba'i gzhi dang /
NK130(tho)001:6798: lta ba rbad kham gyis rgyu 'bras khyad du bsad
NK130(tho)001:6799: pas rang phyi ma ngan song gi gnas las ma
NK130(tho)001:6800: 'phags la / tshe 'dir yang las kyi srin po
NK130(tho)001:6801: bas snying rje chung ba sogs kyi skyon de 'dug
NK130(tho)001:6803: mdo rgyud kyi go rim ma phye ba'i skyon kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6804: mdo dang bya spyod kyi lha rnams la yang nang
NK130(tho)001:6805: mchod dang sha khrag gis mchod pa la sogs te
NK130(tho)001:6806: / gtsang ma lha yi rigs la dri chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:6807: dri chu khu chu khrag gi mchod phul bas //
NK130(tho)001:6808: ro myags 'dam du skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:6809: sde snod gsum gyi chos la skur btab pas //
NK130(tho)001:6810: mnar med dmyal bar skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:6811: sgrol bas srog chags gsod pa'i rnam smin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6812: las kyi srin po skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:6813: sbyor bas 'dod chags dar ba'i rnam smin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6814: mngal gyi srin bur skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:6815: sha khrag gcin gyis dkon mchog gsum mchod cing //
NK130(tho)001:6816: ldem dgongs mi shes drang thad chos spyod pa //
NK130(tho)001:6817: gnod sbyin srin por skye'o theg chen pa //
NK130(tho)001:6818: de ltar spyod pa'i sangs rgyas e ma mtshar //
NK130(tho)001:6819: khyed kyi spyod pa 'di kas sangs rgya na //
NK130(tho)001:6820: rngon pa nya pa shan pa smad 'tshong ma //
NK130(tho)001:6821: gcig kyang ma lus byang chub thob par nges //
NK130(tho)001:6822: khyed cag grong gi mkhan po sngags pa kun //
NK130(tho)001:6823: nged cag theg chen yin ces ma zer bar //
NK130(tho)001:6824: phyin ci log gi lta ba 'di spongs la //
NK130(tho)001:6825: ma nor dri med sde snod gsum la spyod //
NK130(tho)001:6826: snga phyogs mi dge bcu spyod mthol bshags gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6827: de ltar ma byas chos log 'di spyod na //
NK130(tho)001:6828: las kyi rnam par smin pas mi bslu ste //
NK130(tho)001:6829: ston pa'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dag las //
NK130(tho)001:6830: chos nyid stong par gsungs pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:6831: las kyi rnam par smin par yid ches byos //
NK130(tho)001:6832: las rnams mi bslu rang gi phyi bzhin 'brang //
NK130(tho)001:6833: 'byung ba bzhi la rnam smin mi 'gyur bar //
NK130(tho)001:6834: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi bzod pas //
NK130(tho)001:6835: spyod ngan 'di spangs sde snod gsum po spyod //
NK130(tho)001:6836: theg pa chen por smon cing 'dod pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6837: tshogs gnyis gsog cing gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis spongs //
NK130(tho)001:6838: sbyin pa la sogs pha rol phyin bcu spyod //
NK130(tho)001:6839: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa mtha' dag sgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:6840: byams dang snying rjes 'gro don rdzogs par gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6841: de ltar spyod na theg pa chen po yin //
NK130(tho)001:6842: khyed cag 'ban 'ji rnams la bskur pa 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:6843: theg chen spyod pa mang por bsnyen par gyis //
NK130(tho)001:6844: zhes pa thugs brtse bas bslab bya yin la /
NK130(tho)001:6845: de ltar ma byas na khyed rnams lta spyod log pa 'di ka spyad na ni /
NK130(tho)001:6846: gti mug mun pa'i tshogs kyis shes rab rmongs //
NK130(tho)001:6847: 'dod chags rgya mtsho'i 'dam du rnam shes bying //
NK130(tho)001:6848: nga rgyal chen po'i ri bos ngan 'gror mnan //
NK130(tho)001:6849: phrag dog rlung dmar 'tshubs pas 'khor bar g.yeng //
NK130(tho)001:6850: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i mdud pa dam pos bcings //
NK130(tho)001:6851: thar pa thob pa dka' mor mi mchi'am //
NK130(tho)001:6852: pu hrangs kyi rgyal po lha bla mas bod kyi sngags pa rnams la bardzangasa pa rdzogs so //
NK130(tho)001:6853: de ltar skyon bzhi bstan nas de dag las bzlog par gyis shig ces gsungs pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:6854: chos rgyal byang chub sems dpa' 'di'i dgongs pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:6855: bod kyi sngags pa rnams kyang sde snod gsum gyi
NK130(tho)001:6856: sgor zhugs nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i ngan spyod
NK130(tho)001:6857: de rnams rang shugs la khegs nas bstan pa rnam
NK130(tho)001:6859: gsang sngags kyi tshul la yang bslab na mdo sngags
NK130(tho)001:6860: zung 'brel du gyur nas bstan pa khyab che zhing
NK130(tho)001:6861: dar bar 'gyur ba la dgongs pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:6862: 'di ni rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud du /
NK130(tho)001:6863: thabs dang mi ldan ye shes dang //
NK130(tho)001:6864: bslab pa dag kyang bshad pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6865: dpa' bo chen pos nyan thos rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6866: de la gzud pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:6868: bka' shog 'di dang lo ts+aa ba chen po rin
NK130(tho)001:6869: chen bzang po'i sngags log sum 'byin gyi dgongs don
NK130(tho)001:6870: la khyad par mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:6871: lha bla ma ye shes 'od kyi bka' shog gi dgongs 'grel rdzogs so ////
NK130(tho)001:6872: de nas slad du lha bla ma'i bka' shog 'di
NK130(tho)001:6873: la khyod kyis lan ji lta ba bzhin ma byas
NK130(tho)001:6874: 'dug pas dngos lan thebs po zhig cis kyang byed
NK130(tho)001:6875: dgos zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi ngor smras pa /
NK130(tho)001:6877: 'o kol mi mjed lho yi 'dzam gling 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:6879: bla na med pa'i theg par ston pas gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:6881: gcen po kho res rgyal srid gcung trong de la
NK130(tho)001:6882: gtad nas rab tu byung ste mtshan ye shes 'od
NK130(tho)001:6883: ces bya'o // des mtshan nyid kyi theg pa bkar
NK130(tho)001:6884: shes kyang sngags pa rnams kyis sbyor sgrol la sogs
NK130(tho)001:6885: spyod log gis bka' yin min the tshom du gyur
NK130(tho)001:6886: ces bya'o // te / rin chen bzang po la
NK130(tho)001:6887: sogs pa'i khye'u nye shu rtsa gcig rgya gar la
NK130(tho)001:6890: rin chen bzang po sngags mtshan nyid thams cad la mkhas par gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:6892: lan 'di kho nas thebs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6893: zhes pa'i bar gyi lan ni gong du bstan pa des chog go //
NK130(tho)001:6895: grong na gnas pa'i mkhan po sngags pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6896: theg pa de gsum gang dang 'brel med par //
NK130(tho)001:6897: nged cag theg chen yin zhes zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6898: theg pa chen po'i spyod tshul gtan med par //
NK130(tho)001:6899: theg pa chen po yin zhes zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6900: sprang po rgyal po yin ces zer dang 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:6901: theg chen min par theg chen khas 'che ba //
NK130(tho)001:6902: bong bus seng ge'i pags pa gyon dang 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:6903: gzung 'dzin gnyis spangs tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:6904: sa bcu'i rgyal tshabs 'phags pa byams pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:6905: shes bya'i sgrib pa da dung ma byang na //
NK130(tho)001:6906: de bas snyig ma'i sems can 'phags sam ci //
NK130(tho)001:6907: 'dod lnga bud med rdzab las ma thar bar //
NK130(tho)001:6908: chos kyi sku yin zer ba ya mtshan che //
NK130(tho)001:6909: mi dge bcu spyod khyi phag brtul zhugs can //
NK130(tho)001:6910: mu stegs 'ban 'ji ba yi chos spyod khyed //
NK130(tho)001:6911: nged cag sangs rgyas yin zhes zer ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:6912: bdud kyis bslus sam yang na smyo bar nges //
NK130(tho)001:6914: 'dod yon lnga spyod cing bud med dang bcas pas
NK130(tho)001:6915: theg chen gyi gral du mi chud pa 'di ni
NK130(tho)001:6916: pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa pa yang mi
NK130(tho)001:6917: bzhed de / 'phags pa sdud pa las /
NK130(tho)001:6918: gal te byang chub sems dpa' 'dod yon lnga spyod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6919: sangs rgyas chos dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun skyabs song ste //
NK130(tho)001:6920: sangs rgyas 'grub bya snyam du kun mkhyen yid byed na //
NK130(tho)001:6921: mkhas pa tshul khrims pha rol phyin gnas ring par bya //
NK130(tho)001:6924: 'dod la spyod pa thabs mkhas dang //
NK130(tho)001:6926: gsang sngags pa ni 'dod yon lnga la nges par bsten par gsungs te /
NK130(tho)001:6928: dka' thub sdom pa mi bzad pa //
NK130(tho)001:6930: 'dod pa'i longs spyod thams cad la //
NK130(tho)001:6933: sngon gyi rnal 'byor rgyud pa rgyal po rab gsal zla ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:6934: gsang 'dus pa'i rgyal po bi pu kalpa dang /
NK130(tho)001:6935: rnal 'byor ma rgyud pa'i rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au ti
NK130(tho)001:6936: la sogs pa de rnams kyang khyim pa bud med
NK130(tho)001:6937: dang bcas pa kho na yin la /
NK130(tho)001:6938: in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i khab tu bcom ldan 'das kyis theg pa thun mong gi chos bstan pas /
NK130(tho)001:6940: lum+ba'i tshal ni nyams dga' bar //
NK130(tho)001:6941: wa nyid seng ger gyur srid kyang //
NK130(tho)001:6942: 'dod yon spangs pa'i thar pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6943: bdag ni nam yang mi 'tshal lo //
NK130(tho)001:6945: dbang po rab gsang sngags kyi snod du gzigs nas
NK130(tho)001:6946: dbang bskur rgyud gsungs pas rgyal po 'khor dang bcas
NK130(tho)001:6947: pas grol ba thob pa yang gsar ma'i gzhung la
NK130(tho)001:6948: grags te / de dag kyang sde snod gsum la brten pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:6949: nged cag sangs rgyas yin no zhes pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:6950: bcom ldan 'das kyi bzhed pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:6952: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid de mtshan sum
NK130(tho)001:6953: cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa yang sems can rnams
NK130(tho)001:6956: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK130(tho)001:6959: bde gshegs snying po sems can thams cad la gnas par gsungs shing /
NK130(tho)001:6960: jo bo rjes dam tshig thams cad bsdus pa las /
NK130(tho)001:6961: thams cad chos kyi skur rtogs pa kun tu bzang po'i rgyas thebs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:6964: sems rtogs na ye shes yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan
NK130(tho)001:6965: du mi 'tshol ba'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par
NK130(tho)001:6967: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa de sangs rgyas su khas blangs pa la 'gal ba med do //
NK130(tho)001:6968: rgyal ba byams pa dang spyan ras gzigs la sogs
NK130(tho)001:6969: pa 'di dag bskal pa mang po'i sngon rol du
NK130(tho)001:6970: sangs rgyas zin pa yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:6971: da lta byang chub sems dpa'i tshul dang shes bya'i sgrib pa ma byang ba drang don yin /
NK130(tho)001:6972: gna' sngon bod yul dbus su chos byung ba //
NK130(tho)001:6974: chos par ming btags sngags log bod du dar //
NK130(tho)001:6975: zhes pa'i bar gyi lan ni gong du brjod zin to //
NK130(tho)001:6976: sgrol ba dar bas ra lug dmyal thag gcod //
NK130(tho)001:6977: ces pa ra lug bsgral lo zhes 'di'i rgyud gzhung nas ma bshad /
NK130(tho)001:6980: sku dgra lnga zhes bshad de /
NK130(tho)001:6982: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK130(tho)001:6983: dam nyams log dang 'khu ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:6985: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK130(tho)001:6986: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK130(tho)001:6989: srog don bka' dam las kyis nyams //
NK130(tho)001:6990: mtshan ma 'dod pas nyams dang bdun //
NK130(tho)001:6993: pha ma mkhan po slob dpon gsod //
NK130(tho)001:6994: rdo rje nang dme byed pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:6995: srog las nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:6996: slob dpon bka' rku ngan spyad sems //
NK130(tho)001:6997: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun gcod dang //
NK130(tho)001:6998: gsang ba gzhan la spel ba rnams //
NK130(tho)001:6999: don las nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7000: rnal 'byor gsang sngags tshul spyod la //
NK130(tho)001:7003: rtags kyi nor bstan log par mthong //
NK130(tho)001:7004: bka' las nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7005: skur ba'i gzhi med lta ba bor //
NK130(tho)001:7006: log par spyad pa dang du len //
NK130(tho)001:7007: gzhung bor phyin ci log la mkhas //
NK130(tho)001:7008: dam las nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7009: sngon chad mkhon pa'i sa med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:7010: rgod cing bzhin bzlog gnod cing 'dzugs //
NK130(tho)001:7011: rang gi nyes pa mi dran par //
NK130(tho)001:7012: bdag la mthu dang rtsal 'ded pa //
NK130(tho)001:7013: las kyis nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7014: gnyis med don la phyogs char 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:7015: lta ba sgro skur ras chod mkhan //
NK130(tho)001:7016: skye med chos la mtshan mar 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:7017: lha srin bran du ngas 'khol gyi //
NK130(tho)001:7018: mthu 'gran byed pa su zhig yod //
NK130(tho)001:7019: nga nyid dpa' yin nyams su ma mo byung //
NK130(tho)001:7020: zer zhing gzhan la khro zhing 'tshe //
NK130(tho)001:7021: mtshan mas nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7022: shes rab rnam gsum rtsal med par //
NK130(tho)001:7023: myur du mthu rtsal che 'dod dang //
NK130(tho)001:7024: las kyi gtso ru mtshan ma spyod //
NK130(tho)001:7025: rang gi gdong pa khrag gis byugs //
NK130(tho)001:7026: mi thod zhing chen mtshan mar thogs //
NK130(tho)001:7027: dmar gyi dong bu glo la btags //
NK130(tho)001:7028: 'jig rten ma mo brten byed cing //
NK130(tho)001:7029: gzhung bor mtshams med las rnams byed //
NK130(tho)001:7030: tho co rlangs po'i spyod pas bka' gzhung smad //
NK130(tho)001:7031: rnal 'byor pa la ya ga brdar //
NK130(tho)001:7032: dus gsum sangs rgyas zhabs nas drangs //
NK130(tho)001:7034: sha za ma mo gzan tshogs bkrams //
NK130(tho)001:7035: chags sems mi las nor snying 'dru //
NK130(tho)001:7038: gnyan cing btsun yang thabs kyis smod //
NK130(tho)001:7039: thob tu 'dod nas gsang sngags rku //
NK130(tho)001:7040: gzo 'dod sgrub pa'i yo byad rku //
NK130(tho)001:7041: dug tu shes kyang lto ru bza' //
NK130(tho)001:7042: 'dod pas nyams pa bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7046: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK130(tho)001:7047: theg pa chen po'i spyi dgra dang //
NK130(tho)001:7048: rdo rje theg pa smod pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:7049: rgyal khams yongs la 'tshe ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:7052: de rnams dam can las la bkol nas sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgral /
NK130(tho)001:7053: bsgral ba'i rnam shes de yang gnas spor ba yin
NK130(tho)001:7054: gyi dngos su srog chags sgrol ba ma lags so
NK130(tho)001:7055: // sbyor ba dar bas mi rigs 'chol par 'dres //
NK130(tho)001:7057: sngags kyi nye lam yas babs dang mas brtan gyi
NK130(tho)001:7058: dga' ba bzhi'i 'gros kyis byang sems rdo rje nor
NK130(tho)001:7059: bu'i rtse mo nas phyir 'da' bar mi rung bas
NK130(tho)001:7061: rigs brgyud 'jog pa'i 'dod chags la sbyor ba zhes gsang sngags pa'i lugs ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7062: sman sgrub dar bas khyi phag 'tsho ba chad //
NK130(tho)001:7064: spyir sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dang sman rnams sbyor ba yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7065: khyi phag gi 'tsho ba chad pa tsam gyi sman sgrub byas pa ni su yang med do //
NK130(tho)001:7066: dpe kha cig tu nad pa'i gso rkyen zad ces 'byung ste de lta na'ang /
NK130(tho)001:7067: sman sgrub ni rnying ma ba ma zad bon pos kyang byed la /
NK130(tho)001:7068: gsar ma ba bdud rtsi ril bu'ang mang du sgrub mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:7069: des nang pa'i sman zad pa'i gtam ci yang mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7070: bam sgrub dar bas dur sa'i mchod pa stong /
NK130(tho)001:7072: sngags gsar ma las kyang ro las mkha' spyod sgrub pa la sogs pa gsungs la /
NK130(tho)001:7073: 'dir ni mtshan nyid tshang ba'i bam de dngos grub kyi rdzas su sgrub pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:7074: ro thams cad kyis bam sgrub tu rung bar ma bshad pas skyon de yang mi 'bab bo //
NK130(tho)001:7075: mchod sgrub dar bas mi la gson sgrol byung /
NK130(tho)001:7077: spyir gsang rnying gi rgyud rnams su gsungs pa'i sgrol
NK130(tho)001:7078: ba zhes bya 'di gson po kho na sgrol ba
NK130(tho)001:7079: yin gyi gshin po la bsgral rgyu med kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7080: lha bla ma'i skabs der sngags la bsnyad pa'i spyod tshul ngan pa de byung ba yin mchi /
NK130(tho)001:7082: bdud rtsi lnga'am rdzas lnga la mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya /
NK130(tho)001:7083: bkug la rdo rje phur pas gdab /
NK130(tho)001:7084: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK130(tho)001:7085: ces gsung ba snying po las gsungs pa ltar gzugs
NK130(tho)001:7086: brnyan la de'i bla bkug nas sgrol ba yin la
NK130(tho)001:7087: / mi dngos su sgrol bar ma gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:7088: srin po sha za mchod pas mi nad phyugs nad byung //
NK130(tho)001:7091: gnod sbyin srin po 'byung po dang //
NK130(tho)001:7092: yi dwags sha za rjes byed dang //
NK130(tho)001:7093: smyo byed mkha' 'gro la sog la //
NK130(tho)001:7094: rgyun du 'am yang na zla ba'am //
NK130(tho)001:7095: de bzhin lo gcig khyud 'khor dang //
NK130(tho)001:7096: dkyil 'khor sbyin sreg bzlas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:7097: de bzhin gnod pa byung dus su'am //
NK130(tho)001:7098: zla ba yar ngo'i tshes bcu dang //
NK130(tho)001:7099: mar ngo yi ni tshes bcu la //
NK130(tho)001:7100: ji ltar 'os shing rigs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:7101: rang gi ci 'byor rjes mthun par //
NK130(tho)001:7102: nan tan du ni gtor ma sbyin //
NK130(tho)001:7105: 'byung po thams cad pa'i gtor ma //
NK130(tho)001:7107: bya spyod rnal 'byor la sogs pa'i cho ga las kyang 'byung po'i gtor ma mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:7108: de'i phyir go ba longs na gtor ma brgya rtsa
NK130(tho)001:7109: gcig gtong ba de'i khog tu yang sha za srin
NK130(tho)001:7110: po la sogs pa mchod pa yin mod /
NK130(tho)001:7112: bden dang bral ba legs ldan lha //
NK130(tho)001:7113: srin po'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK130(tho)001:7114: lho nub gdon gyi tshogs bcas la //
NK130(tho)001:7115: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK130(tho)001:7116: zhes zer bas gsar rnying khyad par med pa 'dra'o //
NK130(tho)001:7117: mi gsur dud pa btang bas yul gyi lha klu 'phangs //
NK130(tho)001:7121: na len+t+ra'i srung ma ma h+aa k+aa la phyag bzhi
NK130(tho)001:7122: pa la sogs pa mchod gtor dang bskang ba'i skabs
NK130(tho)001:7123: su'ang sha chen gyi spos zhes phyag len la mdzad
NK130(tho)001:7124: / ro sreg ni sbyong rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7126: bde dgyes la sogs pa kun la yod pas /
NK130(tho)001:7127: gsung 'dis ni de dag la yang gnod par ma gyur tam /
NK130(tho)001:7128: las kyi srin po bas ni snying rje chung //
NK130(tho)001:7130: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK130(tho)001:7131: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur bas //
NK130(tho)001:7132: de ltar rdo rje can gzigs nas //
NK130(tho)001:7133: rang nyid dgyes pa'i rdo rjer mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:7135: gdug pa can la sangs rgyas kyis kyang khro bo'i skur bzhengs pa lags mod /
NK130(tho)001:7136: khra dang spyang ki bas ni sha dad che //
NK130(tho)001:7138: so thar gyi skabs su'ang 'dul ba las /
NK130(tho)001:7139: de dge bsnyen dad pa can las blang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7140: des byin lan bstab par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7141: sha'i bdag nyid kyi sman de yang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7142: thams cad shan pa'i lag nas blang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7143: de ni bya ba nyid yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7145: sha bsngosa pa shes na bza' bar mi bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7146: stag gi rgod ma bza' bar mi bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7147: zhes pa nas sha'i byin len stob pa na /
NK130(tho)001:7148: bcad pa las byung ba nyid ma yin nam /
NK130(tho)001:7150: de ma yin na dang pos so //
NK130(tho)001:7153: mi'i sha ni thams cad du'o //
NK130(tho)001:7155: bsngosa sha ma yin pa'i sha gnang ba yin te sdom gsum las /
NK130(tho)001:7156: nyan thos rnam gsum dag pa'i sha /
NK130(tho)001:7157: bzar rung gal te mi za na //
NK130(tho)001:7158: lha sbyin gyi ni brtul zhugs 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:7160: sngags la ni dam tshig gi rten du sha nges par spyod dgos te /
NK130(tho)001:7162: glang po'i sha dang rta yi sha /
NK130(tho)001:7163: de bzhin dam pa khyi yi sha /
NK130(tho)001:7164: zas kyi phyir ni bza' bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:7165: zhes gsungs te der ma zad //
NK130(tho)001:7166: sha lnga dang ni bdud rtsi lnga //
NK130(tho)001:7167: rnam rtog spang phyir ci rigs bsten //
NK130(tho)001:7169: 'di la pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston zhabs kyis /
NK130(tho)001:7170: gtsang mi gtsang la sogs pa rtog pa'i 'ching ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:7171: rtog pa de spangs nas de dag bdud rtsir byin
NK130(tho)001:7172: gyis brlabs nas spyad na chos rnams la tha dad
NK130(tho)001:7173: kyi rtog pa 'byung ba rdzun par nges shes 'byung
NK130(tho)001:7174: la / mi ma yin kha cig de nyid la dga' bas chos bzhin du skyong ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7175: de'i gdams ngag 'dzin par yod do //
NK130(tho)001:7176: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga ni mtshon pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:7177: yul gang na sha la sogs pa mi gtsang bar 'dzin pa de la ma chags par spyod de /
NK130(tho)001:7179: zhes gsang sngags thabs myur ba'i yan lag tu bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:7180: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7182: ngan zos ngan spyod thams cad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:7183: thams cad 'grub par byed pas na //
NK130(tho)001:7184: nyes pa dag tu yongs mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:7187: sha za ba dag snying rje med //
NK130(tho)001:7188: sha ni snying rje can gyis za //
NK130(tho)001:7190: gzhan yang rgyas par yod mod kyi de tsam gyis mtshon par nus so //
NK130(tho)001:7191: bong rangs glang rangs pas ni 'dod chags che //
NK130(tho)001:7193: ston pas gsang sngags ni gdul bya 'dod chags can gyi don du gsungs pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:7195: skyes bu 'dod chags can don du //
NK130(tho)001:7197: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde bzhi po'ang 'dod chags bzhi dang sbyar nas gsungs pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:7198: dbang gsum pa'i nyams len gyi gang zag dbang po
NK130(tho)001:7199: rab de 'dod chags shin tu che ba la ngos
NK130(tho)001:7201: chags bral la sogs chags pa che //
NK130(tho)001:7203: 'dod pa chen po bde ba che //
NK130(tho)001:7204: zhes sogs kyi don yin pas so //
NK130(tho)001:7205: khang rul sbur gog pas ni skyur dad che //
NK130(tho)001:7208: chang med pa la ye shes ci //
NK130(tho)001:7209: chang ni ye shes skye ba'i rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:7210: zhes gsungs shing dus kyi 'khor lo las /
NK130(tho)001:7211: chang dang sgron ma sangs rgyas rnams dang bzang po'i
NK130(tho)001:7212: yul rnams mtha' dag 'khor lo la ni brten par
NK130(tho)001:7214: rnal 'byor dbang phyug bir+wa pa'i lo rgyus kyis kyang nges par bya zhing /
NK130(tho)001:7216: rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas 'dus ste //
NK130(tho)001:7217: thams cad zos shing kun spyod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:7219: snying rjer ldan pas smos ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:7221: khyi dang phag pa bas ni gtsang tsog chung //
NK130(tho)001:7224: bshang gci zas su zos na ni //
NK130(tho)001:7225: de dag sgrub pa'i snod du 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:7227: yid bzang brtan pa'i blo ldan pas //
NK130(tho)001:7228: khu ba phyungs nas bza' bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:7229: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs kun gyi //
NK130(tho)001:7230: sngags rnams kun gyi byin gyis rlob //
NK130(tho)001:7231: zhes gsungs pa la sogs pa'i don gyis so //
NK130(tho)001:7232: gtsang ma lha yi ris la dri chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:7233: dri chu khu chu khrag gi mchod phul bas //
NK130(tho)001:7234: ro myags 'dam du skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:7235: zhes pa la pan chen bu ston zhabs kyis /
NK130(tho)001:7236: bshang gci la sogs pa la bdud rtsir ming btags
NK130(tho)001:7237: nas lha la phur na sdig tu 'gyur ro zhe
NK130(tho)001:7239: don dam pa de kho na nyid kyi yul la
NK130(tho)001:7240: 'gal bar smra na lung yang dag pa ma yin
NK130(tho)001:7242: kun rdzob thabs kyis spyod pa la nyes pa med do //
NK130(tho)001:7243: dka' thub dang khrus dang gtsang sbra la mos pa
NK130(tho)001:7244: dag la drang ba'i don du de dag bya bar
NK130(tho)001:7245: bstan pa dang / gtsang dme med pa la dga'
NK130(tho)001:7246: ba rnams drang ba'i don du de dag mi bya
NK130(tho)001:7247: bstan pa dang / bar bstan te / bsam pa
NK130(tho)001:7248: bzang pos zin na gnyis ka yang byang chub kyi
NK130(tho)001:7249: lam du 'gyur ba la 'gal ba med de /
NK130(tho)001:7250: sems kyi sgrib pa rnam par sbyong ba las /
NK130(tho)001:7251: bsam pa bzang pos mchil lham zhig /
NK130(tho)001:7252: thub pa'i dbu la bzhag pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:7253: gzhan gyis de ni bsal byas pa //
NK130(tho)001:7254: gnyis kas rgyal srid thob par gyur //
NK130(tho)001:7255: de phyir bsam pa'i rtsa ba la //
NK130(tho)001:7256: bsod nams sdig pa rnam par gnas //
NK130(tho)001:7257: lung las de skad gsungs pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:7258: sems dge ba la nyes pa med //
NK130(tho)001:7260: de bzhin du bshang gci la sogs pa mi gtsang ba'i dngos por zhen pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7261: bcas pas thabs dang bral bas phul na sdig par 'gyur bar gsungs kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7262: thabs dang bcas pas rang bzhin gyis gdod nas dag par rtogs pa nyes pa med de /
NK130(tho)001:7263: sangs rgyas la dug dang bdud rtsi la khyad par med cing /
NK130(tho)001:7264: mi gtsang ba bshang lci dang gtsang ba bsod pa'i zas la'ang khyad par med de /
NK130(tho)001:7265: dper na khyim bdag dang la sbas kyis kha zas bsod pa la dug rnon po btab pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7266: sgyu ma mkhan bzang pos mi gtsang ba'i dngos po
NK130(tho)001:7267: la kha zas bsod pa sgyu mas sprul pa drangs
NK130(tho)001:7268: bar brtsams pas 'gyod pa skyes te /
NK130(tho)001:7269: gzhan drang bar gsal bas de nyid drangs shig gsungs nas gsol te /
NK130(tho)001:7270: dge ba byang chub tu bsngo bar mdzad pa lta bu'o //
NK130(tho)001:7272: gong du bshang gci khrag dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:7273: sha dang nyi yi sbyin sreg ni //
NK130(tho)001:7274: lha ni khyod kyis gsungs pa nyid //
NK130(tho)001:7275: ji ltar ye shes sems dpa' la //
NK130(tho)001:7276: mi gtsang bas ni kha bkang na //
NK130(tho)001:7277: sdig pa ji ltar skye mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:7278: gal te sdig las ji ltar 'bras //
NK130(tho)001:7279: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NK130(tho)001:7280: mi shes rmongs pa'i sems can gang //
NK130(tho)001:7281: ye shes thabs ni rnam par spangs //
NK130(tho)001:7282: phyi rol dngos por mngon zhen pas //
NK130(tho)001:7283: rtog pa'i d+r+aa bas d+r+aa bar byas //
NK130(tho)001:7284: de yi sdig dang bsod nams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:7285: cha gnyis rnam par rtog pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:7286: 'di rnams chos ni rang bzhin dag /
NK130(tho)001:7287: ma skyes pa dang gnas med cing //
NK130(tho)001:7288: sems can ye shes 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:7289: don dam las ni bsod nams nyid //
NK130(tho)001:7290: thabs ni sangs rgyas rnams kyis bstan //
NK130(tho)001:7291: skye ba dang ni spangs med na //
NK130(tho)001:7292: bsod nams min la su zhig zhen //
NK130(tho)001:7294: sde snod gsum gyi chos la skur btab pas //
NK130(tho)001:7295: mnar med dmyal bar skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:7298: gal te bskal pa bye bar dge ba'i las lam bcu //
NK130(tho)001:7299: spyad kyang dgra bcom rang rgyal nyid la 'dod bskyed na //
NK130(tho)001:7300: de tshe tshul khrims skyon byung tshul khrims nyams pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:7301: sems bskyed de ni phas pham bas kyang shin tu lci //
NK130(tho)001:7304: dmyal bar 'gro ba byang chub kyi //
NK130(tho)001:7305: gtan gyi gegs byed ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:7306: nyan thos dang ni rang sangs rgyas //
NK130(tho)001:7307: byang chub kyi ni gtan gyi gegs //
NK130(tho)001:7310: khas mi len pa'i lta ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7311: zhes dbu ma'i lta ba smad pas de dag kyang de ltar du mi 'gyur ram /
NK130(tho)001:7312: sgrol bas srog chags gsod pa'i rnam smin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:7313: las kyi srin por skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:7315: snying rjes sgrol ba ni byang chub kyi lam yin te /
NK130(tho)001:7316: ded dpon snying rje chen pos mi nag mdung thung
NK130(tho)001:7317: can bsad pas bskal pa mang pa'i tshogs 'dums pa
NK130(tho)001:7318: bzhin no // sbyor bas 'dod chags dar ba'i rnam smin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:7319: mngal gyi srin bur skye ba snying re rje //
NK130(tho)001:7321: de ni sngags kyi lam 'dir thabs kyis zin pas ma yin la /
NK130(tho)001:7323: bram ze'i khye'u bla mas tshong dpon gyi bu mo
NK130(tho)001:7324: la spyad pas tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK130(tho)001:7326: sngags gsar ma'i bla med pas kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7328: ma dang sring mo bu mo la //
NK130(tho)001:7331: sha khrag gcin gyis dkon mchog gsum mchod cing //
NK130(tho)001:7332: ldem dgongs mi shes drang thad chos spyod pa //
NK130(tho)001:7333: gnod sbyin srin po skye'o theg chen pa //
NK130(tho)001:7334: zhes pa bde mchog nyung ngu'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:7335: rang rdzas thig les sangs rgyas dang //
NK130(tho)001:7336: byang chub sems dpa' mchod par bya //
NK130(tho)001:7338: deng sang gsar rnying thams cad kyi nang mchod dang
NK130(tho)001:7339: gtor ma dang tshogs 'khor la sha lnga bdud rtsi
NK130(tho)001:7341: khyed kyi spyod pa 'di kas sangs rgyas na //
NK130(tho)001:7342: rngon pa nya pa shan pa smad tshong ma //
NK130(tho)001:7343: gcig kyang ma lus byang chub thob pa nges //
NK130(tho)001:7345: de dag thabs kyis ma zin pas rang ga mar spyod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7346: sngags kyi spyod pa mtshungs pa'i skabs nam yang med kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7347: tha mal pas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen 'ban po chung ma can du mthong ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7348: dpal sha ba ri dbang phyug ri dgas gsod pa'i rngon par mthong ba bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:7349: khyed cag grong gi mkhan po sngags pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:7350: nged cag theg chen yin zhes ma zer bar //
NK130(tho)001:7351: phyin ci log gi lta ba 'di spongs la //
NK130(tho)001:7352: zhes pa lta ba dang spyod pa nor 'dug pas yi ge ma dag pa'i skyon yin pa 'dra'o //
NK130(tho)001:7353: ma nor dri med sde snod gsum la spyod /
NK130(tho)001:7355: 'dir theg pa rim pa dgu la rim gyis 'jug pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7356: gcig car 'jug pa gnyis gsungs pas gang ltar yang
NK130(tho)001:7357: rung ste sde snod gsum la spyod pa shugs las
NK130(tho)001:7358: 'grub bo // snga phyogs mi dge bcu la mthol bshags gyis //
NK130(tho)001:7361: bdag cag sems can lags pas 'khrul pa byung //
NK130(tho)001:7362: chos rnams sgyu ma lags pas bshags pas 'byang //
NK130(tho)001:7363: zhes dang na rag dong spyugs la sogs pa chos skad shin tu mthun no //
NK130(tho)001:7364: de ltar ma byas spyod log 'di spyad na //
NK130(tho)001:7366: chab shog 'dir sngags gsar ma gsungs pa'i tshul yang sbas //
NK130(tho)001:7367: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa dag kyang smad pas //
NK130(tho)001:7368: de lta na chos spong du 'gyur bas so //
NK130(tho)001:7369: ston pa'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dag las //
NK130(tho)001:7370: chos nyid stong pa yin pa bden mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:7371: las kyi rnam par smin par yid ches gyis //
NK130(tho)001:7372: las rnams mi bslu rang gi phyi bzhin 'brang //
NK130(tho)001:7373: 'byung ba bzhi la rnam smin mi 'gyur bar //
NK130(tho)001:7374: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi bzod pas //
NK130(tho)001:7375: spyod ngan 'di spongs sde snod gsum po spyod //
NK130(tho)001:7376: ces pa shin tu med de /
NK130(tho)001:7377: stong pas rgyu 'bras khyad du gsod pa ni mu stegs rgyang 'phen pa'i grub mtha' yin la /
NK130(tho)001:7378: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ni stong nyid snying rje'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:7379: lta ba mtho yang spyod pa zhi ba pa theg pa 'di'i dngos bstan yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7380: theg pa chen por smon cing 'dod pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:7381: tshogs gnyis gsog cing gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis spong //
NK130(tho)001:7382: sbyin pa la sogs pha rol phyin bcu spyod //
NK130(tho)001:7383: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa mtha' dag sgrub //
NK130(tho)001:7384: byams dang snying rjes 'gro don rdzogs par gyis //
NK130(tho)001:7385: de ltar spyod pa theg pa chen po yin //
NK130(tho)001:7386: zhes pa rnams logs su bsgrub mi dgos par bum dbang gi sdom pa'i khongs su 'byung ste /
NK130(tho)001:7388: 'di dag thams cad r+ts+wa sogs bzhin du btang //
NK130(tho)001:7389: de bzhin tshul khrims bzod pa brtson 'grus dang //
NK130(tho)001:7390: bsam gtan shes rab bla na med pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:7391: bdag dang gzhan la phan par bya ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:7392: skad cig re re zhing yang bskyed par bgyi //
NK130(tho)001:7394: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:7396: zang zing mi 'jigs chos dang byams //
NK130(tho)001:7397: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK130(tho)001:7399: ma bsgral ba rnams bdag gis bsgral //
NK130(tho)001:7400: ma grol ba rnams bdag gis dgrol //
NK130(tho)001:7401: dbugs ma phyungs rnams dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK130(tho)001:7403: ces pa 'dis theg pa chen po'i tshul mtha' dag bsdus pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:7404: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs de ltar bsags pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:7405: gzung 'dzin gnyis ma spangs rang sar grol bas 'bras
NK130(tho)001:7406: bu ye shes kyi tshogs kyang de las gzhan du
NK130(tho)001:7407: ci / gti mug mun pa'i tshogs kyis shes rab rmongs //
NK130(tho)001:7408: 'dod chags chen po'i 'dam du rnam shes byings //
NK130(tho)001:7409: nga rgyal chen po'i ri bos ngan 'gror mnan //
NK130(tho)001:7410: phrag dog rlung dmar 'tshubs pas 'khor bar g.yengs //
NK130(tho)001:7411: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i mdud pa dam pos bcings //
NK130(tho)001:7412: thar pa thob pa dka' mor mi mchi'am //
NK130(tho)001:7414: nyon mongs pa dug lnga po de yang pha rol
NK130(tho)001:7415: tu phyin pa'i theg pa nas spang byar mdzad kyang
NK130(tho)001:7416: / gsang sngags pas lam du blangs pas dug lnga ye shes lngar grol ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:7418: chags pas chags pa dag 'gyur te //
NK130(tho)001:7419: zhe sdang nyid kyis zhe sdang sbyang //
NK130(tho)001:7420: gti mug nyid kyis gti mug sbyang //
NK130(tho)001:7421: nga rgyal nyid kyis nga rgyal sbyang //
NK130(tho)001:7422: phrag dog gis ni phrag dog sbyang //
NK130(tho)001:7423: rdo rje 'dzin sogs thams cad sbyang //
NK130(tho)001:7426: ji ltar tshad pa'i tshig pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:7427: me nyid la ni bdug par bya //
NK130(tho)001:7428: de bzhin 'dod chags mes tshig pa //
NK130(tho)001:7429: 'dod chags me yis bdug par bya //
NK130(tho)001:7430: skye bo mi bzad pa yi las //
NK130(tho)001:7431: gang dang gang gis 'ching gyur ba //
NK130(tho)001:7432: thabs dang bcas na de nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:7436: bzlog pa'i sgom pa 'di nyid ni //
NK130(tho)001:7437: sangs rgyas mu stegs kyis mi shes //
NK130(tho)001:7439: bdag 'dzin ni 'khor ba'i rtsa ba yin pas slob dpon chos kyi grags pas kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7440: bdag yod na ni gzhan du shes //
NK130(tho)001:7441: bdag gzhan cha las 'dzin dang sdang //
NK130(tho)001:7442: de dag dang ni 'brel ba las //
NK130(tho)001:7444: zhes pas de las nges par grol dgos shing //
NK130(tho)001:7445: grol bar bya ba'i thabs ni 'dir rgyud las //
NK130(tho)001:7446: srid pa'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin nyid //
NK130(tho)001:7447: phyi nang kun brtags ye stong grol //
NK130(tho)001:7449: 'dzin pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye gdod ma'i
NK130(tho)001:7450: gnas lugs stong par chen por grol bas na thar
NK130(tho)001:7451: pa thob pa la dka' mo mi bdog go //
NK130(tho)001:7452: rgyal bas lung bstan chos rgyal sems dpa' che /
NK130(tho)001:7453: gang gi bka' shog dgongs pa can gyi lan //
NK130(tho)001:7454: mi shes bzhin du bgyis pa mthol lo bshags kyi //
NK130(tho)001:7455: dge ba de yang 'gro kun grol phyir bsngo //
NK130(tho)001:7456: de'i sras tha chung pho brang zhi ba 'od kyi bka' shog ni 'di yin te /
NK130(tho)001:7458: du hrangs kyi pho brang zhi ba 'od gsang sngags phyi nang gi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7461: dkyil 'khor cho ga mtha' dag la mkhas pa'i zhal snga nas mdzad de /
NK130(tho)001:7462: bod kyi rgyal khams kyi sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK130(tho)001:7463: la gnas shing rdo rje theg pa la zhugs pa
NK130(tho)001:7464: rnams la brtse bar dgongs nas chu pho spre'u'i lo
NK130(tho)001:7466: sangs rgyas kyi bka' ltar bcos pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7468: sgrub thabs snga phyir bod du rgya gar ma'i ming
NK130(tho)001:7469: btags shing bod kyis byas pa ni 'di dag ste
NK130(tho)001:7470: / sngar gyi dus kyi phyi rgyud kyi ngan song sbyong rgyud kyi 'grel pa che chung ngam /
NK130(tho)001:7471: rgyan dam pa la sogs pa cho ga che phran mang du yod pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7472: khams nas byung ba rnams la ma nor ba cher med /
NK130(tho)001:7473: de'ang 'di dang mthun par dpyad na /
NK130(tho)001:7474: kri ya'i cho ga rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7475: 'grel pa ltar bcos pa'i bsnyel rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7476: nang pa la sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyud la bcu gsum pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7480: le'u lag la sogs pa rnams ni 'dres mar snang /
NK130(tho)001:7481: zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas la sogs pas byas pa'i gsang ba snying po'i 'grel pa spar bka' dang /
NK130(tho)001:7482: sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa'i 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7483: mig bcu drug la sogs pa'i 'grel pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7484: rdo rje las rim la sogs pa'i sgrub thabs rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7485: cho ga che phran rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7486: dar rje dpal gyi grags pas byas zer ba'i mdo
NK130(tho)001:7487: lnga la zur che chung gis byas pa'i 'grel pa
NK130(tho)001:7488: rnams dang / 'khor lo sting rdzogs dang /
NK130(tho)001:7491: rnal 'byor mig gi sgron ma la sogs pa'i sgrub thabs rtsa 'grel rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7492: mya ngan las 'das pa che chung la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7493: phur pa'i rgyud dang khu byug rol pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7494: de'i bshad rgyud k+ai la ya'i tan+t+ra dang /
NK130(tho)001:7498: k+ai la ya tan+t+ra chung ngu dang /
NK130(tho)001:7499: byi to'i rgyud du gsol ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7504: zhe sdang sems su dag pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7505: gsang sngags drug gi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7508: 'phros pa man gi rgyud lnga zer te /
NK130(tho)001:7511: gzhan yang gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches
NK130(tho)001:7512: byas pa'i dpal khro bo'i rgyud la sogs pa rgyud
NK130(tho)001:7514: bdud rtsi bam po brgyad pa la sogs pa sgrub thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7515: sgrub thabs dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7516: yang gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches byas
NK130(tho)001:7517: pa'i rdzogs pa chen po nam mkha' che'i 'grel pa
NK130(tho)001:7518: rig pa'i nyi ma la sogs pa man ngag tu
NK130(tho)001:7519: gsol ba dang / gnod sbyin gyi rgyud rag ti dang /
NK130(tho)001:7523: 'dra men bong lto la sogs pa cho ga dpag tu med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7524: +aa tsar+ya bi ma la mi tras bsgyur ba'i sems phyogs kyi phyis 'gyur bcu gsum la /
NK130(tho)001:7525: rmad du byung ba le'u bzhi bcu zhe gsum dang /
NK130(tho)001:7526: byang chub sems bde 'byams rin po che dang /
NK130(tho)001:7527: lta ba bal nag la sogs pa'i 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7529: yig chung dang bcas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7530: nyang stod khro gdas su drang nga shag tshul gyis
NK130(tho)001:7531: byas pa'i sems sde bco brgyad kyi rgyud rnams la
NK130(tho)001:7537: dbang bskur gyi man ngag dang /
NK130(tho)001:7539: sems nyams kyi man ngag dang /
NK130(tho)001:7540: srid pa rgyud lung la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7541: ma mo'i rgyud lung la sogs pa ma mo'i chos thams cad dang /
NK130(tho)001:7542: gzhan yang rgyal po'i chos lnga la sogs te rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7545: cho gar ming btags pa dpag tu med do //
NK130(tho)001:7546: phyis gsar du byung ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7549: sgrub thabs la +aa tsar+ya dmar pos byas pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i thig le dang /
NK130(tho)001:7550: ye shes snying po'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7555: dbang gi man ngag gsogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7557: dbang rin chen 'khor lo la sogs pa'i man ngag rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au tis mdzad zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7558: sgron gsal gyi ti ka b+ha ba ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:7559: rim lnga'i 'grel pa slob dpon klu'i byang chub kyis mdzad zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7560: kun rig rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga gsar
NK130(tho)001:7561: ma le'u nye shu rtsa bzhi pa'i 'grel pa dang
NK130(tho)001:7563: de'i sgrub thabs dang bcas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7564: o rgyan gyi yul nas sems phyogs kyi chos byung
NK130(tho)001:7565: zer te byas pa srog 'byung nam mkha'i rgyud 'grel
NK130(tho)001:7568: rlangs dpal gyi ye shes kyis bsgyur ba'i phyag na rdo rje gos sngon can gyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7571: sbyin sreg gi cho ga dang /
NK130(tho)001:7572: sgrub thabs b+ha ba ma che chung la sogs pa dpag tu med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7573: pan+di ta mee tri pa'i chos le rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7574: n+aa ga rdzu nas mdzad zer ba'i phyag rgya bzhi pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7576: dbang rnam par nges pa rtsa 'grel dang bcas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7577: phyag rgya bzhi pa'i man ngag dang /
NK130(tho)001:7580: rdo rje phag mo'i byin rlabs dang /
NK130(tho)001:7581: sgrub thabs mu stegs pa dang bsres nas snang bas byar mi rung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7582: gzhan yang man ngag gser phreng la sogs pa do ha ko sha'i glu la bslad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7583: bal po sh+r+ai sing ha'i glu la bslad pa la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7585: 'di rnams gang yang yang dag pa'i lam ma yin
NK130(tho)001:7586: cing bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par mi
NK130(tho)001:7587: 'gyur bas / skyabs gnas dang lam du sus kyang byar mi rung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7588: rab tu byung ba rnams kyis 'dul ba ltar bsrung zhing /
NK130(tho)001:7589: bka' gsang sngags la zhugs pa rnams kyis kyang 'dul ba la brten pa dang mi 'gal bar /
NK130(tho)001:7593: gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa'i bar la dam tshig ma nyams par byas la 'bad do //
NK130(tho)001:7594: shes rab kyi rgyud ni mchog tu gyur pa yin
NK130(tho)001:7595: kyang dgongs pa can gyi tshig don ma shes nas
NK130(tho)001:7596: rab tu byung ba bslab pa dang phral ba mang
NK130(tho)001:7597: bas ma byas kyang 'gal ba med pa tsam /
NK130(tho)001:7598: khyad par du rdzogs pa chen po ni lta ba
NK130(tho)001:7599: mu stegs kyi rim pa dang bsres pas 'di byas
NK130(tho)001:7600: na ngan song gi lam du 'gro bar 'gyur zhing
NK130(tho)001:7601: / bla na med pa'i byang chub la gegs byed
NK130(tho)001:7602: pas rnam pa thams cad du byar mi rung ngo
NK130(tho)001:7603: / // bod kyis byas pa'i sngags dang yi ge la /
NK130(tho)001:7604: mi g.yo ba'i sngags la brten nas phyag na rdo rje'i sgrub thabs yin zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7605: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje'i sngags la brten nas
NK130(tho)001:7606: bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje'i sgrub thabs dang
NK130(tho)001:7607: man ngag yin zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7608: gnyan +aa tsar+ya dpal dbyangs kyis byas pa'i sgron ma rnam drug dang /
NK130(tho)001:7611: man ngag tu byas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7612: gzhan yang bod kyis byas pa'i sgrub thabs mang du yod pas blo gtad du mi btub /
NK130(tho)001:7613: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi lam yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7614: bka' gdams kyi chos brgyud du grags pa 'di rnams
NK130(tho)001:7615: kyis chos log 'di rnams nyams su mi blang ngo
NK130(tho)001:7616: // pho brang zhi ba 'od kyis bod kyi chos pa rnams la phrin du bardzangasa pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:7618: 'dis rdzogs pa chen po dang rnying ma'i rgyud la
NK130(tho)001:7619: sogs pa 'ga' zhig bkag kyang rnying ma gzhan rnams
NK130(tho)001:7620: ma bkag / gsar rnying gnyis ka'i khrod na brtsams rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7621: 'grel pa sgrub skor la sogs pa bod kyis byas
NK130(tho)001:7622: pa rgya gzhung la bsnyad pa rnams 'gog par rang
NK130(tho)001:7623: gzhung gis gsal / ngan song sbyong ba'i 'grel pa
NK130(tho)001:7624: che chung zhes pa 'di slob dpon kun snying gis
NK130(tho)001:7626: pan+di tas phrag dog byas nas kho rang cog bu phub nas yi ge 'bri yis 'dug /
NK130(tho)001:7627: rgya gar na 'grel pa 'di 'dra med byas pas /
NK130(tho)001:7628: dge tshul khyung grags kyis byas par grags pa de nyid yin par snang /
NK130(tho)001:7629: 'di kun snying gis mdzad pa yin pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK130(tho)001:7630: pan+di ta gzhon nu bum pas slob dpon kun snying
NK130(tho)001:7631: 'gog pa na 'di'i gzhung drangs nas khyi +aa nan+da
NK130(tho)001:7632: gar+b+ha zhes bya ba yin zhes grags /
NK130(tho)001:7633: sgyu 'phrul brgyud cu pa la sogs pa sgyu 'phrul
NK130(tho)001:7634: sde brgyad po 'di rnams ni rgya 'grel rnams su'ang
NK130(tho)001:7635: lung mang po drangs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7636: bod kyi mkhas pa mang pos tshad mar mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:7637: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud ni zhib 'od 'dis tshad mar mdzad de /
NK130(tho)001:7638: de'i 'grel pa spar bkab zur gyis byas so gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:7639: spar bkab ni dze ta ri'i slob ma 'jam dkar
NK130(tho)001:7640: gyi grub thob slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rje zhes
NK130(tho)001:7641: pa des mdzad nges pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:7642: tshig bzang zhing barlinga bas bod rtsom gyi nyams gtan nas med /
NK130(tho)001:7643: sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa'i 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7644: mig bcu drug pa yang 'grel pa rgya gar ma
NK130(tho)001:7645: sha stag yin te 'di dag gsar rnying thun mong
NK130(tho)001:7646: bar snang / rnying ma la kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo /
NK130(tho)001:7647: dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i mdo /
NK130(tho)001:7649: ye shes rngams pa glog gi 'khor lo'i mdo /
NK130(tho)001:7650: sems lung chen mo'i mdo dang lnga po 'di a nu yo ga yin /
NK130(tho)001:7651: 'di lnga rgyud ma yin na a nu yo ga'i rtsa ba bod 'dir mi rnyed pa 'dra zhing /
NK130(tho)001:7652: 'di dag la lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK130(tho)001:7654: bru sha'i lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes gsum gyis
NK130(tho)001:7655: sa bcad ti ka stong thun la sogs pa mdzad
NK130(tho)001:7656: / lo ts+aa ba de gsum dar rje dpal gyi grags pa'i bla ma yin /
NK130(tho)001:7657: yang dar rje dang dus mtshungs kyi thog ra lo ts+aa ba nam mkha'/
NK130(tho)001:7659: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rnams kyi 'grel ti ka
NK130(tho)001:7660: dang yig cha yod pas dar rjes brtsams pa'i yul
NK130(tho)001:7661: mi snang ngo // de'i 'grel pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:7662: 'khor lo stong rdzogs la sogs pas yang de dag gi cha lag tu dgongs nas bkag pa 'dra'o //
NK130(tho)001:7663: rnal 'byor lam rim ni slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa de yin par snang ste /
NK130(tho)001:7664: dus phyis lo ts+aa ba nam mkha' bzang pos 'di'i rgya dpe gzigs pas tshad mar mdzad do //
NK130(tho)001:7665: myang 'das che chung dang phur pa'i rgyud de rnams 'grel pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7666: 'phros pa man ngag gi rgyud lnga la sogs pa
NK130(tho)001:7667: de dag kyang gsar ma la ma grags pa tsam
NK130(tho)001:7668: las gzhan gtan tshigs mi snang /
NK130(tho)001:7669: phur pa myang 'das che chung gi rgyud 'di phur pa lha nag gi rtsa ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:7670: yar 'grog pa gu rus yang dag gi rgyud 'di la brten nas phur pa lha nag byas /
NK130(tho)001:7671: rgyud kyi rnam bshad bshad 'bum rdo rje'i don gsal zhes bya ba brtsams /
NK130(tho)001:7672: de'i gong na phur pa lha nag gi ming med /
NK130(tho)001:7673: lha nag gi grub thob mang du byon pas brtsams rgyud kyi don mi snang /
NK130(tho)001:7674: +aa tsar+ya bi ma la mi tras bsgyur ba'i sems phyogs kyi phyis 'gyur bcu gsum la /
NK130(tho)001:7675: rmad du byung ba'i le'u bzhi bcu zhe gsum dang /
NK130(tho)001:7676: byang chub kyi sems bde 'byams rin po che dang /
NK130(tho)001:7678: nyang stod khro gangs su drang shag tshul gyis brtsams
NK130(tho)001:7679: pa'i sems sde bco brgyad kyi chos skor rnams la
NK130(tho)001:7682: ye shes gsang ba la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7685: rmad byung la sogs pa bi ma la'i phyis 'gyur
NK130(tho)001:7686: bcu gsum gyi steng du bee ro'i snga 'gyur lnga
NK130(tho)001:7687: bsnan pa la zer ba de ma dgongs pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:7688: de la bee ro'i snga 'gyur lnga ni nam mkha' che /
NK130(tho)001:7692: rdzogs pa spyi gcod dang lnga'o //
NK130(tho)001:7693: kha cig 'og ma gnyis po'i tshab tu khyung chen lding ba /
NK130(tho)001:7694: bsgom don drug pa gnyis la byed /
NK130(tho)001:7697: ye shes gsang ba rnams sems sde bco brgyad mi gtogs /
NK130(tho)001:7698: 'di'i shan dpal 'dzin gyis kyang ma phyed pas /
NK130(tho)001:7699: grub matha'i 'ben ma mthong bar dgag pa'i mda' 'phen pa zhes pa'i tshul du zad /
NK130(tho)001:7700: 'di rnams la zhal mthun pa su yang ma byung ste /
NK130(tho)001:7701: 'gos lhas btsas kyis rmad byung la sogs pa phyis
NK130(tho)001:7702: 'gyur bcu gsum sangs rgyas ye shes kyis byas gsungs
NK130(tho)001:7703: / 'di na bi ma las bsgyur zer ba tsam byas te bkag /
NK130(tho)001:7704: kun byed rgyal po drang shag tshul gyis byas zer /
NK130(tho)001:7705: la la ni bee ro tsa nas byas zer /
NK130(tho)001:7706: yang kha cig ni gsang ba snying po bee ros
NK130(tho)001:7707: byas so zer te gtan tshigs yang dag pa ni
NK130(tho)001:7708: su la'ang smra rgyu mi 'dug go //
NK130(tho)001:7709: ma mo srid pa rgyud lung dang /
NK130(tho)001:7710: lung bam brgyad la sogs pa ma mo'i skor rnams ni bod rtsam 'dra rung ba yod kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7711: gdul bya bod dang bo 'dra ba gzhan dag gi dbang du byas nas gsungs par bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:7713: bod du chos kyi ming yang med pa'i gong du
NK130(tho)001:7714: rgya gar du dar nas rom+bu gu h+ya dang d+aa
NK130(tho)001:7715: na sam kri ta la sogs pa ma mo'i grub
NK130(tho)001:7716: thob mang du byon don med /
NK130(tho)001:7717: slob dpon pad+ma la bde gshegs 'dus pa mkha' 'gro
NK130(tho)001:7718: mas ma gtad pa'i gong der ma mo'i rgyud lung
NK130(tho)001:7719: rnams rom+bu gu h+ya la zhus pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:7720: rgyal po'i chos lnga ni bee ro tsa na'i snga 'gyur lnga po la zer te /
NK130(tho)001:7721: gzhan zhig yin snyam du dgongs pa 'dra'o //
NK130(tho)001:7722: de'i sdebs rnams la'ang rnam dag ma yin pa'i gtan
NK130(tho)001:7723: tshigs 'gong rgya ma byung bar 'dug /+aa tsar+ya dmar
NK130(tho)001:7724: pos byas pa'i phyag rgya chen po thig le'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:7726: rgyud 'dis skya pan+di ta la sogs pa dam pa mang pos tshad mar mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:7727: ye shes snying pa'i rgyud kyi lung mang po lo chen rin chen bzang po'i bstan bcos na yod /
NK130(tho)001:7728: dbang rin chen 'khor lo'i man ngag kyang bstan bcos yin mod kyi ma dag pa'i cha ma mchis /
NK130(tho)001:7729: dbang rin 'khor rang ni lo chen gyis tshad mar bzung ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:7730: rlangs dpal gyi seng ges bsgyur ba'i phyag na rdo rje gos sngon can gyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7733: sbyin sregs kyi cho ga 'di rnams sngon gnubs pa rnams la shin tu dar /
NK130(tho)001:7735: phyis su byung ba'i phyag na rdo rje gtum po'i
NK130(tho)001:7736: chos skor bla ma wa la tsan+da la rje ras
NK130(tho)001:7737: chung pas zhus pa 'di dang khyad par cang ma
NK130(tho)001:7738: mchis / gzhan char yang rnam gsum dang rin chen snye ma la sogs pa ni ma mthong /
NK130(tho)001:7739: phyag na rdo rje b+ha ba ma ni /
NK130(tho)001:7740: rang gi yab lha bla mas pu hrangs kha phyar gyi lha khang bzhengs dus /
NK130(tho)001:7741: mtsho ma dros pa'i byang ngos na shug pa zheng
NK130(tho)001:7742: du 'dom brgyad yod pa zhig bcad pas shing de
NK130(tho)001:7743: las khrag zags / byang phyogs nas sdom g.yag tsam zhig dang /
NK130(tho)001:7744: nub nas sbal pa phyar ba tsam /
NK130(tho)001:7745: shar nas sdig pa glang tsam /
NK130(tho)001:7746: lho nas sbrul gdung ma tsam zhig byung ba dang mi thams cad ha las /
NK130(tho)001:7747: de rnams kyang lha 'dre'i zhung yin pas thon pa dang yal song /
NK130(tho)001:7748: shing de gcod pa'i mi rnams mdzes zin pas /
NK130(tho)001:7749: lha bla mas pan+di ta la 'bul ba gser mang po bskur nas zhur btang bas /
NK130(tho)001:7750: kha che nas byung ba'i phyag na rdo rje'i chos skor yin /
NK130(tho)001:7751: phyis su yag grwa pa mngon shes nas brgyud pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7752: lce dol sgang pa nas brgyud pa'i srol gnyis byung /
NK130(tho)001:7753: gnyi ga las phyag na rdo rje'i grub thob mang du byon /
NK130(tho)001:7755: ma dag pa'i cha ci yang med do //
NK130(tho)001:7756: mi tri pa'i rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:7757: klu sgrub kyi phyag rgya bzhi pa'ang mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gis tshad mar mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:7758: rnal 'byor ma'i byin rlabs dang rdo rje phag mo'i
NK130(tho)001:7759: sgrub thabs ni bir+wa pa dang n+aa ro pa la
NK130(tho)001:7760: sogs pas mdzad de deng sang du'ang sa skya pa
NK130(tho)001:7761: dang drags po bka' brgyud pa la shin tu dar
NK130(tho)001:7762: / phag zhal g.yas su byung ba la mu stegs kyi ltar lta ba'ang rang blo chung /
NK130(tho)001:7763: rgyal ba'i yum chen mo 'di lta bu la brnyas pa sdig shin tu lci /
NK130(tho)001:7764: mu stegs dang 'bres zer ba ni /
NK130(tho)001:7765: de dus pha rgyud ma rgyud pa gnyis chags sdang
NK130(tho)001:7766: byung bas de'i gtam yin man ngag gser phreng ni
NK130(tho)001:7767: ru lu gser phreng yin pas slob dpon h'u ka
NK130(tho)001:7768: ra'i man ngag gi rdzogs rim yin /
NK130(tho)001:7770: rdo rje 'da' ka ma ni man ngag lta phreng
NK130(tho)001:7771: gi cha lag yin pas ma dag pa med do
NK130(tho)001:7772: // spyir pho brang zhi ba 'od 'di yang lha bla ma'i dgongs pa dang mthun par /
NK130(tho)001:7773: rab tu byung ba dang sngags pa rnams kyis kyang 'dul ba'i khrims srungs /
NK130(tho)001:7775: ma rgyud ma byas na yang rung //
NK130(tho)001:7777: de dus chags lam dar ba de jo bo rjes bkags pa las /
NK130(tho)001:7779: khyad par du rdzogs pa chen po lta ba mu stegs dang 'dres pas mi rung /
NK130(tho)001:7780: zhes gsungs pa 'di lang+kara gshegs pa'i lung /
NK130(tho)001:7783: mtshan ma sna tshogs 'di dag ni //
NK130(tho)001:7784: mu stegs can lam 'khrid par byed //
NK130(tho)001:7785: ces gsungs pa 'di la brten nas mu stegs rtag
NK130(tho)001:7786: lta ba dang rdzogs chen gyi grub mtha' 'dra bas
NK130(tho)001:7787: so snyam du dgongs mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:7788: de lta na sbyor drug gi sor bsdud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7789: rim lnga pa'i snang mched thob gsum yang de ltar du thal ba'i skyon yod de /
NK130(tho)001:7790: 'od gsal gyi ngo bo gcig yin pas so //
NK130(tho)001:7791: bod kyis byas pa'i sngags dang yi ge la /
NK130(tho)001:7792: mi g.yo ba'i sngags la brten nas phyag na rdo rje'i sngags dang /
NK130(tho)001:7796: zhes byung ba la mi g.yo ba'i sngags su bsam par zad /
NK130(tho)001:7797: sngags kyi sgra don gtum po 'jigs byed chen po /
NK130(tho)001:7798: zhes pa yin na khro bo thams cad la 'thad mod /
NK130(tho)001:7799: der ma zad sngags phyogs 'dra ba lha gzhan la yang yod /
NK130(tho)001:7800: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje'i sngags la brten nas bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje'i sgrub thabs /
NK130(tho)001:7801: zhes pa yang kha che'i pan+di ta dz+ny+aa na sh+r+ai
NK130(tho)001:7802: nas stag pa jo bzang sogs la grags pa'i phyag
NK130(tho)001:7804: de'i sngags la ni l+aam ba ra d+ha ra badz+ra
NK130(tho)001:7805: p+aa ni ra dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa zhes
NK130(tho)001:7806: pa'i sgra don / phyag na rdo rje gos sngon
NK130(tho)001:7807: can 'chang ba'i bka' bzhin gyis gzhi tshugs zhes byung
NK130(tho)001:7808: pa'i sgra don / bas / de ni 'byung po
NK130(tho)001:7809: rnams la phyag na rdo rje'i bka' bzhin gyis zer
NK130(tho)001:7810: pa'i sgra don / bas / ba yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7811: phyag na rdo rje'i 'khor gzhan zhig yin par dgongs
NK130(tho)001:7812: pa'i sgra don / bas / ba yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7813: / phyag na rdo rje'i sngags gzhan dag tu ma
NK130(tho)001:7814: h+aa yak+sha sen pa ta ye zhes 'byung ba /
NK130(tho)001:7815: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po zer ba yin pa la /
NK130(tho)001:7817: gnod sbyin zhes so sor bzung ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:7818: mi g.yo ba kho na las tsan+da zhes pa lha
NK130(tho)001:7819: khro bo gzhan dang phyag rdor la mi 'ong ba
NK130(tho)001:7820: ma yin te / na mahtsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye zhes pa /
NK130(tho)001:7821: phyag na rdo rje gtum po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK130(tho)001:7822: zhes pa yin pa sogs la thugs gzhigs ma chug pa 'dra'o //
NK130(tho)001:7824: gdams ngag dad bskyed sgron ma la sogs pa'i sdebs de yin na ni /
NK130(tho)001:7825: mdzad pa po slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas yin /
NK130(tho)001:7826: tshig dang don shin tu bzang bas gnyan dpal dbyangs kyis byas pa'i yul mi snang /
NK130(tho)001:7827: lar de dus tshad mar mi 'dzin pa'i chos mang
