NK130(tho)001:7828: po phyis su lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis rgya gar
NK130(tho)001:7830: bod du sngar gyi rgya dpe rnying pa lo ts+aa
NK130(tho)001:7831: ba dag gis gzigs pas chos yang dag tu song
NK130(tho)001:7833: chos spyod mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud 'di yang dge
NK130(tho)001:7834: tshul khyung grags kyis bsgyur bas bod na brtsams rgyud
NK130(tho)001:7836: nag tsho lo ts+aa bas o tan+t+ra pu ri'i gtsug lag khang gzigs pa la byon pas /
NK130(tho)001:7837: de na pan+di ta rnams rgyud de la slob gnyer
NK130(tho)001:7838: byed pas der pan+di ta la zhus nas bod du
NK130(tho)001:7840: de ltar bka' shog 'di gnang ba po pho brang zhi ba 'od de ni jo bo rje dang /
NK130(tho)001:7841: lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang po gnyi
NK130(tho)001:7842: ga'i yon bdag kyang yin la slob ma yang yin
NK130(tho)001:7843: pa'i mkhyen pa can yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7844: mnga' ris stod kyi rgyal po mdzad pas gzhung lugs
NK130(tho)001:7845: rnams la gzigs rtog cher mdzad rgyu ma byung ba
NK130(tho)001:7846: 'dra ste / de'i dus kyi gtam du grags pa rnams yi ger bris par snang ste /
NK130(tho)001:7847: 'di la sa skya pan chen gyis kyang //
NK130(tho)001:7848: de yi slob ma zhi ba 'od //
NK130(tho)001:7849: des kyang sngags log sun 'byin pa //
NK130(tho)001:7850: zhes bya'i bstan bcos mdzad ces zer //
NK130(tho)001:7851: ces pa tsam las ched du basngagasa pa ma mdzad snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:7852: lha pho brang zhi ba 'od kyi chab shog lan du gsol pa rdzogs so ////
NK130(tho)001:7853: da ni lo ts+aa ba chen po 'gos lhas btsas
NK130(tho)001:7854: kyis mdzad do zhes pa'i 'byams yig la rgyas bsdus
NK130(tho)001:7856: da lta gnyis mthong ba 'di las lhag pa'i brjod
NK130(tho)001:7857: bya zhig logs su med pa'i phyir mi bden pa
NK130(tho)001:7858: 'dra la / 'di dag kyang ma dag pa'i cha ni 'og tu 'chad /
NK130(tho)001:7859: de bas na lo ts+aa ba mkhas pa chen po des ma mdzad par sems so //
NK130(tho)001:7861: bod kyi chos pa rnams la sbrings pa /
NK130(tho)001:7862: bskal pa bzang po 'di la dus bzhi las /
NK130(tho)001:7863: bde bar gshegs pa 'khor ba 'jigs 'jig rten du byon pa'i dus su /
NK130(tho)001:7864: sems can thams cad ma bslab par dge ba bcu
NK130(tho)001:7865: spyod pas rang gi ngang gis rdzogs pa dang ldan
NK130(tho)001:7867: de nas bar gyi bskal pa gnyis pa la bde
NK130(tho)001:7868: bar gshegs pa gser thub 'jig rten du byon pa'i
NK130(tho)001:7869: dus su / dge ba bcu las srog gcod /
NK130(tho)001:7871: tshig rtsub gsum spong bas gsum ldan zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7872: de nas bar bskal gsum pa la 'od srungs byon pa'i dus su /
NK130(tho)001:7873: sems can rnams kyis srog gcod tshig rtsub gnyis spang bas gnyis ldan zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7874: de yan chad du pha rol tu phyin pa'i chos gsungs 'bras bu byang chub la bkod pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:7875: de nas sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa byon pa'i dus su /
NK130(tho)001:7876: snyigs ma lnga bdo mi dge ba bcu la spyod pas rtsod ldan zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:7877: de'i dus su gsang sngags gson me lta bu'i chos 'byung ste bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7879: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud dang gsum gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:7880: de nas phyag na rdo rjes lung bstan nas o
NK130(tho)001:7881: rgyan gyi ri la thabs rgyud dang shes rab kyi
NK130(tho)001:7884: sangs rgyas gshegs nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis na rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud gsungs zer te /
NK130(tho)001:7885: pan+di ta thams cad la dris pas mi bden gsung /
NK130(tho)001:7886: de nas rim gyis bod kyi rgyal blon byang chub
NK130(tho)001:7887: sems dpa' rnams kyi sku ring la lo ts+aa ba
NK130(tho)001:7888: rnams kyis sde sdo gsum dang /
NK130(tho)001:7889: rgyud sde bzhi bsgyur zhing gtan la phab pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7890: de nas mi rab gcig na lo ts+aa ba ka ba dpal btsegs dang /
NK130(tho)001:7891: lce bkra shis dpal gyis dpal gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:7894: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rnams bsgyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:7895: de rnams ni bka' dri med pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7896: zhes pa la ma dag pa'i cha 'di ltar yod de bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:7898: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud dang gsum gsungs zer ba 'dis /
NK130(tho)001:7899: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rtsa ba nas chad /
NK130(tho)001:7900: rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi sku ring
NK130(tho)001:7901: la lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis sde snod gsum dang
NK130(tho)001:7903: zhes pa 'dis tshig snga phyi nang 'gal /
NK130(tho)001:7904: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba la sogs pa rgyud
NK130(tho)001:7905: sde gsum du bzhed pa'i lugs kyi bya ba dang
NK130(tho)001:7907: rnal 'byor zhes gsum du bsdus nas /
NK130(tho)001:7908: rnal 'byor la phyi nang gnyis su 'byed pa de dang 'di ma mthun /
NK130(tho)001:7909: o rgyan gyi ri la thabs shes kyi rgyud gsungs so zer /
NK130(tho)001:7910: la la sangs rgyas gshegs nas lo brgya dang bcu gnyis na rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud gsungs zer /
NK130(tho)001:7911: pan+di ta rnams mi bden zer /
NK130(tho)001:7912: zhes pa 'di ni gsang sngags gang du gsungs pa'i
NK130(tho)001:7913: gnas rtsad mchod pa de ka ma gtogs gzhan dgos
NK130(tho)001:7915: de nas bod kyi rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa'
NK130(tho)001:7916: rnams kyi sku ring la lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis
NK130(tho)001:7918: de nas mi rabs gcig na lo ts+aa ba ka
NK130(tho)001:7919: ba dpal brtsegs dang lce bkra shis la sogs pas
NK130(tho)001:7920: gsang 'dus bsgyur zer ba ni dus snga phyi nor
NK130(tho)001:7921: ba yin te / bod du chos kyi dbu brnyes
NK130(tho)001:7922: pa'i thog ma lha tho tho ri nas mes ag
NK130(tho)001:7923: tshom yan chad la chos yod kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7924: rab tu byung ba dang de'i chos 'dul ba med pas sde snod gsum ma tshang /
NK130(tho)001:7926: lce bkra shis dang ka ba dpal brtsegs ni khri
NK130(tho)001:7927: srong lde'u btsan gyi dus kyi lo ts+aa ba yin
NK130(tho)001:7928: pas mi rabs gcig nas zer ba'i don mi snang
NK130(tho)001:7929: / khri srong lde'u btsan gyi dbon sras mnga' bdag
NK130(tho)001:7930: khri ral gyi dus ka lcog la sogs pas snga
NK130(tho)001:7931: / 'gyur / 'gyur ba'i mdo sngags rnams la btsan
NK130(tho)001:7932: po'i bka' lung ltar skad gsar bcad kyis bcos pa
NK130(tho)001:7933: de la sngar med par de dus su bsgyur bar
NK130(tho)001:7934: bsam 'dug pa de kun ma dag go //
NK130(tho)001:7936: dus phyis rma rin chen mchog gis gsang ba snying po brtsams so //
NK130(tho)001:7937: de'i kha skong du sgyu 'phrul le'u lag brtsams so //
NK130(tho)001:7938: rgyal blon gyis rig nas bka' chad dbab par byas pas lo bcur ma rnyed /
NK130(tho)001:7939: dus phyis gtsang gi nyang ror shi'o //
NK130(tho)001:7942: thog ma slob dpon pad+ma dang rma rin chen mchog gis bsgyur ba yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:7943: de rjes bi ma la dang gnyags dz+ny+aa na'i 'gyur yod /
NK130(tho)001:7944: de'i bshad pa'i rgyun yang dar rje dpal gyi grags
NK130(tho)001:7945: pas bsam yas mchim phu dang khams su bshad de
NK130(tho)001:7946: nas brgyud pa la bka' mchim phu mar grags /
NK130(tho)001:7947: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches gtsang du
NK130(tho)001:7948: bshad pas so zur gnubs gsum la mched de rgya
NK130(tho)001:7949: che / de ltar ma yin zhe na yang /
NK130(tho)001:7950: dus phyis 'bri gung lo ts+aa ba ma ni ka sh+r+ai dz+ny+aa nas 'di skad du /
NK130(tho)001:7951: lha btsan po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi sku ring
NK130(tho)001:7952: la slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha was bsgyur ba'o
NK130(tho)001:7953: // slad kyis rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma
NK130(tho)001:7954: la mi tra dang lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na
NK130(tho)001:7955: ku m+aa ras yer ba lha brag bdud 'dul du
NK130(tho)001:7956: bsgyur zhing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:7957: dus phyi bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag
NK130(tho)001:7958: khang du sngon o rgyan gyi rgya dpe yod pa
NK130(tho)001:7959: bcom ldan 'das rig pa'i ral gris rnyed pa'i dpe
NK130(tho)001:7960: byung ba dang / bal po thang b+hi h+aa ra
NK130(tho)001:7961: nas glo bo lo ts+aa ba chen po dpal ldan
NK130(tho)001:7962: byang chub kyis rnyed pa'i rgya dpe las bshus pa'i
NK130(tho)001:7964: sngar gyi 'gyur rnying dang bstun pas khyad che bar mthong nas /
NK130(tho)001:7965: lo ts+aa'i ming can ma ni ka sh+r+ai dz+ny+aa nas
NK130(tho)001:7966: zur khang dga' ldan gling du lcags pho spre'u'i lo
NK130(tho)001:7967: ston zla brgyad pa'i tshes nye shu yan la 'gyur
NK130(tho)001:7968: rnams legs par bcos shing gtan la phab pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:7969: kha cig rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis ma gsungs pa'i /
NK130(tho)001:7970: chos min rnams la chos su zhen cing chags //
NK130(tho)001:7971: kha cig rnam dag chos dang rgyud la yang //
NK130(tho)001:7972: yang dag min zhes the tshom som nyi za //
NK130(tho)001:7973: de 'dra'i log rtog gsal bar bya ched dang //
NK130(tho)001:7974: rnam dag rgyud la bstod cing bskur ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:7975: rgyud 'di legs par bsgyur ba'i bsod nams gang //
NK130(tho)001:7976: de yis 'gro rnams he ru ka dpal shog /
NK130(tho)001:7977: ces pa 'gyur byang du bkod cing 'chad thabs kyi yan lag tu rgyud la mchan bu /
NK130(tho)001:7980: de ltar dus phyis kyang rgya bal gyi dpe las bod du bsgyur ba 'dis /
NK130(tho)001:7981: rma rin chen mchog gis gsang ba snying po brtsams so zhes pa'i gtam 'di nyams par byas so //
NK130(tho)001:7982: de dus ka ba dang lce gnyis kyis rgyud gsang
NK130(tho)001:7983: ba 'dus pa la sogs pa'i rgyud bzhi las ma
NK130(tho)001:7984: bsgyur ba yang mi bden te /
NK130(tho)001:7985: cog gru ting 'dzin dang brang ti dza ya rak+shi
NK130(tho)001:7986: ta la sogs pas rgyud mang po bsgyur ba gsar
NK130(tho)001:7987: ma ba'i chos 'byung rnams su bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:7989: de la brten nas zur che chung gis gsang ba
NK130(tho)001:7990: snying po'i 'grel pa dang dkyil chog dang sgrub thabs
NK130(tho)001:7991: mang po rang gzor byas so //
NK130(tho)001:7992: sgyu 'phrul gyi chos de dag thams cad chos log dri ma can bod kyi rang gzor yin no //
NK130(tho)001:7993: zhes pa'ang de la brten nas byas na rang gzor ga la 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:7994: de ltar na bod du 'gyur gsar ma rnams kyang
NK130(tho)001:7995: 'grel pa dang dkyil chog sgrub thabs mang du snang
NK130(tho)001:7996: ba thams cad dri ma can du 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:7998: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi sku ring la
NK130(tho)001:7999: bee ro tsa nas rgya gar la khungs btsal nas
NK130(tho)001:8000: sems phyogs la sogs nam mkha' che dang /
NK130(tho)001:8004: rig pa'i khu byug dang lnga brtsams pa rgyal blon gyis rig nas tsha ba rong du spyugs so //
NK130(tho)001:8006: gal te rgyud de dag brtsams pa'i nag la bee
NK130(tho)001:8007: ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs pa yin
NK130(tho)001:8008: na / des brtsams pa'i rgyud lnga po de'i dpe thams cad bsdus nas me la bsregs /
NK130(tho)001:8009: de phyin chad bod kyi yul 'dir sus kyang 'di
NK130(tho)001:8010: 'dra 'dzin pa dang 'chad pa byung na chad pas
NK130(tho)001:8011: bcad do zhes dril bsgrags pa na rgyud de dag
NK130(tho)001:8012: gi ming tsam yang ga la 'ong ste /
NK130(tho)001:8013: de ltar ma byung bas deng sang gi bar du dar ba 'di yin mod /
NK130(tho)001:8014: bee ro tsha bar rong du spyugs pa dang rnying
NK130(tho)001:8015: ma'i chos 'phro lus pa la mnga' bdag thugs ma
NK130(tho)001:8016: rdzogs par slob dpon bi ma la mi tra rgya
NK130(tho)001:8018: zhes sba bzhed du bshad khyed kyi gtam 'di dag bden na sba bzhed kyang 'khrul par byas so //
NK130(tho)001:8020: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches rgya gar
NK130(tho)001:8021: la rdzun gyi khungs sbyar nas rmad du byung ba
NK130(tho)001:8022: la sogs pa'i chos bcu gsum byas so //
NK130(tho)001:8023: sngar gyi lnga bsnan pas bco brgyad do //
NK130(tho)001:8024: sems lung chen mo dang kun bod kyis byas pa'i dri ma can yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8025: a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyis byas pa'i sems phyogs kyi rgyud lnga'i 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8027: dar rje dpal gyi grags pas byas pa'i chos la dgongs 'dus dang /
NK130(tho)001:8029: rgyal po'i chos lnga ste dri ma can yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8030: zhes pa dag la 'gog tu med pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK130(tho)001:8031: ni med kyang sems phyogs la dus der kha zer
NK130(tho)001:8032: ba mang bas / bde gshegs zur po che yang rang gi chos la the tshom 'khrungs /
NK130(tho)001:8033: de'i skabs shin tu mang kar nas 'brog mi lo
NK130(tho)001:8034: ts+aa bas chos sbyin gyi gser mang po khyer la
NK130(tho)001:8035: shog bya ba'i chab shog byung /
NK130(tho)001:8036: zur po che 'byon par chas pas sngags pa rnams na re /
NK130(tho)001:8037: dpal chen po'i bsnyen sgrub 'di'i bar chad yin pas
NK130(tho)001:8038: sku mtshams grol ba dang 'byon pa 'thad zhus pas
NK130(tho)001:8039: / yi dam gyi dngos grub mchog ni chos kyi
NK130(tho)001:8040: dngos grub yin pas da lta 'gro gsungs nas gshegs
NK130(tho)001:8041: / / 'brog mi pan+di ta bardzonga ba'i gser gyis
NK130(tho)001:8042: 'thogs pa de la zur gyis gser ka to ra
NK130(tho)001:8043: do phul bas dgyes nas lam 'bras dang /
NK130(tho)001:8044: phyag rgya chen po bsam mi khyab dang /
NK130(tho)001:8045: lam skor dgu la sogs pa ga ya d+ha ra'i chos thams cad rdzogs par gnang bas /
NK130(tho)001:8046: der zur gyis legs par dpyad pa na don 'dra
NK130(tho)001:8047: ba la rang gi sems phyogs zab pa dang lam
NK130(tho)001:8049: bla ma'i bsam mi khyab kyis kho bo'i sems phyogs nor du btang gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:8050: rang gi chos la nges shes rnyed /
NK130(tho)001:8051: bla ma 'di dang ma mjal na kho bos chos spang bar 'dug dgongs nas /
NK130(tho)001:8052: zhabs tog dang sri zhu che /
NK130(tho)001:8053: na bza' ber gsol ba'i thog tu 'brog mi'i mtshar ma khur nas skyas bas mi rnams na re /
NK130(tho)001:8054: ber 'di phangs zad 'gro zer ba la /
NK130(tho)001:8055: zur po che ma zad na ber mi zad ces sogs gsungs /
NK130(tho)001:8056: mdor na rdzogs chen sems phyogs la skur pa 'debs
NK130(tho)001:8057: kyang yang dag pa'i chos yin par lo rgyus 'dis
NK130(tho)001:8058: gsal la / lo rgyus 'di ni lam 'bras pa dag gi yi ge las 'byung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8060: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi rgyud brtsams pa /
NK130(tho)001:8061: de la brten nas bod rnams kyis chos log dri ma can bsam gyis mi khyab pa byas so //
NK130(tho)001:8062: de dag thams cad rgya gar na med cing pan+di
NK130(tho)001:8063: ta mang po la dris pas chos nor ba yin
NK130(tho)001:8065: de dus chos 'dod na pan chen brgya rtsa brgyad bod du bzhugs pa la /
NK130(tho)001:8066: de dag la zhus pas chog gi rang gis brtsom mi dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:8067: chos mi 'dod na ni rang gis brtsom pa yang chos yin pas des ci zhig bya /
NK130(tho)001:8068: spyir rgya gar na med pa tsam gyis chos min par bsgrub na /
NK130(tho)001:8069: nyi ma'i dngos grub kyis rgya gar du gsung rabs
NK130(tho)001:8070: ma bsregs gong du rgya nag tu byon pa'i mdo
NK130(tho)001:8071: sde mang po yod pa de dag dang /
NK130(tho)001:8072: mdo rgyud mang po lha dang klu dang mkha' 'gro'i
NK130(tho)001:8073: yul na yod pa dag kyang deng sang rgya gar
NK130(tho)001:8074: na med cing pan+di ta rnams la rgyus med pas
NK130(tho)001:8075: de dag kyang chos ma yin par 'gyur ram ci
NK130(tho)001:8077: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches pra khog
NK130(tho)001:8078: snang gi rgyud bya ba gshin rje'i rgyud brtsams so
NK130(tho)001:8079: // zhes pa 'di slob dpon shan+ti pas spyod rgyud du bkral /
NK130(tho)001:8080: dpal 'dzin gyis bya rgyud yin zer te gsar ma'i rgyud 'bum na yod do //
NK130(tho)001:8082: zhi khro ra hu la'i gza' rgyud che chung dang /
NK130(tho)001:8083: gdong mo chu 'khyags la sogs pa mang po brtsams so //
NK130(tho)001:8084: de la brten nas bod rnams kyis ma mo'i chos mang po brtsams so //
NK130(tho)001:8085: zhes pa mi rigs te ma mo'i rgyud dang gaza'i rgyud rnams chos skad mi 'ada'o //
NK130(tho)001:8087: rgyud pad+ma dben brtsams te mu stegs kyi chos dang 'dres pa'i dri ma can yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8088: sku'i rgyud rdo rje thogs med dang /
NK130(tho)001:8089: gsung gi rgyud rta mchog rol pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8090: thugs kyi rgyud pun+d+ha ri ka dang /
NK130(tho)001:8091: yon tan gyi rgyud rin po che ma gol pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8092: phrin las kyi rgyud karma m+aa le dang /
NK130(tho)001:8093: k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8094: bdud rtsi bam po brgyad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8096: gshin rje pra khog snang gi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8097: kha skong gi rgyud drug la chos nyid zhi ba'i rgyud /
NK130(tho)001:8102: nam mkha' mdzod kyi rgyud dang drug go //
NK130(tho)001:8103: rgyud kyi rgyal po drug la dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud /
NK130(tho)001:8104: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud /
NK130(tho)001:8106: brtson pa don ldan gyi rgyud /
NK130(tho)001:8107: yon tan rin po che'i rgyud /
NK130(tho)001:8108: karma m+aa le'i rgyud dang drug go //
NK130(tho)001:8109: gzhan yang lung sgrub thabs kyi yi ge bdun cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK130(tho)001:8114: phrin las du ma yod do //
NK130(tho)001:8115: de thams cad gnubs kyis byas pa'i dri ma can yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8116: gnyan chen dpal dbyangs kyis sgron ma rnam drug dang /
NK130(tho)001:8117: lta ba'i yig chung gnyis byas so //
NK130(tho)001:8119: chos ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs gzhan ma rnyed de /
NK130(tho)001:8120: bod kyis byas so zhes pa tsam gyis chos ma
NK130(tho)001:8121: yin par ga la 'grub ste bstan bcos su grub
NK130(tho)001:8122: pa'i phyir ro // 'di la rjes 'gos kyi slob
NK130(tho)001:8123: ma rngog nyi ma seng ges mdzad pa'i bstan bcos
NK130(tho)001:8124: gze ma ra mgor yang de ltar bod kyis byas
NK130(tho)001:8125: pa'i phyir ro // so zhes bris / dus 'khor 'gog pa na /
NK130(tho)001:8126: nyi zla shar du 'gro ba sogs /
NK130(tho)001:8127: zhes sogs byas 'dug pas snying po ci yang mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8128: gal te de dus kyi lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis brtsams pa yin na yang /
NK130(tho)001:8130: mkhas pa rnams kyis brtsams pa'i bstan bcos rgyud sde
NK130(tho)001:8131: dang mthun pa yin pas dri ma can ga la
NK130(tho)001:8132: yin te / slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyis rnam bshad rig par /
NK130(tho)001:8133: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:8134: ngan 'gro srid las skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK130(tho)001:8135: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK130(tho)001:8136: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK130(tho)001:8139: dri ma med pa'i chos la rdo rje 'jigs byed dang /
NK130(tho)001:8141: de la rgya gar gyi pan+di tas byas pa'i 'grel
NK130(tho)001:8142: pa dang sgrub thabs thams cad dri ma med pa
NK130(tho)001:8143: yin no // nang gi la gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8145: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8146: lha mo bzhis zhus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8148: shes rab kyi rgyud la dgyes pa rdo rje dang /
NK130(tho)001:8153: de rnams kyi rgyud phyi ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:8158: de rnams la rgya gar bas byas pa'i 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8159: sgrub thabs mang po yod de dri ma med pa'i chos ma nor ba yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8160: phyi'i la de kho na nyid bsdus pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8163: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8164: de dag gi 'grel pa sgrub thabs dang bcas pa
NK130(tho)001:8165: thams cad ma nor ba dri ma med pa'i chos
NK130(tho)001:8166: yin no // lo ts+aa ba chen po 'gos khug pa lhas btsas pa'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi /
NK130(tho)001:8167: spyod pa'i rgyud stong phrag brgyad /
NK130(tho)001:8168: rtogs pa'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi /
NK130(tho)001:8169: gnyis ka'i rgyud stong phrag drug /
NK130(tho)001:8170: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud stong phrag bcu gnyis te /
NK130(tho)001:8171: rgyas par phye na grangs med do //
NK130(tho)001:8173: dbye ba de dag kyang sho lo ka'i grangs ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8174: rgyud kyi rkang grangs yin la /
NK130(tho)001:8176: bde mchog nam mkha' dang mnyam pa la 'bum dang /
NK130(tho)001:8177: dgyes rdor la 'bum phrag lnga dang /
NK130(tho)001:8178: dus 'khor la stong phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK130(tho)001:8179: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor la khri brgyad stong dang /
NK130(tho)001:8180: de nyid bsdus pa la stong phrag brgyad dang /
NK130(tho)001:8181: gshin rje gshed dmar po la 'bum phrag gsum dang /
NK130(tho)001:8182: don zhags la stong phrag brgyad la sogs par yod par bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:8183: de bas na rgyud kyi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa la 'di ni rgyud do //
NK130(tho)001:8184: 'di ni rgyud ma yin no zhes tshad bzung bar ga la nus /
NK130(tho)001:8185: de'i phyir bka' shog 'di la mkhas pa kha cig gis /
NK130(tho)001:8186: brjod bya bzang po gcig kyang mi snang la //
NK130(tho)001:8187: rjod byed kun kyang grong tshig kho nar snang //
NK130(tho)001:8188: de phyir 'gos kyis mdzad pa'ang min pa 'dra //
NK130(tho)001:8189: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du snang /
NK130(tho)001:8190: gal te mdzad du zin na yang /
NK130(tho)001:8191: mkhas pa rnams kyis shes rab kyis chos la dpyad par bya ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8193: skyes bu shes rab can rnams kyis ni dgongs pa can gyi gsung yin pa nyid du nges so //
NK130(tho)001:8194: spyir na gong du brjod pa bzhin /
NK130(tho)001:8195: de dus chos thams cad dar ches pas so sor
NK130(tho)001:8196: chags sdang gi dbang gis gcig la gcig smod pas
NK130(tho)001:8197: / rngog gis dgyes rdor dang lam 'bras 'gog pa na /
NK130(tho)001:8198: ma mo rol pa'i rgyud dkrugs pas /
NK130(tho)001:8199: ga ya d+ha ra'i gser chos byung /
NK130(tho)001:8201: de dag la yid rton pa'i gnas su ma gyur to /
NK130(tho)001:8202: 'gos lo ts+aa ba'i 'byams yig yin zer ba'i lan du bkod pa rdzogs so ////
NK130(tho)001:8203: da ni bstan pa'i spyi'i rnam gzhag la go gzhi
NK130(tho)001:8204: ma chags pa'i rnying ma ba bdag lta bu'i rigs
NK130(tho)001:8206: thos bsam gyi grwa thag ma chod pas chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid la ni rmongs /
NK130(tho)001:8207: shes rab kyi mig dang bral bas chos rgyus ni med /
NK130(tho)001:8208: shes bya'i phugs thag ma chod par rmongs kyis chos log dri ma can dang /
NK130(tho)001:8209: chos dri ma med pa khyad par dbye ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:8210: yang dag pa'i lam la gzhug pa'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:8211: mkhas pa rnams kyi shes rab kyis chos la dpyad pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8212: sngags pa dang rab tu byung ba rnams nor ba la spyod pa rnams la 'di bskur ro //
NK130(tho)001:8213: lan gsum du rgya gar du phyin nas gtan la phabs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8216: de dag tu ma 'dus pa thams cad chos ma yin na /
NK130(tho)001:8217: gsang sngags gsar ma la gshin rje gshed da gra nag po /
NK130(tho)001:8219: gshin rje gshed dmar po'i rgyud rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8224: 'dul ba don yod par grub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8225: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa che chung dang /
NK130(tho)001:8226: rnam snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8227: bya spyod kyi rgyud phal cher dang /
NK130(tho)001:8229: phyis 'gyur ba'i dkyil chog rdo rje phreng ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8232: bde legs su byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum la sogs
NK130(tho)001:8233: pa mang po zhig chos ma yin par 'gyur ro
NK130(tho)001:8234: // 'dir mkhas pa rnams kyis shes rab kyis chos la dpyad par bya ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8235: zhes 'byung ba ni legs par bshad pa chen po yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8237: ston pas rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs pas na /
NK130(tho)001:8238: rang lugs la ma grags pa de dag chos ma yin no zhes mi bsam ste /
NK130(tho)001:8239: bde mchog sdom pa 'byung ba las /
NK130(tho)001:8240: rnal 'byor rgyud rnams kyi ni tshad //
NK130(tho)001:8241: bye ba phrag ni drug nges te //
NK130(tho)001:8242: de bzhin rnal 'byor ma rgyud grangs //
NK130(tho)001:8243: bye ba phrag ni bcu drug grags //
NK130(tho)001:8244: theg chen las gzhan mdo sde rnams //
NK130(tho)001:8245: dung phyur phrag brgyad gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:8246: de bzhin pha rol phyin pa'i tshul //
NK130(tho)001:8247: sa ya dang ni dung phyur lnga //
NK130(tho)001:8249: gsang sngags phyi pa la yang /
NK130(tho)001:8250: lha dang lha min rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK130(tho)001:8251: gsang sngags rig sngags rnam pa sna tshogs dag /
NK130(tho)001:8252: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK130(tho)001:8253: rig 'dzin sde snod du ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:8255: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa las /
NK130(tho)001:8256: bya zhen gyis rang phyogs bzang por rlom /
NK130(tho)001:8257: rigs pa dang mi rigs pa dpyod pa'i blo gros
NK130(tho)001:8258: dang mi ldan kyang yul khyad par can la skur
NK130(tho)001:8259: ba 'debs / sangs rgyas kyis lung du bstan pa'i
NK130(tho)001:8260: skyes bu chen po lha bla ma ye shes 'od
NK130(tho)001:8261: ba 'debs / dang / lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang po dang /
NK130(tho)001:8262: sa skya pan+di ta chen po dang /
NK130(tho)001:8263: thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston zhabs dang /
NK130(tho)001:8264: karma pa mi bskyod rdo rje la sogs pa rnams
NK130(tho)001:8265: kyis rnying ma'i chos 'di bkag go zhes sgrog cing
NK130(tho)001:8267: dam pa'i tshul las nyams shing dmyal ba sgrub pa'i
NK130(tho)001:8268: sa bon yin pas tshul de lta bu las bzlog
NK130(tho)001:8271: lha bla ma la sogs pa de dag ni sangs
NK130(tho)001:8272: rgyas gnyis pa lta bu'i yongs 'dzin chos kyi spyan
NK130(tho)001:8273: mnga' ba sha stag yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:8274: de rnams mi bzhed nges pas bkags pa yin na
NK130(tho)001:8275: ni rang cag rnams kyis chos sgo 'dir 'jug tu
NK130(tho)001:8277: de ltar ma yin par lha bla ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:8278: lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang pos gsang
NK130(tho)001:8279: sngags kyi sbyor sgrol la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin
NK130(tho)001:8280: par spyod pa bkag kyang chos ma bkag pa ni
NK130(tho)001:8281: bshad zin la / bdag nyid chen po 'gos lo
NK130(tho)001:8282: ts+aa ba'i 'byams yig yin no zhes pa de la
NK130(tho)001:8283: bshad zin la / lan kyang btab / pho brang
NK130(tho)001:8284: zhi ba 'od ni skyes bu dam pa yin mod
NK130(tho)001:8285: kyi bka' shog de la ni 'jig rten pa dag
NK130(tho)001:8286: thos thos bon gyer zhes zer ba'i snang tshul las
NK130(tho)001:8287: yang dag pa'i gtan tshigs gcig ma mchis pas lan
NK130(tho)001:8289: dpal 'dzin gyi rtsod lan kyang rno bar bgyis /
NK130(tho)001:8290: rgyal po'i dbang po mi bskyod rdo rje'i dri ba
NK130(tho)001:8291: de ni rnying ma ba rnams thos bsam la 'bad
NK130(tho)001:8292: pa 'don phyir du gsungs pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8293: 'di la rje rang gis lan zhig mdzad 'dug pa
NK130(tho)001:8294: de yang thebs par ma btab snang ba ni rnying
NK130(tho)001:8295: ma ba dag rang gis lan thob cig pa'i dgongs
NK130(tho)001:8297: thabs la mkhas pa'i bka' drin chen por rig ste
NK130(tho)001:8298: de la lan gyi yi ge zur na yod do
NK130(tho)001:8299: // da ni thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston chen
NK130(tho)001:8300: po'i bzhed pa ji ltar yin pa brjod par bya
NK130(tho)001:8301: // ste / de la bdag nyid chen po 'dis mdzad pa'i chos 'byung chen mor /
NK130(tho)001:8302: snga 'gyur gsang sngags rnying ma ni lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang po dang /
NK130(tho)001:8303: lha bla ma ye shes 'od dang /
NK130(tho)001:8305: 'gos khug pa lhas btsas la sogs pas yang dag pa ma yin par smra la /
NK130(tho)001:8306: bdag cag gi bla ma mkhan chen thar pa lo
NK130(tho)001:8307: ts+aa ba nyi ma rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po ni
NK130(tho)001:8308: / rig ral la sogs pas bsam yas nas rgya dpe rnyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:8309: bal po na yang rgya dpe mang rab la snang bas rgyud yang dag pa'o gsung kho bos ni /
NK130(tho)001:8310: yid kyi nyes pa rang bzhin 'dug pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:8311: mi rigs pa yi gzugs la'ang mi rigs na //
NK130(tho)001:8312: the tshom za ba'i chos la smos ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:8313: de phyir btang snyoms bzhag la nyes pa med //
NK130(tho)001:8315: chos yin pa la ma yin zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8316: ma yin pa la yin zer ba las 'bras mnyam par bshad pas dang /
NK130(tho)001:8317: chos kyi mtshan nyid gang la'ang yod med dag /
NK130(tho)001:8318: mi shes mthong ba med phyir rgyu bzhi yis //
NK130(tho)001:8319: rnam dbye smra ba'i kha ni bdud kyis phyes //
NK130(tho)001:8320: chos la nyes smod thub pa'i gzhung las bkags //
NK130(tho)001:8321: zhes pa bzhin du btang snyoms su bzhag go //
NK130(tho)001:8322: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyis rton pa bzhi dang brtag pa gsum la brten nas dpyad par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:8323: zhes gsungs pa 'di ni rnying ma bkag pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8325: nged kyi bla ma mkhan chen thar lo ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8326: de'i gong gi bla ma 'gos khug pa sogs ni mi mthun par snang /
NK130(tho)001:8327: chos yin pa la ma yin zer ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8328: ma yin pa la yin zer ba ni chos spong ba'i las dang 'bras bu mnyam /
NK130(tho)001:8329: spyan lnga ma thob par la chos gang yod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8331: ji ltar yin pa mi shes /
NK130(tho)001:8332: mi mthong ba'i rgyu mtshan bzhi po 'dis chos la
NK130(tho)001:8333: yin min du smra ba ni bdud kyi las yin
NK130(tho)001:8334: / chos la nyes pa sgrog cing smod pa ni
NK130(tho)001:8335: thub pa dang byams mgon la sogs pa'i gzhung nas
NK130(tho)001:8336: bkags pas nga ni mi smra'o //
NK130(tho)001:8337: gal te rnying ma ji ltar yin dpyad na /
NK130(tho)001:8338: rton pa bzhi dang brtag pa gsum gyis blo dang ldan pa dag gis dpyod cig /
NK130(tho)001:8340: gsang sngags gsang nas sgrub pa yin pas rang nyid rnying ma bar zhal gyis mi bzhes kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8341: yab mes kyi bka' srol ltar rnying ma'i lha du ma thugs dam du mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:8342: sbyor rdzogs gnyis kyi grub mtha' phal cher gcig pas /
NK130(tho)001:8343: sbyor drug gi nyams myong gzhan la gsang ba'i skabs su /
NK130(tho)001:8344: sbyor drug pa 'di tsho la ma bshad byas kyang
NK130(tho)001:8345: brang shag phad kyis mnan pa ltar mi la 'chad
NK130(tho)001:8346: / kho pa rdzogs chen pa la gdab pa gtor
NK130(tho)001:8347: ma mgo thog tu bzhag nas mna' dgag kyin yod
NK130(tho)001:8348: / pa 'dra / ci yang mi la mi 'chad pa 'dug ces sogs basngagasa pa cher mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:8350: de ltar phur pa don yod grub pa'i rigs yin
NK130(tho)001:8351: pa dang rnying ma ba rnams phur pa phrin las
NK130(tho)001:8352: kyi lha zer bas las kyi rigs su byas so
NK130(tho)001:8354: rnying ma chos log yin na des phur pa phrin
NK130(tho)001:8355: las kyi lha zer ba de dpang du mdzad ci
NK130(tho)001:8356: dgos / gzhan yang 'dul 'dzin rnal 'byor byang chub seng ge'i zhu lan du /
NK130(tho)001:8357: yang gsang sngags snga 'gyur pa 'ga' zhig gis spyod
NK130(tho)001:8358: pa gsang ba phyogs thams cad du bsgrags pa la
NK130(tho)001:8359: nyes pa med par byed pa 'di yang rang gi
NK130(tho)001:8360: gzhung dang 'gal bas yang dag pa ma yin te
NK130(tho)001:8362: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK130(tho)001:8363: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK130(tho)001:8364: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:8367: de la sogs pa snga 'gyur gyi bka' dang bstan
NK130(tho)001:8368: bcos du ma las ma smin pa la gsang ba
NK130(tho)001:8370: zhes sogs gsungs te des na chos yang dag par mi bzhed pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8374: mngon pa'i chos nyid dang mi 'gal ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:8375: de yang theg pa gsum rang rang gi gzhung dang sbyor dgos pas /
NK130(tho)001:8376: bka' las sngar yin na sngags rnying ma kun kyang
NK130(tho)001:8377: mngon pa kun las btus dang tshad ma rnam nges
NK130(tho)001:8379: zhan shos kun kyang mngon pa kun btus dang tshad ma bsdus pa re slob kyin 'dug ste /
NK130(tho)001:8380: deng sang sngags pa gsar rnying kun rang re'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:8381: 'grel re'i lta rtog kyang mi nus pa 'dug gsung
NK130(tho)001:8382: nas bskul / zhes rnam thar snyim pa'i me tog che bar bkod snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8383: sngags kyi 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa dang sbyor ro //
NK130(tho)001:8384: de dag gi tshul ni dpal 'dzin gyi skabs su brjod zin la /
NK130(tho)001:8386: sngags kyi 'dul ba ni spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig dang /
NK130(tho)001:8387: mdo sde ni bskyed rdzogs kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK130(tho)001:8388: mngon pa'i chos nyid ni lta ba phyin ci ma log pa la bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:8390: drang don la mi rten nges don la rten /
NK130(tho)001:8391: gang zag la mi rton chos la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8392: tshig la mi rton don la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8393: rnam shes la mi rton ye shes la rton pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:8394: de las 'dir lta dgongs kyi phul du gyur pas don la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8396: sems dang ye shes 'byed pas ye shes la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8398: theg dman zil gyis gnon pas nges don la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8400: spyod pa dang cha lugs tshul mi 'chos par lam du byed pas chos la rton /
NK130(tho)001:8401: gang zag la mi rton pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:8402: de ltar rton pa bzhi po de dang brtag pa gsum gyis chos rnam dag tu sgrubs shig ces /
NK130(tho)001:8403: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu'i dgongs pa ni de nyid do //
NK130(tho)001:8404: da ni sa skya pan+di ta'i bzhed pa brjod par bya ste /
NK130(tho)001:8405: 'jam pa'i dbyangs 'dis sdom gsum rab dbyer /
NK130(tho)001:8406: gzhan yang gsang sngags gsar rnying la /
NK130(tho)001:8407: zhes sogs kyis gsar rnying gnyis ka la lhad zhugs tshul gsungs te /
NK130(tho)001:8409: da lta'i phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK130(tho)001:8410: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:8412: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen de gang la ngos 'dzin na /
NK130(tho)001:8413: rdzogs chen brgyud pa dang po la sh+r+ai seng ha'i
NK130(tho)001:8414: slob ma rgya nag gi grub thob mang pos gsungs
NK130(tho)001:8415: pa'i rdzogs chen yod pa de dag dang /
NK130(tho)001:8416: a ro'i chos skor du rdzogs chen rgya gar bdun brgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8417: rgya nag nas brgyud pa gnyis yod pa de ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8418: 'di dag gi lta spyod la 'khrul pa med do //
NK130(tho)001:8420: 'di ni chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan gyi sku
NK130(tho)001:8421: ring la hwa shang ma h+aa ya nas bshad pa'i
NK130(tho)001:8423: de ji ltar yin pa yang /
NK130(tho)001:8424: de dus hwa shang de la bod phal che ba dad cing 'dun /
NK130(tho)001:8425: slob ma yang mngon shes thob pa mang du byung /
NK130(tho)001:8426: nyang ting 'dzin bzang po yang de'i slob ma yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:8427: rgyal pos pan chen bi ma la la /
NK130(tho)001:8428: bdag la bla mchod nyang ting 'dzin bzang po bya ba rgya'i hwa shang gi slob ma /
NK130(tho)001:8429: sha'i spyan mnga' bas zhing khams 'bum phrag mang po dus gcig la gzigs pa /
NK130(tho)001:8430: ting nge 'dzin thun gcig la mnyam par bzhag pas
NK130(tho)001:8431: zhag bdun du 'tsho ba'i zas mi dgos pa zhig
NK130(tho)001:8432: yod zhus pas / pan+di tas zhal ngo gnag ste n+aa ga pu ra hi sa m+aa d+hi /
NK130(tho)001:8433: zhes gsungs nas chos gos kyis dbu phur song /
NK130(tho)001:8434: der lo ts+aa ba la ci gsung dris pas /
NK130(tho)001:8435: sdug sran can gyi sgom klur skye ba'i ting nge 'dzin yin gsung zer /
NK130(tho)001:8436: de rgyal pos nyang ban la bshad pas nyang ban
NK130(tho)001:8437: chos kyi las 'phro sad de sngar gyi chos spangs
NK130(tho)001:8438: te bi ma la brten nas 'od lus grub /
NK130(tho)001:8439: de tsa na ston min dang btsen min du grags
NK130(tho)001:8440: nas bsam yas su rgya dkar nag gi chos la
NK130(tho)001:8441: chags sdang ches pa la rgyal pos pan chen ka
NK130(tho)001:8442: m+aa la sh+ai la spyan drangs pas ha shang rtsod
NK130(tho)001:8443: pa phams pa de'i grub mtha' yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8444: 'grel pa mkhan po rnams kyis phyag rdzogs la gzigs rtog cher ma mdzad pas yin na /
NK130(tho)001:8445: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen de la 'di yin no zhes rtsad ma chod snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8447: kha cig 'bras bu'i mthar thug ni //
NK130(tho)001:8448: 'od gsal yin ces smra ba thos //
NK130(tho)001:8449: zhes pa 'di rdzogs chen bkag pa yin zer //
NK130(tho)001:8450: 'di ni rdzogs chen gyi 'od gsal ma yin /
NK130(tho)001:8451: brgyad stong pa las gsungs pa'i /
NK130(tho)001:8452: sems la sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'od gsal ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:8453: zhes pa'i don rgyal ba yang dgon pas /
NK130(tho)001:8454: 'od gsal ni snang med spros bral yin la zhes pa de la dgongs so //
NK130(tho)001:8456: gter nas byung ba'i glegs bam dang //
NK130(tho)001:8457: gzhan nas brkus pa'i chos lugs dang //
NK130(tho)001:8458: brtsams chos dang ni rmi lam chos //
NK130(tho)001:8459: blo bzung ma yi chos lugs la //
NK130(tho)001:8460: brgyud pa rdo rje 'chang la bsnyag /
NK130(tho)001:8461: de la'ang gzhan dag lung len pa //
NK130(tho)001:8462: chos dang 'gal ba lta ci smos //
NK130(tho)001:8463: rang lugs dang yang 'gal ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:8464: zhes pa 'di rnying ma la yin no zer kyang ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8465: rnying ma bas rdo rje 'chang la brgyud pa mi bsnyag de'i gong na rigs lnga dang /
NK130(tho)001:8466: kun tu bzang po yod pa la bsnyag /'di ni
NK130(tho)001:8467: ro snyom skor drug la sogs pa bka' brgyud la
NK130(tho)001:8468: grags pa'i gter chos rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8469: phag mo gru pas sa skya pa chen po las gsan pa de phyag chen du btags pas /
NK130(tho)001:8470: de dag la gzhan nas brkus pa'i chos lugs zhes dgongs pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:8472: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba rnams ni //
NK130(tho)001:8474: rjes su rnal 'byor shin tu ni //
NK130(tho)001:8475: rnal 'byor zhes bya rnam pa bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:8476: theg pa'i rim pa yin ces zer //
NK130(tho)001:8478: ces bya ba de yang rje btsun 'dis dgag pa mdzad pa ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8479: 'dod tshul de gsar ma ltar na mi 'thad /
NK130(tho)001:8480: rnying ma ltar na 'thad de 'thad tshul ma shes zhes bzhed par mngon te /
NK130(tho)001:8481: de yang gsang sngags gsar ma'i lugs la bla med
NK130(tho)001:8482: kyi gong na de las mtho ba'i theg pa med
NK130(tho)001:8483: kyang / a ti yo ga ye shes skye ba'i
NK130(tho)001:8484: thabs kyi chos de la theg pa'i rim pa nges
NK130(tho)001:8485: par 'thad do zhes dgongs pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:8487: des na gsang sngags gsar ma la //
NK130(tho)001:8488: rnal 'byor chen po'i ltag na ni //
NK130(tho)001:8489: de bas mtho ba'i rgyud sde med //
NK130(tho)001:8490: bsgom pa'i dmigs pa nyid kyang ni //
NK130(tho)001:8491: rnal 'byor chen po'i gong na med //
NK130(tho)001:8492: de las skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK130(tho)001:8493: dmigs pa med cing brjod bral bas //
NK130(tho)001:8494: theg pa'i rim pa mi bzhed do //
NK130(tho)001:8495: lugs 'di legs par shes gyur na //
NK130(tho)001:8496: a ti yo ga'i lta ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:8497: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK130(tho)001:8498: brjod bral brjod byar byas pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:8499: mkhas pa'i dgongs pa min ces bya //
NK130(tho)001:8500: zhes sngags gsar ma'i dgongs don de ltar gsungs nas /
NK130(tho)001:8501: da rnying ma'i lugs bzhin byed na 'di ltar yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8503: des na thos pa'i lta ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:8504: dbu ma yan chad thams cad mthun //
NK130(tho)001:8505: de phyir lta ba'i lung sbyor kun //
NK130(tho)001:8506: pha rol phyin bzhin thams cad mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:8507: de rtogs pa yi thabs la ni //
NK130(tho)001:8508: lta ba'i rim pa yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:8511: gsar ma ltar na bla med kyi gong na de las lhag pa'i rgyud sde med /
NK130(tho)001:8513: a nu dang a ti yo ga'i dgongs don de
NK130(tho)001:8514: ni sngags gsar ma ba'i bla med kyi ye shes
NK130(tho)001:8515: yin par 'dug pas theg pa yin ces zer du
NK130(tho)001:8516: mi rung / gal te theg pa ru bsgrang na brjod bral de brjod byar song ba'i skyon 'bab /
NK130(tho)001:8517: gzhan yang khyed lta ba khyad par 'phags pa des theg pa gong 'og 'byed pa mi 'thad /
NK130(tho)001:8518: lta ba dbu ma las lhag pa sngags la med /
NK130(tho)001:8519: khyed rang gi lta ba de yang dbu mar 'dug ste /
NK130(tho)001:8520: bi ma la'i sems phyogs kyi spyi tshangs las /
NK130(tho)001:8521: 'di ltar gsal ba'i dus na rtog ce'am /
NK130(tho)001:8527: thams cad las 'das te 'dis ni theg pa chen
NK130(tho)001:8528: po'i mdo sde dbu ma la sogs pa gdar sha
NK130(tho)001:8529: bcad de the tshom dang gleng gzhi thams cad dang
NK130(tho)001:8530: bral bas na / rnam rtog mi mnga' ci yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK130(tho)001:8532: lta ba 'dis thag bcad nas gsang ba'i theg pa yang /
NK130(tho)001:8533: ye shes la theg par mi rung ba yang ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8535: shes bya'i gnas dang mtshan nyid de 'jug dang //
NK130(tho)001:8536: de la gnas dang de dngos dbye ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:8537: nyes pa gsum dang de 'bras spangs pas dang //
NK130(tho)001:8538: ye shes theg pa mchog gyur khyad par 'phags //
NK130(tho)001:8540: gong ma dag las zur tsam yang ma brjod do //
NK130(tho)001:8542: 'on kyang lta ba de rtogs pa'i thabs kyi rim
NK130(tho)001:8543: pa de brjod par bya ba'i chos kyi tshul de
NK130(tho)001:8544: dag la theg pa'i rim pa yod pa yin no
NK130(tho)001:8545: // zhes lta ba dang lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs kyi chos gnyis su phye nas yang /
NK130(tho)001:8546: la la theg pa rim dgu la /
NK130(tho)001:8547: lta ba'i dbye ba yod ces zer //
NK130(tho)001:8548: zhes theg pa rim pa dgu yod par zhar la grub cing /
NK130(tho)001:8549: lta ba gnyis las med par bzhed de /
NK130(tho)001:8550: nyan thos dang ni theg chen la //
NK130(tho)001:8551: lta ba'i dbye ba yod mod kyi //
NK130(tho)001:8552: pha rol phyin dang gsang sngags la //
NK130(tho)001:8553: lta ba'i dbye ba bshad pa med //
NK130(tho)001:8554: pha rol phyin pa'i spros bral las //
NK130(tho)001:8555: lhag pa'i lta ba yod na ni //
NK130(tho)001:8556: lta de spros pa can du 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:8557: spros bral yin na khyad par med //
NK130(tho)001:8559: 'on kyang spros bral rtogs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:8560: thabs la gsang sngags khyad par 'phags //
NK130(tho)001:8562: lta sgom rnam dbye ma phyed cing //
NK130(tho)001:8563: thabs dang shes rab ma shes pas //
NK130(tho)001:8565: zhes dka' ba'i gnas ma go dogs nas yang dang yang du rgyas par bkral ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:8566: 'di dag ni rnying ma'i bstan pa gsal bar byed
NK130(tho)001:8567: pa'i rnam bzhag bka' drin bla na med pa'i gnas
NK130(tho)001:8569: rgyal po dar mas bstan pa bsnubs //
NK130(tho)001:8570: de rjes chos log du ma 'phel //
NK130(tho)001:8571: de tshe bla ma ye shes 'od //
NK130(tho)001:8572: chos rgyal de yis skyes bu mchog /
NK130(tho)001:8573: rin chen bzang po kha cher bardzangasa //
NK130(tho)001:8574: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis byin brlabs pa //
NK130(tho)001:8575: mkhas pa de yis sngon med pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:8576: chos rnams phal cher bsgyur zhing zhus //
NK130(tho)001:8577: chos dang chos min rnam 'byed pa //
NK130(tho)001:8578: zhes bya'i bstan bcos mdzad nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:8579: chos log thams cad nub par mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:8580: de yi slob ma zhi ba 'od //
NK130(tho)001:8581: des kyang chos log sun 'byin pa //
NK130(tho)001:8582: zhes pa'i bstan bcos mdzad ces zer //
NK130(tho)001:8585: lhas btsas zhes bya'i lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:8586: des kyang chos log sun 'byin pa //
NK130(tho)001:8587: zhes bya'i bstan bcos mdzad nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:8588: chos log thams cad nub par mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:8589: de nas chos rje sa skya pa //
NK130(tho)001:8590: chen po bzhugs pa yan chod du //
NK130(tho)001:8591: chos log spyod pa nyung zhes thos //
NK130(tho)001:8592: zhes pa 'di rnams rnying ma 'gog pa yin no zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:8594: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang pos sbyor sgrol sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa bkags kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8595: rnying ma'i chos ma bkags la /
NK130(tho)001:8596: de gtso bor smos nas chos log thams cad nub par mdzad do //
NK130(tho)001:8598: 'gos lo ts+aa bas sngags rnying ma bkag pa yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8599: de la brten nas sngags pas spyod pa log par
NK130(tho)001:8600: byed pa da ga khegs pa la basngagasa pa mdzad
NK130(tho)001:8601: pa yin gyi / rgyud gzhung bkag pa la basngagasa pa brjod pa ni ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8602: rang gi yab mes gong ma rnams kyang sngags rnying ma kho na'i grub thob pa yin pas so //
NK130(tho)001:8603: des na rje btsun 'dis 'gog pa'i chos log ni /
NK130(tho)001:8605: deng sang phag ma'i byin rlabs dang //
NK130(tho)001:8606: sems bskyed rmi lam ma la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:8607: yi dam bsgom pa krong bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:8608: dkar po chig thub la sogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:8609: chos log du ma deng sang 'phel //
NK130(tho)001:8611: rdzogs chen dang rnying ma zhes ma byung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8612: glo bo lo ts+aa ba'i dris lan du /
NK130(tho)001:8613: sngags gsar ma la ra li nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK130(tho)001:8614: rnying ma la bam ril thod pa mkhar la sogs
NK130(tho)001:8615: pa rgyud bardzusa ma gsar rnying gnyis ka la yod
NK130(tho)001:8616: tshul gsungs so // de ltar rje btsun 'dis ni
NK130(tho)001:8617: lo chen dang 'gos kyi 'byams yig tu grags pa
NK130(tho)001:8618: des rnying ma'i chos bkag pa la basngagasa pa ma
NK130(tho)001:8619: tshul gsungs so // yin / don ma go ba'i
NK130(tho)001:8620: gang zag gis sbyor sgrol mthu gtad ser ba la
NK130(tho)001:8621: sogs pa sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa de khegs
NK130(tho)001:8622: pa la basngagasa pa brjod pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:8623: de dag gis 'dzin pa'i chos rnal ma nub bo zhes bzhed pa ma yin /
NK130(tho)001:8624: gal te yin na de dus tshang ma bsnubs zin pa la da lta 'di tsam dar ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8625: gzhan yang rnying ma 'gog pa po rnams kyis khri
NK130(tho)001:8626: srong lde'u btsan gyi dus nas byung bar bshad pa
NK130(tho)001:8627: yin pas / rgyud 'di dag sus gang du btsal /
NK130(tho)001:8628: gang nas rnyed de dar bar byas pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:8629: de bas na rnying ma ba'i chos nub ma myong ba la /
NK130(tho)001:8632: sdom gsum gyi 'grel mdzad mkhan po dag gis dgongs pa 'di ltar du cung ma bkral kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8633: phyag rdzogs kyi gzhung lugs la nan tan du ma gzigs pa nyid du mngon no //
NK130(tho)001:8634: da ni bcom ldan rig pa'i ral gris /
NK130(tho)001:8635: bslab gsum rgyan gyi me tog tu gsungs pa la brjod par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:8637: kha cig sangs rgyas bstan pa la //
NK130(tho)001:8638: theg pa rim dgu yod do lo //
NK130(tho)001:8639: theg pa rim pa dgu nyid du //
NK130(tho)001:8640: rgyal dang rgyal sras mi bzhed do //
NK130(tho)001:8642: theg pa'i nang tshan gyi dbye bas dgur 'dod na /
NK130(tho)001:8643: nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde bzhi la gyes pa bco brgyad dang /
NK130(tho)001:8644: rang sangs rgyas la gsum dang /
NK130(tho)001:8645: byang chub sems dpa' la dbu ma sems tsam /
NK130(tho)001:8646: de la'ang so sor dbye bas dgur nges pa 'jig pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8648: de'i rgyu mtshan rgyas par gsungs 'dug pa la /
NK130(tho)001:8649: dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po'i lung /
NK130(tho)001:8650: nga yi bstan pa'i theg pa dgu po yang /
NK130(tho)001:8651: zhes pa de rnam pa dgu po yang zhes bya bar bcos 'dug pas /
NK130(tho)001:8652: 'di la rgya dper theg pa'i skad dod ya na
NK130(tho)001:8653: zhes yod pa zha lu lo chen gyis gsungs par
NK130(tho)001:8654: grags / gal te rnam pa yin na yang /
NK130(tho)001:8655: de'i rjes kyi tshig de la /
NK130(tho)001:8656: sems can rnams kyi mthu dang mos par bshad /
NK130(tho)001:8657: 'di ltar thabs kyis mchog gi ye shes la /
NK130(tho)001:8658: rab tu gzud pa'i phyir na ngas bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:8660: nyan rang byang sems gsum gyi theg pa de yang
NK130(tho)001:8661: sems can dbang po tha ma dang 'bring dang rab
NK130(tho)001:8662: kyi bsam pa dang bstun nas gsungs pa yin kyang
NK130(tho)001:8663: / de dag gi sgo nas mi thul ba'i sems can gyi gnas ris mtha' yas pa yod pas /
NK130(tho)001:8664: de dag so so'i bsam pa dang bstun nas gsungs
NK130(tho)001:8665: pa'i theg pa'i rnam grangs dpag tu med pa yod
NK130(tho)001:8666: par ni / bde mchog gi rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:8667: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK130(tho)001:8668: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK130(tho)001:8670: theg pa zhes pa'i don yang 'phags pa sdud pa las /
NK130(tho)001:8671: ci phyir 'di ni byang chub theg ces bya zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:8672: de gang zhe nas sems can thams cad mya ngan zlog /
NK130(tho)001:8673: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te /
NK130(tho)001:8675: sems can thams cad byang chub la 'god pa'i phyir
NK130(tho)001:8676: du gsungs pa'i theg pa nam mkha' lta bur rgya
NK130(tho)001:8677: che ba yod pa nyid du 'grel pa las bshad
NK130(tho)001:8678: cing / de bas na theg pa rim pa dgur
NK130(tho)001:8679: byas pa ni 'dzam bu'i gling gi gdul bya rags
NK130(tho)001:8680: pa tsam gyi dbang du yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:8681: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan dang gzhan na gdul bya
NK130(tho)001:8682: gzhan dang gzhan dag la theg pa sna tshogs pa
NK130(tho)001:8684: theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis /
NK130(tho)001:8685: 'gro ba'i don la ston pa po //
NK130(tho)001:8691: rnal 'byor chen po zhes 'byung ba de ni bskyed
NK130(tho)001:8692: rdzogs bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa la
NK130(tho)001:8695: shin tu rnal 'byor gnyis rgyud sde'i rim pa khungs thub pa'i gzhung nas bshad pa med do //
NK130(tho)001:8696: zhes gsungs pa'ang mi thad de /
NK130(tho)001:8697: de gnyis rgyud sde gong 'og gi rim pa yin ces gsar ma'i gzhung na med kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8698: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa mtho dman gyi brjod
NK130(tho)001:8699: bya rang rang gi gzhung du byung bas rgyud sde'i
NK130(tho)001:8700: rim pa nyid du mngon sum du grub ste /
NK130(tho)001:8701: bya rgyud pa lta ba bas spyod pa gtso cher bstan pa la /
NK130(tho)001:8702: spyod rgyud pas lta spyod cha mnyam du bstan pas rgyud sde gong 'og tu song ba bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:8703: shin tu rnal 'byor zhes pa a ti yo ga las mtho ba'i theg pa spyi ti dang /
NK130(tho)001:8704: yang ti gnyis kyang yod de /
NK130(tho)001:8705: ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i rim pa la mtho dman du byung ba yin mod /
NK130(tho)001:8707: gter ma rnying ma snyan brgyud sogs //
NK130(tho)001:8708: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'i //
NK130(tho)001:8709: don dang mthun na skyon med yin //
NK130(tho)001:8710: mi mthun rang bzor shes par bya //
NK130(tho)001:8711: khungs thub pa'i rgyud gzhung med par rna ba brgyud nas byung ba ni snyan brgyud de /
NK130(tho)001:8712: bka' phyag gi man ngag rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8715: zhi gcod la sogs pa gzhung med pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8716: lam 'bras la sogs pa'i lam skor gzhung med pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8717: bde mchog snyan brgyud la sogs pa rnams so //
NK130(tho)001:8718: rtsa ba'i sogs pa don ni /
NK130(tho)001:8721: mi mkhas pas brtsams nas mkhas pa la kha 'phangs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:8722: gter ma la sogs pa 'di rnams la ni mkhas pa la grags pa'i gzhung med pas /
NK130(tho)001:8723: rang ga'i bshad pa 'dir brjod kyis mi lang ba zhig yod de /
NK130(tho)001:8724: de ni gsung rabs rtsod pa med pa rnams dang mthun mi mthun brtag dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:8725: de la mthong ba dang thos pas sdig pa 'dzad
NK130(tho)001:8726: pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams dang
NK130(tho)001:8727: / so sor 'brangs ma la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8729: mdo sde zab mo rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:8730: zos pas mkha' spyod thob pa ni skye ba bdun
NK130(tho)001:8731: pa'i sha yin par mdo rgyud nas bshad pa yin
NK130(tho)001:8732: no // de las gzhan pa'i mthong grol dang /
NK130(tho)001:8733: btags grol la sogs pa ni gsung rabs gang las byung ba yin brjod dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:8734: 'ja' dang ring srel la sogs pas ni bzang por bsgrub mi nus te /
NK130(tho)001:8738: gter yig gis gang zag lung bstan pa yang rdzun yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8739: de ni sangs rgyas sprul sku kho na'i mdzad pa yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:8740: byams pa dang 'jam dpal la sogs pas kyang lung bstan pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:8741: de bzhin du sgrub pa bka' brgyad dang /
NK130(tho)001:8742: theg pa rim pa dgu'i dbang yang khungs thub pa gang las byung brjod dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:8743: rdzogs pa'i byang chub dpal nor dbang bskur yin //
NK130(tho)001:8744: zhes pa'i tshig tsam gyi nyan thos la'ang dbang bskur 'dod na /
NK130(tho)001:8745: kri kri'i rmi lam lung bstan pa las spre'u rgyal
NK130(tho)001:8746: por dbang bskur ba yang bshad pas spre'u'i dbang bskur
NK130(tho)001:8748: zhes gsungs pa las phal cher la brjod ma dgos /
NK130(tho)001:8749: btags grol dang mthong grol ni shin tu zab pa'i phyir a ti yo ga pa'i khyad chos yin /
NK130(tho)001:8750: a nu yo ga man chad du cha mthun tsam yod de /
NK130(tho)001:8751: so sor 'brangs ma'i 'khor lo bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:8752: mthong grol ni dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang mtshungs te /
NK130(tho)001:8753: mthong grol gyi ngo bo ni chos nyid 'od gsal
NK130(tho)001:8754: gyi dkyil 'khor re mor byas pa yin pa dang
NK130(tho)001:8755: / rgyal ba rigs lnga la sogs pa'i lha dang sngags kyang mthong grol dang /
NK130(tho)001:8756: dkyil 'khor dag tu 'byung ba'ang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:8757: 'ja' 'od ni btags grol bcangs pa'i ro la ston
NK130(tho)001:8758: dpyid la sogs pa'i dus gzhan du yang 'byung bas
NK130(tho)001:8759: / dbyar ka'i 'ja' dang stabs 'grig pa lta bu ma yin /
NK130(tho)001:8760: ring srel dud 'gro dang gdan gyi cho 'phrul la'ang 'byung snang bas bden mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:8761: 'dir grol ba'i tshad ring srel la mi bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:8762: sku gsung thugs kyi rtags gsum yod pa'i /
NK130(tho)001:8764: sgra 'od zer dang me dud rtags /
NK130(tho)001:8766: rnal 'byor phyir mi ldog pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:8767: rtags su rdo rje rin chen pad //
NK130(tho)001:8768: las dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung //
NK130(tho)001:8769: sha khrag rus dang sgal tshig dang //
NK130(tho)001:8772: sha ri chu ri ba ri yis //
NK130(tho)001:8773: skye med yon tan longs sku thob //
NK130(tho)001:8774: nya ri pany+tsa ram gyis ni //
NK130(tho)001:8775: sprul sku sku lnga nges par thob //
NK130(tho)001:8776: gsung thob rtags su me 'od sgra //
NK130(tho)001:8777: 'ja' tshon nam mkha' dwangs gsal ba //
NK130(tho)001:8778: nges par thugs thob rtags yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8780: de la gdung dang ring srel ni so so ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:8782: ring srel gzhig par nus pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:8783: gdung ni 'jig par nus ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:8785: sha ri ram ni snum la 'gril //
NK130(tho)001:8786: sram khreg rdo rje'i gdung du bzhag /
NK130(tho)001:8788: 'di la slob dpon byang chub bzang pos /
NK130(tho)001:8792: chos kyi ring srel zhes gsang ba ring srel gyi 'grel par so sor phye'o //
NK130(tho)001:8793: gter lung gis gang zag lung bstan pa mi bden /
NK130(tho)001:8794: byams pa dang 'jam dpal gyis kyang lung ma bstan /
NK130(tho)001:8796: jo bo rje dang 'brom ston pas bka' gdams kyi
NK130(tho)001:8797: gang zag dang gnas gzhi mang po 'byung ba'i lung
NK130(tho)001:8798: bstan bka' gdams glegs bam na bzhugs pa 'dis gsal
NK130(tho)001:8799: la / gzhan yang ma 'ongs pa'i lung bstan pa
NK130(tho)001:8800: tsam ni mngon par shes pa thob pa dag gi
NK130(tho)001:8801: la / yul yin pas / phyi rol pa'i drang srong dang /
NK130(tho)001:8803: zhi gnas kyi snyoms 'jug thob pa dag la'ang yod pas /
NK130(tho)001:8804: sangs rgyas sprul sku la sbyar du mi rung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:8805: sgrub pa bka' brgyad ni gshin rje'i gshed dang /
NK130(tho)001:8807: mchod bstod dang drags sngags gnyis kyi gtso bo /
NK130(tho)001:8808: phur pa dang gsum ni phyag rdor yin par gsar rnying mthun cing /
NK130(tho)001:8811: yang dag gi lha mo brgyad la sogs pa yang ma rgyud kye rdor dang cha mthun /
NK130(tho)001:8812: ma mo ni 'jig rten gyi ma mo dang mkha'
NK130(tho)001:8813: 'gro rnams dbang du bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor yin te
NK130(tho)001:8814: 'di'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo che mchog he ru
NK130(tho)001:8815: ka de nyid sngags gsar mar bde mchog yin te
NK130(tho)001:8817: che ba'i che mchog lha yi lhar gyur pa /
NK130(tho)001:8818: kun bzang he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK130(tho)001:8820: mgon po phyag bzhi ba bde mchog gi sprul pa yin par bshad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8821: rnying ma bas che mchog khros pa yin ces bshad pa gung mthun /
NK130(tho)001:8822: rig 'dzin ni gsang sngags kyi bka' bsdu ba po rdo rje chos yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:8823: khungs thub pa gang las byung zhes gsungs pa /
NK130(tho)001:8824: gsar ma rang gi khrod na yod do //
NK130(tho)001:8825: theg pa rim pa dgu la dbang 'byung ba yang /
NK130(tho)001:8826: theg pa de dag nyams su len pa la rgyu mtshan nyid ltar nyams su len pa bas /
NK130(tho)001:8827: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi sgo nas nyams su len pa lam ches myur ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:8828: gsang sngags de yang dbang la ma brten nas mi 'grub pas /
NK130(tho)001:8829: thog mar theg pa rim pa dgu'i dbang bskur nas
NK130(tho)001:8830: de nas theg dgu'i khrid nyams su len pa lags
NK130(tho)001:8831: so // 'di ni dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i
NK130(tho)001:8832: lugs kyi lam 'bras su snang gsum gyi sngon du
NK130(tho)001:8833: rgyu dbang bskur bas lam de nyid gsang sngags kyi
NK130(tho)001:8834: lam du 'gyur bas bsgrod thag nye ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8835: grol byed lam gyi sngon du smin byed kyi dbang
NK130(tho)001:8836: thob dgos par bzhed pa dang grub mtha' mthun no
NK130(tho)001:8838: dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sde la sogs pa la ni khungs thub pa'i gzhung med do //
NK130(tho)001:8841: de la gsang sngags ni ltung ba'i sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK130(tho)001:8842: dper na bum pa lta bu gcig la yang dngos
NK130(tho)001:8843: po tha mal par bzung na ltung ba 'byung ste
NK130(tho)001:8844: / sa phyogs rdul shin tu che ba zhig tu
NK130(tho)001:8845: man+da la cig phyis te bzhag na de ma khad
NK130(tho)001:8846: rdul chags nas 'ong ba dang 'dra gsung /
NK130(tho)001:8847: de lta na sangs rgyas myur du 'grub pa rang dka' ba 'dra zhus pas /
NK130(tho)001:8848: de sbyang ba'i thabs bya ba rgya 'ur rdo gcig
NK130(tho)001:8849: gis 'ded pa lta bu'i gdams pa rdo rje sems
NK130(tho)001:8850: dpa'i bsgom bzlas bya ba gsang sngags pa la yod
NK130(tho)001:8851: / ces gsungs te dam tshig 'bum sde las lhag
NK130(tho)001:8852: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod par jo bos
NK130(tho)001:8854: ru dras srid gsum dbang du byas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:8856: ru dra zhes pa drag pa'i skad don yin /
NK130(tho)001:8857: drag po ni dbang phyug gi ming ste des sa
NK130(tho)001:8858: 'og sa steng sa bla gsum dbang du byas pa
NK130(tho)001:8859: dang / de'i tshe dpal he ru kas brtul ba'i lo rgyus bde mchog pa kun la grags /
NK130(tho)001:8860: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8861: ru dra mang du byung zhing srid gsum dbang du byas par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:8863: sangs rgyas pham par byas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8865: zhes gsungs pa de dag ni sangs rgyas gzhan gyi 'dul skal yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8866: 'dul byed de dag gi che ba bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:8867: gdul bya drang ba'i don du bstan pa yin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK130(tho)001:8869: sangs rgyas 'das nas sangs rgyas las lhag pa'i ston pa lo brgya nas 'byung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:8870: de tshe snga ma la rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi spun yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8871: rdzun gyi phreng ba lung dang rig pa'i gnod pa 'bab pa mang po yod do //
NK130(tho)001:8873: sangs rgyas las lhag pa'i ston pa mi srid pa yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8874: gdul bya la de ltar basngagasa pa yin pas skyon med de /
NK130(tho)001:8875: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa der ma zad /
NK130(tho)001:8876: dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni thams cad la snang bas
NK130(tho)001:8877: sangs rgyas thams cad las dge ba'i bshes gnyen lhag
NK130(tho)001:8879: mngal gyis ma gos pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:8881: gsang sngags ston pa gsum ni mngon sum du gsal bas su yis khegs /
NK130(tho)001:8882: tshe snga ma la rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan
NK130(tho)001:8883: gyi mched yin par ni slob dpon bo d+hi sa
NK130(tho)001:8884: t+wa yang bzhed pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8885: de'i phyir de dag 'khrul pa ma yin pa yang go dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:8886: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i chos tshul mtha' yas phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8887: grub mtha' rang blo'i phyogs rer ma 'dren ces /
NK130(tho)001:8888: gsol ba 'debs kyi sngon byon mkhas pa'i gzhung /
NK130(tho)001:8889: bdag blo byis pas gzhal ba'i yul min pas /
NK130(tho)001:8890: nongs gang mthol bshags 'di las dge ba gang /
NK130(tho)001:8891: thob de 'gro kun byang chub reg phyir bsngo //
NK130(tho)001:8892: da ni pan chen sh+aakya mchog ldan pas legs bshad
NK130(tho)001:8893: gser thur du dpal 'dzin gyi lung bkod pa de
NK130(tho)001:8894: la / bya ba chos kyi rje skal bzang pas legs bshad gser thur gzigs pas /
NK130(tho)001:8895: pan chen de nyid la dogs gcod kyi yi ge legs bshad sgo dbye zhes bya ba springs /
NK130(tho)001:8896: de'i lan du pan chen des nges don rab gsal
NK130(tho)001:8897: zhes pa mdzad nas bskur ba'i bsdu tshom brjod par
NK130(tho)001:8898: bya ste / de la pan chen de nyid kyis gser thur du rnying ma ma bkag pa'i tshul /
NK130(tho)001:8899: ma bkag na dpal 'dzin gyi lung 'dren pa'i rgyu
NK130(tho)001:8900: mtshan ci snyam pa la lan dang gnyis su phye
NK130(tho)001:8902: sdom gsum gyi gzhung rtsa ba na //
NK130(tho)001:8903: gsang sngags rnying ma'i kun rdzob kun //
NK130(tho)001:8905: gzhan yang gsang sngags gsar rnying la //
NK130(tho)001:8906: zhes sogs rnying ma'i mtshan smos nas dpyad pa'i gzhir bzhag pa 'ga' zhig snang /
NK130(tho)001:8907: kho bo cag gi gser thur gyi yi ge dkyus
NK130(tho)001:8908: ma na ni gsar rnying la chos yin min gyi
NK130(tho)001:8909: rnam dbye byas pa lta ci smos /
NK130(tho)001:8910: rnying ma zhes pa'i tshig tsam yang brjod pa'i lam
NK130(tho)001:8911: nas byung ba med kyi steng du dri ba dang
NK130(tho)001:8913: 'gos lo ts+aa ba sogs kyis chos log dri ma
NK130(tho)001:8914: can du bshad pa'i rnam grangs mang po de dag
NK130(tho)001:8915: de ltar du 'thad na ha cang thal bar 'gyur
NK130(tho)001:8916: ba'i glan ka dag bkod nas /
NK130(tho)001:8917: bod du sbyar ba'i rgyud du 'dod pa dag gi
NK130(tho)001:8918: nang na'ang bka' dang 'dra ba'i bstan bcos dag yod
NK130(tho)001:8919: pa yin / zhes rang gi lugs gsal por smras pa de la mi rtog par /
NK130(tho)001:8920: grub mtha' la ma zhugs pa'i khyim pa dag gis
NK130(tho)001:8921: dpal 'dzin gyis byas pa'i tshig de dag kha bton
NK130(tho)001:8922: du byas pa na grub mtha' par khas 'che ba'i
NK130(tho)001:8923: smra ba po dag kyang la la dag rtog dpyod
NK130(tho)001:8924: ma btang bar gang thos dbyangs su gyer ba'am /
NK130(tho)001:8925: smra ba po kha cig 'ga' dang 'ga' la phra ma bgyi ba'i bsam pa sngon du btang nas /
NK130(tho)001:8926: gzhung rtsa ba na ci yod mi rtog par 'bel
NK130(tho)001:8927: gtam gyi tshig kho na la skyor 'byin byed pa
NK130(tho)001:8929: zhes spyir btang nas de'i don 'chad pa na /
NK130(tho)001:8930: khong rang gi bzhed pa mdor bsdus te brjod /
NK130(tho)001:8931: sdom gsum rab dbye'i dgongs pa ji ltar yod pa /
NK130(tho)001:8932: dpal 'dzin gyi na yams 'god pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK130(tho)001:8933: na yams de la blang dor ji ltar yod pa dang bzhis bstan te /
NK130(tho)001:8934: khong rang gi bzhed pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:8935: gsar rnying zhes grags pa'i chos dang gang zag shan phye ste /
NK130(tho)001:8936: gnyis ka'i gang zag 'khrul med du khas len mi nus /
NK130(tho)001:8937: chos gnyis ka 'khrul med du khas len te /
NK130(tho)001:8938: gang zag la 'khrul pa yod mnyam dang chos la med mnyam du mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8939: de ltar ma yin par rnying ma'i chos 'khrul pa yin na /
NK130(tho)001:8940: ka cog la sogs pas bsgyur ba'i sde snod gsum /
NK130(tho)001:8941: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud sogs bstan pa snga dar la byon pa'i 'gyur chos spyi dang /
NK130(tho)001:8942: khyad par bla med kyi gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK130(tho)001:8944: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor rnams chos ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:8945: de rnams rnying ma'i tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad kyi gtso bo yin cing /
NK130(tho)001:8946: rtsa ba de gsum la brten nas rnying mar grags
NK130(tho)001:8947: pa'i chos mang zhig byung bar 'chad pa'i phyir ro
NK130(tho)001:8948: // bye brag tu yang phur chos ma yin na /
NK130(tho)001:8949: de dag gi rgya dpe dang lo ts+aa ba tshad ldan gyi 'gyur yod cing /
NK130(tho)001:8950: rtsod pa can gyi rgyud gzhan rgyud 'bum du mi 'dzud pa'i dpyod ldan bcom ldan rig ral dang /
NK130(tho)001:8951: bu ston rin po che sogs kyis rtsod med du mdzad pas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:8953: bod du snga 'gyur gyi lta spyod la log par
NK130(tho)001:8954: rtog pa mang du byung ba de phyis rtsod pa
NK130(tho)001:8955: can du gyur pa la brten nas sngon gyi lta
NK130(tho)001:8956: spyod dag ma dag gnyis ka la rnying ma zhes
NK130(tho)001:8957: btags shing / de bzhin du phyis rgya gar nas
NK130(tho)001:8958: bsgyur ba'i bstan bcos yin nges shes pa rnams dang
NK130(tho)001:8959: btags shing / / de la 'dra min byas nas
NK130(tho)001:8960: bod mang pos rgya gar la khungs phyungs te sbyar
NK130(tho)001:8961: ba'i mdo rgyud bstan bcos su mtshan gsol ba mang
NK130(tho)001:8962: po la yang gsar ma zhes btags so //
NK130(tho)001:8963: des na gsang sngags rnying ma'i rgyud du grags pa'i
NK130(tho)001:8964: chos yin na gsang sngags rnying ma yin par ma
NK130(tho)001:8965: nges shing / gsar ma'i mdo dang bstan bcos su grags pa'i chos yin na yang /
NK130(tho)001:8966: de dang de tshad ldan du ma nges pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:8968: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dngos dang /
NK130(tho)001:8969: de'i slob ma grub pa brnyes pa de dag gis
NK130(tho)001:8970: snod du gyur pa rnams rig 'dzin gyi sa la
NK130(tho)001:8972: gang dang 'tshams pa'i lha dang sngags dang lta ba'i rim pa rnams gsungs shing /
NK130(tho)001:8973: de nyams su blangs pas grub pa brnyes pa mang po byon te /
NK130(tho)001:8974: de dang mthun pa'i snyan brgyud dgongs pa yi ger
NK130(tho)001:8975: btab pa la brten nas rnying mar grags pa'i chos
NK130(tho)001:8976: rnam par dag pa de byung ba yin la /
NK130(tho)001:8977: 'di dag la yang dag par na bstan bcos kyi mtshan nyid tshang ba yin te /
NK130(tho)001:8979: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK130(tho)001:8980: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyi bshad //
NK130(tho)001:8981: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK130(tho)001:8982: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK130(tho)001:8983: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid de tshang ba'i phyir na /
NK130(tho)001:8984: slob dpon pad+mas gsungs pa'i bstan bcos ni sangs rgyas
NK130(tho)001:8985: kyi bka' dang khyad par med par grub pa yin
NK130(tho)001:8986: te / dper na rje btsun byams pa'i chos lnga dang /
NK130(tho)001:8987: dus kyi 'khor lo bsdus pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:8988: de'i 'grel pa dri ma med pa'i 'od dang sogs pa bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:8989: de'i slob ma rig 'dzin gyi sa la bzhugs pa dag gis bshad pa'ang de dang 'dra ste /
NK130(tho)001:8990: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dngos dang /
NK130(tho)001:8991: rgya gar gyi mkhan pos byas pa'i bstan bcos ma yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:8992: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub kyi las la mi 'khrul ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:8993: dper na rje btsun mi la dang sa skya ba
NK130(tho)001:8994: chen po la sogs pa'i bstan bcos rnams bzhin no
NK130(tho)001:8995: // 'phags yul nas 'gyur ba'i bka' dang bstan bcos
NK130(tho)001:8996: dngos ma yin kyang shin tu lkog gyur gyi gnas
NK130(tho)001:8997: la mi bslu ba dag mthong ste /
NK130(tho)001:8998: dper na sman dpyad kyi rgyud sde bzhir grags pa bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:9000: 'di la kun mkhyen go bo'i dngos slob drung gnas rwa dpon pa chen pos /
NK130(tho)001:9001: tshig de dag kyang rnying ma'i rgyud phal mo che
NK130(tho)001:9002: bod kyi bstan bcos su byas 'dug pas rnying ma'i
NK130(tho)001:9003: zhabs drangs / sdom gsum gyi 'grel pa la legs
NK130(tho)001:9004: bshad gser thur brtsams pas sdom gsum rab dbye rtsa
NK130(tho)001:9006: slob dpon pad+ma la rgyud rnam dag tu btub pa tsho khong gi rgyud du ma btub /
NK130(tho)001:9008: sangs rgya ba'i lam phyin ci ma log par ston pa'i rgyu rnams mtshungs pa'i skabs med /
NK130(tho)001:9009: rgyal ba'i bka' dri ma med pa la bka' ma
NK130(tho)001:9010: yin zhes smra ba chos spong ba'i las chen po
NK130(tho)001:9011: yin ces / 'dis sdom gsum rab dbye sgrub pa'i bstan bcos legs bshad me 'od ces bya ba /
NK130(tho)001:9012: gser thur la lan du mdzad pa zhig kyang yod do //
NK130(tho)001:9014: sngags kyi tshig rnams 'phags yul gyi tshig dang mthun
NK130(tho)001:9015: par ma byung yang sngags 'bras 'grub pa mi 'gal
NK130(tho)001:9016: te / sngags 'bras byin gyis rlob pa'i nus mthu dang ldan pa dag gis byas pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9017: dper na rje btsun dam pa rgya gar gyis mdzad pa'i rten 'brel sna tshogs pa rnams bzhiin no //
NK130(tho)001:9019: 'ga' yi brda' byas nyid yin na //
NK130(tho)001:9020: sngags kyi 'bras bu sgrub byed yin //
NK130(tho)001:9022: gang yang rgyud rigs 'ga' zhig gis //
NK130(tho)001:9024: 'di dag gi de gtso bo'i mthu //
NK130(tho)001:9025: de bshad rig pas 'jug phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9027: de'i phyir rgyud du ming btags nas bod kyis sbyar ba la chos log gis ma khyab ste /
NK130(tho)001:9028: bstan bcos rnam dag tu mi 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9030: sngags legs sbyar du med kyang /
NK130(tho)001:9031: sngags 'bras byin gyis rlob pa'i mthu ldan gyis byas par mi 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9032: gang la dmigs pa'i nus pa thon par mthong ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9033: bod kyi lha 'dre dkyil 'khor la bcug cing de'i
NK130(tho)001:9034: sngags yod pas rgya gar ma ma yin pa grub
NK130(tho)001:9035: tu chug kyang / sngags chos rnam dag ma yin pa mi 'grub ste /
NK130(tho)001:9037: de las 'phros pa'i gsang sngags kyi chos 'di dag
NK130(tho)001:9038: ni gdul bya bod kyi mi dang mi ma yin
NK130(tho)001:9039: pa dag gi dbang du byas nas gsungs pa'i phyir
NK130(tho)001:9040: dang / dper na gdul bya la 'phags yul gyi dbang du byas nas gsungs pa'i sngags dang /
NK130(tho)001:9041: lha'i nang nas yul de dang der grags pa'i lha
NK130(tho)001:9042: klu 'byung po'i tshogs kyi gzungs sngags dang sgrub thabs
NK130(tho)001:9043: kyi rim pa mang po dag 'byung ba bzhin no
NK130(tho)001:9044: // bka' dngos ma yin zhing bod kyis sbyar ba
NK130(tho)001:9045: nyams su blangs pas mchog mi 'grub na ha cang
NK130(tho)001:9046: // thal te / rgyud nas gsungs pa'i lha'i sgrub
NK130(tho)001:9047: thabs dang dkyil chog sogs pan grub dang bod kyi
NK130(tho)001:9048: bla mas sbyar ba la lag len du spyod pas
NK130(tho)001:9049: // thal te / so // zhes gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:9050: ci de dag ni rnying ma'i rgyud rnams bstan bcos su sgrub pa'i lung du 'dug /
NK130(tho)001:9051: de ltar de tsam du drangs pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na /
NK130(tho)001:9052: pho brang zhi ba 'od dang 'gos kyi 'byams yig
NK130(tho)001:9053: tu chos log dri ma can du byas 'dug pa
NK130(tho)001:9054: dang / dpal 'dzin gyis rnying mar grags so cog chos ma yin par byas pas /
NK130(tho)001:9055: de'i lan 'di bas lhag pa ma mchis pas bris pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9057: gsang sngags rnying ma ba yang dag cig tu rlom na /
NK130(tho)001:9058: de'i khyad chos kyi gtso bo lta bas che bar khas len dgos pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9059: spyir rnying ma dang khyad par sems phyogs bzhed na /
NK130(tho)001:9060: lta ba khas len dang bral ba /
NK130(tho)001:9061: sgom pa yid byed dang bral ba /
NK130(tho)001:9062: spyod pa blang dor dang bral ba /
NK130(tho)001:9063: 'bras bu re dogs dang bral ba /
NK130(tho)001:9064: zhes pa 'di mi 'dod na sems phyogs khas len gzhan ngo tsam du zad /
NK130(tho)001:9065: 'dod na rnam bzhag de thos na srog 'dor ba tsam byed pa mang bas /
NK130(tho)001:9066: de dgag sgrub ji ltar bgyi /
NK130(tho)001:9067: kho bo ni chos bzhi po de dag khas len pa la spobs par gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:9068: de yang lta sgom 'bras bu gsum po de ni
NK130(tho)001:9069: klu sgrub dang thogs med gnyis ka'i shing rta'i srol
NK130(tho)001:9071: spyod pa'i tshul de la gzhan dag gis /
NK130(tho)001:9072: blong dor med pa spyod pa min //
NK130(tho)001:9073: de ni lta ba'i rnam bzhag yin //
NK130(tho)001:9074: ces zer ba de'i lan ni rnam shes kyi don
NK130(tho)001:9075: blang dor yod kyang lta bas zin pa'i tshe blang
NK130(tho)001:9076: dor gyi mtshan mar mi 'dzin zer ba yin nam
NK130(tho)001:9077: / khyad dpal 'dzin gyi lugs de bzhed pas lta
NK130(tho)001:9078: bas zin pa'i tshe mtshan mar mi 'dzin gsung yang
NK130(tho)001:9079: / / lta bas zin pa'i dus de la sgom pa zer ba min /
NK130(tho)001:9082: gnas skabs su gang snang thams cad rang sems yin pa de bzhed dam mi bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:9083: mi bzhed na sems phyogs dpyis phyin ji ltar 'chad /
NK130(tho)001:9084: kho bo ni de ltar khas len te /
NK130(tho)001:9085: ma blangs na theg pa rim dgu lta ci smos /
NK130(tho)001:9086: mdo sde pa yan chad kyi grub mtha' kun dang 'gal /
NK130(tho)001:9087: des na kho bo ni gzhan snang gi gzugs sku gnyis sangs rgyas dngos ma yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9088: sangs rgyas rang snang la kun rdzob kyi snang ba mi 'char bar khas len pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:9089: yang sems phyogs dang sgyu 'phrul bzhed nges na /
NK130(tho)001:9090: gzhi'i dus su kun rdzob tshad mas mi 'grub pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9091: 'bras bu'i dus su sems can gyi las snang ji
NK130(tho)001:9092: snyed pas sangs rgyas kyi ye shes la mi snang
NK130(tho)001:9093: ngo // zhes pa 'di bzhed dam mi bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:9094: mi bzhed na sems phyogs dang sgyu 'phrul la nges pa gting nas 'drongs pa 'gal /
NK130(tho)001:9095: kho bos ni de ltar khas blangs so //
NK130(tho)001:9097: kun rdzob tshad mas ma grub na las 'bras la skur pa btab /
NK130(tho)001:9098: mnyam bzhag tu ci yang yid la mi byed pa ha shang gi lta ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:9099: sangs rgyas kyi rang snang la kun rdzob mi snang na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:9100: zhes pa'i skyon 'di rang la zug par byed dam spong bar byed /
NK130(tho)001:9101: zug par byed na sgyu 'phrul dang sems phyogs nang nas bud /
NK130(tho)001:9102: skyon 'di spong na lung rig gang gis ji ltar spong /
NK130(tho)001:9103: kho bo ni skyon de 'di ltar spong ste /
NK130(tho)001:9104: kun rdzob thams cad 'khrul snang yin gyi gnas tshul la ma zhugs pas tshad mas ma grub /
NK130(tho)001:9105: yid byed thams cad mtshan 'dzin gyi rtog pa yin
NK130(tho)001:9106: pas mnyam bzhag ye shes dang gzhi gcig tu mi
NK130(tho)001:9107: 'du / sangs rgyas la ma rig pa ma mchis pas yul kun rdzob mi snang ste /
NK130(tho)001:9108: yul kun rdzob ni yul can mthong ba rdzun pa kho na'i spyod yul yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9110: grub mtha' 'cha' lugs 'di med na rnying ma'i chos ji ltar 'dzin /
NK130(tho)001:9111: nga rnying ma pa'o zhes pa'i khas len tsam gyis chog pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:9112: 'di la phyis kyi sde snod klog pa dag na re /
NK130(tho)001:9113: 'di lta bu'i grub mtha' ni gsar byung yin no //
NK130(tho)001:9115: kun rdzob bden pa'i go don spyir tshad ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:9116: bye brag ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes snyed don du 'chad pa 'di ni /
NK130(tho)001:9117: rje tsong kha pas rtsa she'i ti ka mdzad pa 'di tshun gyi kha skad yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:9118: de'i gong du mkhas rmongs mtha' dag mthun par /
NK130(tho)001:9119: kun rdzob ni mthong ba rdzun pa blo 'khrul pa'i rnyed don du 'chad pa sha stag yin /
NK130(tho)001:9120: mnyam gzhag dngos gzhi'i dus su yid byed dang bral ba dgongs pa'i 'di rnying ma lta ci smos /
NK130(tho)001:9121: rngog lo chen po dang jo zhal yan gyi klog
NK130(tho)001:9122: pa ba mkhas pa dang bsam gtan pa 'khrul med
NK130(tho)001:9123: kun gyi yi ge na snang /
NK130(tho)001:9124: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi ye shes la kun rdzob mi
NK130(tho)001:9125: snang ba 'di klog pa ba kun la rlung ltar
NK130(tho)001:9126: grags pa'i gzhung dbu ma la 'jug pa na gsal
NK130(tho)001:9127: hrig ge bzhugs pa la gsar byung gi grub mtha'
NK130(tho)001:9128: zer na / lugs rnying pa zhig gang na yod ston rigs pa las /
NK130(tho)001:9129: dge ldan pa chen pos sku tshe'i mjug la rnyed
NK130(tho)001:9130: pa'i grub matha'i rjes su tsham tshom med par rgyugs
NK130(tho)001:9131: nas / lugs rnying pa 'dzin pa dag la gsar
NK130(tho)001:9132: byung na smra ba ni byung rgyal du smra ba
NK130(tho)001:9133: nas / kho na'i / zhes pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9134: sdom gsum na rnying ma la brtag dpyad cha tsam las med de /
NK130(tho)001:9135: nor ba gsar ma la mang bas so thar byang chub bar du len pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9136: byang sdom dbu ma lugs su mi byed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9137: bdag gzhan barje ba bsgom du mi rung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9138: dbang med par gsang sngags bsgom pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9139: yod pa'i dge ba chos dbyings la bsngo rgyur byed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9140: jo bo lugs kyi sems bskyed jo bo'i dgongs pa dang 'gal ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9141: don dam sems bskyed cho gas len pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9142: n+aa ro'i brgyud 'dzin du khas len pa po dbang dang rim gnyis mi bsgom pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9143: phag mo'i byin rlabs kyis chos sgo 'byed pa sogs
NK130(tho)001:9144: gsar ma la yod pa'i chos log ji snyed gsar
NK130(tho)001:9145: ma'i chos ma yin pa bzhin du /
NK130(tho)001:9146: rnying ma la yod pa'i chos log ji snyed pa rnying ma'i chos ma yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:9147: de dang de bkag pa la chos gsar rnying bkag par mi 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:9149: skabs don rnying ma'i chos ma yin pa la de'i
NK130(tho)001:9150: chos su sgro btags pa de lung rig gis sun
NK130(tho)001:9151: phyung ba la rnying ma bkag go zhes smra ba
NK130(tho)001:9152: po rnams ni / rang nyid gti mug pas chos
NK130(tho)001:9153: log la zhen nas lag len byed pa de la
NK130(tho)001:9154: rnying ma'i chos su zhen cing khas blangs pa las
NK130(tho)001:9155: byung ba'i ngan rtog yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9156: dper na sbyor sgrol gyi don yang dag pa ni
NK130(tho)001:9157: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa bsgral nas chos
NK130(tho)001:9158: kyi dbyings su sbyor ba zhes bya ba yin pa
NK130(tho)001:9159: la / de ma go bar chags sdang las gyur
NK130(tho)001:9160: pa'i sbyor sgrol chos su smra ba dag bkag pa
NK130(tho)001:9161: na rnying ma bkag go zhes cho nge 'don pa
NK130(tho)001:9163: sdom gsum nas gsar ma la nor ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9164: rnying ma la dpyad tshul rnams smos pa'i mthar /
NK130(tho)001:9165: 'di ni chos rjes skya pan+di ta'i bzhed pa gsal
NK130(tho)001:9166: ba nyid du bstan bcos 'dir dngos bstan du byung
NK130(tho)001:9167: bas sba bar ma nus so //
NK130(tho)001:9171: rje btsun sa skya pan+di ta'i //
NK130(tho)001:9172: bstan bcos nyid kyi dbang byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:9174: 'ga' la zug rdur ma gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:9175: zhes gsungs kyang sdom gsum gyi gtam drang por bshad
NK130(tho)001:9176: na rnying ma'i gsal byed yin par rang gis kyang
NK130(tho)001:9177: zhal gyis bzhes pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:9179: rnying ma'i chos kun 'phags yul nas //
NK130(tho)001:9180: bsgyur bar 'bad pas sgrub mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:9181: slob dpon sprul pa'i sku nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:9182: gsungs pa nyid du grub pas chog /'phags pa'i yul nas phyis 'gyur ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:9183: sngags dang brda skad ma mthun yang //
NK130(tho)001:9184: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub la //
NK130(tho)001:9185: mi bslu nges phyir de tshad ma //
NK130(tho)001:9186: dper na yul chen so so nas //
NK130(tho)001:9187: grub pa mchog rnams kyis blangs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9188: chos kyang glegs bam so so las //
NK130(tho)001:9189: 'phags pa'i yul du bsgyur ba min //
NK130(tho)001:9190: rdo rje sems dpa'i snang thob pa //
NK130(tho)001:9191: bka' yi bsdu ba po nyid kyis //
NK130(tho)001:9192: yul khams so so'i skad nyid du //
NK130(tho)001:9193: bshad pas chog par gsungs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:9194: rnying ma'i chos rnams 'phags yul nas //
NK130(tho)001:9195: 'gyur bar nges rnams sgrub mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:9196: ma nges pa rnams bstan bcos su //
NK130(tho)001:9198: gang 'di'i rnam rtog rang gzo'i lam //
NK130(tho)001:9200: bod kyi yul du sngon byon pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9201: chen po rnams kyis deng bshad pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9203: 'di ni sngon gyi mkhas grub rnams kyis rnying ma'i
NK130(tho)001:9204: rgyud rnams bstan bcos su bshad pa ma mthong bas
NK130(tho)001:9207: mdor na yang phur sogs rgya dpe can lo ts+aa
NK130(tho)001:9208: ba don mthun gyis bsgyur ba las mkhas pa la
NK130(tho)001:9209: mthun par grags pa rnams ni spyir rgya gar ma
NK130(tho)001:9210: dang / khyad par rgyud rnam dag tu grub zin pas na slar sgrub mi dgos /
NK130(tho)001:9211: de las 'phros pa de dag gi gzhung rnams dang
NK130(tho)001:9212: mi 'gal ba rnams ni slob dpon rin po ches
NK130(tho)001:9213: mdzad pa'am / dngos slob kyis de'i gsung gi bcud phyungs te bris pa yin kyang rung ste /
NK130(tho)001:9214: de'i don nyams su blangs pas dngos grub gnyis brnyes
NK130(tho)001:9215: pa mang du byung 'dug pa kho nas chos rnam
NK130(tho)001:9217: rgya gar ma dang bka' bstan bcos kyi dpyad pas ci zhig bya /
NK130(tho)001:9219: 'di yang bstan bcos yin du chug kyang slob dpon
NK130(tho)001:9220: pad+mas mdzad pa de rgya gar mar mi dpyod pa
NK130(tho)001:9223: gzhan du na rgya gar du yang grub pa thob pa'i slob dpon rnams kyis o rgyan dang /
NK130(tho)001:9224: sham+b+ha la la sogs pa yul gyi gnas bzhan dang
NK130(tho)001:9225: gzhan nas pusti blangs te 'phags yul ba'i skabs su
NK130(tho)001:9227: don gyi snying po thugs su chud nas 'phags yul
NK130(tho)001:9228: gyi skad du bris pa kho na yin pas de
NK130(tho)001:9229: rnams kyang the tshom pa'i gnas su ma gyur tam
