NK130(tho)001:9230: / 'di ltar 'chad pa 'di yang mkhas pa thams
NK130(tho)001:9231: cad kyi lugs yin gyi kho bos rang gzor byas
NK130(tho)001:9234: grub thob rnams kyis o rgyan dang sham+b+ha la sogs
NK130(tho)001:9235: nas blangs pa'i rgyud sde rnams kyi don thugs su
NK130(tho)001:9236: chud mod kyi / lo rgyus dag tu glegs bam
NK130(tho)001:9237: spyan drangs pa'i tshul kho na snang bas don la
NK130(tho)001:9238: chud mod kyi / mi gnas so // 'di la rtse le rig 'dzin chen po ni /
NK130(tho)001:9239: gsung 'di ni gsang sngags rnying ma yang dag tu
NK130(tho)001:9240: sgrub pa'i lung rig dang dper brjod sla zhing chun
NK130(tho)001:9241: che ba / don la gnas shing tha snyad kyis glags mi rnyed pa /
NK130(tho)001:9242: 'dod mkhan mkhas pa'i grogs po mang zhing dpyod ldan gyi yid tshim pa /
NK130(tho)001:9243: rang cag rnams kyis ji tsam 'bad kyang phyogs tsam yang mi 'grub pa'i sgrub byed 'di lta bu /
NK130(tho)001:9245: gzhan dag ni 'di la lung 'dren rgyu ci yang med bzhin du lung rig zer ba mi 'thad /
NK130(tho)001:9246: rig pas sgrub tshul 'di dag kyang rgyud ma yin pa'i shes byed kho nar snang /
NK130(tho)001:9247: gsang ba snying po rgyud ma yin pa byas nas
NK130(tho)001:9248: mjug tu bcom ldan pa'i gsang ba snying po bka'
NK130(tho)001:9249: sgrub drangs pa 'di yang rgyab 'gal du song zer
NK130(tho)001:9250: / bya ba chos rje skal bzang pa thugs mtshim
NK130(tho)001:9251: pa'i lan gyi tshigs su bcad pa ni 'og tu
NK130(tho)001:9252: / 'chad do // de nas legs bshad gser thur
NK130(tho)001:9253: du dpal 'dzin gyi na yams 'dren pa'i sgrub byed
NK130(tho)001:9256: sngags kyi khyad chos lta ba min //
NK130(tho)001:9257: dbu ma las lhag ga la yod //
NK130(tho)001:9259: ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum //
NK130(tho)001:9260: 'dus pa'i bskyed rdzogs nyams len gyi //
NK130(tho)001:9261: rim pa tsam gyis so sor phye //
NK130(tho)001:9263: 'di la sa pan gyi bzhed pa /
NK130(tho)001:9264: de rtogs pa yi thabs la ni //
NK130(tho)001:9265: theg pa'i rim pa yod pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:9266: zhes sogs gong du sa pan gyi skabs su bsgrubs zin to //
NK130(tho)001:9268: rdo rje theg pa'i khyad chos ni //
NK130(tho)001:9269: dbang dang rim pa gnyis su 'dus //
NK130(tho)001:9271: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga dang //
NK130(tho)001:9273: phyi rol pa yang bskyed rim byed //
NK130(tho)001:9274: dag pa bsgom pa sangs rgyas chos //
NK130(tho)001:9276: gsang sngags gsar ma'i khrod na yang //
NK130(tho)001:9277: rdo rje 'jigs byed sam lugs dang //
NK130(tho)001:9278: dus 'khor lce spyang glu gar dang //
NK130(tho)001:9280: mgon po dang ni lha mo'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:9281: brgya dang lnga bcu lhag la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:9282: rang gzo'i rdzun rgyud du ma snang //
NK130(tho)001:9283: zhes pa rnams kyis rnam dpyod dang thos pa che ba yang mtshon nus shing /
NK130(tho)001:9285: bde mchog ra li la sogs pa ga ya d+ha
NK130(tho)001:9286: ra dang 'brog mi'i chos spangs mgon po dang lha
NK130(tho)001:9287: ma'i rgyud rdzun ma yin na gzhan rgyud yang dag
NK130(tho)001:9289: lha mgon gnyis kyi sgrub skor gang nas 'tshol /
NK130(tho)001:9290: ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum /
NK130(tho)001:9291: gsang 'dus pa'i bskyed rdzogs kyis bye /
NK130(tho)001:9292: rgyud sde so sor ma phye zer ba /
NK130(tho)001:9293: de ga rnying ma'i rang lugs ma 'chugs pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:9294: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK130(tho)001:9295: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga /
NK130(tho)001:9296: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga zer ba de yin /
NK130(tho)001:9297: rnying ma sor bzhag des rnying ma 'gog pa yang thos pa gti thug pa ma yin nam /
NK130(tho)001:9299: sgrub dus bla mar rang bsgom nas /
NK130(tho)001:9300: rang gi 'og tu rta mgrin bsgom /
NK130(tho)001:9301: zer ba 'di yig cha de na gtan nas med de /
NK130(tho)001:9302: bsnyen dus bla ma rta mgrin gyi spyi bor byung bas /
NK130(tho)001:9303: sgrub dus rang bla mar bsgom pa na yang rta
NK130(tho)001:9304: mgrin rang gi 'og tu yong bar bsam 'dug pa
NK130(tho)001:9305: rnam dpyod che ches nas rang mtshang bstan 'dug go
NK130(tho)001:9307: rgyal po dar mas bstan pa bsnubs //
NK130(tho)001:9308: de rjes chos log du ma 'phel //
NK130(tho)001:9310: chos log thams cad nub par mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:9311: ces pa'i tshul dang chos skad mthun par byung la /
NK130(tho)001:9312: des skyon du bshad pa dag rnying ma'i rgyud du
NK130(tho)001:9313: btags pa'i nang du byung na khungs dag par yang
NK130(tho)001:9314: bya dgos so // de las gzhan lung de nas
NK130(tho)001:9315: bshad pa'i rtags kyis bsgrub bya zhig bsgrubs 'dug na
NK130(tho)001:9316: lung du byas pa zhes pa'i tha snyad 'jog pa
NK130(tho)001:9317: bya dgos so // yin mod / rang lugs dpyis
NK130(tho)001:9318: phyin par gong du bkod zin pa'i 'og tu lung
NK130(tho)001:9319: du byas pa zhes bya ba'i tha snyad mkhas pa
NK130(tho)001:9321: tha snyad la mi mkhas pa rnams kyi kha na
NK130(tho)001:9322: rgyu ba gang yin pa de tha snyad la mkhas
NK130(tho)001:9323: pa rnams kyi tshig gi lam du spyan 'dren par
NK130(tho)001:9324: mi bya'o // bzhi pa de nas bshad pa la
NK130(tho)001:9325: 'dor len ji ltar yod pa'i tshul la gnyis las
NK130(tho)001:9326: mi bya'o // / rgyud kyi khungs la dang /
NK130(tho)001:9327: lung don la ji ltar yod pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9331: spyir bod du brtsams pa'i rgyud la /
NK130(tho)001:9332: mdzad pa po rig 'dzin gyis brnyes pa dang ma
NK130(tho)001:9333: brnyes pa gang gis sbyar ba yin kyang rung ste
NK130(tho)001:9335: kho bo cag ni rgyud dri ma can zhes ming 'dogs pa yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:9336: rgyud de dang de'i rang ldog nas chos log ces
NK130(tho)001:9337: bya bar smra ba ni spobs pa ma yin te
NK130(tho)001:9339: mi rigs pa yi gzugs la'ang mi rigs na /
NK130(tho)001:9340: the tshom za ba'i chos la smos ci dgos //
NK130(tho)001:9342: des na bstan bcos kyi nang du lhad zhugs pa
NK130(tho)001:9343: tsam gyis bstan bcos de chos log tu bsgrub mi
NK130(tho)001:9344: nus te / de'i nang na chos yang dag pa du ma bzhugs pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9346: 'gos lo ts+aa ba sogs kyis gsang ba snying po rma rin chen mchog gis mdzad par 'chad cing /
NK130(tho)001:9347: de la log pa'i skyon bzhi la sogs pa yod par bshad /
NK130(tho)001:9348: de ltar 'chad pa nyid kyis chos log tu 'grub par mi nges te /
NK130(tho)001:9349: lo ts+aa ba de nyid kyis mdzad par grub pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9350: bcom ldan ral gris gsang snying sgrub pa las kyang 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK130(tho)001:9352: rgyud zab mo gsang ba snying po la /
NK130(tho)001:9353: 'gos lhas btsas la sogs pas sgro skur byas pa de spang bar bya ste /
NK130(tho)001:9354: 'di rgyud yang dag pa yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK130(tho)001:9355: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon bi shwa mi tras mdzad pa la /
NK130(tho)001:9356: ye shes sems dpa' gang rog pa //
NK130(tho)001:9359: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang mu med par gzhi
NK130(tho)001:9360: tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba
NK130(tho)001:9361: la / ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK130(tho)001:9362: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK130(tho)001:9364: bsam gyis mi khyabs pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK130(tho)001:9366: mchod rten sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:9367: pho brang gnas zhes bya ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:9368: zhes pa'i 'grel par rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK130(tho)001:9369: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus thams cad kyang
NK130(tho)001:9370: so so ma yin ngo bo gcig pa'i ye shes
NK130(tho)001:9373: rang bzhin rang bzhin med pa'i rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:9375: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK130(tho)001:9376: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK130(tho)001:9377: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK130(tho)001:9378: skyes tsam nyid na skye ba med //
NK130(tho)001:9385: mi bstan pa'i gsang ba zhes byung /
NK130(tho)001:9387: gsang snying las dbang lnga byung /
NK130(tho)001:9389: mthing ga dkar po ser leb rgan /
NK130(tho)001:9391: mtha' dbus med par lhun gyis grub //
NK130(tho)001:9393: gsang snying las de kho na nyid gsum byung //
NK130(tho)001:9394: zhes pa la sogs pa thams cad la gsang snying gi mtshan smos nas drangs so //
NK130(tho)001:9395: log pa'i skyon bzhi la sogs pa spang ba ni /
NK130(tho)001:9396: 'di skad bdag gis bshad pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:9397: sangs rgyas kyi gsung thams cad sa bcu pa bas
NK130(tho)001:9398: kyang bsdu bar mi nus pas sangs rgyas nyid kyis
NK130(tho)001:9399: bsdus par 'dod pa'i lugs yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9400: gsang 'dus kyi 'grel pa slob dpon mtsho skyes kyi gsang ba grub pa las /
NK130(tho)001:9401: slob dpon phal cher 'di skad brjod //
NK130(tho)001:9402: dpal ldan 'dus pa mdangs can gyi //
NK130(tho)001:9403: rgyud kyi sdud par zhed pa po //
NK130(tho)001:9404: dpa' bo 'jig rten dbang phyug zer //
NK130(tho)001:9405: bla ma'i zhabs kyi bka' drin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:9406: dpal ldan 'dus pa'i snyud pa po //
NK130(tho)001:9407: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin zhes //
NK130(tho)001:9408: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NK130(tho)001:9409: rgyud mdzad po ni thugs rdo rje //
NK130(tho)001:9410: zhes bshad pa bzhin du gsung mkhan nyid kyis bsdus pa'i lugs yin /
NK130(tho)001:9412: chos mngon pa nas kyang 'og min la tshad med par bshad pa yod do //
NK130(tho)001:9413: dus bzhi ni bi shwa mi tra'i 'grel chen nas kyang /
NK130(tho)001:9414: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du de bzhin rig par bya /
NK130(tho)001:9416: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i mgon po kun gyi /
NK130(tho)001:9417: zhes gsar ma nas kyang bshad la /
NK130(tho)001:9418: sangs rgyas gsang bas bskal pa bzhi la bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:9419: rdo rje sems dpa' dbus su byung ba ni /
NK130(tho)001:9420: gtso bo 'pho bar gsar ma nas kyang bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:9421: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK130(tho)001:9423: gsang snying gi rgya dpe las /
NK130(tho)001:9424: p+au tri pra dz+ny+aa ti kash+ya ti /
NK130(tho)001:9426: p+au tra thig gi rgya skad yin /
NK130(tho)001:9427: nyi 'od seng ge'i 'grel pa nas kyang thig la bshad /
NK130(tho)001:9429: rgyud gzhan du kha 'phangs pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:9430: dgyes pa rdo rje la sogs pa phyis gsungs pa thams cad kyang /
NK130(tho)001:9431: dang por gsungs pa'i de nyid bsdus par kha 'phangs nas yod do //
NK130(tho)001:9432: dpal gsang ba'i snying po sgrub pa mang du thos
NK130(tho)001:9433: pa'i dge slong bcom ldan ral gris bkod pa rdzogs
NK130(tho)001:9434: so // gsang snying la 'grel ba sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9435: bi ma la mi tra dang /
NK130(tho)001:9436: nyi 'od geng ge gsum gyi yod do //
NK130(tho)001:9438: zhes pan chen gyis bkod pa 'di la drung nas rwa dbon pa chen pos /
NK130(tho)001:9439: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa //
NK130(tho)001:9440: bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma'i sa //
NK130(tho)001:9441: bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa //
NK130(tho)001:9442: zhes bod kyi gsang snying smra ba dag zer te tshad mar mi rung /
NK130(tho)001:9444: ces gser thur du bkod nas /
NK130(tho)001:9445: rjes su gzhan gyis rtsod pa byung ba na lan
NK130(tho)001:9446: gzhan med pas bcom ldan pa'i lung 'di drangs pa
NK130(tho)001:9447: yang rang la zug pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9449: dper na bcom ldan ral gris gsang snying rnam dag tu bsgrubs pa bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:9450: zhes bkod pas pan chen gyi bstan bcos 'di dag nang 'gal gyi phung po chen po yin /
NK130(tho)001:9451: zhes gsungs pa'ang med pa 'dra ste /
NK130(tho)001:9453: kho bo cag la ni bka' bsdu ba bo gzhan gyis ma bsdus pas rgyud dngos yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9454: lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog gis bsdus pa
NK130(tho)001:9455: la btsan mi btsan gyi khyad par yod pa ma
NK130(tho)001:9457: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK130(tho)001:9458: zhes sogs kyi lung 'dis bstan bcos la tshad mar bsgrubs pas /
NK130(tho)001:9459: bya ba chos rje'i ngor bcom ldan pa'i lung 'dren gyis gsang snying bkar sgrub pa la /
NK130(tho)001:9460: bi shwa mi tra'i rgya 'grel byung ba 'dis /
NK130(tho)001:9461: rang gi bzhed pa la gnod bskyal snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:9462: yang de bzhin du rdzogs pa chen po kun byed rgyal po nyid kyis chos sku'i 'khor la bshad /
NK130(tho)001:9464: lo ts+aa ba bee ro tsa nas brtsams par 'chad
NK130(tho)001:9465: pa la yang chos rnam dag btsan mi btsan gyi
NK130(tho)001:9466: khyad par yod pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:9467: yang la la dag na re /
NK130(tho)001:9468: dpal 'dzin gyi lung khungs su mi byed na chos
NK130(tho)001:9469: log 'phel ba'i rnam grangs 'di dang 'adi'o zhes khungs
NK130(tho)001:9470: dag cing tshig nyung bar bsdus pa'i basngagasa pa mi
NK130(tho)001:9472: chos log 'phel zhes pa ni rtsa bar /
NK130(tho)001:9473: de rjes chos log du ma 'phel //
NK130(tho)001:9474: zhes pa'i nges 'dzin du byas 'dug pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9476: khong gi rgyud de na de yod ces pa rnams
NK130(tho)001:9477: la de na de med do zhes 'chad pa dag
NK130(tho)001:9479: zhes pa ni mi med de /
NK130(tho)001:9480: sa skya pan+di ta bzhed pa'i /
NK130(tho)001:9481: chos log de ni gsar ma la grags pa'i phag
NK130(tho)001:9482: mo'i byin rlabs kyi chos sgo 'byed pa la sogs
NK130(tho)001:9484: rnying ma la dgongs dpal 'dzin gyis rnying ma bkag pa kho na las /
NK130(tho)001:9485: sdom gsum du bshad pa'i chos log rnams ma bkag /
NK130(tho)001:9486: de la khungs dag pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK130(tho)001:9487: dpal 'dzin gyis rnying ma'i rgyud na de na de
NK130(tho)001:9488: yod do byas pa la med do zer ba ma
NK130(tho)001:9490: kun byed rgyal ba'i nyams len du //
NK130(tho)001:9491: rdo rje lus kyi byed bcing dang //
NK130(tho)001:9492: lus gnad lta stangs thams cad bkag /
NK130(tho)001:9494: kun byed chos yang dag pa yin par ni pan chen rang yang bzhed nas /
NK130(tho)001:9495: lung rig gis de'i grub min 'thad pa sgrub /
NK130(tho)001:9496: gzhan du na rnying ma'i rgyud kyi dgongs te gsungs
NK130(tho)001:9497: pa rnams la sdang smras kyis bkag pa kho na
NK130(tho)001:9498: ma gtogs rgyud kyi don go nas bkag pa ma
NK130(tho)001:9499: yin / shes byed bzang shos gsar ma dang ma mthun zer ba tsam yin /
NK130(tho)001:9500: de lta na sems tsam dang ma mthun pas dbu ma chos min zer ram /
NK130(tho)001:9501: de la sogs pa sangs rgya bar byed pa la
NK130(tho)001:9502: so so'i lam gyi dkri tshul tha dad pa yod
NK130(tho)001:9503: pa ma go bar phyogs re la zhen pa'i rmongs
NK130(tho)001:9504: gtam yin / rgyu mtshan zhib tu brtags na /
NK130(tho)001:9505: dpal 'dzin gyi rtsod pa rang gis go ba yod /
NK130(tho)001:9506: des na 'di la khungs dag pa dang rnying ma'i
NK130(tho)001:9507: chos rgyus ga la yod de bka' brgyad dang bde
NK130(tho)001:9508: gshegs 'dus pa phye ba sogs mang /
NK130(tho)001:9509: gsar ma kho rang gis shes pa la yang phyag
NK130(tho)001:9510: rgya chen po thabs su 'dod pa la sogs pa
NK130(tho)001:9511: nor sa tshabs che ba mang /
NK130(tho)001:9512: brjod bya 'grig 'grig ltar byas pa de dag ni log shes nyid du mchis /
NK130(tho)001:9514: 'o na de rnams skyon can nyid du song bar nges sam zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:9515: dag pa bsgom pa la ni gsang ba snying po'i rtsa ba 'di las phal cher thon la /
NK130(tho)001:9516: rgyu 'bras kyi rdo rje 'dzin pa dang mngon par byang chub pa lnga sogs ni /
NK130(tho)001:9518: rgyud 'di tha ma zur la babs /
NK130(tho)001:9519: bya ba yin pas zur che chung gi rtsa rgyud dang bshad rgyud du sbyar /
NK130(tho)001:9520: 'grel pa dang stong thun du sbyar bas thon par yod yong /
NK130(tho)001:9522: rgyal ba rig lnga mnan pa sogs ni /
NK130(tho)001:9523: rdzogs pa chen po'i theg pa la gnas pa'i tshe
NK130(tho)001:9524: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi dbang du byas pa yin
NK130(tho)001:9525: / zhes bshad na lugs de nyid la 'byor pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9526: lugs de la gnas pa'i tshe /
NK130(tho)001:9527: rnal 'byor gang ma gsum gyi lha'i rnal 'byor sogs
NK130(tho)001:9528: bsgom pa de shin tu rnal 'byor la ltos te
NK130(tho)001:9529: snying po'i don ma mthong ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9530: theg pa 'di sa 'og ma thams cad dril gyis gnon par chad pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9531: zhes gsungs pa 'di ni dgongs pa can gyi bka'
NK130(tho)001:9532: gzhan du bsam pa yod na ni ma nges te
NK130(tho)001:9533: / sgra ji bzhin pa ltar na mi 'thad de /
NK130(tho)001:9534: gsang ba snying po las byung ba'i zhi khro'i dkyil
NK130(tho)001:9535: 'khor 'di rnams la slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas
NK130(tho)001:9536: mdzad pa'i sgrub gzhung rgyas bsdus gsum yod pas /
NK130(tho)001:9537: lugs de la dag pa bsgom pa la sogs pa dgos na slob dpon des ci'i phyir mi mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:9538: gal te mi dgos na de nyid btsan pa las lugs gzhan nas rigs bsgre ci dgos /
NK130(tho)001:9539: dper na ma rgyud pa rtsa gtso bor byed pa
NK130(tho)001:9540: de la yang pha rgyud pa'i rlung gtso bor byed
NK130(tho)001:9542: de lta na ni pha rgyud ma rgyud kyi dbye ba phyed par dka'/
NK130(tho)001:9543: rgyal ba rigs lnga mnan pa sogs dgongs pa'i skad yin dngos bstan ma yin /
NK130(tho)001:9544: lugs de la gnas pa'i tshe rnal 'byor gong ma
NK130(tho)001:9545: gsum gyi rnal 'byor sogs bsgom pa de ni shin
NK130(tho)001:9546: tu rnal 'byor la ltos te snying pa'i don mthong
NK130(tho)001:9547: theg pa 'di sa 'og ma zil gyi gnon /
NK130(tho)001:9548: zhes pa yang 'di la mi 'byor te shin tu rnal 'byor zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po yin /
NK130(tho)001:9549: lha bsgom pa sogs kyi bskyed rim de la rdzogs chen mi zer /
NK130(tho)001:9550: gal te zer na'ang sangs rgyas mnan pa'i bskyed rim chos log yin /
NK130(tho)001:9551: dngos bstan de rung na sngon gyi sbyor sgrol sgra
NK130(tho)001:9552: ji bzhin par spyad pa dag kyang chos log tu
NK130(tho)001:9553: ci la 'gyur / shin tu rnal 'byor zhes bya
NK130(tho)001:9554: ba'i rgyud sde 'dir byung ba'i lha de dag kyang
NK130(tho)001:9556: des de la ji ltar gnon /
NK130(tho)001:9557: lha de dag kyang ye nas lhun grub tu gnas
NK130(tho)001:9558: pa yin pas sgom sgrub kyi rtsol ba mi byed
NK130(tho)001:9559: / rnam rtog las 'das pa'i theg pa yin pas
NK130(tho)001:9560: lha bsgom pa la sogs pa'i rtog sgom lugs 'di
NK130(tho)001:9562: a ti yo ga zhes pa'i sgra la shin tu
NK130(tho)001:9563: rnal 'byor du bsgyur ba'i sgra bshad rdzogs chen sems
NK130(tho)001:9564: phyogs la shin tu mang ba yod kyang don du
NK130(tho)001:9565: na / +aa di zhes gdod ma'i skad dod yin /
NK130(tho)001:9566: brda rnying pas gna' skad la a ti zhes bris pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:9567: 'gyur dngos gdod ma'i rnal 'byor zhes zer ba lags /
NK130(tho)001:9568: yang chos kyi rjes rdzogs chen gsan par bshad pas rnam dag tu 'grub bo gsung ba /
NK130(tho)001:9569: 'dir gsan tshul mang po dag bshad pa de dag
NK130(tho)001:9570: gis gang gsan pa thams cad dag par 'grub pa
NK130(tho)001:9571: ma yin no // 'o na ci zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:9572: 'dir chos dang chos ma yin pa'i rnam dbye mdzad pa la gzhan dag na re /
NK130(tho)001:9573: rtsom pa nyid kyis gang thos pa de dag la
NK130(tho)001:9574: ma thos pa de ma dag pa yin no zhes
NK130(tho)001:9575: zer ram snyam pa'i dogs pa bsal ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9576: de phyir chos rnams phal cher thos //
NK130(tho)001:9577: des na bdag la phyogs lhung med //
NK130(tho)001:9579: de lta na yang 'di'i bzhed pas /
NK130(tho)001:9583: blo sbyong rnams kyi don 'khrul par mi bzhed kyang
NK130(tho)001:9584: tha snyad ni rgya gar du grags par mi bzhed
NK130(tho)001:9585: de / deng sang bod na grags pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:9586: zhi byed rdzogs chen gcod la sogs //
NK130(tho)001:9588: chos de pa rang gi lugs la /
NK130(tho)001:9591: zhes de'i tha snyad kyang 'phags yul nas byung bar bzhed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9592: a ti yo ga dang rdzogs pa chen po don gcig bar bzhed la /
NK130(tho)001:9594: rnal 'byor bzhi'i nang gi shin tu rnal 'byor dang /
NK130(tho)001:9595: rdzogs chen gyi lta ba don gcig tu mi bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:9596: de lta na yang rdzogs chen a ti yo ga
NK130(tho)001:9597: zhes pa de phyogs snga ma ba rang la grags
NK130(tho)001:9598: che ba'i dbang du mdzad do //
NK130(tho)001:9599: zhes gsungs pa yang sa pan gyi bzhed pa cung ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9600: a ti yo ga'i lta ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:9601: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK130(tho)001:9602: zhes pa 'dis shin tu rnal 'byor dang don gcig tu bzhed /
NK130(tho)001:9603: rdzogs pa chen po'i tha snyad rgya gar na med pa yang ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9604: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyis /
NK130(tho)001:9605: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes kyi gzugs can zhes pa tha snyad mdzad /
NK130(tho)001:9606: zhi byed ni rje dam pas rgya gar nas bsnams byon pa'i chos lags /
NK130(tho)001:9607: gcod yul kyang zhi byed kyi cha lag yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9608: dam pa dang skye bsod nams bla ma nas brgyud pa la pho gcod zer /
NK130(tho)001:9609: ma gcig nas brgyud pa la mo gcod zer te /
NK130(tho)001:9610: de yang dam pa nas brgyud dgos te /
NK130(tho)001:9612: yar lung rog pa rtsar ma jo mchod nas ma
NK130(tho)001:9613: la snying gtan tshig gsum btab pas mo des grol
NK130(tho)001:9615: blo sbyong ni thogs med sku mched /
NK130(tho)001:9619: jo bo rje la sogs pa'i chos yin /
NK130(tho)001:9620: de dag rgya gar na med do zhes sa pan bzhed pa ma lags so //
NK130(tho)001:9621: yang de lta mod kyi kun byed rgyal po nas
NK130(tho)001:9622: gsungs pa'i lta ba de lta ba'i ldog pa nas
NK130(tho)001:9624: chos de'i brgyud 'dzin rnams kyi spyod pa'i phyogs dang mi sbyor zhing /
NK130(tho)001:9625: spyod pa yal bar dor bas chog pa grub mtha'
NK130(tho)001:9626: dang lags len du byed na rgyu nag mkhan po'i
NK130(tho)001:9628: zhes pa ni bstan bcos 'di'i bzhed pa nyid du nges la /
NK130(tho)001:9629: rdzogs chen gyi chos lugs de ltar 'chad na dpal 'dzin gyis /
NK130(tho)001:9630: khyad par ha shang grub mtha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:9631: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba bsres //
NK130(tho)001:9633: rgyal po g.yu sgra snying po yi //
NK130(tho)001:9634: thugs dam man ngag lta phreng yang //
NK130(tho)001:9635: phyis nas de yi brgyud 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:9636: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos su bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:9637: zhes pa'i nyes pa de dag mi 'jug pa'i nges pa med de /
NK130(tho)001:9639: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:9640: zhes pa'ang don de la bsam pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9642: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen de h+aa shang gi
NK130(tho)001:9643: chos de yin pa 'grel pa po kun gyis rtsad
NK130(tho)001:9644: ma chod pas bden mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:9645: dpal 'dzin gyis man ngag lta phreng la hwa shang gi grub mtha' de rang bsres zer ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:9646: kun byed la man ngag lta phreng mi zer /
NK130(tho)001:9647: kun byed kyi lta ba de lta ba'i ldog pa nas yang dag pa yin na /
NK130(tho)001:9648: lta spyod ya bral du ston pa sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha' ma yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:9649: rtsol sgrub dang bral bar nyams su len pa lags so //
NK130(tho)001:9651: gal te 'o na kun byed rgyal po'i lugs kyi lta ba ma 'khrul ba'i rgyu mtshan ci /
NK130(tho)001:9652: lta ba de'i grogs su bsod nams kyi tshogs dgos
NK130(tho)001:9653: pa kun byed kyi lugs yin na rgyud de rang
NK130(tho)001:9655: de de'i lugs ma yin na rgya nag mkhan po'i chos lugs dang /
NK130(tho)001:9656: lta ba yas babs dang lam gcig car ba zhes
NK130(tho)001:9657: bya ba de'i lugs su song ba ma yin nam
NK130(tho)001:9659: lta ba ma 'khrul bar bstan pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9660: kun rdzob kyi chos med par bshad pas rgyu 'bras la skur pa btab par mi 'grub bo //
NK130(tho)001:9662: kun rdzob gzung 'dzin gyi chos gnyis med cing /
NK130(tho)001:9663: gnyis med kyi ye shes de nyid rang bzhin chos sku dang /
NK130(tho)001:9666: dgyes pa rdo rje la sogs su khas len pa
NK130(tho)001:9667: ni bka' 'khor lo tha ma'i nges don mthar thug
NK130(tho)001:9668: pa dang / gsang sngags phyis 'gyur ba rnams kyis kyang nges don mthar thug dang /
NK130(tho)001:9669: lta ba'i yul dang don dam pa'i bden pa zhig
NK130(tho)001:9670: khas len pa'i tshe de las gzhan yod pa ma
NK130(tho)001:9671: yin te / 'phags pa rnams kyi so so rang
NK130(tho)001:9672: rig pa'i ye shes kyis nyams su myong bya ni
NK130(tho)001:9673: de las gzhan khas mi len pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9674: de nyid la rdzogs pa chen po'i chos su kun byed rgyal po zhes grags so //
NK130(tho)001:9677: 'chad pa po nga chos kyang nga //
NK130(tho)001:9678: rang gi tshogs ldan nyan pa nga //
NK130(tho)001:9680: 'jig rten ston pa bsgrub bya nga //
NK130(tho)001:9682: dngos dang dngos po med pa nga //
NK130(tho)001:9683: nga las 'gro ba thams cad byung //
NK130(tho)001:9684: nga las gnas gsum po yang byung //
NK130(tho)001:9685: nga yis 'di kun khyab pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:9686: 'gro ba'i rang bzhin gzhan ma mthong //
NK130(tho)001:9688: rin chen sems las phyir gyur ba //
NK130(tho)001:9689: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK130(tho)001:9690: ces sogs rgya cher gsungs pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:9691: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi bzhugs tshul gcig tu snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:9693: 'o na chos 'di'i lugs la bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK130(tho)001:9694: gsog pa dang sa lam gyi rim pa la yod
NK130(tho)001:9695: par 'chad na / sems can la sangs rgyas lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9696: kun rdzob dang don dam zhes bya ba gnyis med par bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK130(tho)001:9697: yo ga shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs chen la //
NK130(tho)001:9698: rgyu dang 'bras bu yod ces smra byed pa //
NK130(tho)001:9699: de ni rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i don mi ldan //
NK130(tho)001:9700: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su smra byed na //
NK130(tho)001:9701: sgro dang skur pa 'debs pa'i tshig yin te //
NK130(tho)001:9702: de yis gnyis su med pa rtogs pa med //
NK130(tho)001:9703: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyi rtogs pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:9704: gnyis su ma mthong rnam bzhag gcig tu rtogs //
NK130(tho)001:9705: zhes gsal bar gsungs pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:9706: lug der kun rdzob kyi chos rnams med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:9707: kun byed gcig nyid yod par bshad med /
NK130(tho)001:9708: de tsam gyis bsod nams kyi tshogs mi dgos par grub na /
NK130(tho)001:9709: phar phyin theg pa ba dag /
NK130(tho)001:9710: mya ngan 'das pa bden gcig pu //
NK130(tho)001:9711: zhes zer ba dang kye rdo rje las /
NK130(tho)001:9712: bsgom med sgom pa po yang med //
NK130(tho)001:9713: lha med sngags kyang yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:9714: ces pas kyang de ltar du bstan par 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:9715: lugs de bdag gi bsam pa la //
NK130(tho)001:9716: de yang bstan no zhe na ma yin te //
NK130(tho)001:9717: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK130(tho)001:9718: lha dang sngags ni yang dag gnas //
NK130(tho)001:9721: 'khrul ngor yod pas yod pa'i go mi chod cing /
NK130(tho)001:9722: don dam du med pas med pa'i go chod pa'i
NK130(tho)001:9723: rgyu mtshan gyis na don dam las ma gtogs pa'i
NK130(tho)001:9725: de lta na yang bsod nams kyi tshogs yal bar 'dor du rung ba ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:9726: kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i ngor bsod nams kyi tshogs rgya
NK130(tho)001:9727: chen po bsags pa med du mi rung ba'i phyir
NK130(tho)001:9728: / 'khrul ngo yin na de ltar bsags pa la dgos pa med do zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:9730: de med na 'khrul ngo'i ston pa longs sprul gnyis mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9731: ma 'khrul pa'i ston pa chos sku gcig pus chog
NK130(tho)001:9732: mod 'khrul ngo'i ston pas ci zhig bya zhe na
NK130(tho)001:9733: / ji srid ma rig pa'i gnyid ma sad pa
NK130(tho)001:9734: de srid du chos sku'i ston pa gcig pus chog
NK130(tho)001:9736: ma rig pa'i gnyid sad nas gzugs sku'i ston pa sna tshogs pa mig shes la snang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9737: des chos gsung ba'i sgra nyan shes la grags pa sogs mi 'byung yang /
NK130(tho)001:9738: ji srid ma rig pa'i gnyid ma sad pa de
NK130(tho)001:9739: srid du ston pa chos kyi sku mngon sum du
NK130(tho)001:9741: sems can rang snang gis bsdus pa'i gzugs sku gnyis kyi snang ba 'char dgos la /
NK130(tho)001:9742: de 'char ba la sangs rgyas rnams kyi sngon gyi smon lam dang /
NK130(tho)001:9743: gdul bya rang rang gis bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa la /
NK130(tho)001:9746: don gyi snying po rnal ma byar med la //
NK130(tho)001:9747: rnal 'byor chen po rnams kyis mthong ba ni //
NK130(tho)001:9748: ye nas rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK130(tho)001:9749: rgyu las 'bras bu'i lha yi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK130(tho)001:9750: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi yis rdzogs byas nas //
NK130(tho)001:9751: 'phro 'du'i bdag nyid lhun gyis grub par blta //
NK130(tho)001:9752: zhes de ltar gsungs pa 'di dang /
NK130(tho)001:9754: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK130(tho)001:9755: lha dang sngags ni yang dag gnas //
NK130(tho)001:9756: zhes gsungs pa de don mthun par grub pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9758: de ltar de tsam du bris pa 'dis ni pan chen rin po che 'di'i bzhed pas /
NK130(tho)001:9759: rnying ma'i rgyud rnams bod kyi bstan bcos su mdzad
NK130(tho)001:9760: kyang de dag gi don ma 'khrul pa yin pa'i
NK130(tho)001:9761: shes byed du mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob
NK130(tho)001:9762: pa mang du byung zhes gsungs pas /
NK130(tho)001:9763: de lta na sangs rgyas kyi bka' rnams kyis kyang
NK130(tho)001:9764: de las ches lhag pa zhig bstan pa med pas
NK130(tho)001:9765: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyis bstan pa rnam dag
NK130(tho)001:9766: tu go bar 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:9767: 'gos dang dpal 'dzin la sogs pas byas pa dag gi rtsod spong du gyur 'dug pas bris pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9768: pan chen gyis gong du bshad pa'i rnam bzhag de
NK130(tho)001:9769: dag la bya ba chos rjes dpyad pa ni 'di
NK130(tho)001:9770: ltar snang ste / 'dir ni rdzogs chen sems phyogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:9771: sems las ma gtogs chos med kyang //
NK130(tho)001:9772: snang ba sems su mi bzhed de //
NK130(tho)001:9773: sems dang sems byung gcig pa min //
NK130(tho)001:9774: kun rdzob med bzhin snang ba'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:9775: don la ma grub 'khrul snang yin //
NK130(tho)001:9776: gdod nas dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK130(tho)001:9778: dper na d+ha d+hu ra zos pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9779: snang ba 'khrul snang yin mod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:9780: de nyid d+ha d+hu ra ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:9781: de bzhin sems kyi snang ba yang //
NK130(tho)001:9782: sems min nyi ma'i 'od zer yang //
NK130(tho)001:9783: nyi ma dngos nyid min dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:9784: gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis po de //
NK130(tho)001:9785: sangs rgyas nyid du mi bzhed na //
NK130(tho)001:9786: longs sku rgyal ba rigs drug dang //
NK130(tho)001:9787: sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa des //
NK130(tho)001:9788: da dung sangs rgyas ma thob pa //
NK130(tho)001:9789: mdo rgyud gang nas bshad pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:9790: thams cad sems su 'dod bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:9791: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs dang sku //
NK130(tho)001:9792: phye nas thugs ni sangs rgyas dang //
NK130(tho)001:9793: sku ni sangs rgyas min pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:9795: yid la mi byed mnyam bzhag la //
NK130(tho)001:9796: gnyis 'dzin bkag pa'i bsam gtan dang //
NK130(tho)001:9797: rang grol rgya yan sor bzhag gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:9798: 'dra gnyis nor sa srid pa'i sa //
NK130(tho)001:9799: phyi ma yin na nged dang mthun //
NK130(tho)001:9800: gong ma de ni h+aa shang lugs //
NK130(tho)001:9801: yid dpyod rang sa 'khrul snang yin //
NK130(tho)001:9802: 'khrul snang rtog pa de spangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:9803: byung ba'i ye shes nged mi 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:9806: 'khor ba spangs nas gzhan du ni //
NK130(tho)001:9807: mya ngan 'das pa yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:9808: ces gsungs rje btsun sa skya pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9810: dngos su 'gal bar ma mdzad cing //
NK130(tho)001:9811: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK130(tho)001:9812: log pa'i kun rdzob mi snang yang //
NK130(tho)001:9813: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:9814: chos kun gsal la ma 'dres pa //
NK130(tho)001:9815: rnam rtog mi mnga' sa ler mkhyen //
NK130(tho)001:9816: 'di ni sems phyogs grub mtha' yin //
NK130(tho)001:9817: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen gzigs pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9818: mkhyen gnyis med ces ma bzhed cig /
NK130(tho)001:9820: bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa //
NK130(tho)001:9821: gsang snying smra ba'i lugs yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:9822: tshad mar mi rung zhes pa'i gsung //
NK130(tho)001:9823: 'di dang bod du sbyar ba'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:9825: chos su grub na chos de nyid //
NK130(tho)001:9826: tshad ma nyid du mi rung na //
NK130(tho)001:9827: de las gzhan du chos spong ci //
NK130(tho)001:9829: mkhas pas ngos bzung rgya dpe la //
NK130(tho)001:9830: rgya gar pan chen 'grel pa yod //
NK130(tho)001:9831: snga phyi bar gsum bsgyur ba'i rgyud //
NK130(tho)001:9833: des na khyod las rgya dpe'i nyams //
NK130(tho)001:9834: che ba'i kha che pan chen dang //
NK130(tho)001:9835: mkhas mchog thar pa lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:9836: bcom ldan rig pa'i ral gri sogs //
NK130(tho)001:9837: mkhas pas tshad mar bzung 'dis chog /
NK130(tho)001:9838: rang gi lung rig ltar snang gis //
NK130(tho)001:9839: rgyud lung 'gog par ma nus pas //
NK130(tho)001:9840: tshig skyob bod ma yin na yang //
NK130(tho)001:9841: chos ma yin ces mi 'gog lo //
NK130(tho)001:9842: bod ma'i chos lugs mi 'gog na //
NK130(tho)001:9843: chos de tshad mar 'dzin par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:9844: gsang snying smra ba rnams kyi lugs //
NK130(tho)001:9845: mi rung ba yi dril bsgrags nas //
NK130(tho)001:9846: slar yang mkhas pas rtsod pa na //
NK130(tho)001:9847: gzhan sems srung pa'i mi chos 'di //
NK130(tho)001:9848: mkhas kyang blun po mgu ba tsam //
NK130(tho)001:9849: rgyus yod rnams kyis khrel ba'i gnas //
NK130(tho)001:9851: rgyud kyi dngos bstan la med cing //
NK130(tho)001:9852: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la //
NK130(tho)001:9853: 'grel mdzad rgya gar mkhas pas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:9854: rgyud sde'i rang rkang nyid bkral gyi //
NK130(tho)001:9855: bod rgan rnams kyi lugs bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:9856: rang bzo'i rig pas 'dir ma bsgres //
NK130(tho)001:9857: de dag tshad ma'i skyes bu yin //
NK130(tho)001:9858: rgyal ba rigs lnga mnan pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:9859: rdzogs pa che la 'byor ro lo //
NK130(tho)001:9860: rnam par rtog pa'i sgom pa las //
NK130(tho)001:9863: theg dman zil gyis gnan pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:9864: rang gzhung kho nas 'grub pa la //
NK130(tho)001:9865: don med sangs rgyas gnon mi dgos //
NK130(tho)001:9866: zhi rdzogs gcod dang blo sbyong gi //
NK130(tho)001:9867: tha snyad rgya gar na med lo //
NK130(tho)001:9868: dam pa sangs rgyas jo bo rje //
NK130(tho)001:9870: de kun rgya gar pan chen yin //
NK130(tho)001:9871: chos kyang de dag so so'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:9872: yin phyir rgya gar na med ces //
NK130(tho)001:9874: de phyir sa pan 'di mi bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:9875: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:9876: shin tu rnal 'byor mi gcig par //
NK130(tho)001:9877: sa pan bzhed ces mu cor smra //
NK130(tho)001:9878: de lta na ni bstan bcos der //
NK130(tho)001:9879: theg pa dang ni ye shes gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:9880: dbye ba'i skabs der 'chad par rigs //
NK130(tho)001:9881: rnying ma chos su sgrub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:9882: dpal 'dzin gzhung la khungs bcol ba //
NK130(tho)001:9883: gzhan dang 'gal ba lta ci smos //
NK130(tho)001:9884: rang lugs dang yang 'gal ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:9886: khyed kyi bstan bcos gser thur 'dis //
NK130(tho)001:9887: sdom gsum rab dbye rtsad nas bcom //
NK130(tho)001:9888: sa pan grub mtha' phye mar byas //
NK130(tho)001:9889: mgon des phyogs sngar gang bzhag pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:9890: bod kyi chos log smra rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:9891: rgyan dang byed po mchog tu gyur //
NK130(tho)001:9892: kun mkhyen bsod nams seng ge dang //
NK130(tho)001:9893: ra dbon smra ba'i seng ge sogs //
NK130(tho)001:9894: sa skya pa yi bstan 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:9895: bkag kyang khegs par ma nus pa //
NK130(tho)001:9896: snyigs ma'i dus kyi chos nyid yin //
NK130(tho)001:9897: bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:9898: zhes pa'i skabs 'di nas rnying ma la rtsod lan mang po 'dug ste /
NK130(tho)001:9899: phal cher pan chen rin po che de nyid la 'dzugs pa'i gnas su gyur pas ma bris so //
NK130(tho)001:9900: rgyal ba mchog des mchog tu lung bstan pa //
NK130(tho)001:9901: lha rgyal 'gro ba'i bla ma ye shes 'od //
NK130(tho)001:9902: thub dbang bstan srog lo chen rin chen bzang //
NK130(tho)001:9903: gang de'i drin gyis 'tsho ba'i mkhas rnams dang //
NK130(tho)001:9904: mkhas grub phul du byung ba'i 'gos lo ts+aa //
NK130(tho)001:9905: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos sa skya pan+di ta //
NK130(tho)001:9906: sangs rgyas gnyis pa pan chen bu ston rje //
NK130(tho)001:9907: lnga rig pan chen mkhas pa sh+aakya mchog /
NK130(tho)001:9908: rgyal ba mi bskyod rdo rje karma pa //
NK130(tho)001:9909: thar ba'i lam mkhan bla ma de rnams kyis //
NK130(tho)001:9910: chos tshul zab mo gsang sngags snga 'gyur 'dir //
NK130(tho)001:9911: dpyad cing rnam par dpyad pa mang mdzad mod //
NK130(tho)001:9912: ded dpon mkhas rnams nor bu rin po che'i //
NK130(tho)001:9913: dri ma sbyong gi rdo ba la min ltar //
NK130(tho)001:9914: chos mchog 'di la byi dor byas pa gang //
NK130(tho)001:9915: bka' drin bla med mkhas pa'i phyag rjes yin //
NK130(tho)001:9916: de phyir rnam pa kun tu phyag byar 'os //
NK130(tho)001:9917: thog med dus nas dge ba'i 'bras chung bas //
NK130(tho)001:9918: thos bsam sgom gsum bdud kyis thabs la bslus //
NK130(tho)001:9919: log shes gsal bas chos mchog sun 'byin pa //
NK130(tho)001:9920: ltar snang mkhas pa rnams dang 'di mi mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:9921: ji bzhin gzigs pa'i mkhas rnams zhing gzhan gshegs //
NK130(tho)001:9922: bstan pa spyi yi bshes gnyen chos dkon pas //
NK130(tho)001:9923: ngan rtog phreng bas thub bstan dkrug bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:9924: bstan 'dzin chen por rlams pa'ang bdag yid skyo //
NK130(tho)001:9925: shes bya phyogs re'i mtha' rgya ma chod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:9926: dpe bsogs gzhan nas brkus pa'i grub mtha' dang //
NK130(tho)001:9927: rang blo phyogs re bsres pa'i bstan bcos kyi //
NK130(tho)001:9928: gsang sngags bstan pa smod pa lhag par skyo //
NK130(tho)001:9929: rang bzhin rmong sems shes rab rtsal chung zhing //
NK130(tho)001:9930: thos pa chung bas bsam pa'i yul dang bral //
NK130(tho)001:9931: mi mkhas blun po bdag 'dra'i rtsom pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:9932: skyo ba'i gnas las gzhan du ma gyur mod //
NK130(tho)001:9933: 'on kyang dus mthar dam chos bshad pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:9934: bzung dang bsrung ba'i phan yon mtha' las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:9935: de phyir rang gzhan dge ba spel slad du //
NK130(tho)001:9936: bris 'di nongs gang mkhas pa ye shes grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:9937: chos la sdang ba nges bsal ba //
NK130(tho)001:9938: bsod nams 'bras bu gting dpag med //
NK130(tho)001:9941: deng sang skal bar ldan pa ches dkon la //
NK130(tho)001:9942: yod kyang yid ches gnas su 'dzin dka' yang //
NK130(tho)001:9943: rang yid chos la goms pa bskyed phyir dang //
NK130(tho)001:9944: mi dbang bka' yis bskul phyir 'di bkod do //
NK130(tho)001:9945: bsod nams 'di yis skye ba kun tu bdag /
NK130(tho)001:9946: ris med dam chos rgya mtsho'i mdzod 'dzin cing //
NK130(tho)001:9947: rlabs chen rgyal sras spyod pas 'gro ba kun //
NK130(tho)001:9948: kun bzang rgyal ba'i sa la 'god par shog /
NK130(tho)001:9949: dam pa'i chos gsang sngags snga 'gyur la rtsod pa
NK130(tho)001:9950: spong ba legs bshad nges pa don gyi 'brug sgra
NK130(tho)001:9951: zhes bya ba / rgyal ba'i bstan pa ris med
NK130(tho)001:9952: pa la mi phyed pa'i dad pa mchog tu gyur
NK130(tho)001:9953: zhes bya ba / cing / shes bya'i gnas mtha'
NK130(tho)001:9954: dag la rnam par dpyod pa'i mkhyen rab kyi spyan
NK130(tho)001:9955: zhes bya ba / cing / mnga' ba / khyad
NK130(tho)001:9956: par gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i tshul la spobs
NK130(tho)001:9958: sa chen po chos kyis skyong ba'i khri dpon nor bu pad+ma rgyal po'i bka' bskul ba las /
NK130(tho)001:9959: snyoms las can sog bzlog pas khro mo zhes pa
NK130(tho)001:9960: shing pho 'brug gi lo gro zhun zla ba'i tshes
NK130(tho)001:9961: gcig yan chad la rdzogs par sbyar ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:9962: lo 'di yan la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa lo sum stong bdun brgya so lnga 'das /
NK130(tho)001:9963: lhag ma bdun brgya re lnga yod /
NK130(tho)001:9964: de steng rtags tsam 'dzin pa lnga brgya dang bcas pa gnas pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:9966: gdod nas dag pa'i rig pa 'od po che //
NK130(tho)001:9967: ye shes snang ba rgyas pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK130(tho)001:9968: nam yang 'khrul ma myong ba'i kun tu bzang //
NK130(tho)001:9969: khyab bdag 'khor lo'i mgon des 'gro 'di srungs //
NK130(tho)001:9970: 'di ltar bdag cag gis gong du bshad pa'i rtsod lan gyi rim pa de dag la /
NK130(tho)001:9973: mdo rgyud kyi lung sbyor yang drang nges sna tshogs pa yod kyang /
NK130(tho)001:9974: rnying ma ba dag gis ji ltar yin pa'i tshul la tshur dri ba lta zhog /
NK130(tho)001:9975: gsar ma ba mdo sngags la sbyangs pa dag gis
NK130(tho)001:9976: kyang cang mi smra ba ni skyo ba'i dbang du
NK130(tho)001:9977: gyur / yang bdag lta bu la mkhas pa dag
NK130(tho)001:9978: gis chos kyi gtam 'dri zhing gleng ba'i yul du
NK130(tho)001:9979: ma gyur pa ni bden mod /
NK130(tho)001:9980: de lta na'ang drang nges kyi rnam dbye phyed par bya ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9981: rang nyid kyi the tshom bsal bar bya ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:9982: bstan bcos 'di'i kha bskang ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:9983: slar yang rang gis mthong zhing go ba'i mdo rgyud dag dang /
NK130(tho)001:9984: khyad par dge ba'i bshes gnyen snar thang pa rgyang
NK130(tho)001:9985: ro byang chub 'bum zhes pa de'i gsung rgyun shog
NK130(tho)001:9986: 'khyar 'ga' rnyed pa las bsnyad de brjod par bya'o
NK130(tho)001:9988: chos zab khyad du gsod pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:9990: zhes pa de la gong du lan rnal ma med
NK130(tho)001:9991: pas 'di la ni lan rnal ma 'di yin te
NK130(tho)001:9992: / rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis /
NK130(tho)001:9993: a nu man chad gol sgrib kyi theg pa yin pas /
NK130(tho)001:9994: 'dir rang gi lta ba mchog tu rtogs pa'i slad
NK130(tho)001:9995: du de dag gi tshul ngos bzung ba tsam yin
NK130(tho)001:9996: la / nam yang khyad du gsod par mi 'dod /
NK130(tho)001:9997: rdzogs pa chen po'i byin rlabs las shar ba'i rtsal
NK130(tho)001:9998: bstan pa'i sgo sna tshogs pa yin te rol pa'am
NK130(tho)001:10000: de yang a ti'i lugs kyis rgyu'i theg pa yang sngags su 'dus /
NK130(tho)001:10001: sngags kyang yo ga rnam pa bzhir 'dus /
NK130(tho)001:10002: yo ga 'og ma gsum yang a ti yo gar 'dus /
NK130(tho)001:10003: a ti ni thig le nyag gcig bya rtsol dang bral ba'i ngang du ye na gnas pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:10005: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab cing //
NK130(tho)001:10006: rgya mtsho'i ngang du ro gcig gnas pa ltar //
NK130(tho)001:10007: chos rnams rdzogs pa chen por 'dus gsal zhing //
NK130(tho)001:10008: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK130(tho)001:10010: theg pa de kun yang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang /
NK130(tho)001:10011: gdul bya'i las 'phro 'dzom pa na dgos ched gnyis kyi dbang gis 'byung ste /
NK130(tho)001:10012: dgos pa gang la dgos na /
NK130(tho)001:10013: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa lam lnga dang sa bcu'i sgo nas nyon mongs pa spong ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10014: sbyong ba'i rtsol bar byas nas dus bskal pa grangs
NK130(tho)001:10015: med pa gsum la sogs pa nas sangs rgyas thob
NK130(tho)001:10018: a ti'i grub mtha' sa lam la sbyang bsgrod med pa mi go ba rnams kyi ched du byung /
NK130(tho)001:10020: gsang sngags phyi nang gi sgor zhugs pa rnams la dgos /
NK130(tho)001:10021: ched ni bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i dngos grub sgrub tu med
NK130(tho)001:10022: pa ste ye grol chen po'i don rtogs pa'i ched
NK130(tho)001:10023: du byung / de yang sa dang lam la spong zhing sbyong ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:10024: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi rtsol zhing sgrub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10025: phyi nang sgo phugs byed pa tshi chad pas //
NK130(tho)001:10026: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK130(tho)001:10028: de la a nu man chad kyi gol sgrib ni /
NK130(tho)001:10029: sems kyi rtsal cir yang shar bas te /
NK130(tho)001:10030: sems skye ba med pa las rtsal 'gags med du
NK130(tho)001:10031: shar bas rang snang stong pa yin par ma shes
NK130(tho)001:10032: pas / da lta'i snang ba 'di thams cad sems can spyi mthun gyi las las grub /
NK130(tho)001:10033: bde sdug thams cad sngon gyi las las byung bar
NK130(tho)001:10034: lta bas 'jig rten lha ma'i theg par gol lo
NK130(tho)001:10035: // 'o na rdzogs chen pas lta ba de spong ngam zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:10037: sems can gyi rtsal ma 'gags pa so so skye
NK130(tho)001:10038: bo lha mi'i theg pa ltar shar yang de ltar
NK130(tho)001:10039: ma grub ste / de la snang ba dang las
NK130(tho)001:10040: rang rgyud pa med de gnyis med rang grol ba'i
NK130(tho)001:10041: ma grub ste / / de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK130(tho)001:10042: ci ste las kyis dbang bsgyur na //
NK130(tho)001:10043: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:10044: ces pas las kyi ngo bo med par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10045: de bzhin du sems stong pa de'i rtsal ma 'gags pas mu stegs rtag chad ltar shar /
NK130(tho)001:10046: nyan thos pa'i bdag med phyed dang gnyis /
NK130(tho)001:10047: rang rgyal gyi bdag med gnyis /
NK130(tho)001:10048: sems tsam pa'i thams cad sems su blta ba /
NK130(tho)001:10050: kri ya pa kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK130(tho)001:10051: don dam pa dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba /
NK130(tho)001:10053: yo ga pa'i don dam mtha' bral /
NK130(tho)001:10054: kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK130(tho)001:10055: ma h+aa yo ga'i bden gnyis dbyer med /
NK130(tho)001:10056: a nu'i dbyings dang ye shes te /
NK130(tho)001:10057: sems kyi rtsal ma 'gags pas theg pa de dag gi lta ba ltar shar ba yin kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10058: lta ba de dang de dag tu blta ba'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK130(tho)001:10059: mtha' bral thig le nyag gcig de'i ngang las ma
NK130(tho)001:10060: g.yos bzhin du rtsal 'gags pa med pa rang byung
NK130(tho)001:10061: gi ye shes de theg pa 'og ma de rnams
NK130(tho)001:10062: kyi lta spyod ltar shar ba yin pas mi 'gog
NK130(tho)001:10064: mi sgrub pa'i don yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10065: de yang rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs na /
NK130(tho)001:10066: theg pa la mtho dman med pas mnyam pa nyid du rang grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:10067: yang kha cig /'di ltar rdzogs chen sems phyogs dang phyag rgya chen po la sogs pa bsgom pas /
NK130(tho)001:10068: rang don du chos sku thob kyang gzhan don gyi gzugs sku gnyis mi 'byung ste /
NK130(tho)001:10069: de gnyis kyi rgyu'i gtso bo bskyed rim ma bsgom pas so //
NK130(tho)001:10071: de ltar na phar phyin theg pa las byung ba'i sangs rgyas mi srid par thal ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10072: chos sku'i rtsal las gzugs sku 'byung ba de yang ma go ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:10073: 'di ni mu stegs pa kha cig /
NK130(tho)001:10074: goms pa las gyur pa'i thams cad mkhyen pa med do zhes 'dod pa dang 'dra bas /
NK130(tho)001:10075: de ltar ma yin te mdo las //
NK130(tho)001:10076: de ltar goms pa snga ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:10077: snga ma sems chos brtse ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:10078: chags bral blo sogs gzhan dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:10079: gsal ba de ni rtsa ba yin //
NK130(tho)001:10081: skad cig snga ma snga ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:10082: skad cig re re sngon ma de'i //
NK130(tho)001:10083: rgyu yin phyir na de yi rgyu //
NK130(tho)001:10084: thams cad tshe na'ang mthong ba nyid //
NK130(tho)001:10087: blo yi mthu stobs gsal ba med pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10088: dbang po rnams kyang blun pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK130(tho)001:10089: btsas ma thag tu sus kyang ma bstan par //
NK130(tho)001:10090: kha zas za bar rtsom par byed pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10091: nu zho 'thung bar rtsom par byed pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:10092: de dag tshe rabs gzhan la goms pa'i mthu //
NK130(tho)001:10093: zhes goms pa'i stobs kyis dud 'gros kyang de ltar byed na /
NK130(tho)001:10094: lam goms pa'i rnal 'byor pa de ci'i phyir thams cad mkhyen par mi 'gyur /
NK130(tho)001:10095: de bas na goms pa las gyur pa'i thams cad mkhyen pa yod pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:10097: rnam pa du mar thabs mang po //
NK130(tho)001:10098: yun ring dus su goms pa las //
NK130(tho)001:10099: de la skyon dang yon tan dag /
NK130(tho)001:10100: rab tu gsal ba nyid du 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:10101: des na thugs kyang gsal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10102: rgyu yi bag chags spangs pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:10103: thub chen gzhan don 'jug can gyi //
NK130(tho)001:10104: bse ru la sogs khyad 'di yin //
NK130(tho)001:10105: de don phyir na thabs goms pa //
NK130(tho)001:10106: de nyid ston pa yin pa bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:10108: yang rnying ma ba snga mas /
NK130(tho)001:10110: myang grol sogs pa ma mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10112: 'di yang don la mi gnas te /
NK130(tho)001:10113: btags grol myong grol lta bu grol nges pa des grol bar 'gyur ba de mkhyen pa yin mod /
NK130(tho)001:10114: thams cad mkhyen pa yin pas thams cad kyis grol bar 'gyur ro zhes ga la ston /
NK130(tho)001:10116: 'o na mi gtsang zos pa'i rgyus /
NK130(tho)001:10117: grol ba zhig kyang mkhyen dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:10118: zhes rgol ba de 'jug par snang la /
NK130(tho)001:10119: mu stegs gcer bu pa dag gis kyang sangs rgyas
NK130(tho)001:10120: la thams cad mkhyen pa yin na nged kyi gzhung
NK130(tho)001:10122: sangs rgyas kyis nged kyi gzhung sun ma phyungs pas thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10124: slob dpon legs ldan 'byed kyis dbu ma snying po las /
NK130(tho)001:10125: gcer bur rgyu bas thub pa la /
NK130(tho)001:10126: kun ma bstan pas kun mkhyen min //
NK130(tho)001:10127: zhes smra khyu mchog sogs ma nges //
NK130(tho)001:10128: brjod du med par brjod pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10130: de dag gi ston pa khyu mchog dang /
NK130(tho)001:10132: snod kyi rje la sogs pas ma nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:10133: 'dir chos kyi sgo zab mo rdzogs chen lta bu dang /
NK130(tho)001:10134: thabs zab mo btags grol dang myong grol lta bu
NK130(tho)001:10135: yang gdul bya snod dang mi ldan pa la mi
NK130(tho)001:10136: ston pa la sogs pa rgyu mtshan du ma yod
NK130(tho)001:10137: do // slob dpon ma ti tsi tras brtsod pa mi mnga' bar bstod pa las /
NK130(tho)001:10138: mkha' la lcags kyis 'ju ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:10139: brtsad pas khyod la bardzi mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:10140: rlung gi bzlog phyogs gtor ba'i rdul //
NK130(tho)001:10144: 'jig rten mtha' dang ldan nam zhes //
NK130(tho)001:10145: zhus na rgyal ba mi gsung bzhugs //
NK130(tho)001:10146: gang phyir de ltar zab mo'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:10147: snod min 'gro la mi gsung ba //
NK130(tho)001:10148: de nyid phyir na mkhas rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:10149: kun mkhyen thams cad mkhyen par bzhed //
NK130(tho)001:10151: de ltar btags grol dang myong grol dang chos zab
NK130(tho)001:10152: mo rnams ni snod dang mi ldan pa la bcom
NK130(tho)001:10155: de ma mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen par mi 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:10156: zhes mu stegs gcer bu pa ltar ma smra zhig /
NK130(tho)001:10157: yang sngags gsar ma ba kha cig dang /
NK130(tho)001:10158: rgya ba g.yung la sogs pa rnying ma ba 'ga' zhig gis /
NK130(tho)001:10159: phar phyin theg pa'i sangs rgyas dman pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10160: sngags kyi sangs rgyas mchog tu 'dzin no //
NK130(tho)001:10161: 'di yang sangs rgyas la bzang ngan du 'dzin pa ni don la mi gnas te /
NK130(tho)001:10162: gsang sngags phyin ci ma log par ston pa'i slob dpon a b+ha y+aa ka ras /
NK130(tho)001:10163: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la ma
NK130(tho)001:10164: ltos par bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK130(tho)001:10165: pa'i byang chub kyi dri yang med do //
NK130(tho)001:10166: zhes man ngag snye mar gsungs la /
NK130(tho)001:10167: gsang sngags kyi lta ba'i mthar thug pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:10168: sangs rgya ba'i rgyu'i gtso bo yang de yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:10169: de bas na sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK130(tho)001:10170: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs zin pa
NK130(tho)001:10171: yin pa la / da dung 'pho ba'i chags pa ma spangs /
NK130(tho)001:10172: zhes sogs kyi 'chal gtam gyi rjes su mi rgyug go //
NK130(tho)001:10173: yang dpal 'dzin gyis rnying ma la /
NK130(tho)001:10174: mdo sde la mi 'jug /'dul ba la mi snang /
NK130(tho)001:10176: las 'bras la sogs med par ston pa ni chad
NK130(tho)001:10177: lta dang mtshungs pas lam gzhan nye bar ston pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10178: phyir blun po dag gis byas so zer ba'i /
NK130(tho)001:10180: de dag ni sngon nyan thos pas theg chen 'gog pa dang 'dra ste /
NK130(tho)001:10182: sde snod gsum du ma bsdus dang /
NK130(tho)001:10183: lam gzhan nye bar ston phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:10184: theg chen sangs rgyas gsung ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:10185: rig byed mtha' pa'i lta ba bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:10186: zhes de dag gis 'dod pa bkod pa dang khyad par mi snang la /
NK130(tho)001:10187: 'dir ni ting nge 'dzin gtso bor ston pas sngags kyi mdo sde la 'jug pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10188: sdom pa dang dam tshig gis gzhi bzung bas 'dul ba la snang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10189: zab pa dang rgya che ba ston pas mngon pa'i chos nyid dang mi 'gal ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:10194: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs /
NK130(tho)001:10196: bstan pa spyi dang lhan cig tu byung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10197: chos log 'byung ngo zhes sangs rgyas kyis sngar lung ma bstan pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10198: rtog ge'i spyod yul ma yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10199: de bas na bka' nyid du grub pa min te /
NK130(tho)001:10201: theg pa gong 'og rgya gar du yang grags pa'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:10202: gsang sngags phyi nang yod na yo mnyam dang /
NK130(tho)001:10203: med na med mnyam yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10204: ye shes kyis spang bya'i gnyen po byed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10207: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun la sogs pa
NK130(tho)001:10208: med pa yang don dam pa zhes sgra gzhan gyi
NK130(tho)001:10210: tshul 'di ni mdo sde rgyan du bcom ldan 'das byams pas gsungs pa /
NK130(tho)001:10211: rang gi nyid la 'jug pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10212: rang gi nyid la snang phyir dang //
NK130(tho)001:10213: zab pa'i phyir dang rgya che'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10214: chos nyid dang yang 'gal ba med //
NK130(tho)001:10216: sngar lung ma bstan lhan cig byung //
NK130(tho)001:10217: spyod yul ma yin grub pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10218: yod dang de bzhin med pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10219: gnyen po dag ni sgra gzhan phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10220: zhes rgyu mtshan de dag gis theg pa chen po bka' ru bsgrubs par mdzad pa bzhin du /
NK130(tho)001:10221: 'dir yang tshul de dag gis rdzogs pa chen po bka' ru bsgrub bo //
NK130(tho)001:10222: sngar lung ma bstan lhan cig byung /
NK130(tho)001:10223: zhes pa 'dis mtha' 'khob bod tsam re'i chos log sangs rgyas kyis lung bstan mi lang /
NK130(tho)001:10224: zhes dpal 'dzin gyis zer ba de yang khegs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10225: rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i theg pa zhes mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po las /
NK130(tho)001:10226: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum po dag /
NK130(tho)001:10227: bcom ldan nges par gsungs lags na //
NK130(tho)001:10228: mnyam pas blang dor med spyod cing //
NK130(tho)001:10229: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:10230: nges pa'i theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:10232: de ltar theg pa 'di chos kyi mchog tu sangs rgyas kyis lung bstan pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:10233: chos ma yin par lung bstan pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10234: gzhan yang 'phags pa thogs med kyis theg pa chen po bsdus pa las /
NK130(tho)001:10235: shes bya'i gnas dang mtshan nyid de 'jug dang //
NK130(tho)001:10236: de la gnas dang de dngos dbye ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:10237: nyes pa gsum dang de 'bras spangs pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10238: ye shes theg pa mchog gyur khyad par 'phags //
NK130(tho)001:10239: bstan 'di 'di ltar gzhan du ma mthong la //
NK130(tho)001:10240: 'di dag byang chub mchog rgyur mthong bas na //
NK130(tho)001:10241: sa bcu bstan pas khyad zhugs gang yin la //
NK130(tho)001:10242: theg pa chen po sangs rgyas bkar 'dod do //
NK130(tho)001:10244: dbyig gnyen gyis rnam bshad rig pa las /
NK130(tho)001:10245: ji ltar sangs rgyas gsung ma yin //
NK130(tho)001:10246: 'gal ba'i phyir ro gzhan de bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:10247: de nges don yin rim mi shes //
NK130(tho)001:10248: des don med par ji ltar shes //
NK130(tho)001:10249: de sgra ji bzhin don yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10250: zhes sogs rgyu mtshan du ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:10252: gang phyir lung las lam 'di ni //
NK130(tho)001:10253: med par byang chub med par gsungs //
NK130(tho)001:10254: gal te theg chen ma grub na //
NK130(tho)001:10255: khyed kyi lung de ji ltar grub //
NK130(tho)001:10257: ngag gang mdo sde la 'jug de //
NK130(tho)001:10258: gal te sangs rgyas gsung 'dod na //
NK130(tho)001:10259: theg chen phal cher khyed rang gi //
NK130(tho)001:10260: mdo dang mtshungs pa min nam ci //
NK130(tho)001:10262: mdo gang 'od srung chen po la //
NK130(tho)001:10263: sogs pas gting dpogs ma gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:10264: de ni khyod kyis ma rtogs pas //
NK130(tho)001:10265: bzung bya min par su zhig byed //
NK130(tho)001:10267: 'phags pa 'od srung chen po la sogs pas kyang
NK130(tho)001:10268: theg dman gyi gdul bya'i ngor theg chen gyi mdo
NK130(tho)001:10269: sde rnams rtogs pa'i tshul ma bstan na khyed cag
NK130(tho)001:10273: sngon du skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang //
NK130(tho)001:10274: stong nyid snying rje'i nyams len dang //
NK130(tho)001:10275: sems can kun don bsngo ba sogs //
NK130(tho)001:10276: chos dang 'dra ba mang yod kyang //
NK130(tho)001:10277: bar du gcod pa'i chos log dgu //
NK130(tho)001:10278: rdzun rgyud rnams la nyer gnas phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10279: dug can kha zas zhim po ltar //
NK130(tho)001:10280: 'gro ba bslu ba'i chos su snang //
NK130(tho)001:10282: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud gzhung la //
NK130(tho)001:10283: phyag rgya gsum dang bslab gsum yod //
NK130(tho)001:10284: de dag bon po'i gzhung la'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:10285: 'on kyang tshig don nor ba mang //
NK130(tho)001:10286: zong du bong sha 'tshong ba la //
NK130(tho)001:10287: ri dwags rnga ma bstan dang mtshungs //
NK130(tho)001:10290: theg pa chen po gang zhig las //
NK130(tho)001:10291: thams cad snying rje'i bdag nyid dang //
NK130(tho)001:10292: ye shes dri ma med bshad la //
NK130(tho)001:10293: de la sems yod su zhig smod //
NK130(tho)001:10294: skyon yon mngon par mi shes pa'am //
NK130(tho)001:10295: yon tan skyon du blta ba'am //
NK130(tho)001:10296: yon tan ldan la sdang ba zhig /
NK130(tho)001:10297: theg pa che la smod par zad //
NK130(tho)001:10298: zhes thub pa dgongs rgyan du lung du drangs snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:10301: bdag med la sogs ston phyir dang //
NK130(tho)001:10302: dkon mchog gsum gyi bdag nyid che //
NK130(tho)001:10303: ston phyir slob pa'i theg pa bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:10306: gsang sngags ni gnod sbyin dang srin po la sogs pas bshad pa yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:10307: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:10308: srog gcod pa dang ma byin pa len pa la
NK130(tho)001:10309: sogs pa rgyal bas gsungs pa'i chos kyi tshul dang
NK130(tho)001:10312: yang sbyong rgyud kyi 'grel pa mkhan kha cig /'dod
NK130(tho)001:10313: chags chen po'i lha gar gyi dbang phyug la sogs
NK130(tho)001:10314: pas 'khrig pa'i chos la bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir
NK130(tho)001:10315: bshad pa ste / de lta ma yin na /
NK130(tho)001:10316: de bzhin gshegs pa gcig gi zhal nas dam pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10317: chos rin po che gsungs pa la 'gal ba du
NK130(tho)001:10318: ma ni thabs mi mkhas pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:10319: the tshom gyi dbang gis sems can grol bar mi 'gyur ba'i phyir smyon pa'i tshig lta bu'o //
NK130(tho)001:10321: yang bod snga rabs pa kha cig gis /
NK130(tho)001:10322: de bzhin gshegs pas gsung par nges kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10324: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10325: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10326: rdzun du smra ba la sogs pa rnams sgra ji
NK130(tho)001:10327: bzhin par bzung nas gsang sngags kyi tshul zab mo
NK130(tho)001:10328: rnams log par spyod par byed do //
NK130(tho)001:10331: sangs rgyas kyi gsung rabs thams cad ni nges don kho na yin te /
NK130(tho)001:10332: gzhan du na bcom ldan 'das rdzun gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:10334: 'di dag thams cad la smras pa /
NK130(tho)001:10335: bcom ldan 'das kyis gdul bya 'ga' zhig rim gyis gzhug par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:10336: 'ga' zhig slob dpon med par rang gar 'jug pa dgag pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10340: ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10342: nges pa'i don du gsungs pa rnams ma rtogs shing ma go ba'i gtam yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10343: 'di ltar gdul bya 'ga' zhig yang dag pa'i lam
NK130(tho)001:10344: la zhugs pa'i ched du bardzusa te byar ba'i sems
NK130(tho)001:10345: can dang gzugs la sogs pa yod par gsungs pa
NK130(tho)001:10346: lta bu zhugs pa ldem por dgongs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10347: ngo bo nyid gsum la dgongs nas chos thams cad
NK130(tho)001:10348: med pa dang sgyu ma dang nam mkha' dang 'dra'o
NK130(tho)001:10349: // zhes gsungs pa lta bu mtshan nyid ldem por dgongs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10350: sangs rgyas la brnyas pa la sogs pa'i gnyen por
NK130(tho)001:10351: theg pa ma chog gsungs pa lta bu gnyen po
NK130(tho)001:10353: don zab mo'i ched du yi ge rnams bsgyur te
NK130(tho)001:10354: gsungs pa lta bu bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa
NK130(tho)001:10357: nyan thos dang ni ngo bo nyid //
NK130(tho)001:10358: de bzhin nyes pa 'dul ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:10359: brjod pa zab pa nyid la ni //
NK130(tho)001:10360: ldem por dgongs pa 'di rnam bzhi //
NK130(tho)001:10362: gnyen po ldem por dgongs pa la yang /
NK130(tho)001:10363: nga nyid de'i tshe sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs su gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:10364: zhes gsungs pa lta bu chos sku mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10365: sangs rgyas gang ga'i klung gi bye ma snyed la
NK130(tho)001:10366: bsnyen bkur byas na chos 'di thos par 'gyur ro
NK130(tho)001:10367: // zhes pa lta bu don gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10368: gang dag bsod nams byas te bde ba can du
NK130(tho)001:10369: smon lam 'debs pa de dag der skye bar 'gyur
NK130(tho)001:10370: ro // zhes pa lta bu dus gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10371: sbyin pa ni dman la tshul khrims ni mchog go //
NK130(tho)001:10372: zhes pa lta bu gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs te gsungs pa dang bzhi yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10373: yang lung dang rig pas tshig dang don gcus te ma bstan par /
NK130(tho)001:10374: sgra de nyid kyis chos kyi de kho na nyid
NK130(tho)001:10375: drang por ston pa ni sgra ji bzhin pa ste
NK130(tho)001:10377: khyod kyis srog chags gsod mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:10378: ma byin pa yang blang mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:10379: rdzun dang 'dod la spyod pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:10380: dngos grub 'dod pas bya ba min //
NK130(tho)001:10382: lung dang rig pas gcus nas tshig dang don s+n+rel
NK130(tho)001:10383: zhir ston pa ni sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa
NK130(tho)001:10385: yang chos thams cad stong pa nyid du ston pa ni nges pa'i don dang /
NK130(tho)001:10386: sems can dang gang zag dang skyes bu la sogs par ston pa ni drang ba'i don te /
NK130(tho)001:10388: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa dag /
NK130(tho)001:10389: nges don mdo sde dag gis bye brag shes //
NK130(tho)001:10390: gang la sems can gang zag skyes bu bstan //
NK130(tho)001:10391: chos de thams cad drang don shes par gyis //
NK130(tho)001:10393: rgyas par ni mdo dgongs pa nges 'grel la sogs par shes par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:10394: de yang bcom ldan 'das kyis srog gcod pa spong ba'i bslab pa bcas pas /
NK130(tho)001:10395: de spong bas 'jigs shing skrag pa'i gdul bya dag kyang yod de /
NK130(tho)001:10396: de dag la tshul khrims dang ting nge 'dzin la
NK130(tho)001:10397: sogs pas rgyud rnam par dag pa'i gang zag chos
NK130(tho)001:10398: dang ldan pa 'ba' zhig tu ma zad kyi /
NK130(tho)001:10399: srog gcod pa ma spangs par yang theg pa dam pa 'di la 'jug tu rung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:10400: zhes ma brtags na nyams dga' ba'i tshig thos nas dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10401: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa sogs la 'jug par 'gyur la /
NK130(tho)001:10402: zhugs nas kyang yang pa'i lam gyi don mthong ba
NK130(tho)001:10403: nyid kyis skrag par mi 'gyur bar srog gcod pa
NK130(tho)001:10404: las kyang nges par bzlog par 'gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:10405: de bas na rim gyis 'jug pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10406: srog gcog pa la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin pa
NK130(tho)001:10407: ma yin par ldem por dgongs pas gsungs pa yin
NK130(tho)001:10408: no zhes lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang
NK130(tho)001:10409: pos rgyud dgongs pa lung ston dang /
NK130(tho)001:10410: rdo rje rtse mo dang de nyid bsdus pa la sogs dang sbyar nas rgyas par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10411: yang 'di ni bla ma'i man ngag la rag las par bya ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10412: don sbas nas tshig gzhan srog gcod pa la sogs pa gsungs pa yin te /
NK130(tho)001:10413: slob dpon sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyis ko sa la'i rgyan las /
NK130(tho)001:10414: ci'i phyir 'di ltar ldem po'i dag tu gsung zhe na /
NK130(tho)001:10415: glegs bam mthong ba tsam gyis thub chod du sngags 'dzin pa dgag pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10416: slob dpon gyi man ngag med par dngos grub thob par 'gyur ba ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10419: slob dpon med par 'jug par ma 'gyur cig snyam
NK130(tho)001:10420: du dgongs pa 'jig rten pa dang 'gal pa'i tshig
NK130(tho)001:10421: gis spyod pa'i khyad par ston pa'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10422: srog gcod pa yi sems can gang //
NK130(tho)001:10423: rdzun du smra la dga' ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:10424: gzhan gyi nor la chags pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:10425: rtag tu 'dod la spyod gang dang //
NK130(tho)001:10426: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10428: de las kyang srog gcod pa sgra ji bzhin du
NK130(tho)001:10429: bzung ba ni rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho
NK130(tho)001:10430: ba rnams kyi nang na chen po ste /
NK130(tho)001:10431: ngan song gi rgyu'i gtso bor gsungs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10432: ston pa'i bstan pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK130(tho)001:10433: srog gcod pa ni sgra ji bzhin par mi bzung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:10434: 'o na ji ltar yin ce na /
NK130(tho)001:10435: thams cad gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:10436: sems can kun gyi dngos po kun //
NK130(tho)001:10437: rang sems chos ni bsdus pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:10438: chos bdag med pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK130(tho)001:10440: zhes bdag tu 'dzin pa gsod pa la dgongs pa 'di yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10441: slob dpon zla ba grags pas kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10442: sems can thams cad bsad na ni //
NK130(tho)001:10443: zhes bya ba ni stong pa nyid du bya bas rnam par bshig pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:10445: gang gi phung po dngos med par //
NK130(tho)001:10446: zhi gnas las byung sems kyis byas //
NK130(tho)001:10447: de ni srog gcod byed pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:10448: theg pa mchog la gnas pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:10450: gzhan yang srog gcod pa ni nyon mongs pa gsod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10451: 'jigs tshogs la lta ba gsod pa la sogs pa la dgongs te gsungs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10452: zhes sngon gyi slob dpon dag gis rgyas par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10453: de bzhin du ma byin len dang /
NK130(tho)001:10455: rdzun smra ba rnams kyang sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa ni dgongs pa lung ston pa'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:10456: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gang //
NK130(tho)001:10457: de ni rdzas su shes bya ste //
NK130(tho)001:10458: de 'phrog byed pa gang yin pa //
NK130(tho)001:10459: gzhan gyi nor la chags par 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:10460: gang zhig don ni dngos gcig pa //
NK130(tho)001:10461: de bzhin nyid la rtag sbyor ba //
NK130(tho)001:10462: sems can de nyid 'dod la dga' //
NK130(tho)001:10463: sgrub pa mchog la chags par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:10464: nang dang de bzhin phyi rol dag /
NK130(tho)001:10465: rten 'byung gnyis su ston pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:10466: de ni rdzun smra dga' ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:10467: gnas med la gnas rnal 'byor pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:10469: 'di ltar 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes gang
NK130(tho)001:10470: yin pa de bsgrub par bya ba'i dam pa yin
NK130(tho)001:10471: pas rdzas kyi mchog lta bu yin la /
NK130(tho)001:10472: de ni gzhan de bzhin gshegs pa la mnga' bas /
NK130(tho)001:10473: de yang dag par blang ba'i thabs kyis bdag gi
NK130(tho)001:10474: rgyud la bskyed pa la gzhan gyi nor 'phrog pa
NK130(tho)001:10475: zhes bya'o // de bzhin du yang dag pa'i ye
NK130(tho)001:10476: shes chos dbyings la dmigs pa'i tshul gyi gnyis su
NK130(tho)001:10477: med cing ro gcig par rtag tu sbyor ba ni
NK130(tho)001:10479: de lta bu la dga' ba ni 'dod pa la dga' ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:10481: kun rdzob dang ni don dam dag /'di ni dbang po gnyis yin la //
NK130(tho)001:10482: zung du 'jug par grags pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:10483: de dag gnyis med de sbyor ba //
NK130(tho)001:10484: de la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:10485: de dag thams cad nye bar spyad //
NK130(tho)001:10486: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK130(tho)001:10487: 'dod chags chen po'i tshul mchog go //
NK130(tho)001:10489: snod dang bcud kyis bsdus pa'i phyi nang gi chos
NK130(tho)001:10490: thams cad ni rtag pa dang ma byas pa la
NK130(tho)001:10492: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ste so so'i rgyu rkyen la rag las nas 'byung bas /
NK130(tho)001:10493: sgyu ma lta bu brdzun cing bslu ba'i chos can
NK130(tho)001:10494: yin par ston pa ni rdzun du smra ba yin
NK130(tho)001:10495: la / de nyid don dam par rang bzhin med pa'i gzhi la brten pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10497: lha'i bu chos thams cad ni brdzun pa sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK130(tho)001:10498: nga yang de bzhin du ston par byed do //
NK130(tho)001:10499: des na nga ni rdzun du smra ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:10501: gang yang mngon spyod kyi las su sgra ji bzhin
NK130(tho)001:10502: par gsungs pa de yang gang zag lhag pa'i bsam
NK130(tho)001:10503: pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10504: mngon shes dang ldan pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10505: las kyi sbyor ba phyin ci ma log cing kha
NK130(tho)001:10506: na ma tho ba med pas gzhan gyi don nges
NK130(tho)001:10507: par 'grub par byed nus pa dag gis bya bar
NK130(tho)001:10508: gsungs kyi / gzhan du ni ma yin par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10509: ci ste gsod pa dang ma byin par len pa
NK130(tho)001:10510: la sogs pa'i tshig yod pas bka' ma yin na
NK130(tho)001:10511: ni sde snod gzhan la yang yod pas ha cang
NK130(tho)001:10513: sor mo'i phreng ba la phan pa'i mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:10514: bdag ni ma byin len spong khrims mi 'dzin /
NK130(tho)001:10515: gzhan gyi nor brku'i tshul ni rab tu 'dzin //
NK130(tho)001:10516: ma byin pa ni byang chub lags zhes bgyi //
NK130(tho)001:10517: de ni sus kyang su la'ang ma bstsal te //
NK130(tho)001:10518: byang chub shing drung bcom ldan bzhugs nas kyang //
NK130(tho)001:10519: khyad kyis brnyes pa med cing bshig pa med //
NK130(tho)001:10520: de ni chos rnams kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK130(tho)001:10521: de ni bla na med pa'i chos lags so //
NK130(tho)001:10522: zhes bya ba la sogs pa bslab pa'i tshig rnams ldem po'i ngag gis rgya cher gsungs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10524: pha dang ma ni bsad bya zhing //
NK130(tho)001:10525: rgyal po gtsang sbra can gnyis dang //
NK130(tho)001:10527: mi de dag par 'gyur zhes bya //
NK130(tho)001:10529: pha ni las kyi bag chags sa bon du 'dug pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:10530: ma ni sred pa ste phyi ma la sred cing chags pa'i sems so //
NK130(tho)001:10531: rgyal po ni las kyi sa bon dang ldan pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10532: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pas phyi ma la nye
NK130(tho)001:10533: bar len pa'o // gtsang sbra can gnyis ni dge sbyong dang bram ze ste /
NK130(tho)001:10535: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nye bar len pa'i phung po dang /
NK130(tho)001:10536: gtsang ba dang dag pa dang grol bar 'dod pas lta ba snyems pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10537: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa des gtsang ba dang grol bar 'dod pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:10538: yul 'khor ni sems kyi yul dbang po drug go //
NK130(tho)001:10539: de'i 'khor ni phyi'i yul gzugs la sogs pa'o //
NK130(tho)001:10540: de dag legs par sbyang pa'i mi ni dag par 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:10543: snying po med la snying por shes //
NK130(tho)001:10544: phyi ci log la rnam par gnas //
NK130(tho)001:10545: nyon mongs pas ni rab nyon mongs //
NK130(tho)001:10546: byang chub dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:10548: blo rnam par g.yeng ba la snying po med par
NK130(tho)001:10549: shes pa dang tshul bzhin ma yin pa las phyin
NK130(tho)001:10550: ci log tshul bzhin du yid la byed pa la
NK130(tho)001:10551: gnas pa dang / dka' ba spyod pa'i ngal bas
NK130(tho)001:10552: nyon mongs pa rnams kyis ni byang chub blo rnam
NK130(tho)001:10553: bar g.yeng ba med pa la snying por shes pa
NK130(tho)001:10554: gnas pa dang / dang / zer ba yin no thob par 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:10555: zhes ldem dgongs gsungs pa'i chos kyi de kho na
NK130(tho)001:10556: nyid rnams tshul 'di dag gis skyon med par khong
NK130(tho)001:10557: du chud par bya ba yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10558: de tsam mi nus na btang snyoms kyis bdag nyid bsrung bar bya yi /
NK130(tho)001:10560: klu sgrub kyis rin chen phreng bar /
NK130(tho)001:10561: de bzhin gshegs dgongs gsungs pa rnams //
NK130(tho)001:10562: shes par sla min de yi phyir //
NK130(tho)001:10563: theg gcig theg pa gsum gsungs pas //
NK130(tho)001:10564: btang snyoms kyis ni bdag bsrung bya //
NK130(tho)001:10565: btang snyoms kyis ni sdig mi 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:10566: sdang bas sdig 'gyur dge ba min //
NK130(tho)001:10568: des theg pa che chung dang rgyud sde gong 'og
NK130(tho)001:10569: la sogs pa 'gal ba ltar snang ba thams cad
NK130(tho)001:10570: kyang gdul bya'i dbang gis 'gal ba med pa yin
NK130(tho)001:10571: te / dper na rgya cher rol pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10573: thub dbang mngon par sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag
NK130(tho)001:10574: bdun du chos ma gsungs pa dang sangs rgyas phal
NK130(tho)001:10575: po che dang sa bcu ba'i mdo las /
NK130(tho)001:10576: zhag bdun phrag gnyis pa la gzhan 'phrul dbang byed
NK130(tho)001:10577: kyi gnas su mdo sde sa bcu pa gsungs pa
NK130(tho)001:10578: mi 'gal ba ni rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba
NK130(tho)001:10579: dang / gdul bya'i dbang las yin zhes slob dpon dbyig gnyen dang /
NK130(tho)001:10580: nyi ma grub gnyis kyis sa bcu pa'i 'grel pa dang 'grel bshad las gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10581: de bzhin du myang 'das chen po dang rgya cher
NK130(tho)001:10582: rol pa dang lung gzhi las sgra gcan 'dzin gyi
NK130(tho)001:10583: ma grags 'dzin ma yin par gsungs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10584: so sor 'brang sa ma las sa mtsho ma yin par gsungs pa yang mi 'gal bar gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10585: de 'dra'i rig can shin tu mang yang de tsam gyis go bar sla'o //
NK130(tho)001:10586: yang sh+aakya thub pa dang rnam par snang mdzad dang
NK130(tho)001:10587: 'khor los sgyur ba la sogs pa sku sna tshogs
NK130(tho)001:10588: pa dang / de dag gis chos mi 'dra ba
NK130(tho)001:10589: du ma gsungs pa yang gdul bya'i ngor thabs la
NK130(tho)001:10591: rang bzhin tha dad pa dang 'gal ba dang 'dod
NK130(tho)001:10592: chags dang bcas pa la sogs pa ma yin no
NK130(tho)001:10594: rdo rje dra ba'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:10595: gang dang gang gi gzugs kyis ni //
NK130(tho)001:10597: de dang de ni rnam ston te //
NK130(tho)001:10598: sna tshogs nor bu ji bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:10599: 'dul ba'i thabs ni gang gang gis //
NK130(tho)001:10601: rnam pa de dang de dag gis //
NK130(tho)001:10602: chos rnams ston pa mdzad pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:10604: de bzhin du mdo las kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10605: bdun gyi las rnams thugs chud kyang //
NK130(tho)001:10606: bdud kyi rjes su 'jug mdzad pa //
NK130(tho)001:10607: thabs kyi pha rol phyin brnyes pa //
NK130(tho)001:10608: de rnams bya ba kun ston mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:10609: yan lag gang dang gang gis ni //
NK130(tho)001:10610: sems can chos la dga' gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:10611: bya ba thams cad ston pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:10612: thabs chen legs par bslabs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:10613: de yi bslab pa mtha' yas shing //
NK130(tho)001:10614: spyod yul yang ni mtha' yas la //
NK130(tho)001:10615: ye shes phun tshogs mtha' yas pas //
NK130(tho)001:10616: sems can mtha' yas grol mdzad ba'o //
NK130(tho)001:10617: de yi mngon mtha' bskal pa'am //
NK130(tho)001:10618: bye ba'am ni bye ba brgyar //
NK130(tho)001:10619: sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs na yang //
NK130(tho)001:10620: tshig gis legs pa brjod mi nus //
NK130(tho)001:10621: gang zhig shes rab dman pa yi //
NK130(tho)001:10622: sems can dman pa ma gtogs pa //
NK130(tho)001:10623: mkhas pas chos 'di thos nas ni //
NK130(tho)001:10624: su zhig byang chub 'tshol mi byed //
NK130(tho)001:10626: de'i phyir theg pa chen po gsang sngags ni bde
NK130(tho)001:10627: bar gshegs pa'i gsung mchog tu zab pa myur du
NK130(tho)001:10628: bla na med pa'i byang chub /
NK130(tho)001:10629: 'dod pa rnams kyis mtha' drug dang dgongs pa brgyad
NK130(tho)001:10630: la sogs pa'i sgo nas shes par bya dgos so
NK130(tho)001:10631: // de la sngags kyis lha la sogs pa dgug
NK130(tho)001:10632: cing gsang ste brjod pa rnams ni gsang sngags dang
NK130(tho)001:10633: // / ma rig pa'i gnyen por gyur bas lha mo'i gzugs su bzhugs pa ni rig sngags dang /
NK130(tho)001:10634: de gnyis kyi chos kyi don dang tshig mi brjed
NK130(tho)001:10635: par 'dzin cing khyad par gyi rim pa thob par
NK130(tho)001:10637: zhes sgra sbyor bam po gnyis pa las 'byung ba ltar ro //
NK130(tho)001:10638: de ltar yang gang zhig skye ba gzhan du goms
NK130(tho)001:10639: pa'i bag chags kyi stobs kyis nag tshal dang dben
NK130(tho)001:10640: pa la dga' zhing khrus dang man+dala bri ba dang
NK130(tho)001:10641: mchod pa dang sbyin sregs dang dka' thub dang bzlas
NK130(tho)001:10642: brjod la sogs pa'i bya ba med par yid mnyam
NK130(tho)001:10644: de kho na nyid bsgom pa'i nus pa chung ba
NK130(tho)001:10645: mtshan ma can gyi spyod pa la dga' ba dag
NK130(tho)001:10646: la phyi'i spyod pa de dag shas cher ston pa
NK130(tho)001:10647: bya ba'i rgyud legs grub la sogs pa rgyud chen
NK130(tho)001:10648: po gsungs te / slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas bsam gtan phyi ma'i 'grel pa las /
NK130(tho)001:10649: 'di ni phyi'i lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10651: gang zhig bya ba'i khyad par la yang mos shing /
NK130(tho)001:10652: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod pa rgya chen po
NK130(tho)001:10653: la sbyor ba'i nang gi bdag nyid can gyi tshul
NK130(tho)001:10654: yang mi 'dor bar spro ba dag la bya ba
NK130(tho)001:10655: dang rnal 'byor gyi cha gnyis ka dang ldan pa
NK130(tho)001:10656: gnyi ga'i rgyud rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang
NK130(tho)001:10657: chub pa la sogs pa gsungs pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10658: de yang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas rnam snang mngon byang gi bsdus don las /
NK130(tho)001:10659: 'di ni phyi dang nang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK130(tho)001:10660: rnal 'byor gnyis thun mong du gyur pa yin pas
NK130(tho)001:10662: de nyid ni gsang sngags dang rjes su mthun pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10663: spyod pa shes rab dang thabs gtso bor gyur pa
NK130(tho)001:10664: rgya cher ston pas sngon gyi mkhas pa dag gis
NK130(tho)001:10665: spyod pa'i rgyud ces kyang bshad do //
NK130(tho)001:10666: yang gang zhig de kho na nyid la mngon par dga' ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK130(tho)001:10667: rnal 'byor la lhag par mos pa /
NK130(tho)001:10668: phyi'i bya ba la mi dga' bar ting nge 'dzin
NK130(tho)001:10669: gyis rgyud dag par byed pa rnams la bya ba'i
NK130(tho)001:10671: rnal 'byor gyi yan lag gtso bo ston pa rnal
NK130(tho)001:10672: 'byor gyi rgyud de kho na nyid bsdus pa la
NK130(tho)001:10675: de nyid bsdus pa'i bstod 'grel las /
NK130(tho)001:10676: rgyud 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gtso bo yin te rnal 'byor gco bo yin //
NK130(tho)001:10678: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig dbang po rno ba /
NK130(tho)001:10679: de kho na bsgom pa la rab tu 'dun pa /
NK130(tho)001:10680: sngon goms pa'i stobs kyis bya ba dang dngos po
NK130(tho)001:10681: thams cad la tha dad pa'i 'du shes mi 'jug
NK130(tho)001:10682: pa / theg pa chen po la sems rnam par sbyangs pa /
NK130(tho)001:10683: shes rab dang gnyis su med pa'i spyod pa la
NK130(tho)001:10684: mngon par dad pa'i bdag nyid chen po rnams la
NK130(tho)001:10685: de kho na nyid rnal 'byor gtso bor mdzad de
NK130(tho)001:10686: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis 'jug cing spros pa
NK130(tho)001:10687: med pa dang / shin tu spros pa med pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10688: spyod pa ston pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud dpal
NK130(tho)001:10689: gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa gsungs pa yin
NK130(tho)001:10690: med pa dang / no // bshad pa'i tshul de
NK130(tho)001:10691: dag ni lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang
NK130(tho)001:10692: po'i gzhung bzhin bkod pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10693: yang spros pa las 'das pa'i rnal 'byor dbyings dang
