NK130(tho)001:10694: ye shes dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid kyi rnal 'byor
NK130(tho)001:10695: la mngon par dga' ba dag la a nu yo
NK130(tho)001:10696: ga'i rgyud sde rnams gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10697: yang gang zag dbang po yang rab rtogs pa dang
NK130(tho)001:10698: grol ba dus mnyam par 'gyur ba'i rigs can dag
NK130(tho)001:10699: la spros pa las 'das pa'i theg pa rdzogs pa
NK130(tho)001:10700: chen po a ti yo ga'i rgyud rnams gsungs so
NK130(tho)001:10701: // chos kyi tshul 'di gnyis kyang brtson pa can
NK130(tho)001:10702: du gyur pa la dge ba'i bshes gnyen rgyang ro
NK130(tho)001:10703: byang chub 'bum gyi bstan bcos las 'di ltar byung
NK130(tho)001:10704: // ste / yang spu hrangs kyi lo ts+aa ba lha pho brang zhi ba 'od na re /
NK130(tho)001:10705: sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyud bcu gsum pa dang bcu dgu
NK130(tho)001:10706: dgu pa de bzhin bcu pa dang brgyad cu pa
NK130(tho)001:10707: dang le'u lag la sogs pa rnams ni phyi ba
NK130(tho)001:10709: yang dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo dang kun 'dus rig
NK130(tho)001:10710: pa'i mdo dang rngams pa glog gi 'khor lo'i mdo
NK130(tho)001:10711: dang khu byug rol pa'i mdo dang sems lung chen
NK130(tho)001:10712: po'i mdo dang 'di rnams dar rje dpal gyi grags
NK130(tho)001:10713: pas byas so // yang dpal 'bar khro bo'i rgyal po la sogs pa'i rgyud drug dang /
NK130(tho)001:10714: bdud rtsi bam po brgyad pa la sogs pa gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis byas so //
NK130(tho)001:10715: yang kun byed rgyal po dang mdo bcu gsang ba
NK130(tho)001:10716: la sogs pa dang ye shes gsang ba sogs drang
NK130(tho)001:10717: nga shag tshul gyis byas so //
NK130(tho)001:10718: yang phur pa'i rtsa rgyud khu byug rol pa dang
NK130(tho)001:10719: bshad rgyud k+ai la ya'i rgyud che chung dang dgongs
NK130(tho)001:10720: pa lung ston dang gsang ba gnyer sbas dang rdo
NK130(tho)001:10721: rje gsang ba bkod pa dang k+ai la ya bi
NK130(tho)001:10722: do'i rgyud dang stag mo kha gdangs dang seng ge
NK130(tho)001:10723: kha gdangs dang phag mo kha gdangs dang gsang phur
NK130(tho)001:10724: kha gdangs dang tshub nag rol pa dang zhe sdang
NK130(tho)001:10725: yongs su dag pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:10726: 'phros pa man ngag gi rgyud lnga dang /
NK130(tho)001:10727: gab pa sngags drug gi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:10728: gnod sbyin gyi rgyud ro hi ta dang lcags phye
NK130(tho)001:10729: 'bar ba dang phag mo'i rgyud dgu pa dang nam
NK130(tho)001:10730: mkha' che'i rgyud rlangs dpal gyi seng ges bsgyur zer
NK130(tho)001:10731: ba dang / phyag na rdo rje gos sngon can gyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:10732: +aa tsar+ya bi ma la mi tras bsgyur zer ba'i
NK130(tho)001:10733: sems phyogs kyi rgyud bcu gsum las rmad du byung
NK130(tho)001:10734: ba le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis dang srid pa rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10735: lung la sogs pa ma mo'i rgyud dang rgyal po'i
NK130(tho)001:10736: chos lnga la sogs pa bod kyis byas so //
NK130(tho)001:10737: yang phyag rgya chen po thig le'i rgyud dang gsang
NK130(tho)001:10738: chen thig le'i rgyud dang ye shes thig le'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10739: dang ye shes snying pa'i rgyud +aa tsar+ya dmar pos
NK130(tho)001:10740: byas so // de dag dang de dag gi 'grel
NK130(tho)001:10741: pa dang dbang gi man ngag dang sgrub thabs la
NK130(tho)001:10742: sogs pa mang po'i don nyams su blangs kyang bla
NK130(tho)001:10743: na med pa'i byang chub thob par mi 'gyur ro
NK130(tho)001:10745: yang lo ts+aa ba chen po 'gos khug pa lhas btsas na re /
NK130(tho)001:10746: rma rin chen mchog gis gsang ba snying po dang de'i kha skong du sgyu 'phrul le'u lag brtsams /
NK130(tho)001:10747: de la brten nas zur che chung gis gsang ba
NK130(tho)001:10748: snying po'i 'grel pa dang dkyil chog dang sgrub thabs
NK130(tho)001:10749: mang po rang bzor byas so //
NK130(tho)001:10750: des na sgyu 'phrul gyi chos de dag kyang bod
NK130(tho)001:10751: kyis rang bzor byas pa'i chos log dri ma can
NK130(tho)001:10752: yin no // yang bee ro tsa nas rgya gar
NK130(tho)001:10753: la khungs btsal nas sems phyogs la nam mkha' che
NK130(tho)001:10754: sku la 'jug pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa spyi gcod
NK130(tho)001:10755: rig pa'i khu byug dang lnga brtsams pas rgyal blon
NK130(tho)001:10756: gyis rig nas tsha ba rong du spyugs so //
NK130(tho)001:10757: yang gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches rgya
NK130(tho)001:10758: gar la rdzun gyi khungs sbyar nas rmad du byung
NK130(tho)001:10759: la sogs pa bcu gsum byas so //
NK130(tho)001:10760: yang dar rje dpal gyi grags pas dgongs 'dus dang
NK130(tho)001:10761: kun 'dus dang rgyal po'i chos lnga brtsams te dri
NK130(tho)001:10763: yang gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches k+ai
NK130(tho)001:10764: la ya bcu gnyis kyi rgyud dang pra khog snang
NK130(tho)001:10765: gi rgyud dang ra hu la'i gaza'i rgyud che chung
NK130(tho)001:10766: dang / gdong mo chu 'khyags la sogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10768: pad+ma dbang chen gyi skor la sku'i rgyud rdo rje
NK130(tho)001:10769: thogs med dang gsung gi rgyud rta mchog rol pa
NK130(tho)001:10770: dang thugs kyi rgyud pun+da ri ka dang yon tan
NK130(tho)001:10771: gyi rgyud rin po che ma go la dang phrin
NK130(tho)001:10772: las kyi rgyud karma m+aa le dang lnga brtsams so
NK130(tho)001:10773: // yang de nyid kyis chos nyid zhi ba'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10774: dpal 'bar khro bo'i rgyud tshogs rgyun chen po gnas
NK130(tho)001:10775: lung chen po'i rgyud gtor ma chen po'i rgyud nam
NK130(tho)001:10776: mkha' mdzod kyi rgyud dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud kun
NK130(tho)001:10777: tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10778: ting nge 'dzin mchog gi rgyud rtsom pa don ldan
NK130(tho)001:10779: rgyud la sogs pa brtsams pa ni /
NK130(tho)001:10780: bod kyis rang bzor byas pa'i chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10782: 'di dag kyang phal che ba mi bden te /
NK130(tho)001:10783: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud le'u nye shu rtsa gnyis dang rgyud phyi ma /
NK130(tho)001:10786: gang gi the tshom kun med par //
NK130(tho)001:10787: dngos po kun la rnam par dpyad //
NK130(tho)001:10788: ces pa'i bar gyi dri ba mang po dang //
NK130(tho)001:10789: legs so legs so rgyal ba kun //
NK130(tho)001:10790: zhes pa la sogs pa lan dang bcas pa ston pa la rgya dpe yod cing /
NK130(tho)001:10791: 'grel pa'ang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10793: bi ma la mi tras mdzad pa gsum bod du 'gyur yod la /
NK130(tho)001:10794: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel chen bi shwa mi dras mdzad pa las kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10795: ye shes sems dpas gang reg pa //
NK130(tho)001:10798: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang mu med pa na
NK130(tho)001:10799: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsal
NK130(tho)001:10800: ba la / ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i
NK130(tho)001:10801: gzhal yas khang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad
NK130(tho)001:10802: ba la / pa / zhes bya ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10803: zhes pa la sogs pa bcom ldan ral gris bsgrubs pa ltar 'dis kyang de ltar du bsgrubs te /
NK130(tho)001:10804: kho bo'i bla mas dpal gsang ba snying po sgrub pa las gsung pa 'di yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10805: de bzhin du 'di la glen gzhi dang /
NK130(tho)001:10807: ston pa log pa la sogs pa'i skyon spong ba yang de nyid las rgyas par gsungs so //
NK130(tho)001:10808: yang dgongs pa 'dus pa la sogs pa rgya mtsho'i
NK130(tho)001:10809: ri ma la yar phyag na rdo rjes gsungs pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10810: rgyud yin cing / de bru sha'i lo ts+aa ba
NK130(tho)001:10811: che btsan skyes kyis rgya gar nas bsgyur ba yin
NK130(tho)001:10812: rgyud yin cing / la / rngams pa glog gi
NK130(tho)001:10813: 'khor lo'i rgyud kyang slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i dkyil
NK130(tho)001:10814: 'khor gyi cho ga mun sel sgron mar lung drangs
NK130(tho)001:10815: pas rgyud yang dag par gsal zhing /
NK130(tho)001:10816: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba rdo rje khros pa la /
NK130(tho)001:10817: slob dpon pad+ma'i dus kyi snga 'gyur zhig dang /
NK130(tho)001:10818: phyis dpyal lo dang sa skya pas bsgyur ba ste /
NK130(tho)001:10819: 'gyur gsum snang bas yang dag pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10820: zhes kho bo'i bla ma gsung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:10821: de bzhin du rje btsun grags pa dang bla ma
NK130(tho)001:10822: dam pa chos kyi rgyal pos mdzad pa'i rgyud kyi
NK130(tho)001:10824: gsang sngags snga 'gyur la gsang ba snying po /
NK130(tho)001:10828: thabs kyi zhags pa rnams rgyud yang dag yin pa 'dra /
NK130(tho)001:10829: lhag ma rnams legs par brtags la bya dgos so //
NK130(tho)001:10831: yang phyag rgya chen po thig le'i rgyud la sogs
NK130(tho)001:10832: pa lo ts+aa ba kam chos kyi ye shes dang
NK130(tho)001:10833: / phyugs mtshams dgra bcom la sogs pas bsgyur ba
NK130(tho)001:10834: kye rdo rje'i bshad rgyud dang cha mthun gyi rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10835: du mkhas pa rnams la grags pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:10836: khyad par du phyag rgya chen po'i thig le la
NK130(tho)001:10837: slob dpon zab pa'i rdo rje dang slob dpon shes
NK130(tho)001:10838: rab gsang bas mdzad pa'i 'grel pa yod la /
NK130(tho)001:10839: slob dpon a b+ha yas kyang man ngag gi snye ma lnga par /
NK130(tho)001:10841: phyag rgya chen po'i thig le las //
NK130(tho)001:10843: de ltar phyag rgya chen po'i thig le las //
NK130(tho)001:10844: zhes lung mang du drangs shing /
NK130(tho)001:10845: snye ma nyi shu rtsa gcig par yang /
NK130(tho)001:10846: ji ltar phyag rgya chen po'i thig le las gsungs pa /
NK130(tho)001:10847: ri bong can gyi cha bzhin du //
NK130(tho)001:10848: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyas par drangs pa rnams ni yang dag pa'i shes byed yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10849: spyod pa'i rgyud 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed khro bo rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:10851: rtsa ba'i rgyud dang rgyud phyi ma dang phyi ma'i
NK130(tho)001:10852: phyi ma rnams sngags don rnam gzigs la sogs pa'i
NK130(tho)001:10853: rgyud 'grel na drangs yod pas rgyud yang dag pa
NK130(tho)001:10855: yang kho bo cag gi bla ma'i zhal nas //
NK130(tho)001:10856: dus phyis byung ba'i rgyud la dus 'khor gyi gzhung
NK130(tho)001:10857: drug shar phyogs ba ren+d+ra'i tse lu yo ga'i ma
NK130(tho)001:10858: tse lu +aa tsar+ya zhes bya bas rnyed de /
NK130(tho)001:10859: de mkhas pa rig ral sgo drug dang dus mnyam pas /
NK130(tho)001:10860: pan chen de dag gis gzigs pas 'jig rten gyi
NK130(tho)001:10861: khams le'u la sogs pa ba ra ta drang srong
NK130(tho)001:10862: rgyas pa'i gzhung 'bum phrag gcig yod pa dang mthun
NK130(tho)001:10863: par byung / rtsa rlung la sogs pa'ang sangs rgyas pa'i rgyud dang mi mthun par byung /
NK130(tho)001:10864: theg pa gsum dang 'gal bar 'dug pas de gang nas byung dris pas /
NK130(tho)001:10865: 'di nas byung tse lu pa rang la gtugs tsa
NK130(tho)001:10866: na'ang bshad lugs lnga tsam byas nas nges pa mi
NK130(tho)001:10867: 'dug pas nang pa'i mkhas pa rnams kyis ma blangs
NK130(tho)001:10868: so // de ltar dus 'khor sangs rgyas pa'i chos
NK130(tho)001:10869: su ma chud pa la de nas mi rabs gnyis
NK130(tho)001:10870: na slob dpon +aa b+ha ya ka ra gup+tasa /
NK130(tho)001:10871: rgyud sde bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga chen po rdo rje phreng ba'i mjug tu bris shing /
NK130(tho)001:10872: de'i sdom tshig dang dus 'khor la 'jug pa la
NK130(tho)001:10873: sogs pa'i cha lag mdzad nas sangs rgyas pa'i gzhung
NK130(tho)001:10875: 'on kyang 'di la gza' skar shar du 'gro ba
NK130(tho)001:10876: dang rgya nag bod kyi byang na yod pa la
NK130(tho)001:10877: sogs pa blun pos kyang rig pa'i nor ba mang
NK130(tho)001:10878: po yod cing / dbu'i skyes bu nye shu rtsa lnga nas /
NK130(tho)001:10879: rong pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan pas rgyud phyi ma spar du bzhengs pa'i mjug byang du /
NK130(tho)001:10880: dzam gling byang phyogs rgya nag yul chen gyi //
NK130(tho)001:10881: rgyal po'i pho brang ta'i ru zhes grags pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:10882: mkhar gyi lho phyogs nam ki zhes pa'i sder //
NK130(tho)001:10883: sngon med spar 'di bsgrub 'dod blo skyes nas //
NK130(tho)001:10885: rgya'i yig tshang las se chen rgyal po'i mnga' 'bangs
NK130(tho)001:10886: kyi yul mtha' nas sham+b+ha la'i yul gyi mtha' ma
NK130(tho)001:10887: ri gangs can la zhag bcu gnyis kyis slebs pa
NK130(tho)001:10888: bshad pas rgya nag bod kyi byang na yod par
NK130(tho)001:10889: gsal la / gza' skar shar du 'gro ba ma
NK130(tho)001:10890: zad 'gros bzhi yod pas lho nub byang gsum du'ang
NK130(tho)001:10892: rang lugs mang po mu stegs pa la byas yod pas /
NK130(tho)001:10893: slob dpon 'jigs med 'byung gnas sbas pas dpal sam+buta'i
NK130(tho)001:10894: brtags pa drug pa'i rab tu byed pa dang po'i
NK130(tho)001:10895: 'grel pa man ngag gi snye ma'i snye ma nyi
NK130(tho)001:10897: 'o na dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa dang
NK130(tho)001:10898: de'i rjes su 'brang ba'i gzhung nas theg pa gsum
NK130(tho)001:10899: dang 'gal bar rnam par bzhag par byas pa des
NK130(tho)001:10900: na de'i gzhung byed pa'i grags pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10901: pad+ma dkar po dang rdo rje snying po dang phyag
NK130(tho)001:10902: na rdo rje'i ming can gyi byang chub sems dpa'
NK130(tho)001:10903: ma yin no // zhes mang du mkhyen pa rnams gsungs la /
NK130(tho)001:10904: des na 'gal ba thams cad mi spong ba la /
NK130(tho)001:10905: 'gal ba 'ga' tsam yang spong bar rtsol bar byed do //
NK130(tho)001:10907: de la mang du mkhyen pa ni mkhas pa sgo drug la sogs pa rnams so //
NK130(tho)001:10908: des na de dag ma rgyud du byed kyang phyi
NK130(tho)001:10909: nang 'dres pa yin pas pu sti gud du byas
NK130(tho)001:10910: la bzhugs kyi / rgyud 'bum rnams kyi dbur 'dri ba'ang mi 'thad do //
NK130(tho)001:10913: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i bshad rgyud rdo rje phreng ba le'u lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa las /
NK130(tho)001:10914: rdo rje 'jigs byed dbang phyug dang //
NK130(tho)001:10915: he ru ka dang dus 'khor lo //
NK130(tho)001:10916: dang po'i sangs rgyas la sogs mtshan //
NK130(tho)001:10917: zhes de dag rnam grangs su gsungs shing //
NK130(tho)001:10918: man ngag gi snye ma lnga pa las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:10919: gtsug tor nas ni smin mtshams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:10921: de phyir mya ngan 'das par gnas //
NK130(tho)001:10922: zhes pa'i bar du dus kyi 'khor lo las brjod de /
NK130(tho)001:10923: zhes yid ches pa'i khungs su mdzad la /
NK130(tho)001:10924: kha che'i slob dpon na ro ta pa dang nyi
NK130(tho)001:10925: ma dpal ye shes la sogs pa mkhas grub chen
NK130(tho)001:10926: po rnams kyis rgyud yang dag tu mdzad nas dbang
NK130(tho)001:10927: mdor bstan la sogs pa 'grel bar mdzad cing /
NK130(tho)001:10928: theg pa gsum dang 'gal ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:10929: snod kyi 'jig rten gyi rnam bzhag ba ra ta'i
NK130(tho)001:10930: gzhung dang mthun par bstan pa la sogs pa ni
NK130(tho)001:10931: nyi ma'i shing rta la sogs pa'i gdul bya theg
NK130(tho)001:10932: chen la drangs ba'i phyir te /
NK130(tho)001:10933: man ngag gi snye ma nyi shu rtsa gcig pa de nyid las /
NK130(tho)001:10934: gang dus kyi 'khor lo las gsungs pa /
NK130(tho)001:10935: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor logs shig tu gton nas gsungs
NK130(tho)001:10936: pa ni mu stegs pa'i mngon par zhen pa dang
NK130(tho)001:10937: ldan pa nyi ma'i shing rta la sogs pa'i gdul
NK130(tho)001:10938: bya rnams nges pa'i don la gzhug par bya ba
NK130(tho)001:10939: la dgongs nas / drang ba'i don gyi snod kyi
NK130(tho)001:10940: 'jig rten ba ra ta la sogs pa'i rjes su
NK130(tho)001:10941: 'jug pa nyid kyis ri rab kyi matha'i bar du
NK130(tho)001:10942: rnam par bzhag pa la sogs pa bstan pa bzhin
NK130(tho)001:10943: shes pa nyid du shin tu rgyas par bshad pa'o
NK130(tho)001:10944: la dgongs nas / // zhes pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:10945: dus kyi 'khor lo nas bstan pa rgyud gzhan dang
NK130(tho)001:10946: mi 'gal ba don cha nas 'ga' zhig bdag nyid
NK130(tho)001:10947: kyi gzhung gi cha dang rjes su mthun pa dang
NK130(tho)001:10948: / 'ga' zhig gdul bya'i bsam pa'i rjes su 'jug pas kha cig spangs la /
NK130(tho)001:10949: de la gzhan pa'i 'gal ba rnams ma spangs kyang /
NK130(tho)001:10950: de rnams kyi nyes pa ci yang med do zhes
NK130(tho)001:10951: gsungs pa'i phyir slob dpon chen po a b+ha ya
NK130(tho)001:10952: ka ra la sogs pa'i mkhas pa chen po rnams
NK130(tho)001:10953: rgyud yang dag tu bzhed pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:10954: zhes bshad pa 'di rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK130(tho)001:10955: grag pa la sogs pa'i ming can byang chub sems
NK130(tho)001:10956: dpa' ma yin par smra ba'ang rgol bar bkod tha
NK130(tho)001:10958: yang kha cig chos spyod thams cad kyi man ngag mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:10959: slob dpon 'jam dpal grags pas mdzad pa'i rtsa ltung
NK130(tho)001:10960: rgya cher 'grel gnyis dge tshul khyung grags kyis byas
NK130(tho)001:10963: 'di la nag tsho lo ts+aa ba'i zhal snga nas
NK130(tho)001:10964: kyi dang po rgya gar du ma phyin gong du
NK130(tho)001:10965: de ltar gtsigs mi 'dug pa la /
NK130(tho)001:10966: phyis bi kra ma sh+ai la'i pan+di ta rnams 'di la bshad nyan byed kyin 'dug par /
NK130(tho)001:10967: de la bdud rtsi'i thig pa zhes bya ba'i gdams
NK130(tho)001:10968: ngag ngo mtshar can cig 'dug pa'ang nag tshos bsgyur
NK130(tho)001:10969: te shin tu gtsigs che bar mdzad pas thams cad
NK130(tho)001:10972: bod du 'gyur ba'i chos zhig la jo bo dang
NK130(tho)001:10973: rgya brtson 'grus seng ges bsgyur ba'i rtsa ltung rgya
NK130(tho)001:10974: cher 'grel 'gyur bzang ba yin gsung yang kha cig
NK130(tho)001:10975: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i bshad rgyud gnyis su med
NK130(tho)001:10976: pa mnyam pa nyid rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud lo
NK130(tho)001:10977: ts+aa ba chos kyi blo gros kyis bsgyur bar grags
NK130(tho)001:10978: pa 'di rgya pho ba lung pas byas pas bod
NK130(tho)001:10980: yang bcom ldan pa la la bod brdzun mas bslu
NK130(tho)001:10981: ba'i phyir slad nas mi mthun pa mang po byas
NK130(tho)001:10982: par snang bas yang dag pa ma yin no zhes
NK130(tho)001:10983: zer / yang chos kha cig thun mong ma yin
NK130(tho)001:10984: pa'i gsang ba la bsre bslad bya ba'i gzhi rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10985: mtshan nyid pa zhig yod pa yang srid /
NK130(tho)001:10986: spyir rgyud kha 'thor ba'i lung mang po dang mdo
NK130(tho)001:10987: sde'i khungs po bris 'dug pas thams cad bod kyis
NK130(tho)001:10988: byas pa'ang ma yin mtshams sbyor dang lhad mang po
NK130(tho)001:10989: zhugs 'dug / de'i rgyu mtshan gyis gtso bo'i badz+ra
NK130(tho)001:10990: d+h+ri ka la sogs pa'i sngags gtub rnams rgya gar
NK130(tho)001:10991: gyi spyod tshul med par bod kyi lugs su byas
NK130(tho)001:10992: zhugs 'dug / 'dug / gzhan yang tshig gi sbyor ba rags pa mang po gda'/
NK130(tho)001:10994: 'di yang kar sh+aakya grags pa la sogs pa rgyud
NK130(tho)001:10995: yang dag tu bzhed cing pan+di ta smri tis rang
NK130(tho)001:10997: khyad par du slob dpon 'jigs med 'byung gnas sbas pas /
NK130(tho)001:10998: de skad du yang gnyis su med pa rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:10999: b+ha ga skal ldan sangs rgyas nyid //
NK130(tho)001:11000: des na chags pa bsun mi 'don //
NK130(tho)001:11001: zhes man ngag gi snyem ma dang por khungs su mdzad do //
NK130(tho)001:11002: ci ste snga ma ming mthun sbyar bar sems na /
NK130(tho)001:11003: slob dpon gyis drangs pa'i gzhi rgyud yang dag bstan dgos la /
NK130(tho)001:11004: bod du ma 'gyur pa'ang yid ches pa'i lan du mi rung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:11005: zhes rgyang ro byang chub 'bum gsungs te /
NK130(tho)001:11006: dus phyis gnyis med rnam rgyal chung ba 'di kun
NK130(tho)001:11007: mkhyen bus bsgyur ba yin pas shin tu bden no
NK130(tho)001:11008: // lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang pos kyang /
NK130(tho)001:11009: gnyis su med pa mnyam pa nyid rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las /
NK130(tho)001:11010: sangs rgyas kun sogs gsod pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:11011: sems can smad par mi bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11012: zhes ldem por dgongs pa yon por ston pa'i skabs su khungs su mdzad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11014: tha dad pa yang ma yin te /
NK130(tho)001:11015: bcom ldan 'das kyis thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang
NK130(tho)001:11016: ba zhes bya ba rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las
NK130(tho)001:11017: / de nas gzhan yang thams cad mkhyen pa'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa bshad par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11018: 'jam dpal ni rgyal po zas gtsang mar gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11019: 'jig rten dbang phyug ni lha mo sgyu 'phrul du gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11020: dpal lha mo ni grags 'dzin no //
NK130(tho)001:11021: rdo rje sems dpa' ni sgra gcan 'dzin no //
NK130(tho)001:11022: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba ni sh+aa ri'i bu'o //
NK130(tho)001:11023: kun tu bzang po ni gnas brtan kun dga' bor gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11024: lha'i dbang po brgya byin ni gnas brtan lha sbyin no //
NK130(tho)001:11025: rnam par snang mdzad chen po ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub par gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11026: zhes gsungs pa las shes par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11027: zhes rnam par mdzad dang sh+aakya thub pa tha mi
NK130(tho)001:11028: dad par ston pa'i skabs su khungs nyid du mdzad
NK130(tho)001:11029: do // yang rje pa kha cig rdo rje sa
NK130(tho)001:11030: 'og gcig ma gtogs lhag ma rdo rje sa 'og
NK130(tho)001:11031: dang 'jig rten gsum 'dul la sogs pa mang po
NK130(tho)001:11032: snang ste bod ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11034: de bzhin du kha cig rdo rje me lce'i rgyud dge tshul khyung grags kyis byas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11035: ri kha cig sog ma med kyi rtog pa rgyas pa'ang bod kyis byas zer /
NK130(tho)001:11037: rdo rje sa 'og le'u bdun pa ni lo ts+aa
NK130(tho)001:11038: ba dge slong bya'i gdong can rin chen bzang pos
NK130(tho)001:11039: bsgyur ba la brtsod pa med pas yang dag yin
NK130(tho)001:11040: la / rdo rje sa 'og le'u bcu gsum pa
NK130(tho)001:11041: zangs kar 'phags pa shes rab kyis bsgyur ba ni
NK130(tho)001:11042: dpe kha che dgon pa la zhus pas yang dag
NK130(tho)001:11043: la / yin no // ci ste rgyud 'di las /
NK130(tho)001:11044: bzhi pa yi ni lnga pa la //
NK130(tho)001:11045: yi ge +ai ni rab tu sbyar //
NK130(tho)001:11046: mthar gnas pa yi gsum pa la //
NK130(tho)001:11047: lnga pa yi ni mtha' dang sbyar //
NK130(tho)001:11049: lnga gyi a btub chad pas rgyud ma yin par rtog na /
NK130(tho)001:11051: dper na lo ts+aa ba chos kyi bzang pos bsgyur ba'i mi g.yo ba'i gzungs las /
NK130(tho)001:11052: gnyis pa'i dang por bcas pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:11053: gsum pa dag gi lngar ldan cing //
NK130(tho)001:11054: bzhi pa yi ni bzhi pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:11056: tsan d+ha zhes btus kyang yang dag pa yin pa bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:11057: rdo rje sa 'og le'u nyer lnga pa chos kyi
NK130(tho)001:11058: rje sa skya pan+di tas bsgyur ba la brtsod pa
NK130(tho)001:11060: lha min dbang pa'i sgo glegs 'joms byed pa //
NK130(tho)001:11061: gsung rabs dam pa dpal ldan kun dga' yi //
NK130(tho)001:11062: rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur 'di la sgra nyams pa //
NK130(tho)001:11063: gang lags de la mkhas rnams bzod par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:11064: sa 'og 'khrul 'khor bde legs rin chen gter //
NK130(tho)001:11065: gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa dam pa'i bka' //
NK130(tho)001:11066: gangs can 'gro la phan pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK130(tho)001:11067: bsgyur ba 'di la bdag gis sgra nyams pa //
NK130(tho)001:11068: gang lags de la mkhas rnams bzod par mdzod //
NK130(tho)001:11069: bsgyur ba'i bsod nams 'dzin bcas rnams la byin //
NK130(tho)001:11071: 'jig rten gsum 'dul lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang pos bsgyur ba yin la /
NK130(tho)001:11072: rdo rje me lce'i rgyud 'grel pa mkhan pos rnal 'byor chen por bkral ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:11073: sogs ma med kyi rtogs pa lo ts+aa ba sh+aakya
NK130(tho)001:11074: brtson 'grus kyis bsgyur bas rgyud yang dag tu mkhas
NK130(tho)001:11076: klu'i rgyal po sogs ma med kyi gtam brgyud kyis
NK130(tho)001:11077: yang dag ma yin par dgag mi nus pa'i phyir
NK130(tho)001:11078: ro // yang bod kha cig 'dul ba don yod par grub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11079: gsang ba rgyan gyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11080: phyag na rdo rje drag po gsum 'dul gyi rgyun rnams yang dag pa ma yin par smra la /
NK130(tho)001:11082: phyag na rdo rje mi g.yo ba //
NK130(tho)001:11083: zhes bkag pa'i rgyud rnams kyang gong du bstan pa'i rgyud yang dag pa de rnams yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11084: yang bod rnams bde mchog ra li'i rgyud rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:11085: thams cad gsang ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11086: gsang ba nor bu'i thig le la sogs pa yang dag pa ma yin par smra'o //
NK130(tho)001:11088: lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen bzang pos rgyud
NK130(tho)001:11089: kyi rgyal po chen po 'dul ba don yod par
NK130(tho)001:11090: grub pa las / de tshe 'khrig pa brten mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:11091: brtul zhugs 'di ni skyon med yin //
NK130(tho)001:11092: sdig ldan ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK130(tho)001:11093: gang la'ang khro dang chags mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:11095: gsang ba rgyan ces bya ba'i rgyud las kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11096: dam tshig dus dang byin brlab pa'i //
NK130(tho)001:11097: dus ma gtogs pa gzhan du ni //
NK130(tho)001:11098: rdzun gyi tshig ni smra mi bya //
NK130(tho)001:11099: chang ni btung bar mi bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11100: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11101: zhes sgra bzhin par ston pa'i skabs su de dag yid ches kyi khungs su sbyar ba'i phyir dang /
NK130(tho)001:11102: drag po gsum 'dul lo ts+aa ba chos kyi bzang po'i 'gyur brtsod med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:11103: ra li la gnas sam yul nyi shu rtsa bzhi la rgyud nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK130(tho)001:11104: cha mthun gyi rgyud brgyad dang bcas pas sum cu rtsa gnyis la rgya dpe yod cing /
NK130(tho)001:11105: pan+di ta ga ya d+ha ras lo ts+aa ba 'brog
NK130(tho)001:11106: mi sh+aakya ye shes dang smyos yon tan grags gnyis
NK130(tho)001:11107: ka la rgyud yang dag tu byas nas bshad do
NK130(tho)001:11108: zhes kho bo'i bla ma gsung la /
NK130(tho)001:11110: thams cad gsang ba'i rgyud kyi bshad sbyar gsang ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11111: sgron mar 'di rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du bkral ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11112: phyir yang dag pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11113: de bzhin du sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK130(tho)001:11114: thugs gsang ba'i mdzod lo ts+aa ba dge blos bsgyur
NK130(tho)001:11115: 'di kha dpal 'dzin cig bod ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:11116: kha ri cig rnal 'byor chen por 'dod pa yang
NK130(tho)001:11117: slob dpon sh+aan+ti pas rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du bshad
NK130(tho)001:11118: pas gsal lo // gsang ba nor bu thig le yang sa pan gyi 'gyur yin te /
NK130(tho)001:11120: dam pa'i rgyud 'di gangs can 'di na sngon //
NK130(tho)001:11121: rnam pa kun tu bsgyur ba ma rnyed nas //
NK130(tho)001:11122: mkhas pa bdo bar gshegs pa'i dpal dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:11123: sgra rig kun dga' rgyal mtshan bdag gis bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:11124: dam pa'i bkas bskul nas ni gus pa yis //
NK130(tho)001:11125: dpal ldan sa skya'i gtsug lag khang du bsgyur //
NK130(tho)001:11126: dge ba de yis sems can thams cad kyis //
NK130(tho)001:11127: gsang don rtogs nas sangs rgyas sar 'gro shog /
NK130(tho)001:11129: yang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba rgyan gyi bkod pa bsgyur ba'i mjug tu yang /
NK130(tho)001:11130: mda' lnga'i gtsug lag yid kyi srung shing gis //
NK130(tho)001:11131: dregs pa'i d+r+wa ba rnam par dral ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:11132: rgyud rgyal rgya mtsho chen po ltar zab 'di //
NK130(tho)001:11133: bsgyur la 'gal gang de la 'phags rnams dgongs //
NK130(tho)001:11135: slob dpon 'jigs med 'byung gnas kyis kyang man ngag gi snye ma bdun par /
NK130(tho)001:11136: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK130(tho)001:11137: dang thugs kyi gsang ba rgyan gyi bkod pa'i rgyud
NK130(tho)001:11139: zhes yid ches pa'i khungs su mdzad pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11140: gzhan yang rgyud rdo rje gtsug tor dang /
NK130(tho)001:11142: rdo rje dkyil 'khor chen po dang /
NK130(tho)001:11143: phyag na rdo rje kun las bstus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11145: dngos grub bstan par byed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11146: dam tshig de kho na nyid 'phyed pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11148: dgongs pa bla na med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11157: yi ge drug pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK130(tho)001:11159: mngon pa'i dam tshig gi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11161: a ra li chen po dang /
NK130(tho)001:11162: thams cad mkhyen pa 'jigs byed dang /
NK130(tho)001:11164: dam tshig gsum gyi rgyan dang /
NK130(tho)001:11165: gsang ba rgyan gyi sdong po dang /
NK130(tho)001:11167: gsang ba dbang po'i thig le dang /
NK130(tho)001:11169: rgyud thams cad kyi snying po bla na med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11170: mngon par 'byung ba bla na med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11175: rtogs pa kun las btus pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11176: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug dang /
NK130(tho)001:11177: rnal 'byor rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11179: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa rdo rje'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11180: rdo rje khro bo snyoms 'jug gsang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11181: rdo rje dri ma med pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11183: dbang kun nas skyed byed dang /
NK130(tho)001:11184: phyag na rdo rje snying po 'byung gnas dang /
NK130(tho)001:11187: shin tu rab tu gnas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11188: rdo rje cod pan dbang bskur ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11189: dkyil 'khor chen po bkod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11190: dam tshig mngon par 'byung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11192: don yod pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11193: rdo rje dbu rgyan la sogs pa rnams ni ye shes zhabs lugs dang /
NK130(tho)001:11194: rnam snang mngon byang gi 'grel pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11200: zhi ba 'tsho'i de kho na nyid grub pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11202: man ngag gi snye ma dang /
NK130(tho)001:11203: mi 'jigs pa'i gzhung 'grel la sogs pa'i gzhung mang
NK130(tho)001:11204: por drangs pa'i tshig de dag yod pa bslu ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11205: bsam pas ming mthun du sbyar ba ma yin pa
NK130(tho)001:11206: rnams ni rgyud yang dag yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11207: zhes kho bo'i bla ma chos kyi rgyal po bcom ldan ral gris gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11208: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK130(tho)001:11209: de ltar bstan pa 'di dag gis ni /
NK130(tho)001:11210: pan chen gser mdog can pas dpal 'dzin pa rnam dpyod dang thos pa che bar mtshon nus shing /
NK130(tho)001:11211: zhes gsungs pa de la rnam dpyod dang thos pa chung ba nyid du grub pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11212: yang gang yang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das nye ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11213: sras brgyad dang bcas pa la sogs pa'i mtshan brgya
NK130(tho)001:11214: rtsa brgyad pa rnams kyang rgyud kyi sde tshan du
NK130(tho)001:11215: gsungs so // des na gzungs kyi ming can mdo yin pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11216: mdo'i ming can rgyud yin pa rnams kyang ma 'dres par shes par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11218: yang mdo phal po che las byung ba 'jig rten gdags pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11221: gzhon nu ma gser mdog gi rtog pa brjod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11222: gzhon nu ma bdun gyi rtogs brjod dang /
NK130(tho)001:11223: dga' ba'i bshes gnyen gyi rtog pa brjod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11224: kun la'i mig gi rtog pa brjod pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11225: mya ngan med kyi sgo nas klu btul ba'i le'u dang /
NK130(tho)001:11227: gnas bstan spyan drang ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11228: dgra bcom pa dge 'dun 'phel gyi lung bstan pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11229: thub pa drang srong gar lha'i ltas kyi snang ba bstan pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11230: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi rtsis dang /
NK130(tho)001:11231: skyes pa rabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11232: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la bstod pa basngagasa par
NK130(tho)001:11233: 'os pa basngagasa pa la sogs pa 'byung mod kyi
NK130(tho)001:11234: / 'di la mngon pa sde bdun ni mdo sde pa la sogs pas bkar mi 'dod la /
NK130(tho)001:11235: gzhan dag kyang sangs rgyas yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas 'phags pa rnams dang /
NK130(tho)001:11236: snyan ngag mkhan chen po 'phags pa dpa' bo la
NK130(tho)001:11237: sogs pas mdzad pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i bstan bcos
NK130(tho)001:11238: yin no // yang gangs can gyi mkhas pa klu mes dbang phyug grags ni /
NK130(tho)001:11239: bdag med pa dris pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11240: zung gi mdo chos kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK130(tho)001:11241: stag sna'i rtog pa brjod pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11242: mig bcu gnyis pa'i mdo la sogs pa bka' ma yin cing /
NK130(tho)001:11243: bcom ldan 'das kyi gtsug tor chen po'i mdo bkar the tshom za'o zhes 'chad do //
NK130(tho)001:11245: sgrub par byed pa'i tshad ma med cing /
NK130(tho)001:11246: gsung rabs la tshad mar gyur pa'i lo pan rnams
NK130(tho)001:11247: kyis mdzad pa'i dkar chag dag las 'di dag mdo
NK130(tho)001:11248: yang dag tu bshad pas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:11249: bdag med dris pa'i mdo lo ts+aa ba chen po
NK130(tho)001:11250: rin chen bzang pos bsgyur ba la brtsod pa med
NK130(tho)001:11251: do // yang bod kha cig lung phran tshegs sgo drug pa yan chad las ma 'gyur zhing /
NK130(tho)001:11252: de yang 'khrugs pa dang chad par yod la /
NK130(tho)001:11253: gzhung bla ma brtsod pa can yin cing /
NK130(tho)001:11254: so sor thar pa'i mdo gnyis kyang dgra bcom pas byas pas bstan bcos yin ces zer ro //
NK130(tho)001:11255: 'di dag kyang bshad par bya ste /
NK130(tho)001:11256: spyir lung bzhi tshangs bar ka ba dpal brtsegs kyis bsgyur ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11257: gzhi 'grel slob dpon dge legs bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa ji snyed 'gyur ba tshang bar bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:11258: bka' lung bzhi 'gyur ba'i mjug na /
NK130(tho)001:11259: thub dbang zla ba'i zhal nas byung gyur pa //
NK130(tho)001:11260: gsung gi me tog char pa yid 'od rnams //
NK130(tho)001:11261: lta ba ngan bzlog rnyi ba med pa yi rang bzhin yun ring skye rgu'i nang gnas shog /
NK130(tho)001:11262: ces pa lo ts+aa bas mdzad pa'i bsngo ba'i tshigs su bcad pa'ang yod /
NK130(tho)001:11263: lung rnam 'byed slob dpon du la lta'i 'grel pa dang bcas pa'ang tshang bar bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:11265: 'grel pa cog gru klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur /
NK130(tho)001:11266: ma'i rnam 'byed ban d+he dpal gyi lhun po dang /
NK130(tho)001:11267: ka ba dpal brtsegs kyis bsgyur ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:11268: 'gyur byang gi dkar chag tu lung phran tshegs bsgyur 'phro bam po lnga bcu zhes 'byung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11269: phran tshegs bsgyur ba kha cig gi mjug tu slad
NK130(tho)001:11270: kyis sgra bsgyur ba'i dpe reg zing dang yang gtugs
NK130(tho)001:11271: shing / bam po ma tshang ba rnams kyang mtshams mtshams su bri /
NK130(tho)001:11272: ban po 'di dag dang po nyid nas 'gyur tam /
NK130(tho)001:11273: ma 'gyur yang lo ts+aa ba ban d+he chen po dpal 'byor la zhu zhing brtag /
NK130(tho)001:11274: ces pa la sogs pa 'byung bas /
NK130(tho)001:11275: 'di la bam po 'khrugs pa dang cung zad ma tshang ba la sogs pa bden mod kyi /
NK130(tho)001:11276: 'on kyang dge ba'i bshes gnyen zhing mo che ba byang chub seng ge zhes bya ba la /
NK130(tho)001:11277: lung sde bzhi po'i dpe rnams btsal te lung phran
NK130(tho)001:11278: tshegs ma tshang ba rnams phran tshegs kha cig nas
NK130(tho)001:11279: byung bas kha bskang ba ni /
NK130(tho)001:11280: bam po sum cu rtsa gnyis pa'i dbu /
NK130(tho)001:11281: sman chen po'i skabs bden nam brdzun blta'o //
NK130(tho)001:11283: bam po sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i dbu /
NK130(tho)001:11284: ji tsam na de grong khyer nas byung ba dang /
NK130(tho)001:11285: bram ze mong brtul zhes bya bas gos kyi mtha' ma nas 'jus nas /
NK130(tho)001:11286: zhes bya ba'i bar bam po gcig dang /
NK130(tho)001:11288: nga yang sman gyi de bzhin no //
NK130(tho)001:11289: zhes bya ba'i 'og tu sdom tshig yig tshar gcig dang /
NK130(tho)001:11290: de nas bam po sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i smad /
NK130(tho)001:11291: ne tso spyod gsal gyi skabs rdzogs pa'i /
NK130(tho)001:11292: e ma'o 'di ltar khyod mkhas pa sha stag dang phrad pa ni bsod nams dang ldan no //
NK130(tho)001:11295: bam po bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa'i stong /
NK130(tho)001:11297: dge slong ma yi bkur sti bri //
NK130(tho)001:11298: zhes gsungs pa'i bar bam po dgu dang /
NK130(tho)001:11299: sdom tshig de'i 'og tu yang sdom tshig yig tshar gcig dang /
NK130(tho)001:11300: de nas ba po bzhi bcu rtsa lnga pa'i mjug
NK130(tho)001:11301: bram ze'i khye'u mi sdug gi gleng gzhi'i skabs kyi
NK130(tho)001:11302: / dge sbyong rnams kyi yon po'i spyad log pa'i
NK130(tho)001:11303: 'tsho ba de lta bu las slar log pa yin
NK130(tho)001:11305: bam po bzhi bcu rtsa drug pa'i dbu /
NK130(tho)001:11306: de nas de'i tshe bram ze pad+ma'i snying po khyim
NK130(tho)001:11307: mchog gi sa mthon po zhig na shas che ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11308: bram ze rgan rabs rnams dang lhan cig 'dus shing
NK130(tho)001:11310: zhes bya ba'i bar bam po bzhi bcu rtsa bdun dang /
NK130(tho)001:11311: de nas bam po bzhi bcu rtsa dgu'i mjug kun dga' bo la gdams pa'i skabs kyi /
NK130(tho)001:11313: dge slong 'di lta bu ni gling dang /
NK130(tho)001:11316: chos kyi skyabs kyis gnas par bya'o //
NK130(tho)001:11317: gling gzhan dang skyabs gzhan gyis ni ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11319: bam pa lnga bcu pa'i mjug /
NK130(tho)001:11321: tsam+ba la dang tshe yi 'du byed mdzad //
NK130(tho)001:11322: ces pa'i bar bam po gcig ste /
NK130(tho)001:11323: bsdams pas bam po bcu gnyis chad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11324: sdom tshig yig tshar gnyis chad pa kha bskang zhing
NK130(tho)001:11325: 'khrugs pa bsdebs pa dang bcas pas lung phran tshegs
NK130(tho)001:11326: sgo brgyad ka rdzogs par bzhugs /
NK130(tho)001:11327: des na lung phran tshegs rdzogs par ban d+he dpal 'byor gyis bsgyur /
NK130(tho)001:11328: 'grel pa dge ba'i blo gros kyis bsgyur ba yin /
NK130(tho)001:11329: 'di'i sgo drug pa yan chad phal cher ba la mi mthun pa med la /
NK130(tho)001:11330: the tshom dang yang dgon pa la //
NK130(tho)001:11332: phyis na 'das pa dang bcas par 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:11333: zhes pa'i bar gyi sgo bdun pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11334: dge slong ma yi bkur sti bri //
NK130(tho)001:11336: bdun brgyas yang dag par brjod pa zhes bya ba'i ming du gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11337: zhes pa'i bar gyi sgo brgyad pa rdzogs par slob
NK130(tho)001:11338: dpon tshul khrims bskyang gis mdzad pa'i 'grel pas phran
NK130(tho)001:11339: tshegs kyi tshig gi rnam par bshad pa dang gtugs
NK130(tho)001:11340: te kho bos legs par gtan la phab pa yin
NK130(tho)001:11341: no // sgo gnyis po 'di 'grel pa ma gtogs gzhan gyis mtshams bye ba mi snang ngo //
NK130(tho)001:11342: 'dul ba gzhung dam pa zhu ba ma rdzogs pa ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa'i bcu tshan /
NK130(tho)001:11343: btsun pa re zhig dge slong mas pha gu rim
NK130(tho)001:11344: pa gnyis sam gsum las lhag par brtsag par bgyid
NK130(tho)001:11345: pa na mtshan 'gyur te dge slong du red nas
NK130(tho)001:11346: lags par gyur na cir 'gyur lags /
NK130(tho)001:11348: zhes rim pa gnyis su brtsig pa yan chad kyi
NK130(tho)001:11349: zhus lan yod pa bam po bcu gnyis pa dang
NK130(tho)001:11350: / zhu ba rdzogs pa dge 'dun lhag ma'i sman
NK130(tho)001:11351: gyi ltung ba yan chad kyi zhus lan yod pa
NK130(tho)001:11352: bam po lnga bcu rtsa gsum pa dang gnyis yod
NK130(tho)001:11353: / / de la zhu ba rdzogs pa'i rgya dpe gzhung shin tu dag pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11354: zhu ba rdzogs pa'i ma dag par grags te /
NK130(tho)001:11356: slob dpon mdo sde 'dzin pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis lung zhu ba'i 'grel par /
NK130(tho)001:11357: kha che ba las zhes bya ba 'di la ni 'di skad ces grags te /
NK130(tho)001:11358: ston pa 'das pa'i gsung rabs bram ze rgyal po
NK130(tho)001:11359: rgyal shes zhes bya ba bstan pa la sdang ba
NK130(tho)001:11361: des bstan pa la gnod pa mang po byas par gyur te mchod rten dag kyang bshig /
NK130(tho)001:11362: dge 'dun gyi kun dga' rab dag kyang bsregs /
NK130(tho)001:11364: sangs rgyas kyi bka' glegs bam rnams kyang phung por bcer nas bsregs so //
NK130(tho)001:11365: de nas rim gyis dge slong rnams kyis yul dang
NK130(tho)001:11366: gnas sna tshogs rnams nas sde snod gsum gyi glegs
NK130(tho)001:11367: bam thams cad bsdus nas bcom brlag tu yang dag
NK130(tho)001:11368: par bsdu ba byas te gzhung bla ma'i glegs bam
NK130(tho)001:11370: de dag gis 'di ltar kha che'i yul na dge
NK130(tho)001:11371: slong zhig gzhung bla ma 'don to zhes thos nas
NK130(tho)001:11372: / de dag de'i phyir kha che'i yul du dengs nas de'i drung du phyin te smras pa /
NK130(tho)001:11373: kho bo cag ni khyed gzhung bla ma 'don to zhes thos pa gang yin pa ste /
NK130(tho)001:11374: jo bo kha ton gyis shig /
NK130(tho)001:11377: cung zad cig ni mi dran no //
NK130(tho)001:11379: ji lta bu dran pa de kho na bzhin du smros shig /
NK130(tho)001:11381: des de kho na bzhin du kha ton du byas so //
NK130(tho)001:11382: dge slong rnams kyis kyang gzhung bsdu ba byas te /
NK130(tho)001:11383: phyis tshig gi don rnam par dpyad pa'i sgo nas
NK130(tho)001:11384: sbyar bar bya'o snyam du bsam nas bris pa las
NK130(tho)001:11385: / phyis 'phral gyi bya bas rnam par g.yengs nas
NK130(tho)001:11386: dus ring mo zhig gi bar du ji lta ba
NK130(tho)001:11388: dge slong gzhan dag kyang yul gzhan du 'don par gyur to //
NK130(tho)001:11389: de nyid kyi phyir yang dag par bsdu ba'i gzhi
NK130(tho)001:11390: nyams pas gzhung bla ma 'di la 'don pa rnam
NK130(tho)001:11391: pa du ma la don kyang rnam pa du ma
NK130(tho)001:11392: ste / de'i phyir btsun pa yon tan 'od kyis 'dul ba'i bshad pa las /
NK130(tho)001:11393: yang dang yang du zhus pa las 'di skad 'byung ngo //
NK130(tho)001:11395: de bas na 'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyis zhus
NK130(tho)001:11396: pa 'di kha che'i dge slong las rnyed pas na
NK130(tho)001:11397: / nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa kha che ba zhes bya ste /
NK130(tho)001:11399: 'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa'i gzhung rgya
NK130(tho)001:11400: gar yul la yang sho lo ka nyis stong tsam
NK130(tho)001:11401: gyi tshad gcig la la la na spyod pa kho
NK130(tho)001:11402: na'o // zhes smra ba'i pham pa gtan la dbab pa'i skabs nas gsung pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11403: des na zhu ba ma rdzogs pa ni yul dbus
NK130(tho)001:11404: kyi dge slong 'ga' zhig gi blo la snang ba'am
NK130(tho)001:11405: / mes ma tshig pa phyis rnyed par grags pas /
NK130(tho)001:11406: dang po'i gzhung ma nyams pa nyid yin pas dag pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11407: zhu ba rdzogs pa ni yang dag par bsdu ba'i gzhi so nyams pas ma dag pa yin /
NK130(tho)001:11408: de gnyis mi mthun pa byung ba na zhu ba ma rdzogs pa la brten /
NK130(tho)001:11409: slob dpon mdo sde 'dzin pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK130(tho)001:11410: gyi 'grel pa yang zhu ba ma rdzogs pa'i 'grel
NK130(tho)001:11411: par byung / ma rdzogs pa de ni dang po 'gyur nas bod du dpe ma dar bas /
NK130(tho)001:11412: sdong gi dus su zhu ba rdzogs pa yi ge
NK130(tho)001:11413: ma dag pa la brten nas lag len 'khrugs pa
NK130(tho)001:11414: mang du byung / slad kyi mchim bu nas dgas
NK130(tho)001:11415: chung ba dang dge slong tshul khrims yon tan gyis
NK130(tho)001:11416: mang du byung / rnyed / de nas dge slong
NK130(tho)001:11417: 'dul ba 'dzin pa chen po dbang phyug tshul khrims
NK130(tho)001:11418: mang du byung / rnyed / kyis gsan pas /
NK130(tho)001:11419: des dpe yon mang po dang bcas te bzhed nas
NK130(tho)001:11420: lag len mi mthun pa thams cad sgro 'dogs der
NK130(tho)001:11421: mang du byung / rnyed / kyis gsan pas / chod / ces gsungs pa 'di yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11422: 'di gnyis ka yang ban d+he klu'i rgyal mtshan la
NK130(tho)001:11423: sogs pa'i dus su 'gyur bas the tshom mi bya'o
NK130(tho)001:11424: // 'di'i gzhi la sogs pa yang bshad pa'i lung yin par yang /
NK130(tho)001:11425: 'dul ba gzhung ni dam pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:11427: ma 'ongs pa yi gang zag gi //
NK130(tho)001:11428: ma rtogs la sogs gsal ba'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:11429: gzhi dang rnam 'byed la sogs kyi //
NK130(tho)001:11430: 'grel bshad nges pa don gyi lung //
NK130(tho)001:11431: zhus nas rgyal bas bka' stsal te //
NK130(tho)001:11432: de dag rnams kyang gang zhe na //
NK130(tho)001:11435: lnga tshan bcu drug tshan dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:11436: gleng gzhi brkyang pa gtam gyi gzhi //
NK130(tho)001:11437: ma na wi ka ma mo dang //
NK130(tho)001:11438: lus sogs sten pa tha ma ste //
NK130(tho)001:11440: thog mar zhus pa de yang ni //
NK130(tho)001:11441: rnam 'byed ltung ba sde bzhi dang //
NK130(tho)001:11442: rab byung la sogs gzhi rnams kyi //
NK130(tho)001:11444: de nyid dris lan zhes kyang grags //
NK130(tho)001:11445: de nas 'dul byed dag yin te //
NK130(tho)001:11446: pham pa bzhi dang lhag ma ni //
NK130(tho)001:11447: smyan gyi ltung ba yan chad dag /
NK130(tho)001:11448: gtan la 'bebs par byed pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:11449: de nas gcig las 'phros pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:11450: gcig nas bcu yi bar du yin //
NK130(tho)001:11451: gcig la 'dzegs pa zhes kyang grags //
NK130(tho)001:11452: de nas 'dul ba lnga tshan te //
NK130(tho)001:11453: lnga lnga ston phyir lnga tshan no //
NK130(tho)001:11454: bcu drug sde tshan ston pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:11455: de nas 'dul ba bcu drug yin //
NK130(tho)001:11456: gleng gzhi dag la sgo lnga ste //
NK130(tho)001:11457: re re tshigs bcad bcu drug yin //
NK130(tho)001:11458: gleng gzhi dag la brten pa'i phyir //
NK130(tho)001:11459: gleng gzhi zhes ni btags pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:11460: rkyang pa sgo bzhi re re'ang //
NK130(tho)001:11461: tshigs bcad bcu bcu de nyid la //
NK130(tho)001:11462: si la bu zhes bya ba bslab pa'i gzhi //
NK130(tho)001:11463: rigs mi mthun pa phra mo rnams //
NK130(tho)001:11464: ston phyir don dang ldan pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:11465: 'dul ba gtam gyi dngos po rnams //
NK130(tho)001:11466: ldebs kyi tshul du byung ba ste //
NK130(tho)001:11467: sdom gyi tshig tu bsdus pa med //
NK130(tho)001:11468: m+au la'i sgra ste gzhi dang ni //
NK130(tho)001:11469: rtsa ba dngos po la yang 'jug /
NK130(tho)001:11470: de phyir gtam gyi gzhir yang 'gyur //
NK130(tho)001:11471: ma na wi ka sgo dang po //
NK130(tho)001:11472: tshigs bcad bcu yin gnyis par ni //
NK130(tho)001:11473: bcu dang lhag pa dag tu 'dod //
NK130(tho)001:11474: shin tu phra zhing che bas na //
NK130(tho)001:11475: bram ze'i bu mo lta bu zhes //
NK130(tho)001:11476: don dang mthun pa'i mtshan yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11477: 'dul ba ma mo lta bu la //
NK130(tho)001:11478: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i phung po dang //
NK130(tho)001:11479: rab tu ldan dang bya ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:11480: phung po gsum du shes par bya //
NK130(tho)001:11481: ma dang 'dra phyir ma mo yin //
NK130(tho)001:11482: lus dang dmigs pa byin rlabs dang //
NK130(tho)001:11483: mtshan nyid gleng gzhi ngo bo dang //
NK130(tho)001:11484: 'bras bu'i don rnams mtha' ma ste //
NK130(tho)001:11485: u pa li yis dris pa ni //
NK130(tho)001:11486: de dag rnams kyis rdzogs pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:11487: mtshan gyi grangs kyi rim pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:11488: mtshan gyi bshad pa de yin pas //
NK130(tho)001:11489: de ltar bsdoms nas blta bar bya //
NK130(tho)001:11490: zhes kho bo cag gi nye bar 'dzin pa chen
NK130(tho)001:11491: po mchims thams cad mkhyen pa nam mkha' grags gsungs
NK130(tho)001:11492: pa ltar ro // so so thar pa'i mdo gnyis
NK130(tho)001:11493: kyang rnam 'byed gnyis kyis rtsa ba yin pas bde
NK130(tho)001:11495: dgra bcom pas bsdebs pas bka' ma yin par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK130(tho)001:11496: dper na ched du brjod pa'i tshoms dgra bcom pa
NK130(tho)001:11497: chos skyob kyis bsdebs pa yar mkhas pa rnams bkar
NK130(tho)001:11499: yang bod kha cig 'dul ba mdo'i rnam bshad slob
NK130(tho)001:11500: dpon shes rab 'byed kyis mdzad pa sro ma yungs
NK130(tho)001:11501: kar yan chad las ma gyur zer ro //
NK130(tho)001:11503: nges par thegs pa'i tshul du rtogs pa ste //
NK130(tho)001:11505: phyi ma dang mthun la snga ma dang 'gal ba ni rung bar ro //
NK130(tho)001:11506: zhes pa'i mthar thug pa'i bshad pa rnams rdzogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11507: gnas kyi dngos por gtogs pa phran tshegs 'phags pa'i zhes bya ba'i bar du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK130(tho)001:11509: gzhi gcig la tha dad du 'khrul pa'ang yod pa /
NK130(tho)001:11510: dper na 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i 'dus pa bcu bdun pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11511: mdo sde sna tshogs pa'i tshar gyi gang pos zhus pa tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11513: mdo sde sna tshogs pa'i pho brang 'khor skyong gi mdo tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11515: mdo sde sna tshogs pa'i glog thob kyis zhus pa'i mdo tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11516: 'dus pa nyi shu rtsa gsum pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11517: mdo sde sna tshogs pa'i byams pas zhus pa chung ngu'i mdo tha dad du rtogs pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11518: 'dus pa bzhi bcu rtsa drug pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11519: sher phyin bdun brgya pa tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11520: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11521: gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje'i le'u tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11522: sangs rgyas kyi yul bsam gyis mi khyab bstan pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11523: lha'i bu dang dpal bzang gis zhus pa tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11524: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod yul gyis thabs kyi yul
NK130(tho)001:11525: la rnam par 'phrul pa bstan pa'i ma do dang
NK130(tho)001:11526: / bden pa po'i le'u tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11527: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod yul bstan pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11528: khye'u rin chen gyis zhus pa tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11529: chos yang dag par 'dud pa'i mdo dang /
NK130(tho)001:11530: 'phags pa chos bsgro ba tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11531: de bzhin du rgyud la yang /
NK130(tho)001:11532: 'khor lo bde mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11533: bde mchog nyung ngu'i rgyud tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11534: gshin rje gshed nag po'i 'khor lo las thams cad grub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK130(tho)001:11535: gdong drug gi rgyud tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11536: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo kun nas 'od dang /
NK130(tho)001:11537: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo sgron ma mchog tha dad du rtogs pa sogs yin la /
NK130(tho)001:11539: dpal kye rdo rje'i rgyal cher 'grel pa rab tu
NK130(tho)001:11540: gsal ba'i kha sbyong zhes bya ba slob dpon ka
NK130(tho)001:11541: ya s+tha bsgres pos mdzad pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11542: slob dpon dam ka d+aa shas mdzad zer ba'i kha
NK130(tho)001:11543: sbyor shin tu dri ma med pa tha dad du
NK130(tho)001:11544: rtog pa dang / dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK130(tho)001:11545: 'khor gyi cho ga bzhi brgya lnga bcu pa'i 'grel
NK130(tho)001:11546: pa slob dpon dri med dpal gyis mdzad pa dang
NK130(tho)001:11547: rtog pa dang / / slob dpon rin chen 'byung
NK130(tho)001:11548: gnas zhi bas mdzad zer ba tha dad du rtog
NK130(tho)001:11549: rtog pa dang / / pa dang / rgyu gdags pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11550: rgyu gdags pa don rig zer ba tha dad du rtog pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11551: 'brel pa brtag pa'i rang 'grel du grags pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11552: slob dpon dul lhas mdzad zer ba tha dad du rtog pa sogs yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11555: kha cig 'gyur gyi bye brag gis tha dad par snang ba yin gyi /
NK130(tho)001:11556: don la tha dad pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11557: gzhan yang slob dpon 'jigs med 'byung gnas sbas pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11558: a b+ha ya ka ra gup+ta tha dad du rtog pa la sogs pa mang zhing /
NK130(tho)001:11559: mkhas pa dag gis kyang ji ltar ba bzhin thugs
NK130(tho)001:11560: su ma chud pa'i skyon yin pas thos pa rgya
NK130(tho)001:11561: bskyed de legs par brtags shing dpyad par bya rigs
NK130(tho)001:11562: la / de ltar ma nus na btang snyoms su 'jog rigs kyi /
NK130(tho)001:11563: de ni chos ma yin slob dpon de dag gis mdzad pa ma yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11564: zhes chos spong ba'i las gsogs par mi bya la /
NK130(tho)001:11565: phyis byon pa'i mkhas pa rnams kyis bstan bcos dang /
NK130(tho)001:11568: bstan 'gyur gyi dkar chag dag tu phud pa dang /
NK130(tho)001:11569: brtson pa can du byas pa rnams bstan bcos 'dis gsal bar byas pa yin no //
NK130(tho)001:11570: de lta bas na chos kyi phung po brgyad khri
NK130(tho)001:11571: bzhi stong zhes bya ba'ang nye bar mtshon pa tsam
NK130(tho)001:11572: ste / gro ga rim pa gcig pa dang shing
NK130(tho)001:11573: ta la'i 'dab ma rnams su phag ze'i rtse mos
NK130(tho)001:11574: bris pa'i tshad kyi yi ge rnams kyis gang bar
NK130(tho)001:11575: ste / byas te / gang bar byas pa'i gro
NK130(tho)001:11576: ga'i khur ram ta la'i 'dab ma'i khur ji srid
NK130(tho)001:11577: glang rgod kyis theg pa de ni chos kyi phung
NK130(tho)001:11578: ste / byas te / po gcig go // de
NK130(tho)001:11579: lta bu brgyad khri bzhi stong ni nyan thos kyi
NK130(tho)001:11581: theg pa chen po la dgu khri /
NK130(tho)001:11582: sngags kyi theg pa la stong phrag brgyad yod do //
NK130(tho)001:11583: zhes rab tu sgron gsal las bshad pas /
NK130(tho)001:11584: rang lugs la sngar ma grags shing ma mthong ba'i
NK130(tho)001:11585: mdo rgyud dag la bka' ma yin no zhes ma
NK130(tho)001:11586: sems shig / de ltar bdag lta bu blo dman pas kyang 'di ltar rnyed na /
NK130(tho)001:11587: bsags sbyang can gyi mkhas pa mkhyen spyan yangs pa dag gis gzigs pa rgya bskyed na /
NK130(tho)001:11588: bod yul 'dir sngon chad chos ma yin par grags
NK130(tho)001:11589: pa thams cad yang dag pa'i chos yin nges par
NK130(tho)001:11590: grub pa'i nges shes rnyed par 'gyur ro //
NK130(tho)001:11592: sngon tshe rgya gar 'phags yul du //
NK130(tho)001:11593: nyan thos sde pa du ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:11594: theg chen rgyal sras spyod pa'i gzhung //
NK130(tho)001:11595: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi bka' min ces //
NK130(tho)001:11596: bkag pa byams mgon klu sgrub dang //
NK130(tho)001:11597: thogs med sku mched zhi ba'i lhas //
NK130(tho)001:11598: theg chen sangs rgyas bka' ru bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:11599: sems tsam dang ni dbu ma dang //
NK130(tho)001:11600: rgyud sde bzhi la zab khyad dang //
NK130(tho)001:11601: mtho dman lam gyi nye ring dang //
NK130(tho)001:11602: bshad pa'i tshul dang grub pa'i mtha' //
NK130(tho)001:11603: mi 'dra tha dad du ma yod //
NK130(tho)001:11604: kun kyang sangs rgyas bstan par gcig /
NK130(tho)001:11605: bod 'dir bka' phyag dgas shangs gnyis //
NK130(tho)001:11606: sa skya pa dang zhi rdzogs gcod //
NK130(tho)001:11607: rang tsho thub pa'i chos lugs brgyad //
NK130(tho)001:11608: kun la brtsod pa ma byung med //
NK130(tho)001:11610: pha rgyud ma rgyud chags sdang dar //
NK130(tho)001:11611: chos ma yin zhes so sos smad //
NK130(tho)001:11612: de bzhin gcod la'ang nan ltar sdang //
NK130(tho)001:11614: dwags po bka' brgyud gtogs pa'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:11615: chos ma yin par bzhed pa yang //
NK130(tho)001:11616: de yi gsung rabs bltas pas shes //
NK130(tho)001:11617: kha cig gsung dag lam 'bras kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11618: snyan snyan bsdus pa'i tshig zin yin //
NK130(tho)001:11619: rgyud sde'i dgongs pa min par smra //
NK130(tho)001:11620: ni gu n+aa ro'i chos drug kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11621: 'chal cing bslad ces deng song gi //
NK130(tho)001:11622: kha 'dzin so sos smod res byed //
NK130(tho)001:11624: sngon te lo dang n+aa ros sna drangs nas //
NK130(tho)001:11625: mar pa dang mi las rjes bskyangs ste //
NK130(tho)001:11626: chos zab mo n+aa ro chos drug la //
NK130(tho)001:11627: rtags mngon gyur gyi grub thob grangs las 'das //
NK130(tho)001:11628: dus deng sang tshong 'dus kyi 'o ma bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:11629: tshig ma nges smyon pa'i lab 'chol smra //
NK130(tho)001:11630: don ma nges rang blo'i lam du 'dren //
NK130(tho)001:11631: ming gzhi la lus pa'i stong sob des //
NK130(tho)001:11632: mi kho bo'i blo kha cung ma tshims //
NK130(tho)001:11634: n+aa ro chos drug pa dag ni /
NK130(tho)001:11635: ni gu dang sbyor drug 'chal ces gleng ngo //
NK130(tho)001:11636: mdor na bod du dar ba'i chos //
NK130(tho)001:11637: brtsod pa med pa gcig kyang med //
NK130(tho)001:11638: byang chub lam du thams cad mthun //
NK130(tho)001:11639: skyon dang dri ma ga la yod //
NK130(tho)001:11640: 'on te tshig kyang ma dag la //
NK130(tho)001:11641: don gyi go ba phyin ci log /
NK130(tho)001:11642: lag len spyod pa log pa na //
NK130(tho)001:11643: gang de log pa'i chos su nges //
NK130(tho)001:11644: skyon de dag dang bral ba na //
NK130(tho)001:11645: kun kyang sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK130(tho)001:11646: rtsod pa tsam la nges pa med //
NK130(tho)001:11647: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo che //
NK130(tho)001:11648: thub pa'i bstan pa'i snying po yang //
NK130(tho)001:11649: rgya gar pan chen du ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:11650: chos ma yin par nan gyis byas //
NK130(tho)001:11651: dus zhabs n+aa ro sha ba ris //
NK130(tho)001:11652: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i snying por bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:11653: bod du'ang bcom ldan ral gri dang //
NK130(tho)001:11654: mkhas pa'i dbang po red mda' ba sa //
NK130(tho)001:11655: gtan tshigs mang pos chos 'di bkag /
NK130(tho)001:11656: de la rgyang ro byang 'bum dang //
NK130(tho)001:11657: shar pa ye shes rgyal mtshan sogs //
NK130(tho)001:11658: mang pos dus 'khor chos su bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:11659: spyir na rgya bal bod yul du //
NK130(tho)001:11661: theg mchog gsang sngags rnying ma la //
NK130(tho)001:11662: bod 'dir rtsod pa snga phyir mang //
NK130(tho)001:11663: rtsod lan 'brel med mang po'ang yod //
NK130(tho)001:11664: mkhas pa mgu ba'i legs bshad med //
NK130(tho)001:11665: mkhas pa'i mkhas pa rong zom dang //
NK130(tho)001:11666: rog gi ban d+he shes rab 'od //
NK130(tho)001:11667: mkhas mchog thang ston lo ts+aa ba //
NK130(tho)001:11668: de ltar gsum gyis lung rig dang //
NK130(tho)001:11669: gtan tshigs bzang po du ma yis //
NK130(tho)001:11670: gsang sngags zab mo bka' ru bsgrubs //
NK130(tho)001:11671: mi phyed snying nas dad pa thob //
NK130(tho)001:11672: sangs rgyas dngos su 'du shes skyes //
NK130(tho)001:11673: kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer gyis //
NK130(tho)001:11674: rnying ma bka' sgrub yod par grags //
NK130(tho)001:11675: bdag 'di'i skal bas ma mthong yang //
NK130(tho)001:11676: dgon gzhon zhes pa'i karma pa //
NK130(tho)001:11677: de la dpal 'dzin gyis bskur ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:11678: rtsod lan thebs par mdzad pa mthong //
NK130(tho)001:11679: dus phyis rgyal ba karma pa //
NK130(tho)001:11680: mi bskyod rdo rje'i 'byams yig la //
NK130(tho)001:11681: rtsod lan rim pa gsum tsam mthong //
NK130(tho)001:11682: kun kyang mu cor kho na las //
NK130(tho)001:11683: don ldan tshig gcig mi snang bas //
NK130(tho)001:11684: skyo ba skyes nas mchi ma shor //
NK130(tho)001:11685: rtsom pa'i mtshan nyid mi ldan kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11686: rang lo nyi shu rtsa lnga'i tshe //
NK130(tho)001:11687: dris lan lung rig 'brug sgra byas //
NK130(tho)001:11688: de rjes 'ga' yis bskul ba dang //
NK130(tho)001:11689: pan chen sh+aakya mchog ldan la //
NK130(tho)001:11690: rang phyogs 'ga' zhig sdang ba yi //
NK130(tho)001:11691: sdig las bzlog pa de phyir du //
NK130(tho)001:11692: legs bshad gser gyi thur ma ru //
NK130(tho)001:11693: drangs pa'i dpal 'dzin rtsod pa'i lan //
NK130(tho)001:11694: ngol la ba zhig bris nas yod //
NK130(tho)001:11695: slad du khri dpon mi'i dbang po //
NK130(tho)001:11696: chos rgyal nor bu pad+ma'i bkas //
NK130(tho)001:11697: lha rgyal bla ma ye shes 'od //
NK130(tho)001:11700: brtsod pa rgyas pa'i lan kyang byas //
NK130(tho)001:11701: de dag kun gyi kha skong dang //
NK130(tho)001:11702: bdag cag lta bu'i rigs can gyi //
NK130(tho)001:11703: slad nas 'byon pa'i rnying ma bas //
NK130(tho)001:11704: drang nges rnam dbye ma phyed dogs //
NK130(tho)001:11705: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rgyang ro ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:11706: bstan bcos rnam dag la brten nas //
NK130(tho)001:11707: yi ge'i lam du gsal bar bkod //
NK130(tho)001:11708: sbyangs dang skye bas thob pa'i yon tan gang //
NK130(tho)001:11709: med phyir bdag 'dra rtsom pa'i yul min kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11710: chos tshul zab mo chos ma yin no zhes //
NK130(tho)001:11711: log rtog mun pa'i smag rum stug po yis //
NK130(tho)001:11712: thub bstan skyon med bsgribs pa ma bzod nas //
NK130(tho)001:11713: lug rig nyi 'od bzang pos gsal bar byas //
NK130(tho)001:11714: de las gang zhig thob pa'i dge tshogs kyis //
NK130(tho)001:11715: phan bde'i 'byung gnas rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'di //
NK130(tho)001:11716: phyogs bcur dar zhing yun du gnas pa dang //
NK130(tho)001:11717: 'gro kun byang chub mchog la 'god gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:11718: bdag kyang skye ba tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK130(tho)001:11719: rgyal ba kun gyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK130(tho)001:11720: bstan la sdang ba mtha' dag tshar bcad de //
NK130(tho)001:11721: kun bzang sa la 'god pa nyid gyur cig /
NK130(tho)001:11722: chos kyi rjes su 'brang ba dag la gtam du
NK130(tho)001:11723: bya ba legs bshad bdud rtsi'i dga' ston ces bya
NK130(tho)001:11724: ba / sna tshogs dbyig ces pa shing mo sbrul
NK130(tho)001:11725: gyi lo snon gyis nya ba'i dga' ba dang po'i
NK130(tho)001:11726: ba / tshes la / slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis
NK130(tho)001:11727: pa pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi gdul bya tsam du gtogs
NK130(tho)001:11728: pa'i snyoms las pas chu mig ser po'i dgon par
NK130(tho)001:11729: ba / tshes la / sbyar ba'o // dge'o //
NK130(tho)001:11731: phyag bris ngo bshus las zhal bshus pa'o ////
NK130(tho)001:11733: ngan sems bzang por rloms pa'i dpal 'dzin gyis //
NK130(tho)001:11734: ngan tshig chos su bcos de'i rjes 'brang ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:11735: ngan rtog dug chus myos pa'i hor soga dpung //
NK130(tho)001:11736: ngan 'gro'i g.yang khar phyogs las gyen zloga pa //
NK130(tho)001:11737: nges gsang theg pa mchog gi blo gros ni //
NK130(tho)001:11738: nges par thub bstan rgyal mtshan rtser bsgrengs te //
NK130(tho)001:11739: nges don lung rig dpung ldan nga ro ches //
NK130(tho)001:11740: nges med phyogs kun 'gengs pa 'brug sgra bzhin //
NK130(tho)001:11741: log sred 'byung bya'i khyud khyad du mjug kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11742: gsang bstan nyid mor byed la bsgrib nus min //
NK130(tho)001:11743: bla brdol dam chos spong la 'chol ba'i mes //
NK130(tho)001:11744: rang rgyud thar pa'i sa bon bsreg las ci //
NK130(tho)001:11745: dgongs don tshul bzhin gzhal ba'i blo zhan kyang //
NK130(tho)001:11746: phyogs lhung bag chags goms pa'i rgyu mthun gyis //
NK130(tho)001:11747: cal sgrog grags rjes 'brang ba'i las ngan rnams //
NK130(tho)001:11748: nyams nga'i g.yang sar chas la ma bzod de //
NK130(tho)001:11749: thub bstan lha lam yangs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK130(tho)001:11750: mkhyen dang brtse ba'i nyi zla zung gi 'od //
NK130(tho)001:11751: log rtog smag rum 'joms la mthu dpa' ba //
NK130(tho)001:11752: 'jam mgon blo gros rgyal mtshan mchog de shar //
NK130(tho)001:11753: de phyir gang gi legs gsung phan bde'i sgo //
NK130(tho)001:11754: brgya phrag gcig car dbye ba'i sman gyi 'phrul //
NK130(tho)001:11755: shar 'brug mi dbang phrin las stobs rgyas kyis //
NK130(tho)001:11756: phangs med lhag bsam bzang pos yon sbyar ba'i //
NK130(tho)001:11757: dge bas mkha' mthas gtugs pa'i 'gro ba kun //
NK130(tho)001:11758: tshe rabs yang dag bshes gnyen gyis zin cing //
NK130(tho)001:11759: ma nor theg mchog shing rta la zhon nas //
NK130(tho)001:11760: bla med go 'phang bde blag brnyes gyur cig //
NK130(tho)001:11761: ces 'brug shar rdzong gi mi rje gang gi gsung
NK130(tho)001:11762: bskul bzhin phyi mo'i zhus dag dang chab gcig 'jigs
NK130(tho)001:11763: bral ye shes rdo rjes spel ba dza yan+tu ////
